ETHEREAL PEDDLER.name: Ethereal Peddler
ETHEREAL PEDDLER.flavorText: Yeah, sure. That Ragnaros "fell off the back of a truck".

SHADOW WORD: UNDEATH.name: Shadow Word: Undeath
SHADOW WORD: UNDEATH.flavorText: We like to call it FUNdeath here!

MARK OF THE WILD.name: Mark of the Wild
MARK OF THE WILD.flavorText: Not to be confused with Jim of the Wild.

MECHA-LEAPER.name: Mecha-Leaper
MECHA-LEAPER.flavorText: Now to find my Mecha-Macaw and my Mecha-Titus and we'll be Mecha-Set.

COLD BLOOD.name: Cold Blood
COLD BLOOD.flavorText: "I'm cold blooded, check it and see!"

RAGNAROS THE FIRELORD.name: Ragnaros the Firelord
RAGNAROS THE FIRELORD.flavorText: Ragnaros was summoned by the Dark Iron dwarves, who were eventually enslaved by the Firelord. Summoning Ragnaros often doesn’t work out the way you want it to.

WAILING SOUL.name: Wailing Soul
WAILING SOUL.flavorText: This soul just wails on you. Dang, soul, let up already.

DISPOSE OF EVIDENCE.name: Dispose of Evidence
DISPOSE OF EVIDENCE.flavorText: Just because you did it doesn't mean you have to be guilty.

DENDROLOGIST.name: Dendrologist
DENDROLOGIST.flavorText: He's teaching his little buddy to talk, but all it says is, "I am Gloop."

ESCAPE POD.name: Escape Pod
ESCAPE POD.flavorText: You can only have two in your deck because we are confident that the Draenei will never run into any dire situations that would warrant any more!

FOREST WARDEN OMU.name: Forest Warden Omu
FOREST WARDEN OMU.flavorText: She wishes all things could grow and flourish at Scholomance. If only she knew…

LIVING HORIZON.name: Living Horizon
LIVING HORIZON.flavorText: Even in the darkest of days, the sun never sets on the Badlands.

THE FIRES OF ZIN-AZSHARI.name: The Fires of Zin-Azshari
THE FIRES OF ZIN-AZSHARI.flavorText: One heck of a hot tub.

HOZEN HEALER.name: Hozen Healer
HOZEN HEALER.flavorText: He didn't go to school for healing, but we keep losing all the good healers to Ratchet, so I guess we'll take him.

LIFEDRINKER.name: Lifedrinker
LIFEDRINKER.flavorText: In a pinch, he'll also settle for Holy Water: Zero.

KING KRUSH.name: King Krush
KING KRUSH.flavorText: The best defense against King Krush is to have someone you don’t like standing in front of you.

KOR'VAS BLOODTHORN.name: Kor'vas Bloodthorn
KOR'VAS BLOODTHORN.flavorText: Illidan taught her that demon hunters should sacrifice EVERYTHING… but she still brought Lifesteal just in case.

FEUGEN.name: Feugen
FEUGEN.flavorText: Feugen is sad because everyone likes Stalagg better.

BRIDGE RIFF.name: Bridge Riff
BRIDGE RIFF.flavorText: Can be played in other places too.

BLOODSAIL RAIDER.name: Bloodsail Raider
BLOODSAIL RAIDER.flavorText: "I only plunder on days that end in 'y'."

CORROSIVE BREATH.name: Corrosive Breath
CORROSIVE BREATH.flavorText: It's a breath of fresh terror!

COBALT SCALEBANE.name: Cobalt Scalebane
COBALT SCALEBANE.flavorText: You get a sword! And you get a sword! Everybody gets a sword!

CRYOPRESERVATION.name: Cryopreservation
CRYOPRESERVATION.flavorText: Remember to take the elementals out of the freezer before Mom gets home!

PATCHWERK.name: Patchwerk
PATCHWERK.flavorText: This card is so good, it might need patch work.

SOUND THE BELLS!.name: Sound the Bells!
SOUND THE BELLS!.flavorText: Weirdly, the bells stop ringing after 5.

BLOOD TAP.name: Blood Tap
BLOOD TAP.flavorText: Come join us in the tavern! We have whatever you're drinking on tap. Yes, even that.

GYREWORM.name: Gyreworm
GYREWORM.flavorText: This game of ring toss just got really intense.

EARTHEN SCALES.name: Earthen Scales
EARTHEN SCALES.flavorText: You can make your own Earthen Scales at home. Step 1: Roll around in the dirt. Step 2: Magic.

SHIMMERING TEMPEST.name: Shimmering Tempest
SHIMMERING TEMPEST.flavorText: HATES being summoned for Kirin Tor party lighting.

DARK SKIES.name: Dark Skies
DARK SKIES.flavorText: "It's a drizzle of fire. A fine mist, really."

DESERT HARE.name: Desert Hare
DESERT HARE.flavorText: After they're caught, they’re dessert hares.

OVERLORD RUNTHAK.name: Overlord Runthak
OVERLORD RUNTHAK.flavorText: Knows how to lift everyone up while tearing every enemy down.

SILVERMOON PORTAL.name: Silvermoon Portal
SILVERMOON PORTAL.flavorText: What's Millhouse Manastorm doing in Silvermoon?

FAERIE DRAGON.name: Faerie Dragon
FAERIE DRAGON.flavorText: Adorable. Immune to Magic. Doesn't pee on the rug. The perfect pet!

TRIANGULATE.name: Triangulate
TRIANGULATE.flavorText: "Our mission takes us to the planet of Celes, but I know not of its whereabouts." "Captain, I saw Celes!"

SPARK DRILL.name: Spark Drill
SPARK DRILL.flavorText: Preferred weapon of Dr. Boom's orthodontist.

SUFFOCATE.name: Suffocate
SUFFOCATE.flavorText: He's already floating in the void of space. The shadow magic seems like overkill, idk.

CHILL-O-MATIC.name: Chill-o-matic
CHILL-O-MATIC.flavorText: After a number of island vacations, he thought the Storm Peaks would be a nice change of pace.

ARCH-VILLAIN RAFAAM.name: Arch-Villain Rafaam
ARCH-VILLAIN RAFAAM.flavorText: Minions must wash hands before being LIQUIDATED AND REPLACED BY SOMEONE BETTER.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/de/VO_VAC_304_Male_Nagaling_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_VAC_304_Male_Nagaling_Play_01.wav I found a sea urchin!

CELESTIAL ALIGNMENT.name: Celestial Alignment
CELESTIAL ALIGNMENT.flavorText: "Is my deck any good?" "I mean, if the stars align."

FLAME IMP.name: Flame Imp
FLAME IMP.flavorText: Imps like being on fire. They just do.

FROST ELEMENTAL.name: Frost Elemental
FROST ELEMENTAL.flavorText: When a Water elemental and an Ice elemental love each other VERY much...

FROSTWYRM'S FURY.name: Frostwyrm's Fury
FROSTWYRM'S FURY.flavorText: Terrible destruction, but minty fresh breath!

SCRAPSMITH.name: Scrapsmith
SCRAPSMITH.flavorText: Takes the ugly scraps of armor from dead players and combines them into ridiculous looking PVP armor sets.

PROVING GROUNDS.name: Proving Grounds
PROVING GROUNDS.flavorText: 1v1 me on Proving Grounds, DH only, no items, 4 stocks.

BATTY GUEST.name: Batty Guest
BATTY GUEST.flavorText: His favorite food is chocolate cereal.

SAFETY INSPECTOR.name: Safety Inspector
SAFETY INSPECTOR.flavorText: "All right, you're good. No sign of safety anywhere."

LIFT OFF.name: Lift Off
LIFT OFF.flavorText: It's a bird! It's a plane! It's a burning command center slowly moving to the corner of the map!

CONJURE MANA BISCUIT.name: Conjure Mana Biscuit
CONJURE MANA BISCUIT.flavorText: So THIS is why she was AFK.

RIGHTEOUSNESS.name: Righteousness
RIGHTEOUSNESS.flavorText: Shield yourself in righteousness! It feels like a warm fuzzy blanket.

NOVICE ENGINEER.name: Novice Engineer
NOVICE ENGINEER.flavorText: "Half of this class will not graduate… since they'll have been turned to chickens." - Tinkmaster Overspark, teaching Gizmos 101.

EVIL GENIUS.name: EVIL Genius
EVIL GENIUS.flavorText: You do not want to be on the business end of this intellect!

MECH-BEAR-CAT.name: Mech-Bear-Cat
MECH-BEAR-CAT.flavorText: Crushes buildings with his BEAR hands.

VILEBROOD SKITTERER.name: Vilebrood Skitterer
VILEBROOD SKITTERER.flavorText: It aspires to be a Vilebrood Dancer, but it has eight left feet.

EXPLOSIVE TRAP.name: Explosive Trap
EXPLOSIVE TRAP.flavorText: It traps your food AND cooks it for you!

ROTTEN APPLE.name: Rotten Apple
ROTTEN APPLE.flavorText: The rotten apple doesn't fall far from the corrupted world tree.

ZOK FOGSNOUT.name: Zok Fogsnout
ZOK FOGSNOUT.flavorText: Despite having only 3 digits on each hand, Zok plays Bass like he has 5.

BOLIDE BEHEMOTH.name: Bolide Behemoth
BOLIDE BEHEMOTH.flavorText: There's only so many words that exist for rocks in space.

UNLEASH THE BEAST.name: Unleash the Beast
UNLEASH THE BEAST.flavorText: The Kirin Tor have always been lax in enforcing leash laws.

LADY ASHVANE.name: Lady Ashvane
LADY ASHVANE.flavorText: This is your brain on Azerite.

MOGU CULTIST.name: Mogu Cultist
MOGU CULTIST.flavorText: Mogu cultists have the worst team-building exercises.

COILFANG WARLORD.name: Coilfang Warlord
COILFANG WARLORD.flavorText: Prepare for the staunch conch launch!

BATTLE RAGE.name: Battle Rage
BATTLE RAGE.flavorText: "You won't like me when I'm angry."

SHADOW WORD: FORBID.name: Shadow Word: Forbid
SHADOW WORD: FORBID.flavorText: At last, Priest has no more weaknesses.

FURIOUS FOWLS.name: Furious Fowls
FURIOUS FOWLS.flavorText: They were already mad and you had to call them 'foul'??

AWAKEN!.name: Awaken!
AWAKEN!.flavorText: This is an alarm clock you can't ignore.

DREAD INFERNAL.name: Dread Infernal
DREAD INFERNAL.flavorText: "INFERNOOOOOOOOOO!" - Jaraxxus, Eredar Lord of the Burning Legion

JAN'ALAI, THE DRAGONHAWK.name: Jan'alai, the Dragonhawk
JAN'ALAI, THE DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: You mess with the Bird, you get the Firelord.

GRAND LACKEY ERKH.name: Grand Lackey Erkh
GRAND LACKEY ERKH.flavorText: Esteemed leader of Rafaam's Inhuman Resources department.

SANDHOOF WATERBEARER.name: Sandhoof Waterbearer
SANDHOOF WATERBEARER.flavorText: Used to carrying for his team.

TOMB PILLAGER.name: Tomb Pillager
TOMB PILLAGER.flavorText: After the guild broke up, he could no longer raid the tombs.

DARKSCALE HEALER.name: Darkscale Healer
DARKSCALE HEALER.flavorText: Healing is just something she does in her free time. It's more of a hobby really.

SKELETON CREW.name: Skeleton Crew
SKELETON CREW.flavorText: They don't sweat, breathe or need lit candles... what more could you ask?

ATTORNEY-AT-MAW.name: Attorney-at-Maw
ATTORNEY-AT-MAW.flavorText: When the going gets tough, you don't want a criminal lawyer... you want a criminal lawyer...

MOONLIT GUIDANCE.name: Moonlit Guidance
MOONLIT GUIDANCE.flavorText: Guff always makes the best decisions after 2 AM.

MOGU'SHAN WARDEN.name: Mogu'shan Warden
MOGU'SHAN WARDEN.flavorText: All these guys ever do is talk about the Thunder King. BOOOORRRINNG!

SI:7 EXTORTION.name: SI:7 Extortion
SI:7 EXTORTION.flavorText: "It's a dangerous world out there. It'd be a shame if your protection insurance were to suddenly run out…"

DEATHWING, DRAGONLORD.name: Deathwing, Dragonlord
DEATHWING, DRAGONLORD.flavorText: To his credit, Deathwing really took to heart the feedback he was receiving that he needed to be "more of a team player".

BLATANT DECOY.name: Blatant Decoy
BLATANT DECOY.flavorText: "Hah! You is being tricked by ME! Togwaggle!"

HOLY MAKI ROLL.name: Holy Maki Roll
HOLY MAKI ROLL.flavorText: If you use all 10 mana, that's called the 'Lunch Special.'

AXE BERSERKER.name: Axe Berserker
AXE BERSERKER.flavorText: All the body spray went to her head.

TIGRESS PLUSHY.name: Tigress Plushy
TIGRESS PLUSHY.flavorText: The sheervalue of this card is undeniable.

BONELORD FROSTWHISPER.name: Bonelord Frostwhisper
BONELORD FROSTWHISPER.flavorText: Downside? Not if you want to be a Death Knight!

CONFESSOR PALETRESS.name: Confessor Paletress
CONFESSOR PALETRESS.flavorText: She sees into your past and makes you face your fears. Most common fear: Getting Majordomo out of Sneed's Old Shredder.

BOMB WRANGLER.name: Bomb Wrangler
BOMB WRANGLER.flavorText: Bomb Wranglers tend to have short fuses and even shorter lifespans.

STORMPIKE BATTLE RAM.name: Stormpike Battle Ram
STORMPIKE BATTLE RAM.flavorText: Baa ram ewe! To your dwarves, your beard, Stormpike clan be true!

HOLOMANCER.name: Holomancer
HOLOMANCER.flavorText: Help me, worthy opponent. You're my only hope.

WRAPPED GOLEM.name: Wrapped Golem
WRAPPED GOLEM.flavorText: The end result of one of the greatest wrap battles of all time.

MALEFIC ROOK.name: Malefic Rook
MALEFIC ROOK.flavorText: Was a regular Pawn but Fel in with the wrong toys.

NOZDORMU THE ETERNAL.name: Nozdormu the Eternal
NOZDORMU THE ETERNAL.flavorText: Live life in the fast lane. As long as your opponent does too.

N'ZOTH, THE CORRUPTOR.name: N'Zoth, the Corruptor
N'ZOTH, THE CORRUPTOR.flavorText: Has not been able to get "Under the Sea" out of his head for like FIVE THOUSAND YEARS.

NETHERSOUL BUSTER.name: Nethersoul Buster
NETHERSOUL BUSTER.flavorText: Why did the demon cross the streams? To get to The Other Side.

SNAKE OIL SELLER.name: Snake Oil Seller
SNAKE OIL SELLER.flavorText: This oil is absolutely essential to your gameplan.

SHADOWFLAME.name: Shadowflame
SHADOWFLAME.flavorText: Start with a powerful minion and stir in Shadowflame and you have a good time!

TUSKPIERCER.name: Tuskpiercer
TUSKPIERCER.flavorText: It's the Barrens, everything has tusks! The Quilboar have tusks, the boars have tusks, the tusks have tusks.

ICE BARRIER.name: Ice Barrier
ICE BARRIER.flavorText: This is Rank 1. Rank 2 is Chocolate Milk Barrier.

MASTER OAKHEART.name: Master Oakheart
MASTER OAKHEART.flavorText: His adventuring party consists of Goldshire Footman, Frostwolf Grunt and Hadronox.

WARMAUL CHALLENGER.name: Warmaul Challenger
WARMAUL CHALLENGER.flavorText: Old gladiator rules: first one to die loses.

LOTUS ILLUSIONIST.name: Lotus Illusionist
LOTUS ILLUSIONIST.flavorText: If you think her Xavius and Sylvanas cosplay is great, wait till you see her Reno Jackson!

ANCIENT OF LORE.name: Ancient of Lore
ANCIENT OF LORE.flavorText: Go ahead, carve your initials in him.

CLEAR CONSCIENCE.name: Clear Conscience
CLEAR CONSCIENCE.flavorText: Do you swear to give the buff, the whole buff, and nothing but the buff, so help you Kyrestia?

CAMOUFLAGE MOUNT.name: Camouflage Mount
CAMOUFLAGE MOUNT.flavorText: What mount? I don't see anything…

SHIELDBEARER.name: Shieldbearer
SHIELDBEARER.flavorText: Have you seen the size of the shields in this game?? This is no easy job.

ARCANE INTELLECT.name: Arcane Intellect
ARCANE INTELLECT.flavorText: Playing this card makes you SMARTER. And let's face it: we could all stand to be a little smarter.

ORBITAL MOON.name: Orbital Moon
ORBITAL MOON.flavorText: The blood moon orbits once again.

FLAG RUNNER.name: Flag Runner
FLAG RUNNER.flavorText: I see your argument, but…do you have a flag?

MECHWARPER.name: Mechwarper
MECHWARPER.flavorText: Mechs that summon mechs? What's next? Donuts that summon donuts? Mmmmm.

WITCH OF THE ARCH-THIEF.name: Witch of the Arch-Thief
WITCH OF THE ARCH-THIEF.flavorText: A minion fit for a king.

MINI-MAGE.name: Mini-Mage
MINI-MAGE.flavorText: He is sometimes found hiding in the treasure chest in the Gurubashi Arena.

HOT AIR BALLOON.name: Hot Air Balloon
HOT AIR BALLOON.flavorText: The Gadgetzan Pilgrim's Bounty parade is missing a float this year.

ZIXOR, APEX PREDATOR.name: Zixor, Apex Predator
ZIXOR, APEX PREDATOR.flavorText: A living terror. Teleports at will. Feasts on tainted helboar meat. No head scritches unless you're Leoroxx.

HARMONIC HIP HOP.name: Harmonic Hip Hop
HARMONIC HIP HOP.flavorText: I can name four things that rhyme with 'orange': Four inch, Door hinge, Syringe, and uh… Shmorange.

WALKING DEAD.name: Walking Dead
WALKING DEAD.flavorText: Watch out for the Scourge, KAAARRRRLLLL!

GILBLIN STALKER.name: Gilblin Stalker
GILBLIN STALKER.flavorText: "Shhh, I think I hear something." "Ah, it's probably nothing." - Every Henchman

EXPLOSIVE SHOT.name: Explosive Shot
EXPLOSIVE SHOT.flavorText: Pull the pin, count to 5, then shoot. Then duck.

DRUID OF THE CLAW.name: Druid of the Claw
DRUID OF THE CLAW.flavorText: Cat or Bear? Cat or Bear?! I just cannot CHOOSE!

BLOODSEEKER.name: Bloodseeker
BLOODSEEKER.flavorText: What do you mean shooting them in the back isn’t honorable?!

GUITAR SOLOIST.name: Guitar Soloist
GUITAR SOLOIST.flavorText: She is the hero of the guitar. The guitar hero. Trademark.

DINOTAMER BRANN.name: Dinotamer Brann
DINOTAMER BRANN.flavorText: Brann's new dino-taming hobby is going well—his pet can already make him sit, stand, and roll over!

EXPLORE UN'GORO.name: Explore Un'Goro
EXPLORE UN'GORO.flavorText: It turns out cards DO grow on trees!

HOT COALS.name: Hot Coals
HOT COALS.flavorText: This is what Greatfather Winter gives you when you've been REALLY naughty.

BLESSED CHAMPION.name: Blessed Champion
BLESSED CHAMPION.flavorText: This card causes double the trouble AND double the fun.

VAST WISDOM.name: Vast Wisdom
VAST WISDOM.flavorText: My wisdom is SO vast that I can count up to THREE!

HAMMER OF WRATH.name: Hammer of Wrath
HAMMER OF WRATH.flavorText: A good paladin has many tools. Hammer of Wrath, Pliers of Vengeance, Hacksaw of Justice, etc.

SINISTER STRIKE.name: Sinister Strike
SINISTER STRIKE.flavorText: There's something about this strike that just feels off. Sinister, even.

FARM HAND.name: Farm Hand
FARM HAND.flavorText: I know it's an Undead hand, but bending your pinky in that way can NOT be good for your joints.

OONDASTA.name: Oondasta
OONDASTA.flavorText: Adorning devilsaurs with armor and feathers is a respected job in troll culture, although it has a high turnover rate.

FLAME LEVIATHAN.name: Flame Leviathan
FLAME LEVIATHAN.flavorText: Mimiron likes to take the Flame Leviathan out on some sweet joyrides.

LINE HOPPER.name: Line Hopper
LINE HOPPER.flavorText: There are two things Demon Hunters know: hopping, and cutting.

ELIZA GOREBLADE.name: Eliza Goreblade
ELIZA GOREBLADE.flavorText: Dead men tell no tales, but Undead Pirates are yappers.

INZAH.name: Inzah
INZAH.flavorText: Inzah plays the trumpet, saxophone, piano, guitar, AND bass. No wonder he's always so overloaded!

PILOTED SKY GOLEM.name: Piloted Sky Golem
PILOTED SKY GOLEM.flavorText: The pinnacle of goblin engineering. Includes an espresso machine and foot massager.

ACIDMAW.name: Acidmaw
ACIDMAW.flavorText: With the help of his trusty sidekick Dreadscale, the giant jormungar Acidmaw is ready to face any knight!

FREEZING TRAP.name: Freezing Trap
FREEZING TRAP.flavorText: "Dang, that's cold." - appropriate response to Freezing Trap, or a mean joke.

GOING DOWN SWINGING.name: Going Down Swinging
GOING DOWN SWINGING.flavorText: Halveria was outcast from Gilneas for being too edgy, which she sees as an achievement.

VOLTAIC BURST.name: Voltaic Burst
VOLTAIC BURST.flavorText: Batteries have three components: Cathode, Anode, and Overload.

DEATH BEETLE.name: Death Beetle
DEATH BEETLE.flavorText: Well that'll be useless next expansion. WINK WINK.

SENSE DEMONS.name: Sense Demons
SENSE DEMONS.flavorText: Generally demons are pretty obvious and you don’t need a spell to sense them.

RAIDING PARTY.name: Raiding Party
RAIDING PARTY.flavorText: And a bowl of chips. And some of those little cocktail weenies!

GOLD PANNER.name: Gold Panner
GOLD PANNER.flavorText: "I don't know why everyone's got their overalls in a jumble with Azerite minin' when there's all this GOLD for the takin'!"

FELFIRE BONFIRE.name: Felfire Bonfire
FELFIRE BONFIRE.flavorText: It was then that Marsh and Mallow understood the meaning of their new nicknames.

HOWLING COMMANDER.name: Howling Commander
HOWLING COMMANDER.flavorText: Enlistment in her battalion comes with several pairs of earplugs.

CALL OF THE GRAVE.name: Call of the Grave
CALL OF THE GRAVE.flavorText: Necromancy is motivational speaking for the dead.

ZILLIAX.name: Zilliax
ZILLIAX.flavorText: Everything but the kitchen sink. Oh wait, there's one on his back.

HAGATHA THE WITCH.name: Hagatha the Witch
HAGATHA THE WITCH.flavorText: Curse-bringer, tree-twister, mother of wretched things…Hanzo main.

RAVENHOLDT ASSASSIN.name: Ravenholdt Assassin
RAVENHOLDT ASSASSIN.flavorText: Just mail him a package with a name and 10,000 gold. He'll take care of the rest.

POSSE POSSESSION.name: Posse Possession
POSSE POSSESSION.flavorText: Keep your friends close, your enemies closer, and your shadows at gunpoint.

FRENZIED FELWING.name: Frenzied Felwing
FRENZIED FELWING.flavorText: Not to be confused with the "friendsy” felwing.

E.M.P. OPERATIVE.name: E.M.P. Operative
E.M.P. OPERATIVE.flavorText: "I said this looks like a job for me So everybody just follow me 'Cause we need a little E.M.P. 'Cause it feels so mechy without me…"

FIRELANDS PORTAL.name: Firelands Portal
FIRELANDS PORTAL.flavorText: Come to beautiful Firelands! Where it's "Way nicer than the Abyssal Maw!"

SURFALOPOD.name: Surfalopod
SURFALOPOD.flavorText: Hi! Octopus expert here. This is NOT funny. Octopi only do this when they're extremely rad.

EVASION.name: Evasion
EVASION.flavorText: Works on weapons, missiles, and taxes.

AQUATIC FORM.name: Aquatic Form
AQUATIC FORM.flavorText: How long can YOU hold your breath underwater?

INNER DEMON.name: Inner Demon
INNER DEMON.flavorText: Critical component of any tragic backstory.

KEL'THUZAD.name: Kel'Thuzad
KEL'THUZAD.flavorText: Kel'Thuzad could not resist the call of the Lich King. Even when it's just a robo-call extolling the Lich King's virtues.

MOSH'OGG ANNOUNCER.name: Mosh'Ogg Announcer
MOSH'OGG ANNOUNCER.flavorText: One's play-by-play. The other is off-color.

IMPENDING CATASTROPHE.name: Impending Catastrophe
IMPENDING CATASTROPHE.flavorText: The imps end you, and the cats... well, they astrophe.

SI:7 OPERATIVE.name: SI:7 Operative
SI:7 OPERATIVE.flavorText: What do you mean you're out of ponies?

ALTRUIS THE OUTCAST.name: Altruis the Outcast
ALTRUIS THE OUTCAST.flavorText: Altruis betrayed Illidan to forge his own way in Outland. With Blackjack. And Netherdrakes.

SUNFURY PROTECTOR.name: Sunfury Protector
SUNFURY PROTECTOR.flavorText: She carries a shield, but only so she can give it to someone she can stand behind.

SECOND-RATE BRUISER.name: Second-Rate Bruiser
SECOND-RATE BRUISER.flavorText: He'll be a first-rate bruiser once he gets used to his contacts.

DESECRATED GRAVEYARD.name: Desecrated Graveyard
DESECRATED GRAVEYARD.flavorText: People are dying to get in.

BIOLUMINESCENCE.name: Bioluminescence
BIOLUMINESCENCE.flavorText: The perfect card for Spell Damage Shaman and Spelling Bee Shaman.

MAIEV SHADOWSONG.name: Maiev Shadowsong
MAIEV SHADOWSONG.flavorText: Go directly to Demon Jail. Do not attack minions, do not collect mana crystals.

IMPRISONED SATYR.name: Imprisoned Satyr
IMPRISONED SATYR.flavorText: "C'mon down to Illhoof's bargain bin! When the satyr's free, he'll lower your fee!"

GIFTWRAPPED WHELP.name: Giftwrapped Whelp
GIFTWRAPPED WHELP.flavorText: Don't forget to poke fire-breathing holes in the box!

DUEL!.name: Duel!
DUEL!.flavorText: If you don’t fight to the death, it’s Duel Yielding.

DARK PROPHECY.name: Dark Prophecy
DARK PROPHECY.flavorText: It's always a dark prophecy with Madame Lazul. Where's my happy, fluffy prophecy?!

PATCHES THE PIRATE.name: Patches the Pirate
PATCHES THE PIRATE.flavorText: What do sailors yell when Patches steals their treasure chest full of laws and other things being transported to parliament for a vote? "The Eyes have it!"

HOLY RIPPLE.name: Holy Ripple
HOLY RIPPLE.flavorText: I still prefer the taste of banana fudge ripple.

VILE LIBRARY.name: Vile Library
VILE LIBRARY.flavorText: What type of vial library has 0 vials in it!?

STORM'S WRATH.name: Storm's Wrath
STORM'S WRATH.flavorText: How many dragons does it take to destroy a hot air balloon? One, two, three, CRUNCH!

ABOMINATION.name: Abomination
ABOMINATION.flavorText: Abominations enjoy Fresh Meat and long walks on the beach.

STORMWIND CHAMPION.name: Stormwind Champion
STORMWIND CHAMPION.flavorText: When Deathwing assaulted the capital, this soldier was the only member of his squad to survive. Now he's all bitter and stuff.

GREYBOUGH.name: Greybough
GREYBOUGH.flavorText: The best time to plant a tree was 20 years ago. The next best time is when you lose a minion.

AMANI BERSERKER.name: Amani Berserker
AMANI BERSERKER.flavorText: If an Amani berserker asks "Joo lookin' at me?!", the correct response is "Nah, mon".

ASHEN ELEMENTAL.name: Ashen Elemental
ASHEN ELEMENTAL.flavorText: "The castle was nice but the fireplaces were too small - 2/5 stars"

voicelines.death:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/0/09/VO_DAL_086_Female_BloodElf_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_DAL_086_Female_BloodElf_Play_01.wav Got something to hide?
  • ▶️ KabalCrystalRunner_Underlay_Play.wav <underlay sound>

SHU'MA.name: Shu'ma
SHU'MA.flavorText: How to tell your mother to go away.

WOBBLING RUNTS.name: Wobbling Runts
WOBBLING RUNTS.flavorText: The fourth one fell off in a tragic accident. They don't talk about it.

ONYXIAN WARDER.name: Onyxian Warder
ONYXIAN WARDER.flavorText: Throwing more whelps at the problem might not help, but they certainly will hurt.

PACK TACTICS.name: Pack Tactics
PACK TACTICS.flavorText: "Just you wait, I’ll go get on my main!"

CHRONOBREAKER.name: Chronobreaker
CHRONOBREAKER.flavorText: If he asks to borrow your watch, just say no.

GORILLABOT A-3.name: Gorillabot A-3
GORILLABOT A-3.flavorText: A-1 and A-2 went nuts, when they should have gone bolts.

SPAWN OF SHADOWS.name: Spawn of Shadows
SPAWN OF SHADOWS.flavorText: What did you expect to happen? He's a Spawn. Of Shadows.

DRUID OF THE SWARM.name: Druid of the Swarm
DRUID OF THE SWARM.flavorText: The druid awoke from troubling dreams to find herself transformed into a giant spider.

FANOTTEM, LORD OF THE OPERA.name: Fanottem, Lord of the Opera
FANOTTEM, LORD OF THE OPERA.flavorText: Writing a compelling symphony takes time. Usually around 20 turns or more.

TENTACLED MENACE.name: Tentacled Menace
TENTACLED MENACE.flavorText: He calls this one the "Calamari Special."

TRIPLEWICK TRICKSTER.name: Triplewick Trickster
TRIPLEWICK TRICKSTER.flavorText: You no take candle! Or second candle. You can take third candle though.

ARFUS.name: Arfus
ARFUS.flavorText: There must always be a Lick King.

ANIMATED AVALANCHE.name: Animated Avalanche
ANIMATED AVALANCHE.flavorText: Always sliding down mountains because it can't stop talking with its hands.

DEATHSTALKER REXXAR.name: Deathstalker Rexxar
DEATHSTALKER REXXAR.flavorText: "You were too slow, old friend. The hunt began long ago. And now... it will never end."

DRAKONID OPERATIVE.name: Drakonid Operative
DRAKONID OPERATIVE.flavorText: His job is to spy on the Goons and the Jade Lotus, but he's OBVIOUSLY a dragon so it's pretty hard work.

PHASE STALKER.name: Phase Stalker
PHASE STALKER.flavorText: It's not just a phase! I don't have to tell you anything! GAWSH!

TANARIS HOGCHOPPER.name: Tanaris Hogchopper
TANARIS HOGCHOPPER.flavorText: The Hogchoppers are well-known throughout Kalimdor for being a real, actual group.

EYE FOR AN EYE.name: Eye for an Eye
EYE FOR AN EYE.flavorText: Justice sometimes takes the form of a closed fist into a soft cheek.

SCABBS CUTTERBUTTER.name: Scabbs Cutterbutter
SCABBS CUTTERBUTTER.flavorText: "Never lie, steal, cheat, or drink. Unless you're compelled to, that is…" —Scabbs Cutterbutter

BLOOD MATRIARCH LIADRIN.name: Blood Matriarch Liadrin
BLOOD MATRIARCH LIADRIN.flavorText: All's fair in blood and war.

MAD SUMMONER.name: Mad Summoner
MAD SUMMONER.flavorText: Does he summon because of his madness, or is he mad from all the summoning?

PRIMORDIAL DRAKE.name: Primordial Drake
PRIMORDIAL DRAKE.flavorText: Before he became a rap artist.

FRONT LINES.name: Front Lines
FRONT LINES.flavorText: With the line in the sand crossed, the battle for the Throne of Tides had begun.

BIG GAME HUNTER.name: Big Game Hunter
BIG GAME HUNTER.flavorText: Mere devilsaurs no longer excite him. Soon he'll be trying to catch Onyxia with only a dull Krol Blade.

KABAL COURIER.name: Kabal Courier
KABAL COURIER.flavorText: Hey, you park your kodo under a harpy nest, you get what you deserve.

SEANCE.name: Seance
SEANCE.flavorText: “The spirits spoke to me.” "What did they say?" "You had lethal two turns ago."

BOOTY BAY BODYGUARD.name: Booty Bay Bodyguard
BOOTY BAY BODYGUARD.flavorText: You can hire him... until someone offers him enough gold to turn on you.

HOODED ACOLYTE.name: Hooded Acolyte
HOODED ACOLYTE.flavorText: Wait, what kind of acolyte doesn't wear a hood?

CELESTIAL PROJECTIONIST.name: Celestial Projectionist
CELESTIAL PROJECTIONIST.flavorText: What if we're not really here, y'know? What if we're all just, like, projections in the mind of some cosmic entity? How would we know?

BRAWL.name: Brawl
BRAWL.flavorText: Do you know the first rule of Brawl Club?

IMMORTALIZED IN STONE.name: Immortalized in Stone
IMMORTALIZED IN STONE.flavorText: They all secretly have 'Deathrattle: Become very mortalized.'

ALDOR ATTENDANT.name: Aldor Attendant
ALDOR ATTENDANT.flavorText: Will check to make sure you have a valid libramary card.

KIDNAPPER.name: Kidnapper
KIDNAPPER.flavorText: He just wants people to see his vacation photos.

PRO GAMER.name: Pro Gamer
PRO GAMER.flavorText: Wow... who could have guessed? Another rock user ruining the meta for everyone as usual.

MOUNTAINFIRE ARMOR.name: Mountainfire Armor
MOUNTAINFIRE ARMOR.flavorText: Excuse me. Your mountain is on fire.

ARGENT COMMANDER.name: Argent Commander
ARGENT COMMANDER.flavorText: The Argent Dawn stands vigilant against the Scourge, as well as people who cut in line at coffee shops.

BLISTERING ROT.name: Blistering Rot
BLISTERING ROT.flavorText: Known as 'Fel Gel' to the Illidari, it's excellent protection against harsh Draenic sunshine.

CIRCUS AMALGAM.name: Circus Amalgam
CIRCUS AMALGAM.flavorText: Who needs a petting zoo when you have all the creatures right here?!

ULTRAVIOLET BREAKER.name: Ultraviolet Breaker
ULTRAVIOLET BREAKER.flavorText: You're gonna need more sunscreen. Good thing we stocked up last expansion.

DANG-BLASTED ELEMENTAL.name: Dang-Blasted Elemental
DANG-BLASTED ELEMENTAL.flavorText: We were told that "Dag-Nabbin' Dang-Blastin' Rootin'-Tootin' High-Falutin' Elemental" was too long.

REVENGE OF THE WILD.name: Revenge of the Wild
REVENGE OF THE WILD.flavorText: My roommates only use Revenge of the Passive Aggressive.

GREY SAGE PARROT.name: Grey Sage Parrot
GREY SAGE PARROT.flavorText: Nothing is more terrifying than a parrot squawking "Pyroblast!"

GURUBASHI OFFERING.name: Gurubashi Offering
GURUBASHI OFFERING.flavorText: For a limited time, loa blessings are on a pray-one-get-two deal (on selected sacrifices only).

OGRE-GANG ACE.name: Ogre-Gang Ace
OGRE-GANG ACE.flavorText: 100% chance to not play by the rules.

FIENDISH CIRCLE.name: Fiendish Circle
FIENDISH CIRCLE.flavorText: Like a knitting circle, but less evil.

TREASURE GUARD.name: Treasure Guard
TREASURE GUARD.flavorText: The real treasure was the Naga we met along the way.

WOLFRIDER.name: Wolfrider
WOLFRIDER.flavorText: Orcish raiders ride wolves because they are well adapted to harsh environments, and because they are soft and cuddly.

LESSER JASPER SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Jasper Spellstone
LESSER JASPER SPELLSTONE.flavorText: In ancient woods, elves fought the curse The demon’s shadow to disperse But hatred raged and frail souls turned Now horned and hooved their forests burned.

DARK CULTIST.name: Dark Cultist
DARK CULTIST.flavorText: The Cult of the Damned has found it's best not to mention their name when recruiting new cultists.

MO'ARG DRILLFIST.name: Mo'arg Drillfist
MO'ARG DRILLFIST.flavorText: Also functions as the town dentist.

BAD OMEN.name: Bad Omen
BAD OMEN.flavorText: What good is a sign from alien life if I CAN'T EVEN READ IT?!

VOLCANOSAUR.name: Volcanosaur
VOLCANOSAUR.flavorText: Always fun to say out loud "VOL-CA-NO-SAUUUR!"

KURTRUS, DEMON-RENDER.name: Kurtrus, Demon-Render
KURTRUS, DEMON-RENDER.flavorText: "I dedicated my life to vanquishing demons, but I never thought to face the demons in me. Maybe, in time, I can help quell the demons in you." -Kurtrus, to Cariel

STAR ALIGNER.name: Star Aligner
STAR ALIGNER.flavorText: "You're a Sagittarius? Me too! Just gimme a sec."

FIDDLEFIRE IMP.name: Fiddlefire Imp
FIDDLEFIRE IMP.flavorText: Most find the stages set aflame by the Grimtotem too dangerous to perform on, but to him they're perfect!

ANCIENT SHADE.name: Ancient Shade
ANCIENT SHADE.flavorText: Warning: Do not expose to direct sunlight.

EVIL MISCREANT.name: EVIL Miscreant
EVIL MISCREANT.flavorText: Because there are no G.O.O.D. Miscreants.

SPREADING PLAGUE.name: Spreading Plague
SPREADING PLAGUE.flavorText: In the past, plagues were spread by mice or fleas. These days they're spread by elves.

FEEDING TIME.name: Feeding Time
FEEDING TIME.flavorText: True, they're only 1/1s, but they eat as much as most 4/4s!

ULUU, THE EVERDRIFTER.name: Uluu, the Everdrifter
ULUU, THE EVERDRIFTER.flavorText: Uluu is such a tryhard, he's carrying an entire planet!

SKELETAL DRAGON.name: Skeletal Dragon
SKELETAL DRAGON.flavorText: I wish to complain about this dragon what I purchased not half an hour ago from this very boutique.

WORKSHOP JANITOR.name: Workshop Janitor
WORKSHOP JANITOR.flavorText: She works in a magical toy shop and they just gave her a regular mop? Make it make sense.

HOARD PILLAGER.name: Hoard Pillager
HOARD PILLAGER.flavorText: Better to have stabbed and lost. And then found again!

OVERFLOW.name: Overflow
OVERFLOW.flavorText: It's a high five followed by a low tide.

CHEATY SNOBOLD.name: Cheaty Snobold
CHEATY SNOBOLD.flavorText: This one will knock you out cold.

DARK PEDDLER.name: Dark Peddler
DARK PEDDLER.flavorText: I'm offering you a bargain here! This amazing vacuum cleaner for your soul!

ANNOY-O-MODULE.name: Annoy-o-Module
ANNOY-O-MODULE.flavorText: Every ten seconds it asks if you want to update.

RAVASAUR RUNT.name: Ravasaur Runt
RAVASAUR RUNT.flavorText: Doesn't like to adapt unless others are watching. Some minions are such show-offs.

HAND OF A'DAL.name: Hand of A'dal
HAND OF A'DAL.flavorText: When it meets the Hand of Gul'dan, they're SHAKING.

WEAPONIZED WASP.name: Weaponized Wasp
WEAPONIZED WASP.flavorText: Dr. Boom had one simple request: wasps with flippin' laser beams attached to their heads.

HIRED GUN.name: Hired Gun
HIRED GUN.flavorText: He loves his job and would do it for free! (But don't tell his boss!)

DEATH REVENANT.name: Death Revenant
DEATH REVENANT.flavorText: How's everyone doing? Hurt? Bleeding? Wounded? ... Excellent.

SHARK PUNCHER.name: Shark Puncher
SHARK PUNCHER.flavorText: "And remember, if you come face-to-face with a shark, punch it in the nose." "Yes. Me punch you in nose with shark." "No, th- OW!"

voicelines.attack:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/1/15/VO_WON_138_Male_Ogre_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_WON_138_Male_Ogre_Play_01.wav Rip 'em up!
  • ▶️ Slime_OG_156a_Play.wav <underlay sound>

COLISEUM MANAGER.name: Coliseum Manager
COLISEUM MANAGER.flavorText: Meets monthly with the gladiators to discuss career goals.

FIRE HAWK.name: Fire Hawk
FIRE HAWK.flavorText: It’s our fault for making all those card backs that look like food.

HOLY NOVA.name: Holy Nova
HOLY NOVA.flavorText: If the Holy Light forsakes you, good luck casting this spell. Also, you're probably a jerk.

MALFUNCTION.name: Malfunction
MALFUNCTION.flavorText: Bug Report: This card works perfectly.

CARRION DRAKE.name: Carrion Drake
CARRION DRAKE.flavorText: Fits easily into overhead luggage bins.

GROMMASH HELLSCREAM.name: Grommash Hellscream
GROMMASH HELLSCREAM.flavorText: Grommash drank the tainted blood of Mannoroth, dooming the orcs to green skin and red eyes! Maybe not his best decision.

HALKIAS.name: Halkias
HALKIAS.flavorText: Everybody tough until the sinstones start walking.

CRYSTAL LION.name: Crystal Lion
CRYSTAL LION.flavorText: Standard issue recruit gear: 1 silver sword, 1 Lordaeron insignia, 2 bags of crystal kibble.

FORBIDDEN FLAME.name: Forbidden Flame
FORBIDDEN FLAME.flavorText: WARNING: This flame is not to be used unless you are a licensed acolyte of the Old Gods.

COMPOSTING.name: Composting
COMPOSTING.flavorText: The Treants really give their bodies to the cause.

SPIRIT ECHO.name: Spirit Echo
SPIRIT ECHO.flavorText: I guess you can say they’re… “soul survivors.”

SILENT KNIGHT.name: Silent Knight
SILENT KNIGHT.flavorText: He used to be a librarian. Old habits die hard.

BEAMING SIDEKICK.name: Beaming Sidekick
BEAMING SIDEKICK.flavorText: Sure, I'll carry the water! And the food! And the tents! And the cursed monkey paw!

NINE LIVES.name: Nine Lives
NINE LIVES.flavorText: Beware the night of the living pets!

SHADOW ASCENDANT.name: Shadow Ascendant
SHADOW ASCENDANT.flavorText: When you're at the bottom, there's nowhere to ascend, but up.

IMPRISONED OBSERVER.name: Imprisoned Observer
IMPRISONED OBSERVER.flavorText: Currently serving two turns on charges of aggravated minion slaughter.

ACOLYTE OF DEATH.name: Acolyte of Death
ACOLYTE OF DEATH.flavorText: "I see dead people. A LOT of dead people."

SPIKED HOGRIDER.name: Spiked Hogrider
SPIKED HOGRIDER.flavorText: Did you know the Hogchoppers compete every year at the Mirage Raceway? They do. It's a real group.

MAGTHERIDON.name: Magtheridon
MAGTHERIDON.flavorText: Came from another world to invade Outland and bend it to his will… only to be overthrown by an elf from another world who invaded Outland and bent it to his will.

GRAVELSNOUT KNIGHT.name: Gravelsnout Knight
GRAVELSNOUT KNIGHT.flavorText: The mole of La Mancha rides again!

SILVER SWORD.name: Silver Sword
SILVER SWORD.flavorText: Silver’s malleability limits its utility as an edged weapon. On the other hand... SHINY!

VIOLET SPELLSWORD.name: Violet Spellsword
VIOLET SPELLSWORD.flavorText: If you have to wield a spell and a sword, then neither is performing to expectation.

BRASS KNUCKLES.name: Brass Knuckles
BRASS KNUCKLES.flavorText: For the goon that wants to make a fashion statement.

MIND CONTROL.name: Mind Control
MIND CONTROL.flavorText: Nominated as "Spell Most Likely to Make Your Opponent Punch the Wall."

KINGPIN PUD.name: Kingpin Pud
KINGPIN PUD.flavorText: The good, the bad, and the ugly stats for the Cost.

TEN GALLON HAT.name: Ten Gallon Hat
TEN GALLON HAT.flavorText: It actually only holds three quarters of a gallon, but that doesn't sound as good.

LOCK ON.name: Lock On
LOCK ON.flavorText: Time to lock in. *ahem* I mean lock on.

MAXIMA BLASTENHEIMER.name: Maxima Blastenheimer
MAXIMA BLASTENHEIMER.flavorText: Believe it or not, this is only the faire's fourth most dangerous game.

CORPORAL.name: Corporal
CORPORAL.flavorText: When he’s sitting in the graveyard ready to rez, he’s incorporal.

BASH.name: Bash
BASH.flavorText: You might think bashing doesn't take a lot of practice. It doesn't.

EAGER UNDERLING.name: Eager Underling
EAGER UNDERLING.flavorText: Eager to please, even if it kills him.

IRON HIDE.name: Iron Hide
IRON HIDE.flavorText: Week 6. I remain covered head to toe with scales. They do not yet realize that I am not a dinosaur.

BLOOD TREANT.name: Blood Treant
BLOOD TREANT.flavorText: The blood of my enemies makes for some great fertilizer!

TAKE TO THE SKIES.name: Take to the Skies
TAKE TO THE SKIES.flavorText: This is one step above reaching for the skies.

PUZZLEMASTER KHADGAR.name: Puzzlemaster Khadgar
PUZZLEMASTER KHADGAR.flavorText: Khadgar Khadgar in the ball, who is the smartest white-haired, tall, handsome mage of them all?

RAZORFEN HUNTER.name: Razorfen Hunter
RAZORFEN HUNTER.flavorText: Someone did mess with Tuskerr once. ONCE.

VIBRANT SQUIRREL.name: Vibrant Squirrel
VIBRANT SQUIRREL.flavorText: Oh, they're cute now. Just wait till they unleash a Savage Roar.

HERALD VOLAZJ.name: Herald Volazj
HERALD VOLAZJ.flavorText: His whole job is yelling "Yogg-Saron comin'!"

BLOOD OF G'HUUN.name: Blood of G'huun
BLOOD OF G'HUUN.flavorText: An attempted cure becomes disease, blooming and thriving as rot and decay.

WYRM WEAVER.name: Wyrm Weaver
WYRM WEAVER.flavorText: Studied basket weaving as an undergrad.

NECROTIC GEIST.name: Necrotic Geist
NECROTIC GEIST.flavorText: An eye for an eye, and a ghoul for a ghoul.

SWINETUSK SHANK.name: Swinetusk Shank
SWINETUSK SHANK.flavorText: Comes with a rack of ribs!

MISCHIEVOUS IMP.name: Mischievous Imp
MISCHIEVOUS IMP.flavorText: Why is it when something happens, it is always you three?

ARCANE ARTIFICER.name: Arcane Artificer
ARCANE ARTIFICER.flavorText: Ethereal armor dissipates in 6 hours which can cause extreme awkwardness for first time buyers.

SPELLWARD JEWELER.name: Spellward Jeweler
SPELLWARD JEWELER.flavorText: The fanciest possible way of distracting enemies with shiny things.

CATRINA MUERTE.name: Catrina Muerte
CATRINA MUERTE.flavorText: She always manages to lift your spirits.

SHADOWFIEND.name: Shadowfiend
SHADOWFIEND.flavorText: Hopes to be promoted to "Shadowfriend" someday.

VULPERA SCOUNDREL.name: Vulpera Scoundrel
VULPERA SCOUNDREL.flavorText: A spell is a spell, but the mystery choice could be anything! (It's also a spell.)

CABALIST'S TOME.name: Cabalist's Tome
CABALIST'S TOME.flavorText: What's in there? I bet it's cookie recipes!

SLEEPY DRAGON.name: Sleepy Dragon
SLEEPY DRAGON.flavorText: Local villagers call her "Naps Under the Mountain."

EXCAVATED EVIL.name: Excavated Evil
EXCAVATED EVIL.flavorText: MOM! DAD! DON'T TOUCH IT! IT'S EVIL!!!!!!

KOBOLD STICKYFINGER.name: Kobold Stickyfinger
KOBOLD STICKYFINGER.flavorText: He no take candle. He take sword.

THELDURIN THE LOST.name: Theldurin the Lost
THELDURIN THE LOST.flavorText: He might be lost, but he knows where you can find these hands.

LAKKARI FELHOUND.name: Lakkari Felhound
LAKKARI FELHOUND.flavorText: Guaranteed to track tar all over your carpet.

CYCLOPIAN CRUSHER.name: Cyclopian Crusher
CYCLOPIAN CRUSHER.flavorText: Really puts the rusher in crusher. Uses its one eye to C.

GENTLE MEGASAUR.name: Gentle Megasaur
GENTLE MEGASAUR.flavorText: "Low, low rents! Must enjoy a nomadic lifestyle. Quasi-sentient, bipedal, amphibious humanoids ONLY!"

RECKONING.name: Reckoning
RECKONING.flavorText: He would henceforth be known as "Karmerr, the Doom of Kazzak."

MASTER OF DISGUISE.name: Master of Disguise
MASTER OF DISGUISE.flavorText: She's actually a male tauren. People don't call him "Master of Disguise" for nothing.

DUSKHAVEN HUNTER.name: Duskhaven Hunter
DUSKHAVEN HUNTER.flavorText: After a short paws, she's back to herself again.

JUMBO IMP.name: Jumbo Imp
JUMBO IMP.flavorText: Jumbo in size! Huge in E.V.I.L.!

LIBRAM OF JUDGMENT.name: Libram of Judgment
LIBRAM OF JUDGMENT.flavorText: You really can't judge a book by its cover.

DARKMOON STATUE.name: Darkmoon Statue
DARKMOON STATUE.flavorText: As far as workplace injuries go, Silas is protected by his statue of limitations.

BRIGHTWING.name: Brightwing
BRIGHTWING.flavorText: Little faerie dragons are made of sugar and spice and maniacal vice.

AMANI WAR BEAR.name: Amani War Bear
AMANI WAR BEAR.flavorText: "I used to farm for hours! Now they just come in packs?"

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/fd/TRL_550_AmaniWarBear_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ TRL_550_AmaniWarBear_Play.wav <summon sound>

OMEGA ASSEMBLY.name: Omega Assembly
OMEGA ASSEMBLY.flavorText: They told Dr. Boom he could only pick one. He disagreed.

RAS FROSTWHISPER.name: Ras Frostwhisper
RAS FROSTWHISPER.flavorText: Always the favorite of Headmaster Kel'Thuzad, Ras nonetheless received a chilly reception from the other faculty.

NOFIN CAN STOP US.name: Nofin Can Stop Us
NOFIN CAN STOP US.flavorText: "I'm having a good time! I don't want to stop at all!"

FELSCALE EVOKER.name: Felscale Evoker
FELSCALE EVOKER.flavorText: So it’s a demon and a naga, but NOT a dragon?

LIGHTFORGED CARIEL.name: Lightforged Cariel
LIGHTFORGED CARIEL.flavorText: Her faith, unshakable. Her shield, immovable. Her enemies, irredeemable.

INNERVATE.name: Innervate
INNERVATE.flavorText: Some druids still have flashbacks from strangers yelling "Innervate me!!" at them.

TYPHOON.name: Typhoon
TYPHOON.flavorText: I gotta go Julia, we got satyrs.

RAT TRAP.name: Rat Trap
RAT TRAP.flavorText: MISSING: One giant rat. Please return to King Togwaggle.

BUG COLLECTOR.name: Bug Collector
BUG COLLECTOR.flavorText: The only one who likes BEEEES!!!

IMP-OSTER.name: Imp-oster
IMP-OSTER.flavorText: There is an imposter among us.

FAN OF KNIVES.name: Fan of Knives
FAN OF KNIVES.flavorText: I wouldn't say I LOVE knives, but I'm definitely a fan.

NETHERWALKER.name: Netherwalker
NETHERWALKER.flavorText: You got to Nethercrawl before you can Netherwalk.

AZERITE VEIN.name: Azerite Vein
AZERITE VEIN.flavorText: When the ground trembles near it, are those earthquakes or heartbeats?

DUNEMAUL SHAMAN.name: Dunemaul Shaman
DUNEMAUL SHAMAN.flavorText: He just closes his eyes and goes for it. Raarararrrarar!

MOSSY HORROR.name: Mossy Horror
MOSSY HORROR.flavorText: The hills have eyes. And teeth. Pretty bad breath, too.

VERANUS.name: Veranus
VERANUS.flavorText: As an empty nester, she just misses her little ones.

SHATTERING BLAST.name: Shattering Blast
SHATTERING BLAST.flavorText: Let's be honest, they weren't going to unfreeze anyway.

KABAL SONGSTEALER.name: Kabal Songstealer
KABAL SONGSTEALER.flavorText: Gadgetzan Writer’s Award goes to the player who writes the most compelling fanfic about why this Arakkoa has a golden frog in his hand!

MANAFEEDER PANTHARA.name: Manafeeder Panthara
MANAFEEDER PANTHARA.flavorText: Feeds on mana, crystal kibble, and whatever it was you were just snacking on.

YELLING YODELER.name: Yelling Yodeler
YELLING YODELER.flavorText: Maybe it's OK for the Grimtotem to destroy some music forever.

PRIESTESS VALISHJ.name: Priestess Valishj
PRIESTESS VALISHJ.flavorText: Some of the more stoic priestesses worry that she's living too lavishjly.

SAIDAN THE SCARLET.name: Saidan the Scarlet
SAIDAN THE SCARLET.flavorText: An orc mage accidentally kited him all the way from Stratholme.

XAVIUS.name: Xavius
XAVIUS.flavorText: Xavius has grand nightmares of summoning Sargeras into this world, but a few Satyr will have to do for now.

HOLY LIGHT.name: Holy Light
HOLY LIGHT.flavorText: If you are often bathed in Holy Light, you should consider wearing sunscreen.

PRIESTESS OF ELUNE.name: Priestess of Elune
PRIESTESS OF ELUNE.flavorText: If she threatens to "moon" you, it's not what you think.

FATE SPLITTER.name: Fate Splitter
FATE SPLITTER.flavorText: "What's the matter with these scissors!? The thread won't cut!!"

TRUESILVER CHAMPION.name: Truesilver Champion
TRUESILVER CHAMPION.flavorText: It Slices, it Dices. You can cut a tin can with it. (But you wouldn't want to.)

JADE TELEGRAM.name: Jade Telegram
JADE TELEGRAM.flavorText: Golem-gram for Han'Cho! Golem-gram for Han'Cho!

DOOM!.name: DOOM!
DOOM!.flavorText: We ran out of space for "DOOOOOOOOOOOM!!!!!"

INFESTED WOLF.name: Infested Wolf
INFESTED WOLF.flavorText: A little flea powder will fix that right up.

VICTORIOUS VRYKUL.name: Victorious Vrykul
VICTORIOUS VRYKUL.flavorText: Get three of these and you have a Trikul.

GENZO, THE SHARK.name: Genzo, the Shark
GENZO, THE SHARK.flavorText: Infamous in the seedy underground card rooms of Gadgetzan, he got his nickname winning the coveted Shark Plushie in the city's first Hearthstone tournament.

SECURE THE DECK.name: Secure the Deck
SECURE THE DECK.flavorText: "Tied it down, boss. I don't really know why you asked me to do that."

NOBLE MOUNT.name: Noble Mount
NOBLE MOUNT.flavorText: The Horde rued the day that Cariel was allowed to take her pet to work.

BROOD KEEPER.name: Brood Keeper
BROOD KEEPER.flavorText: Mess with the brood, and you get the dude!

RAGING WORGEN.name: Raging Worgen
RAGING WORGEN.flavorText: If he's raging now, just wait until he gets nerfed.

CANNONMASTER SMYTHE.name: Cannonmaster Smythe
CANNONMASTER SMYTHE.flavorText: "Smythe, it's been a real blast serving the Alliance with you."

OUTFIT TAILOR.name: Outfit Tailor
OUTFIT TAILOR.flavorText: She has this terrible habit of eating melted cheese while on the job.

DEEP SPACE CURATOR.name: Deep Space Curator
DEEP SPACE CURATOR.flavorText: *Gestures to empty room* "...and here is my curated collection of space."

WHETSTONE HATCHET.name: Whetstone Hatchet
WHETSTONE HATCHET.flavorText: A bad hatchet can make a good spear better.

SEAFLOOR SAVIOR.name: Seafloor Savior
SEAFLOOR SAVIOR.flavorText: "TURTLE PROCURED. ADMINISTRATING BANDAGES AND KISSES. BOO BOO MUST BE ELIMINATED."

GRIZZLED WIZARD.name: Grizzled Wizard
GRIZZLED WIZARD.flavorText: When he was young, he was an Outrageous Magus.

TOOTHY CHEST.name: Toothy Chest
TOOTHY CHEST.flavorText: Do you want to eat an adventurer? I want to eat an adventurer!

MARROWSLICER.name: Marrowslicer
MARROWSLICER.flavorText: Perfect for killing the first boss in Icecrown Citadel.

JADE CHIEFTAIN.name: Jade Chieftain
JADE CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: Seeing his Jade Golem grow up into the tall, handsome 6/6 standing before him was the proudest moment of his life.

OZRUK.name: Ozruk
OZRUK.flavorText: Between you and me, Ozruk is a bit obsessed with his body.

ALARMED SECURITYBOT.name: Alarmed Securitybot
ALARMED SECURITYBOT.flavorText: THREAT LEVEL: 5! Which doesn't actually sound that bad to be honest.

MASK OF C'THUN.name: Mask of C'Thun
MASK OF C'THUN.flavorText: Hide in the mask, but it will wear you. Through its gleaming eye, you shall see true.

VOLCANO.name: Volcano
VOLCANO.flavorText: Many young shaman summon a volcano as their first school project.

RALLY!.name: Rally!
RALLY!.flavorText: One for the squire, two for the gnome, three for the glory, and GO, GO, GO!

SPIRIT OF THE SHARK.name: Spirit of the Shark
SPIRIT OF THE SHARK.flavorText: It has Stealth, but its ominous theme music keeps giving it away.

VOODOO DOCTOR.name: Voodoo Doctor
VOODOO DOCTOR.flavorText: Voodoo is an oft-misunderstood art. But it is art.

SHAMBLING CHOW.name: Shambling Chow
SHAMBLING CHOW.flavorText: And step, and shamble, and step, and flip the hair!

DON'T STAND IN THE FIRE!.name: Don't Stand in the Fire!
DON'T STAND IN THE FIRE!.flavorText: Apparently the “Caution: Hot Surface” sign had burned up.

BAZAAR BURGLARY.name: Bazaar Burglary
BAZAAR BURGLARY.flavorText: Just when you set up your "All-Natural Scented Candles" at the farmer's market and then some STUPID KOBOLD COMES AND TAKES THEM ALL!

DREAD CORSAIR.name: Dread Corsair
DREAD CORSAIR.flavorText: "Yarrrr" is a pirate word that means "Greetings, milord."

FURBOLG MOSSBINDER.name: Furbolg Mossbinder
FURBOLG MOSSBINDER.flavorText: Behold, the unstoppable power of MOSS!

DARK ALLEY PACT.name: Dark Alley Pact
DARK ALLEY PACT.flavorText: "With your help, I can finally install some proper lighting in this alley."

FORCE OF NATURE.name: Force of Nature
FORCE OF NATURE.flavorText: "I think I'll just nap under these trees. Wait... AAAAAHHH!" - Blinkfizz, the Unfortunate Gnome

BINDING HEAL.name: Binding Heal
BINDING HEAL.flavorText: By accepting this healing, you agree to the following terms…

AZSHARAN SABER.name: Azsharan Saber
AZSHARAN SABER.flavorText: Even in ancient times, the Night Elves were committed cat people.

BARGAIN BIN BUCCANEER.name: Bargain Bin Buccaneer
BARGAIN BIN BUCCANEER.flavorText: Thrift stores have the best buccaneers.

JEWELED SCARAB.name: Jeweled Scarab
JEWELED SCARAB.flavorText: It's amazing what you can do with super glue!

CRIMSON SIGIL RUNNER.name: Crimson Sigil Runner
CRIMSON SIGIL RUNNER.flavorText: He's not the fastest of the bunch, but he'll take a stab at it anyway.

CARIEL ROAME.name: Cariel Roame
CARIEL ROAME.flavorText: Cariel had pledged her honor to the Alliance, but when someone matching her long-lost sister's description was sighted at the Crossroads, Cariel did the unthinkable: she abandoned her post and set out across the Barrens.

SHIVER THEIR TIMBERS!.name: Shiver Their Timbers!
SHIVER THEIR TIMBERS!.flavorText: Who knew there was overlap between pirates and lumberjacks?

DARKSPEAKER.name: Darkspeaker
DARKSPEAKER.flavorText: People often think that Darkspeaker is the arch nemesis of Lightspeaker, but that title actually belongs to Heavyspeaker.

WITCHWOOD APPLE.name: Witchwood Apple
WITCHWOOD APPLE.flavorText: An apple a day keeps the worgen at bay.

HUNTING MASTIFF.name: Hunting Mastiff
HUNTING MASTIFF.flavorText: "Shh! You're going to start a howl!"

RATTLEGORE.name: Rattlegore
RATTLEGORE.flavorText: He looks bad now, but he was pretty handsome in his 20/20s.

OBSIDIAN STATUE.name: Obsidian Statue
OBSIDIAN STATUE.flavorText: The original artist spent many hours with a fine chisel perfecting the facial expression for maximum tauntiness.

SCARAB EGG.name: Scarab Egg
SCARAB EGG.flavorText: They say you can’t make an omelet without AHHH THEY’RE EATING MY FACE!

WARBOT.name: Warbot
WARBOT.flavorText: Mass production of warbots was halted when it was discovered that they were accidentally being produced at "sample size."

BLAST TORTOISE.name: Blast Tortoise
BLAST TORTOISE.flavorText: Who's that minion? ... Iiiiit's Blast Tortoise! "Blast tortoise."

STORMWIND AVENGER.name: Stormwind Avenger
STORMWIND AVENGER.flavorText: "I swear if you heal me I will DPS."

ANCIENT BREWMASTER.name: Ancient Brewmaster
ANCIENT BREWMASTER.flavorText: Most pandaren say his brew tastes like yak. But apparently that's a compliment.

WEALTH REDISTRIBUTOR.name: Wealth Redistributor
WEALTH REDISTRIBUTOR.flavorText: WOULD YE LIKE CASH BACK? [ ] YAR HAR [ ] YO HO

INNER FIRE.name: Inner Fire
INNER FIRE.flavorText: Good idea: Buffing your minions. Bad idea: Starting a conversation in the Barrens.

ICE TRAP.name: Ice Trap
ICE TRAP.flavorText: I literally watched the Hunter place it down in front of me and I still stepped in it.

VRYKUL NECROLYTE.name: Vrykul Necrolyte
VRYKUL NECROLYTE.flavorText: If at first you don't succeed, vry, vry again.

ELITE TAUREN CHIEFTAIN.name: Elite Tauren Chieftain
ELITE TAUREN CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: He's looking for a drummer. The current candidates are: Novice Engineer, Sen'jin Shieldmasta', and Ragnaros the Firelord.

WAILING VAPOR.name: Wailing Vapor
WAILING VAPOR.flavorText: If you have The Vapors, your Humors might be imbalanced.

WARSONG COMMANDER.name: Warsong Commander
WARSONG COMMANDER.flavorText: The Warsong clan is such drama. It's really not worth it to become a commander.

STARVING BUZZARD.name: Starving Buzzard
STARVING BUZZARD.flavorText: If you feed him, he loses his whole identity.

EVOLVING SPORES.name: Evolving Spores
EVOLVING SPORES.flavorText: The most powerful mushrooms are commonly found in boxes marked with "?".

MASKED CONTENDER.name: Masked Contender
MASKED CONTENDER.flavorText: Knew Mysterious Challenger back when he was a Mysterious Squire.

SHADOWJEWELER HANAR.name: Shadowjeweler Hanar
SHADOWJEWELER HANAR.flavorText: What is a shadowjeweler? A miserable little pile of secrets.

EMBRACE THE SHADOW.name: Embrace the Shadow
EMBRACE THE SHADOW.flavorText: For when your Auchenai Soulpriests call in sick.

KEYMASTER ALABASTER.name: Keymaster Alabaster
KEYMASTER ALABASTER.flavorText: The key to his mastery is a solid stack of backup copies.

PRIEST OF THE DECEASED.name: Priest of the Deceased
PRIEST OF THE DECEASED.flavorText: "Funnel cakes? I haven't had those in years…"

BRU'KAN OF THE ELEMENTS.name: Bru'kan of the Elements
BRU'KAN OF THE ELEMENTS.flavorText: The elements crackled through Bru'kan's veins and his life flashed before his eyes. He knew this moment would come, but he wondered, had he given them enough?

DARK IRON SKULKER.name: Dark Iron Skulker
DARK IRON SKULKER.flavorText: He loves skulking. He skulks after hours just for the joy of it, but his friends are pretty worried he'll get burnt out.

DESPERATE MEASURES.name: Desperate Measures
DESPERATE MEASURES.flavorText: Desperate times call for disparate secrets.

SUPERNOVA.name: Supernova
SUPERNOVA.flavorText: People who enjoy the heat will say this looks like perfect weather.

PUNCH CARD.name: Punch Card
PUNCH CARD.flavorText: Don't forget to punch out when you Cleave.

ILLUMINATE.name: Illuminate
ILLUMINATE.flavorText: BEHOLD THE GLORY OF A NEW CUP!

NIGHT HOWLER.name: Night Howler
NIGHT HOWLER.flavorText: Honestly, he howls during the day, too.

DINOMANCY.name: Dinomancy
DINOMANCY.flavorText: Anyone can dinomance. Just put your lips together and RAAWWWAARGGGH.

ELECTRA STORMSURGE.name: Electra Stormsurge
ELECTRA STORMSURGE.flavorText: "The coin? You used me for THE COIN!?"

BARON RIVENDARE.name: Baron Rivendare
BARON RIVENDARE.flavorText: There used to be five Horsemen but one of them left because a job opened up in the deadmines and the benefits were better.

PROPHET VELEN.name: Prophet Velen
PROPHET VELEN.flavorText: He's been exiled from his home, and all his brothers turned evil, but otherwise he doesn't have a lot to complain about.

PORTAL OVERFIEND.name: Portal Overfiend
PORTAL OVERFIEND.flavorText: It’s like an interdimensional game of demon tag.

WEBSPINNER.name: Webspinner
WEBSPINNER.flavorText: Spider cocoons are like little piñatas!

FLANKING STRIKE.name: Flanking Strike
FLANKING STRIKE.flavorText: Wolves to the left and arrows to the right, here I am stuck in the middle with you.

DRUID OF THE FLAME.name: Druid of the Flame
DRUID OF THE FLAME.flavorText: Druids who fought too long in Northrend were easily seduced by Ragnaros; a mug of hot chocolate was generally all it took.

DEADLY POISON.name: Deadly Poison
DEADLY POISON.flavorText: Rogues guard the secrets to poison-making carefully, lest magi start incorporating poison into their spells. Poisonbolt? Rain of Poison? Poison Elemental? Nobody wants that.

THE REPLICATOR-INATOR.name: The Replicator-inator
THE REPLICATOR-INATOR.flavorText: Dr. Boom is the greatest inventor in the Tri-Zone area!

GIGGLING TOYMAKER.name: Giggling Toymaker
GIGGLING TOYMAKER.flavorText: "HAHAhehehe. Hahaha he." -Me when I'm making toys

DREAMBOUND RAPTOR.name: Dreambound Raptor
DREAMBOUND RAPTOR.flavorText: Dream, dream, dream, dream, dream, dreeeeeeeeam.

PIT MASTER.name: Pit Master
PIT MASTER.flavorText: If you win your duel, he'll throw in some of his famous Pit Master barbecue.

HERALD OF CHAOS.name: Herald of Chaos
HERALD OF CHAOS.flavorText: They used to be called the Heralds of Order before all of this silly Sundering nonsense.

THE GARDEN'S GRACE.name: The Garden's Grace
THE GARDEN'S GRACE.flavorText: The perfect place to hold Conchella.

CURSE OF WEAKNESS.name: Curse of Weakness
CURSE OF WEAKNESS.flavorText: Warlocks refer to this as a "balance change."

SHADOWREAPER ANDUIN.name: Shadowreaper Anduin
SHADOWREAPER ANDUIN.flavorText: "I will tell you what Velen never taught me. Whosoever stands before the Light… inevitably casts a shadow."

AZSHARAN GARDENS.name: Azsharan Gardens
AZSHARAN GARDENS.flavorText: That's not what I meant when I asked you to water the garden.

PARRRLEY.name: Parrrley
PARRRLEY.flavorText: Time to engage in some unfriendly negotiations.

ARCHIMONDE.name: Archimonde
ARCHIMONDE.flavorText: Archimonde joined Sargeras in search of power, and in doing so became one of the strongest forces within the Burning Legion who laid waste to countless planets… but in the end he still lost to a wisp.

ARANASI BROODMOTHER.name: Aranasi Broodmother
ARANASI BROODMOTHER.flavorText: She's got a big brood and a big mood.

EVIL RECRUITER.name: EVIL Recruiter
EVIL RECRUITER.flavorText: I'm starting to think the lackeys aren't evil, just taken advantage of.

LAST STAND.name: Last Stand
LAST STAND.flavorText: If you play two Last Stands in one game, you're a liar.

MINEFIELD.name: Minefield
MINEFIELD.flavorText: Dodge bombs like you're playing Tonksweeper!

SOULBOUND ASHTONGUE.name: Soulbound Ashtongue
SOULBOUND ASHTONGUE.flavorText: He claims to be "soulbound," but I just think he's clingy.

PAINTED CANVASAUR.name: Painted Canvasaur
PAINTED CANVASAUR.flavorText: Oh this is a present? Would you like that gift raptor not?

LADY DARKVEIN.name: Lady Darkvein
LADY DARKVEIN.flavorText: You're so vein. I bet you think this flavor text is about you.

STITCHED CREATION.name: Stitched Creation
STITCHED CREATION.flavorText: To defend Naxxramas from the oncoming adventurers, the Scourge created a monstrosity the world had never seen before: an abomination wearing clothes!!

KODO MOUNT.name: Kodo Mount
KODO MOUNT.flavorText: No matter how big they are or how many times you tell them no, they STILL won't stay off the couch.

LIGHTWELL.name: Lightwell
LIGHTWELL.flavorText: It isn't clear if people ignore the Lightwell, or if it is just invisible.

PARADE LEADER.name: Parade Leader
PARADE LEADER.flavorText: He's always going to reign on his parade.

ARGENT LANCE.name: Argent Lance
ARGENT LANCE.flavorText: The stripes make it look like a candy cane, but we recommend against licking it.

DIVINE FAVOR.name: Divine Favor
DIVINE FAVOR.flavorText: This is not just a favor, but a divine one, like helping someone move a couch with a fold out bed!

SKERAM CULTIST.name: Skeram Cultist
SKERAM CULTIST.flavorText: Just before he comes into play, there is an AWESOME training montage with C'Thun.

DREAD RAVEN.name: Dread Raven
DREAD RAVEN.flavorText: Fun Fact: A group of three Dread Ravens is an unkindness. Four is lethal!

WINDSHEAR STORMCALLER.name: Windshear Stormcaller
WINDSHEAR STORMCALLER.flavorText: Don't ever doubt Al'Akir's love for basic totems.

CHAMELEOS.name: Chameleos
CHAMELEOS.flavorText: He's everyone you want to be.

WILDPAW CAVERN.name: Wildpaw Cavern
WILDPAW CAVERN.flavorText: Adventurers were quite confused when they saw how many boots were frozen to the ceiling.

MIND BLAST.name: Mind Blast
MIND BLAST.flavorText: This spell blasts you directly in the MIND.

STORMCRACK.name: Stormcrack
STORMCRACK.flavorText: WARNING: DO NOT TOUCH THE PURPLE BALL OF LIGHTNING

COBALT SPELLKIN.name: Cobalt Spellkin
COBALT SPELLKIN.flavorText: Spews more spells than a sleep-talking wizard.

GRIMESTREET INFORMANT.name: Grimestreet Informant
GRIMESTREET INFORMANT.flavorText: "Naw, naw. You're talkin' about Grime BOULEVARD. I ain't know nuthin' 'bout that."

FOGSAIL FREEBOOTER.name: Fogsail Freebooter
FOGSAIL FREEBOOTER.flavorText: Goes cheap on wardrobe so he can spend on weaponry.

TOGWAGGLE'S SCHEME.name: Togwaggle's Scheme
TOGWAGGLE'S SCHEME.flavorText: "Many minions equals many treasures for king. Kobold arithmetic!"

COSMIC KEYBOARD.name: Cosmic Keyboard
COSMIC KEYBOARD.flavorText: Mine is signed by Algalon himself.

HUMONGOUS RAZORLEAF.name: Humongous Razorleaf
HUMONGOUS RAZORLEAF.flavorText: Loves goblins. In a light cream sauce.

DEADLY FORK.name: Deadly Fork
DEADLY FORK.flavorText: For a proper setting, place the deadly fork after the salad fork, but before the dinner fork.

SERGEANT SALLY.name: Sergeant Sally
SERGEANT SALLY.flavorText: "Who is she? Where did she come from? We don't even have a police force here in Gadgetzan!!" - Mayor Noggenfogger

VOIDWALKER.name: Voidwalker
VOIDWALKER.flavorText: No relation to "The Voidsteppers", the popular Void-based dance troupe.

BLOOD WITCH.name: Blood Witch
BLOOD WITCH.flavorText: Like a sloppy joe for vampires.

WHIRLWIND.name: Whirlwind
WHIRLWIND.flavorText: The way to tell seasoned warriors from novice ones: the novices yell "wheeeee" while whirlwinding.

AEON REAVER.name: Aeon Reaver
AEON REAVER.flavorText: Ripping centuries asunder helps him manage his busy schedule.

IMPORTED TARANTULA.name: Imported Tarantula
IMPORTED TARANTULA.flavorText: Which forbidden forest did you get this from?

RAZORFEN ROCKSTAR.name: Razorfen Rockstar
RAZORFEN ROCKSTAR.flavorText: Quilboar feel Rock in their blood. And blood in their rocks.

BLESSING OF MIGHT.name: Blessing of Might
BLESSING OF MIGHT.flavorText: "As in, you MIGHT want to get out of my way." - Toad Mackle, recently buffed.

DRUID OF THE PLAINS.name: Druid of the Plains
DRUID OF THE PLAINS.flavorText: Not to be confused with the aeronautically advanced Druid of the Planes.

HERALD OF LOKHOLAR.name: Herald of Lokholar
HERALD OF LOKHOLAR.flavorText: “I don’t care how hot it is. I am not going over there to be your air conditioning."

ONYXIAN DRAKE.name: Onyxian Drake
ONYXIAN DRAKE.flavorText: The best offense is a great defense.

SUMMER FLOWERCHILD.name: Summer Flowerchild
SUMMER FLOWERCHILD.flavorText: "Ugh, those Winter Floweradults just don't get our music."

SPHERE OF SAPIENCE.name: Sphere of Sapience
SPHERE OF SAPIENCE.flavorText: This is what it sounds like when spheres scry.

TREASURE HUNTER EUDORA.name: Treasure Hunter Eudora
TREASURE HUNTER EUDORA.flavorText: How hard could it be to hunt treasure? It doesn't even run away when you shoot it!

URSOL.name: Ursol
URSOL.flavorText: Twin of Ursoc, they were inseparable until death drove Ursoc’s spirit to corruption, while Ursol’s remained at peace.

KNUCKLES.name: Knuckles
KNUCKLES.flavorText: When confronted with accusations of performance-enhancing bananas, Knuckles replied, "I get my fruit from trees I knock down with my bare hands like everyone else."

HIDEOUS HUSK.name: Hideous Husk
HIDEOUS HUSK.flavorText: This is what's known as a zombiotic relationship.

CONTAMINATED LASHER.name: Contaminated Lasher
CONTAMINATED LASHER.flavorText: He corrupts me, he corrupts me not.

STEEL BEETLE.name: Steel Beetle
STEEL BEETLE.flavorText: Steel you can trust—fashioned from the husk of an over-sized creepy-crawly.

BOULDERFIST OGRE.name: Boulderfist Ogre
BOULDERFIST OGRE.flavorText: "ME HAVE GOOD STATS FOR THE COST"

HUNTER'S MARK.name: Hunter's Mark
HUNTER'S MARK.flavorText: Never play 'Hide and Go Seek' with a Hunter.

SKELEMANCER.name: Skelemancer
SKELEMANCER.flavorText: What do you mean there's no such thing as "Skelemancy?" But "Dinomancy" is ok?

STARLIGHT WHELP.name: Starlight Whelp
STARLIGHT WHELP.flavorText: Starlight, star bright, first whelp I see tonight.

CARIA FELSOUL.name: Caria Felsoul
CARIA FELSOUL.flavorText: This is what happens when you keep taking the advice of the little demon on your shoulder.

TENTACLE OF N'ZOTH.name: Tentacle of N'Zoth
TENTACLE OF N'ZOTH.flavorText: Because EVERYDAY is the Day of the Tentacle of N'zoth.

DEATHSPEAKER.name: Deathspeaker
DEATHSPEAKER.flavorText: It helps to speak really, really loud.

WILD PYROMANCER.name: Wild Pyromancer
WILD PYROMANCER.flavorText: BOOM BABY BOOM! BAD IS GOOD! DOWN WITH GOVERNMENT!

TUNDRA RHINO.name: Tundra Rhino
TUNDRA RHINO.flavorText: Tundra rhinos are often mistaken for kodos. Or am I mistaken?

DISCIPLE OF ARGUS.name: Disciple of Argus
DISCIPLE OF ARGUS.flavorText: "Aw nuts, I put both ends in the pencil sharpener."

FROM THE SCRAPHEAP.name: From the Scrapheap
FROM THE SCRAPHEAP.flavorText: Well that's a load of scrap.

GLACIAL MYSTERIES.name: Glacial Mysteries
GLACIAL MYSTERIES.flavorText: The secret is in the frosting.

TOTEMIC REFLECTION.name: Totemic Reflection
TOTEMIC REFLECTION.flavorText: "Upon reflection, I have decided that your board needs more ME."

SHALADRASSIL.name: Shaladrassil
SHALADRASSIL.flavorText: Wow, that Nightmare-B-Gone spray really works! Too bad we didn't have enough for the whole tree.

SLEET SKATER.name: Sleet Skater
SLEET SKATER.flavorText: How do you do, fellow Ice Elementals?

CRYOPRACTOR.name: Cryopractor
CRYOPRACTOR.flavorText: It's really hard to book an appointment, she always gives her clients the cold shoulder.

SOGGOTH THE SLITHERER.name: Soggoth the Slitherer
SOGGOTH THE SLITHERER.flavorText: Don't tell Soggoth, but in the future he gets totally owned by the Master's Glaive and his skull becomes a tourist attraction.

GAIA, THE TECHTONIC.name: Gaia, the Techtonic
GAIA, THE TECHTONIC.flavorText: Always planning ahead, Ini knew she'd need this invention to protect all her other inventions.

BONECALLER.name: Bonecaller
BONECALLER.flavorText: Hello, am I speaking to the undead of the household? We have been trying to reach you about your skeleton's extended warranty.

WICKED STAB (RANK 1).name: Wicked Stab (Rank 1)
WICKED STAB (RANK 1).flavorText: Always go for the glowing weak point.

AUCTIONEER JAXON.name: Auctioneer Jaxon
AUCTIONEER JAXON.flavorText: "Who's up for a brand-new wisp? This thing's in perfect condition, folks! Never been played..."

ICE LANCE.name: Ice Lance
ICE LANCE.flavorText: The trick is not to break the lance. Otherwise, you have "Ice Pieces." Ice Pieces aren't as effective.

NEED FOR GREED.name: Need for Greed
NEED FOR GREED.flavorText: Sorry guys, I TOTALLY meant to click greed.

RAIN OF TOADS.name: Rain of Toads
RAIN OF TOADS.flavorText: "Oh, THAT'S how she brings the warts!"

BUMBLING BELLHOP.name: Bumbling Bellhop
BUMBLING BELLHOP.flavorText: Put some respect on his name: Estebone Soulio Screamcardo Groantoya De la Grossa Ramirooze.

KANRETHAD EBONLOCKE.name: Kanrethad Ebonlocke
KANRETHAD EBONLOCKE.flavorText: After Illidan's downfall, Kanrethad formed the Council of the Black Harvest to study Illidan's fel magic. Some say he was... green with envy.

SP-3Y3-D3R.name: SP-3Y3-D3R
SP-3Y3-D3R.flavorText: The itsy bitsy spider magnetized onto the water spout.

JADE SHURIKEN.name: Jade Shuriken
JADE SHURIKEN.flavorText: Good news is, after you remove it from your wound, you can use it to pay your medical bills!

SCRAP SHOT.name: Scrap Shot
SCRAP SHOT.flavorText: Make your foe's armor your fauna's fashion!

BLOODREAVER GUL'DAN.name: Bloodreaver Gul'dan
BLOODREAVER GUL'DAN.flavorText: "Still you refuse to bend your knee? None can escape death, you old fool. And in death… all will serve me…"

AGAINST ALL ODDS.name: Against All Odds
AGAINST ALL ODDS.flavorText: Time to EVEN out the playing field.

BALINDA STONEHEARTH.name: Balinda Stonehearth
BALINDA STONEHEARTH.flavorText: Imagine her surprise, ending up in a game called Hearthstone.

EXCAVATION SPECIALIST.name: Excavation Specialist
EXCAVATION SPECIALIST.flavorText: With the jungles of Un’goro mapped out and the ruins of Uldum fully uncovered, explorers have to go a little out of their depth in their search of the great unknown.

BLOOD-QUEEN LANA'THEL.name: Blood-Queen Lana'thel
BLOOD-QUEEN LANA'THEL.flavorText: As a young blood-princess she learned the proper way for a lady to curtsy, how to address fellow members of royalty, and how to bite them.

STORM GIANT.name: Storm Giant
STORM GIANT.flavorText: Storm Giant, Frost Giant, Molten Giant... I want Fair-weather and Sunshine Giant!

DESPERATE PRAYER.name: Desperate Prayer
DESPERATE PRAYER.flavorText: Woah, we're halfway there, woah oh...

POP'GAR THE PUTRID.name: Pop'gar the Putrid
POP'GAR THE PUTRID.flavorText: All around the arid badlands The Outlaws chased the Townsfolk Gerry had a train full of sludge POP! goes the sludge train

RESEARCH PROJECT.name: Research Project
RESEARCH PROJECT.flavorText: Abstract: Analyzing systemic applications of coldlight data sets vis-a-vis shuffle-related paradigms. Conclusion: Yay, cards!

DEVOLVING MISSILES.name: Devolving Missiles
DEVOLVING MISSILES.flavorText: Most intermural spell-dueling contests end with a field of wisps.

WARDEN OF CHAINS.name: Warden of Chains
WARDEN OF CHAINS.flavorText: Can’t stay out too late. I gotta head back home to the ol’ ball and chained demon.

RIGHTEOUS PROTECTOR.name: Righteous Protector
RIGHTEOUS PROTECTOR.flavorText: Original name was Tubular Protector, but this seems more bodacious.

SORCERER'S APPRENTICE.name: Sorcerer's Apprentice
SORCERER'S APPRENTICE.flavorText: Apprentices are great for bossing around. "Conjure me some mana buns! And a coffee! Make that a mana coffee!"

PLAGUE STRIKE.name: Plague Strike
PLAGUE STRIKE.flavorText: Not wanting to infect anyone with his cold, the Death Knight politely coughed into his shoulder.

THE CEASELESS EXPANSE.name: The Ceaseless Expanse
THE CEASELESS EXPANSE.flavorText: If you play this for its full Mana cost, you know what? You win. Good day sir!

LEATHERCLAD HOGLEADER.name: Leatherclad Hogleader
LEATHERCLAD HOGLEADER.flavorText: The Hogchoppers, the terrors of Tanaris, can always be found at one tavern or another in Gadgetzan, refueling for totally real and legit adventures that they go on.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/35/VO_CFM_810_Female_Quilboar_Attack_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_CFM_810_Female_Quilboar_Attack_02.wav <death sound>

POUNCE.name: Pounce
POUNCE.flavorText: Comes with an overwhelming urge to jump into the nearest open box.

ARCANE WYRM.name: Arcane Wyrm
ARCANE WYRM.flavorText: Arcane Bolt on you, Arcane Bolt on your cow, Arcane Bolt on your whole family!

JURY DUTY.name: Jury Duty
JURY DUTY.flavorText: The most criminal thing about paladins is that they actually like jury duty.

DANCING COBRA.name: Dancing Cobra
DANCING COBRA.flavorText: Snakes are just tentacles with fangs.

DOLLMASTER DORIAN.name: Dollmaster Dorian
DOLLMASTER DORIAN.flavorText: The children were puzzled by the scratches covering the insides of their toy-boxes.

WANDERING MONSTER.name: Wandering Monster
WANDERING MONSTER.flavorText: Not all who wander are lost. This one is lost though, for sure.

ANTIQUE FLINGER.name: Antique Flinger
ANTIQUE FLINGER.flavorText: One man's treasure is another man's statue to the face.

LORD MARROWGAR.name: Lord Marrowgar
LORD MARROWGAR.flavorText: And now, Lord Marrowgar with the weather.

REDBAND WASP.name: Redband Wasp
REDBAND WASP.flavorText: Also comes in other colors, but red's in fashion this season.

SILVER HAND REGENT.name: Silver Hand Regent
SILVER HAND REGENT.flavorText: The Silver Hand is the best paladin organization. The Argent Crusaders are super jealous.

TIMBER WOLF.name: Timber Wolf
TIMBER WOLF.flavorText: Other beasts totally dig hanging out with timber wolves.

CRIMSON COMMANDER.name: Crimson Commander
CRIMSON COMMANDER.flavorText: "Wait… why do I have a Deathrattle?"

MESSENGER BUZZARD.name: Messenger Buzzard
MESSENGER BUZZARD.flavorText: The bird brings the word (which happens to be bird).

DEATH BLOSSOM WHOMPER.name: Death Blossom Whomper
DEATH BLOSSOM WHOMPER.flavorText: We call her Audrey II. She was named after her mother.

BLESSED GOODS.name: Blessed Goods
BLESSED GOODS.flavorText: Guaranteed to contain no haunted dolls, cursed rings, or corrupted runeblades, or your money back.

SIPHONING GROWTH.name: Siphoning Growth
SIPHONING GROWTH.flavorText: No thanks. This one's all yours, bud.

HEX.name: Hex
HEX.flavorText: If you Hex a Murloc... it really isn't much of a change, is it?

TICKET MASTER.name: Ticket Master
TICKET MASTER.flavorText: You can exchange one ticket for a bear or save up thousands for a tacky light-up paperweight!

REPACKAGE.name: Repackage
REPACKAGE.flavorText: I don't want to play with you anymore.

ASSASSIN'S BLADE.name: Assassin's Blade
ASSASSIN'S BLADE.flavorText: Guaranteed to have been owned by a real assassin. Certificate of authenticity included.

FIRE BREATHER.name: Fire Breather
FIRE BREATHER.flavorText: "Phew! That skull has been stuck between my teeth for hours!"

DEVOUR MIND.name: Devour Mind
DEVOUR MIND.flavorText: A mind is a terrible thing to waste. Seconds, anyone?

MUKLA'S CHAMPION.name: Mukla's Champion
MUKLA'S CHAMPION.flavorText: An elegant gorilla, for a more civilized age.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/82/VO_AT_090_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_090_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e9/VO_AT_090_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_090_ATTACK_02.wav <attack sound>
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/bb/VO_AT_090_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_090_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

RELENTLESS WRATHGUARD.name: Relentless Wrathguard
RELENTLESS WRATHGUARD.flavorText: Ugh, for the love of... could they just send a Relenting Smileguard for once!?

SCARLET SUBJUGATOR.name: Scarlet Subjugator
SCARLET SUBJUGATOR.flavorText: At the Scarlet Monastery, he learned the sacred art of kicking people when they're up.

CHEATY ANKLEBITER.name: Cheaty Anklebiter
CHEATY ANKLEBITER.flavorText: Famed hunter of the deadly Achilliosaur.

RAVENOUS KRAKEN.name: Ravenous Kraken
RAVENOUS KRAKEN.flavorText: He's witewally hitting the squiddy wight now.

BLOWGILL SNIPER.name: Blowgill Sniper
BLOWGILL SNIPER.flavorText: Imagine how much further his darts would go if he had lungs instead of gills!

GRAVE SHAMBLER.name: Grave Shambler
GRAVE SHAMBLER.flavorText: I think one of the necromancers got a little carried away.

RESONANCE COIL.name: Resonance Coil
RESONANCE COIL.flavorText: This thing can snipe minions three screens away!

FIELD OF STRIFE.name: Field of Strife
FIELD OF STRIFE.flavorText: I heard it's lovely there around this time of year.

GRAND TOTEM EYS'OR.name: Grand Totem Eys'or
GRAND TOTEM EYS'OR.flavorText: Some say it can see straight into the soul of any who dare to read its flavor text...

SACRIFICIAL PACT.name: Sacrificial Pact
SACRIFICIAL PACT.flavorText: This is the reason that Demons never really become friends with Warlocks.

GAZLOWE.name: Gazlowe
GAZLOWE.flavorText: Gazlowe was voted "Most Likely to Explode" in high school.

MARSHSPAWN.name: Marshspawn
MARSHSPAWN.flavorText: Hopes to someday promote to Marshsqueen.

NORTHSHIRE CLERIC.name: Northshire Cleric
NORTHSHIRE CLERIC.flavorText: They help the downtrodden and distressed. Also they sell cookies.

INFESTED WATCHER.name: Infested Watcher
INFESTED WATCHER.flavorText: This is why you don't eat watermelon seeds.

SLEEP WITH THE FISHES.name: Sleep with the Fishes
SLEEP WITH THE FISHES.flavorText: If you're sleeping with the fishes, we highly suggest not bringing an electric blanket.

EMPEROR COBRA.name: Emperor Cobra
EMPEROR COBRA.flavorText: The Sholazar Basin is home to a lot of really horrible things. If you're going to visit, wear bug spray. And plate armor.

GOLDWING.name: Goldwing
GOLDWING.flavorText: This HAS to be worth more dust, right?

AWAKEN THE MAKERS.name: Awaken the Makers
AWAKEN THE MAKERS.flavorText: They keep hitting the Snooze button.

TAE'THELAN BLOODWATCHER.name: Tae'thelan Bloodwatcher
TAE'THELAN BLOODWATCHER.flavorText: He's a big fan of Control Death Knight live streams.

NAT PAGLE.name: Nat Pagle
NAT PAGLE.flavorText: Nat Pagle, Azeroth's premier fisherman! He invented the Auto-Angler 3000, the Extendo-Pole 3000, and the Lure-o-matic 2099 (still in testing).

DART THROW.name: Dart Throw
DART THROW.flavorText: Did you know: Hitting the same target twice is only for skilled players. This has been a 'Dart Fact'!

FENCING COACH.name: Fencing Coach
FENCING COACH.flavorText: Good fencers make good neighbors, right?

GRILLMASTER.name: Grillmaster
GRILLMASTER.flavorText: Do you want your steak well done, rare, or LEGENDARY?

ZUL'DRAK RITUALIST.name: Zul'Drak Ritualist
ZUL'DRAK RITUALIST.flavorText: Generosity is a core value in cult culture.

BANE OF DOOM.name: Bane of Doom
BANE OF DOOM.flavorText: My advice to you is to avoid Doom, if possible.

SWITCHEROO.name: Switcheroo
SWITCHEROO.flavorText: Would you rather fight one Whale-sized Goldfish, or 100 Goldfish-sized Whales?

CHUM BUCKET.name: Chum Bucket
CHUM BUCKET.flavorText: Time to go in for the krill.

PARROT SANCTUARY.name: Parrot Sanctuary
PARROT SANCTUARY.flavorText: Did you know? It's very loud in a parrot sanctuary. This has been bird facts with Ranger Gilly.

SILVER HAND KNIGHT.name: Silver Hand Knight
SILVER HAND KNIGHT.flavorText: It's good to be a knight. Less so to be one's squire.

JUNKBOT.name: Junkbot
JUNKBOT.flavorText: One bot's junk is another bot's AWESOME UPGRADE!

SHROOMSCAVATE.name: Shroomscavate
SHROOMSCAVATE.flavorText: As Globb shroominated on his situation, toiling endlessly in the mushroom mines, he came to the startling realization. His boss wasn't a very fun guy.

PENANCE.name: Penance
PENANCE.flavorText: This is what happens when you don’t give a sincere apology.

BITTERTIDE HYDRA.name: Bittertide Hydra
BITTERTIDE HYDRA.flavorText: It's actually only the middle head that's bitter. The others are sweet and spicy.

FEAST OF SOULS.name: Feast of Souls
FEAST OF SOULS.flavorText: Nothing fills you up like soul food!

JAR DEALER.name: Jar Dealer
JAR DEALER.flavorText: What's in the jar? It could be anyone!

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/72/VO_ULD_282_Male_Sethrak_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_ULD_282_Male_Sethrak_Play_01.wav Death is so profitable.

MANTLE SHAPER.name: Mantle Shaper
MANTLE SHAPER.flavorText: You got a fireplace? I've got a guy who shapes mantles.

THROUGH FEL AND FLAMES.name: Through Fel and Flames
THROUGH FEL AND FLAMES.flavorText: It's a Fel spell, but also a FIRE spell.

CATACOMB GUARD.name: Catacomb Guard
CATACOMB GUARD.flavorText: A little dark down here. So much for "serving the Light."

RUMBLETUSK SHAKER.name: Rumbletusk Shaker
RUMBLETUSK SHAKER.flavorText: Rub a dub dub, three trolls in a tub. And who do you think dey be? Da Shaker, Da Breaker, and Da Undatakah. And all of dem comin' for me.

TOXIC ARROW.name: Toxic Arrow
