TOXIC ARROW.flavorText: What doesn't kill you makes you toxic.

FROZEN SHADOWEAVER.name: Frozen Shadoweaver
FROZEN SHADOWEAVER.flavorText: She still wears her Frozen Shadoweave set despite the many, many nerfs. She just can't let it go!

GADGETZAN SOCIALITE.name: Gadgetzan Socialite
GADGETZAN SOCIALITE.flavorText: Comment on her height, and she'll go from flapper to kneecapper in seconds flat.

MAZE GUIDE.name: Maze Guide
MAZE GUIDE.flavorText: "And if you look to your left, you'll see an even larger statue of Sire Denathrius!"

MESSENGER RAVEN.name: Messenger Raven
MESSENGER RAVEN.flavorText: You can make a collect CAW!

ELVEN ARCHER.name: Elven Archer
ELVEN ARCHER.flavorText: Don't bother asking her out on a date. She'll shoot you down.

CLOCKWORK AUTOMATON.name: Clockwork Automaton
CLOCKWORK AUTOMATON.flavorText: Most mechs are pretty chill, but this one is all wound up.

WISPS OF THE OLD GODS.name: Wisps of the Old Gods
WISPS OF THE OLD GODS.flavorText: They're just normal wisps, actually. The "Of the Old Gods" bit is just marketing.

FROSTSABER MATRIARCH.name: Frostsaber Matriarch
FROSTSABER MATRIARCH.flavorText: They say “don’t poke the bear”, but they NEVER said “don’t poke the frostsaber or her cubs”.

MALYGOS, ASPECT OF MAGIC.name: Malygos, Aspect of Magic
MALYGOS, ASPECT OF MAGIC.flavorText: It's official. We can say Malygeese.

MOONBEAM.name: Moonbeam
MOONBEAM.flavorText: The light of the moon may have disappeared from Zin-Azshari after the Sundering, but not its power.

GRIMY GADGETEER.name: Grimy Gadgeteer
GRIMY GADGETEER.flavorText: "You look like a Gadgetgun 3000-Mark IV man, am I right?"

SMUG SENIOR.name: Smug Senior
SMUG SENIOR.flavorText: You want to see something funny? Go visit him in five years.

LADY IN WHITE.name: Lady in White
LADY IN WHITE.flavorText: She was a lady in polka dots until the gnomish laundromat incident.

FAN CLUB.name: Fan Club
FAN CLUB.flavorText: "Well that was weird. Yeah, I just walked up to the president of the fan club, he blabbered on for like 10 minutes, and then gave me a bike voucher..."

HYDRATION STATION.name: Hydration Station
HYDRATION STATION.flavorText: They're drinking in herds... they do drink in herds.

POWER WORD: SHIELD.name: Power Word: Shield
POWER WORD: SHIELD.flavorText: Sure the extra protection is nice, but the shield really reduces visibility.

FROST QUEEN SINDRAGOSA.name: Frost Queen Sindragosa
FROST QUEEN SINDRAGOSA.flavorText: With her final breath, Sindragosa cursed her consort and all who abandoned her to die in Icecrown. When she was reborn by the hands of the Lich King, her first freezing exhale wrought only pain.

MARK OF THE LOA.name: Mark of the Loa
MARK OF THE LOA.flavorText: Ah, yes. Mark. The mightiest Loa.

VOIDTOUCHED ATTENDANT.name: Voidtouched Attendant
VOIDTOUCHED ATTENDANT.flavorText: Don't TOUCH the Void. You don't know where it's been.

ODYN, PRIME DESIGNATE.name: Odyn, Prime Designate
ODYN, PRIME DESIGNATE.flavorText: The best offense is a good defense. 30 defense to be exact.

GROTESQUE RUNEBLADE.name: Grotesque Runeblade
GROTESQUE RUNEBLADE.flavorText: Frost confirmed to be the least gross rune.

MISSILE LAUNCHER.name: Missile Launcher
MISSILE LAUNCHER.flavorText: We asked, "Where do the missiles go?" and he answered, "Yes."

BADLANDS BRAWLER.name: Badlands Brawler
BADLANDS BRAWLER.flavorText: Watch out watch out watch out - R.K.O. outta nowhere!

THE VORAXX.name: The Voraxx
THE VORAXX.flavorText: I am the Voraxx. I speak for the weeds.

GORM THE WORLDEATER.name: Gorm the Worldeater
GORM THE WORLDEATER.flavorText: His diet consists of entire WORLDS! Because moons upset his tummy.

AZSHARAN TRIDENT.name: Azsharan Trident
AZSHARAN TRIDENT.flavorText: Nevermind the barnacles! A well-crafted weapon is eternally useful.

RALLYING BLADE.name: Rallying Blade
RALLYING BLADE.flavorText: As far as blades go, this one is pretty great in the motivation department.

BEATBOXER.name: Beatboxer
BEATBOXER.flavorText: "ERROR. CANNOT COMPUTE 'NO PUNCHING ALLOWED DURING MUSICAL PERFORMANCE'."

MISH-MASH MOSHER.name: Mish-Mash Mosher
MISH-MASH MOSHER.flavorText: In the pit, he feels more alive than ever.

OGRE-GANG OUTLAW.name: Ogre-Gang Outlaw
OGRE-GANG OUTLAW.flavorText: Why don't they just buy another hat?

REPENTANCE.name: Repentance
REPENTANCE.flavorText: Repentance often comes in the moment before obliteration. Curious.

RELIC VAULT.name: Relic Vault
RELIC VAULT.flavorText: Holds Sire Denathrius' most prized possession - his teddy bear, Jeremy Bearimy.

KNIFE VENDOR.name: Knife Vendor
KNIFE VENDOR.flavorText: "They're perfectly safe! These gloves totally aren't hiding any bandages."

ALGALON THE OBSERVER.name: Algalon the Observer
ALGALON THE OBSERVER.flavorText: That's so Algalon, it’s the future he can see.

DEATH ROLL.name: Death Roll
DEATH ROLL.flavorText: There's a Crocolisk on my boot!

CURSED CAMPAIGN.name: Cursed Campaign
CURSED CAMPAIGN.flavorText: Their group has been trying to schedule the next session since Kobolds and Catacombs came out.

IMP-LOSION.name: Imp-losion
IMP-LOSION.flavorText: The shrapnel is waaaaay worse than the explosion.

LEEROY JENKINS.name: Leeroy Jenkins
LEEROY JENKINS.flavorText: At least he has Angry Chicken.

SUL'THRAZE.name: Sul'thraze
SUL'THRAZE.flavorText: “Griftah here with de Sul’chop. One chop, you get four damage. Two chops, eight damage - you gonna change de way you fight."

AZSHARAN DEFECTOR.name: Azsharan Defector
AZSHARAN DEFECTOR.flavorText: "I've got a sinking feeling about this evil Queen."

UNIDENTIFIED ELIXIR.name: Unidentified Elixir
UNIDENTIFIED ELIXIR.flavorText: "Here, taste this." (Slurp) "What is it?" "I don't know, I found it in one of the labs."

BLASTMASTER BOOM.name: Blastmaster Boom
BLASTMASTER BOOM.flavorText: He's gonna fly through the air with the greatest of grease.

FELGUARD.name: Felguard
FELGUARD.flavorText: Yes, he'll fight for you. BUT HE'S NOT GOING TO LIKE IT.

EVASIVE CHIMAERA.name: Evasive Chimaera
EVASIVE CHIMAERA.flavorText: One head only tells the truth, while the other head only tells lies. But they both spit poison.

CONCUSSIVE SHELLS.name: Concussive Shells
CONCUSSIVE SHELLS.flavorText: Zerg patients rated these a solid 7 on the pain chart.

MAGIC CARPET.name: Magic Carpet
MAGIC CARPET.flavorText: Its small yet fierce riders are affectionately known as rug rats.

ROWDY FAN.name: Rowdy Fan
ROWDY FAN.flavorText: "This song is so good, it makes me want to PUNCH SOMEONE IN THE FACE!!"

EGGNAPPER.name: Eggnapper
EGGNAPPER.flavorText: Often misunderstood, it's just that he likes to use the eggs as pillows.

GASLIGHT GATEKEEPER.name: Gaslight Gatekeeper
GASLIGHT GATEKEEPER.flavorText: This girl is such a boss.

PEACEFUL PIPER.name: Peaceful Piper
PEACEFUL PIPER.flavorText: "Is there anything worth more than peace and love on the planet Azeroth?"

ICE BREAKER.name: Ice Breaker
ICE BREAKER.flavorText: A great way to end a conversation.

PLAGUESPREADER.name: Plaguespreader
PLAGUESPREADER.flavorText: What do they mean by Patient Zero? I'm very patient!

DARNASSUS ASPIRANT.name: Darnassus Aspirant
DARNASSUS ASPIRANT.flavorText: She loves mana crystals, she hates mana crystals. So fickle!

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/eb/VO_AT_038_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_038_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/78/VO_AT_038_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_038_ATTACK_02.wav For Elune.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/9/97/VO_AT_038_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_038_DEATH_04.wav <death sound>

ALLIANCE BANNERMAN.name: Alliance Bannerman
ALLIANCE BANNERMAN.flavorText: Back in my day, we had to carry our inspiration uphill both ways to war.

HEAT WAVE.name: Heat Wave
HEAT WAVE.flavorText: This is the hottest summer of your life so far.

GLADIATOR'S LONGBOW.name: Gladiator's Longbow
GLADIATOR'S LONGBOW.flavorText: The longbow allows shots to be fired from farther away and is useful for firing on particularly odorous targets.

REDSCALE DRAGONTAMER.name: Redscale Dragontamer
REDSCALE DRAGONTAMER.flavorText: Sir Finley made this look a lot easier three expansions ago...

HAND OF PROTECTION.name: Hand of Protection
HAND OF PROTECTION.flavorText: This spell has been renamed so many times, even paladins don’t know what it should be called anymore.

BANJOSAUR.name: Banjosaur
BANJOSAUR.flavorText: You'll all be singing along once he gets to the tyranno-chorus.

HOLY SMITE.name: Holy Smite
HOLY SMITE.flavorText: It doesn't matter how pious you are. Everyone needs a good smiting now and again.

FELFIRE IN THE HOLE!.name: Felfire in the Hole!
FELFIRE IN THE HOLE!.flavorText: Fear not, feebleminded friends, for failure to fell your foes with felfire is fundamentally farfetched!

REHYDRATE.name: Rehydrate
REHYDRATE.flavorText: Just doing our part as the Hearthstone development team in reminding you to drink more water!

PRINCE KELESETH.name: Prince Keleseth
PRINCE KELESETH.flavorText: Three Princes stand before you. This one wants to buff his brothers.

GADGETZAN AUCTIONEER.name: Gadgetzan Auctioneer
GADGETZAN AUCTIONEER.flavorText: He used to run the black market auction house, but there was just too much violence and he had to move.

GLITTER MOTH.name: Glitter Moth
GLITTER MOTH.flavorText: Some moths are attracted to flame. This one's attracted to disco.

TWIG OF THE WORLD TREE.name: Twig of the World Tree
TWIG OF THE WORLD TREE.flavorText: For druids who want to branch out.

NIGHTSHADE BUD.name: Nightshade Bud
NIGHTSHADE BUD.flavorText: It actually thrives in partial sunlight.

ELISE THE TRAILBLAZER.name: Elise the Trailblazer
ELISE THE TRAILBLAZER.flavorText: Reno taught her that blazing her own trail is a lot more fun than following someone else's map.

CHILLBLADE CHAMPION.name: Chillblade Champion
CHILLBLADE CHAMPION.flavorText: It slices, it dices, it vaporizes! The Chillblade will make a Champion out of even the lowliest gnome.

JOTUN, THE ETERNAL.name: Jotun, the Eternal
JOTUN, THE ETERNAL.flavorText: He doesn't look like a turtle?

BAYFIN BODYBUILDER.name: Bayfin Bodybuilder
BAYFIN BODYBUILDER.flavorText: Loves to run in flow motion.

GLOWSTONE TECHNICIAN.name: Glowstone Technician
GLOWSTONE TECHNICIAN.flavorText: "Windell! More light!" "I'm givin' it all she's got, Kangor!"

FELSTEEL EXECUTIONER.name: Felsteel Executioner
FELSTEEL EXECUTIONER.flavorText: "My mom said I could be anything I want."

STREETWISE INVESTIGATOR.name: Streetwise Investigator
STREETWISE INVESTIGATOR.flavorText: "Hmmmm… Call it a hunch, but I'm starting to think that there may be some kind of criminal activity going on in Gadgetzan."

RAVAGING GHOUL.name: Ravaging Ghoul
RAVAGING GHOUL.flavorText: But goes by "Ravishing Ghoul" when he hits the club.

TOL'VIR WARDEN.name: Tol'vir Warden
TOL'VIR WARDEN.flavorText: Ferocious in combat… and even more terrifying in pet battles.

TESTING DUMMY.name: Testing Dummy
TESTING DUMMY.flavorText: Don't worry, they're having a blast. MUAHAHAHAHAAAA!

WING WELDING.name: Wing Welding
WING WELDING.flavorText: This is not how you train your dragon.

MINOTAUREN.name: Minotauren
MINOTAUREN.flavorText: "Why's he so mad?" "He's been stuck on one of Hearthstone's hidden maze puzzles for YEARS."

HELMET HERMIT.name: Helmet Hermit
HELMET HERMIT.flavorText: I’d avoid asking if it wants to join the battle. It’s been pretty crabby lately.

WHIRLPOOL.name: Whirlpool
WHIRLPOOL.flavorText: In the southern hemisphere, it actually summons all minions instead.

DEATH METAL KNIGHT.name: Death Metal Knight
DEATH METAL KNIGHT.flavorText: He prefers listening to bands dead rather than live.

PAINTER'S VIRTUE.name: Painter's Virtue
PAINTER'S VIRTUE.flavorText: For when the Light hits the painting at a certain angle.

TEMPLAR CAPTAIN.name: Templar Captain
TEMPLAR CAPTAIN.flavorText: You can combine two of these into a Captain Archon.

LIFESAVING AURA.name: Lifesaving Aura
LIFESAVING AURA.flavorText: One ring to rule them all, and in the sunlight save them.

CARRESS, CABARET STAR.name: Carress, Cabaret Star
CARRESS, CABARET STAR.flavorText: Some Naga use their mastery over the elements to go on villainous conquests. Others put on a show!

BARITONE IMP.name: Baritone Imp
BARITONE IMP.flavorText: He used to be an epic sax guy, but now he's just a common.

EMERALD REAVER.name: Emerald Reaver
EMERALD REAVER.flavorText: Not to be confused with clubbing enthusiast Emerald Raver.

SNOWBALL FIGHT!.name: Snowball Fight!
SNOWBALL FIGHT!.flavorText: Woahwoahwoah, we said no friendly fire!

EXPIRED MERCHANT.name: Expired Merchant
EXPIRED MERCHANT.flavorText: The "best by" date is more like a guideline.

PRISON BREAKER.name: Prison Breaker
PRISON BREAKER.flavorText: Flavor fail! Demolition Renovator did it FIRST!

STORMHAMMER.name: Stormhammer
STORMHAMMER.flavorText: It brings the storm before the calm.

BLADEMASTER OKANI.name: Blademaster Okani
BLADEMASTER OKANI.flavorText: Yet ANOTHER sword fighter that spams counters.

SHOPLIFTER GOLDBEARD.name: Shoplifter Goldbeard
SHOPLIFTER GOLDBEARD.flavorText: "Arr, this plunder be great for Cap'n Fourteeth's baby shower!"

MANA WRAITH.name: Mana Wraith
MANA WRAITH.flavorText: They come out at night to eat leftover mana crystals. "Mmmmmm," they say.

SMUGGLER'S RUN.name: Smuggler's Run
SMUGGLER'S RUN.flavorText: One of the most famous busts in Gadgetzan’s history happened on Smuggler’s Run, where Sergeant Sally apprehended a cadre of Grimy Goons transporting a massive number of illegal fish heads.

THICKHIDE KODO.name: Thickhide Kodo
THICKHIDE KODO.flavorText: The introduction of professions was devastating for kodo populations.

SIMULACRUM.name: Simulacrum
SIMULACRUM.flavorText: It's like déjà vu, times two.

TUSKARR FISHERMAN.name: Tuskarr Fisherman
TUSKARR FISHERMAN.flavorText: If you bring him 500 fish, he'll give you this sweet Kalu'ak Fishing Pole.

YOGG-SARON, HOPE'S END.name: Yogg-Saron, Hope's End
YOGG-SARON, HOPE'S END.flavorText: I spell your doom... Y-O-U-R D-O-O-M!

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/dd/VO_OG_134_Male_OldGod_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_OG_134_Male_OldGod_Play_01.wav Bow down before the God of Death.

HIGH CULTIST BASALEPH.name: High Cultist Basaleph
HIGH CULTIST BASALEPH.flavorText: "It's not a cult! It's a collection of like-minded individuals that enjoy undead. And rituals. And doing what I say. "

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/62/VO_RLK_832_Male_Undead_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_RLK_832_Male_Undead_Play_01.wav Death will not be a mercy for you.

PIT SNAKE.name: Pit Snake
PIT SNAKE.flavorText: It could be worse. It could be a Snake Pit.

DRYSCALE DEPUTY.name: Dryscale Deputy
DRYSCALE DEPUTY.flavorText: He's here to tip the scales in our favor… and moisturize them too.

GLACIER RACER.name: Glacier Racer
GLACIER RACER.flavorText: It’s just not the same without a super suit.

PARAGON OF LIGHT.name: Paragon of Light
PARAGON OF LIGHT.flavorText: She’s all fun and games until someone rings that stupid bell.

SHRINKMEISTER.name: Shrinkmeister
SHRINKMEISTER.flavorText: After the debacle of the Gnomish World Enlarger, gnomes are wary of size-changing inventions.

WALKING FOUNTAIN.name: Walking Fountain
WALKING FOUNTAIN.flavorText: The weirdest part is that it doesn't have legs.

ZOOBOT.name: Zoobot
ZOOBOT.flavorText: The Murloc is taking the picture.

ARMOR VENDOR.name: Armor Vendor
ARMOR VENDOR.flavorText: "You look like the kind of person that would buy three sets of armor. One to wear, a spare, and a spare for the spare."

REEFWALKER.name: Reefwalker
REEFWALKER.flavorText: A gentle giant with some not-so-gentle friends.

CRYPT KEEPER.name: Crypt Keeper
CRYPT KEEPER.flavorText: How many crypts could a Crypt Keeper keep if a Crypt Keeper could keep crypts?

PRIDE SEEKER.name: Pride Seeker
PRIDE SEEKER.flavorText: When you're putting your head in the lion's mouth, you may as well dress the part.

NOSTALGIC CLOWN.name: Nostalgic Clown
NOSTALGIC CLOWN.flavorText: He used to be kind of corrupt, but now he performs purely for the fun of it.

CRIMINAL LINEUP.name: Criminal Lineup
CRIMINAL LINEUP.flavorText: Number 1, could you please sing the opening to "I Want It That Way"?

FROST LICH CROSS-STITCH.name: Frost Lich Cross-Stitch
FROST LICH CROSS-STITCH.flavorText: Do not fear power... Fear those who SEW IT!

GLOW-TRON.name: Glow-Tron
GLOW-TRON.flavorText: They tried for weeks to make a stealth version, but eventually decided to just let it glow.

FORGE OF WILLS.name: Forge of Wills
FORGE OF WILLS.flavorText: Standing in the Forge of Wills fills you with a sense of DETERMINATION.

SMUGGLER'S CRATE.name: Smuggler's Crate
SMUGGLER'S CRATE.flavorText: Are you sure these are the crates that are supposed to go to the Gadgetzan petting zoo?

BABBLING BOOK.name: Babbling Book
BABBLING BOOK.flavorText: His idol is the Green Hills of Stranglethorn, and he won't shut up about it.

BOOGIE DOWN.name: Boogie Down
BOOGIE DOWN.flavorText: Whatever you do, do NOT sashay to the right.

CORRUPT THE WATERS.name: Corrupt the Waters
CORRUPT THE WATERS.flavorText: This is why Hagatha is banned from public pools.

SANDBOX SCOUNDREL.name: Sandbox Scoundrel
SANDBOX SCOUNDREL.flavorText: "Really? A bunch of fake plastic gems AGAIN!?"

GRUMBLE, WORLDSHAKER.name: Grumble, Worldshaker
GRUMBLE, WORLDSHAKER.flavorText: The grumbling grew to a mighty rumbling, and out of the caverns the kobolds came tumbling.

TAINTED REMNANT.name: Tainted Remnant
TAINTED REMNANT.flavorText: A sore sight of eyesores for sore eyes.

INJURED BLADEMASTER.name: Injured Blademaster
INJURED BLADEMASTER.flavorText: He claims it is an old war wound, but we think he just cut himself shaving.

WITCHING HOUR.name: Witching Hour
WITCHING HOUR.flavorText: The gates to the Gilnean pet cemetary MUST remain locked at all times.

CONCEAL.name: Conceal
CONCEAL.flavorText: Rogues conceal everything but their emotions. You can't get 'em to shut up about feelings.

TSUNAMI.name: Tsunami
TSUNAMI.flavorText: Hop in, the water's cold! And angry. And alive.

TOXIC REINFORCEMENTS.name: Toxic Reinforcements
TOXIC REINFORCEMENTS.flavorText: In the event of a sudden loss of cabin pressure, a slingshot will be deployed for convenient evacuation.

CHARGED CALL.name: Charged Call
CHARGED CALL.flavorText: You have a collect call from "AL'AKIR, LORD OF AIR AND THE FOUR WINDS." Do you accept these charges?

WEAPONIZED PI\u00d1ATA.name: Weaponized Piñata
WEAPONIZED PI\u00d1ATA.flavorText: It'll be fine. It's not like they have any reason to hate us.

CHROMIE, TIMEHOPPER.name: Chromie, Timehopper
CHROMIE, TIMEHOPPER.flavorText: "Noz, you're telling me you built a time machine...out of a Hearthstone card?"

JINYU WATERSPEAKER.name: Jinyu Waterspeaker
JINYU WATERSPEAKER.flavorText: Waterspeakers can tell the future! So the Jade Lotus employs them to speculate on the Auction House.

MOONGLADE PORTAL.name: Moonglade Portal
MOONGLADE PORTAL.flavorText: Ain't no party like a Moonglade party ‘cause a Moonglade party got bears.

CORRIDOR CREEPER.name: Corridor Creeper
CORRIDOR CREEPER.flavorText: It likes the smell of dead things, which is curious, as it has no visible nose.

FLYING MACHINE.name: Flying Machine
FLYING MACHINE.flavorText: To operate, this contraption needs a hula doll on the dashboard. Otherwise it's just a “falling machine.”

BLOWTORCH SABOTEUR.name: Blowtorch Saboteur
BLOWTORCH SABOTEUR.flavorText: Before he came along, we went through a lot of duct tape.

BIRDWATCHING.name: Birdwatching
BIRDWATCHING.flavorText: A bird in the hand is worth two in the deck.

THUNDER BLUFF VALIANT.name: Thunder Bluff Valiant
THUNDER BLUFF VALIANT.flavorText: Allowing totems to attack is not cheating. I mean, there isn't anything in the rule books about it.

RESPLENDENT DREAMWEAVER.name: Resplendent Dreamweaver
RESPLENDENT DREAMWEAVER.flavorText: Have you ever had a dream that that you um you had you'd you would you could you'd do you wi you wants you you could do so you you'd do you could you you want so much you could do anything?

HEART OF THE WILD.name: Heart of the Wild
HEART OF THE WILD.flavorText: In each of us beats a wild heart. Except the Forsaken.

STARLIGHT GROOVE.name: Starlight Groove
STARLIGHT GROOVE.flavorText: In space, no one can hear you groove.

BIG DREAMS.name: Big Dreams
BIG DREAMS.flavorText: Just a small town Taunka Livin' in a lonely... waunka

SHADESTONE SKULKER.name: Shadestone Skulker
SHADESTONE SKULKER.flavorText: Sharing is caring - and they don't care.

DARK WISPERS.name: Dark Wispers
DARK WISPERS.flavorText: Don't worry; we fired the person who named this card.

GUARDIAN AUGMERCHANT.name: Guardian Augmerchant
GUARDIAN AUGMERCHANT.flavorText: "What doesn't kill you makes me money!"

FIRE SALE.name: Fire Sale
FIRE SALE.flavorText: Everything is 50% off now that our warehouse burned down.

BANDERSMOSH.name: Bandersmosh
BANDERSMOSH.flavorText: The Shudderwock finds him particularly frumious.

RUNIC EGG.name: Runic Egg
RUNIC EGG.flavorText: Oh man! Runic omelettes are the best!

SI:7 INFILTRATOR.name: SI:7 Infiltrator
SI:7 INFILTRATOR.flavorText: What will she destroy? It’s a secret!

VOLUME UP.name: Volume Up
VOLUME UP.flavorText: You have to pay Mana to do that!? I thought it was just in the settings menu!

KOBOLD BARBARIAN.name: Kobold Barbarian
KOBOLD BARBARIAN.flavorText: What is best in life? To make candle. To keep candle. To hear lamentations of candle-takers.

POSSESSED VILLAGER.name: Possessed Villager
POSSESSED VILLAGER.flavorText: It's like a pinata! A lame disgusting horrific pinata.

KAZAKUS.name: Kazakus
KAZAKUS.flavorText: The mysterious leader of the Kabal is NOT a dragon, and does NOT deal in illegal potions. Any public statements to the contrary will be met with litigation and Dragonfire Potions.

RIGHTEOUS DEFENSE.name: Righteous Defense
RIGHTEOUS DEFENSE.flavorText: Paladins... Always stealing someone else’s thunder. And stats.

FORGE OF SOULS.name: Forge of Souls
FORGE OF SOULS.flavorText: Powerful weaponry forged by Bronjahm, the Godfather of Souls.

PRIMALFIN CHAMPION.name: Primalfin Champion
PRIMALFIN CHAMPION.flavorText: Sure, he'll return your stuff. OVER HIS DEAD BODY!

OVERLORD'S WHIP.name: Overlord's Whip
OVERLORD'S WHIP.flavorText: "This merit badge is for cruelty. This one's for whipping. And this one is for embroidery..."

RANSACK.name: Ransack
RANSACK.flavorText: "Fred's a talking ghoul. He can do whatever he wants." "I want to steal!"

LUCKY COMET.name: Lucky Comet
LUCKY COMET.flavorText: When you wish upon a star, your dreams will take you very far. When you wish upon a comet, your luck will make your opponent...

REMOTE-CONTROLLED GOLEM.name: Remote-Controlled Golem
REMOTE-CONTROLLED GOLEM.flavorText: Someone got a little too excited inventing a can opener.

LESSER RUBY SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Ruby Spellstone
LESSER RUBY SPELLSTONE.flavorText: The final stone undid its master Spun into wards by nameless caster Azari wailed a savage roar Now sealed in nether, evermore.

DRAENEI TOTEMCARVER.name: Draenei Totemcarver
DRAENEI TOTEMCARVER.flavorText: It's nice to find a real craftsman in this day and age of mass-produced totems.

SIR FINLEY, THE INTREPID.name: Sir Finley, the Intrepid
SIR FINLEY, THE INTREPID.flavorText: And exactly how does Finley turn everyone into a murloc?

CHROMATIC EGG.name: Chromatic Egg
CHROMATIC EGG.flavorText: Nefarian was known for creating two things: horrible monsters and excellent breakfasts.

HAND OF GUL'DAN.name: Hand of Gul'dan
HAND OF GUL'DAN.flavorText: His skull also draws three cards. Imagine how many cards he could draw with HIS ENTIRE BODY!

SUNSET VOLLEY.name: Sunset Volley
SUNSET VOLLEY.flavorText: When the light is just right during Golden Hour, that is when you take out the selfie stick and start casting.

KEEPER OF THE GROVE.name: Keeper of the Grove
KEEPER OF THE GROVE.flavorText: These guys just show up and start Keeping your Groves without even asking.

HOGGER.name: Hogger
HOGGER.flavorText: Hogger is super powerful. If you kill him, it's because he let you.

ICE BLOCK.name: Ice Block
ICE BLOCK.flavorText: Ice is nice, and will suffice!

SUSPICIOUS USHER.name: Suspicious Usher
SUSPICIOUS USHER.flavorText: "Oh please, let me take your jacket, luggage, and absurdly large shoulder pads."

DOZING KELPKEEPER.name: Dozing Kelpkeeper
DOZING KELPKEEPER.flavorText: *Yaaaaawn* wake me up in another 5 Mana.

FLIGHTMASTER DUNGAR.name: Flightmaster Dungar
FLIGHTMASTER DUNGAR.flavorText: Flight’s a little bumpy, but there’s plenty of legroom.

voicelines.attack:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/27/VO_SW_079_Male_Human_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_SW_079_Male_Human_Play_01.wav What adventure are you off to today?
  • ▶️ HS_LegendaryStinger_FlightMasterDungar.wav <music stinger>

LIL' EXORCIST.name: Lil' Exorcist
LIL' EXORCIST.flavorText: Warlocks have the town exorcist on speed dial in case they unleash the wrong demon.

LAB PATRON.name: Lab Patron
LAB PATRON.flavorText: When a Lab Patron fails out of school, they become a Grim Patron.

DEMONFUSE.name: Demonfuse
DEMONFUSE.flavorText: Very dangerous when attached to a demonbomb.

STRANGLETHORN TIGER.name: Stranglethorn Tiger
STRANGLETHORN TIGER.flavorText: The wonderful thing about tigers is tigers are wonderful things!

DUST DEVIL.name: Dust Devil
DUST DEVIL.flavorText: Westfall is full of dust devils. And buzzards. And crazed golems. And pirates. Why does anyone live here?

TROLL CENTURION.name: Troll Centurion
TROLL CENTURION.flavorText: Centurion? Ha, come back when you’re a millennion.

WINDSPEAKER.name: Windspeaker
WINDSPEAKER.flavorText: Is there anything worse than a Windspeaker with halitosis?

TOPPLE THE IDOL.name: Topple the Idol
TOPPLE THE IDOL.flavorText: No Old Gods or Kings, only Naga.

TONY, KING OF PIRACY.name: Tony, King of Piracy
TONY, KING OF PIRACY.flavorText: Tony prefers sailing on torrents rather than streams.

ORIGAMI CRANE.name: Origami Crane
ORIGAMI CRANE.flavorText: I was born with 1-Health and paper skin.

COWARDLY GRUNT.name: Cowardly Grunt
COWARDLY GRUNT.flavorText: Cowardice is the wisest part of valor.

BLINK FOX.name: Blink Fox
BLINK FOX.flavorText: It's like, SUPER bad at staring contests.

FRIENDLY BARTENDER.name: Friendly Bartender
FRIENDLY BARTENDER.flavorText: "What'll it be? A Jade Brew? A Grimy Goose? A Kabal Manatini?"

TICKET SCALPER.name: Ticket Scalper
TICKET SCALPER.flavorText: Takes ten percent off the top.

FROZEN OVER.name: Frozen Over
FROZEN OVER.flavorText: We will find out who wins when we return in the spring.

PLAYHOUSE GIANT.name: Playhouse Giant
PLAYHOUSE GIANT.flavorText: WARNING: NOT A PLAYHOUSE. DO NOT ATTEMPT TO CLIMB.

REMIXED RHAPSODY.name: Remixed Rhapsody
REMIXED RHAPSODY.flavorText: "Is this real life?" "No, this is a card game."

PUBLIC DEFENDER.name: Public Defender
PUBLIC DEFENDER.flavorText: Happy to defend any public offender!

THE SUNWELL.name: The Sunwell
THE SUNWELL.flavorText: The Lich King had extinguished the light of the Sunwell once before - it will take all the might Silvermoon can muster to defend it!

LIGHTSPAWN.name: Lightspawn
LIGHTSPAWN.flavorText: Spawn of the Light? Or Pawn of the Lights?

GONE FISHIN'.name: Gone Fishin'
GONE FISHIN'.flavorText: Rogues want me Fish fear me

PILOTED REAPER.name: Piloted Reaper
PILOTED REAPER.flavorText: New facial recognition systems keep out the Lorewalkers and Doomsayers.

SUMMONING PORTAL.name: Summoning Portal
SUMMONING PORTAL.flavorText: NOT LESS THAN 1! Don't get any ideas!

PRIMORDIAL GLYPH.name: Primordial Glyph
PRIMORDIAL GLYPH.flavorText: It's the Ancient Tol'vir symbol for "Whoops!"

QUICKSAND ELEMENTAL.name: Quicksand Elemental
QUICKSAND ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Use a light abrasive to buff blemishes away but use a heavy abrasive to debuff problems.

DRAGONMAW SENTINEL.name: Dragonmaw Sentinel
DRAGONMAW SENTINEL.flavorText: On the side, she's training for the annual Dragonmaw hammer throw tournament.

AZALINA SOULTHIEF.name: Azalina Soulthief
AZALINA SOULTHIEF.flavorText: The cards are always golden on the other side.

CENARIUS.name: Cenarius
CENARIUS.flavorText: Yes, he's a demigod. No, he doesn't need to wear a shirt.

RAINBOW SEAMSTRESS.name: Rainbow Seamstress
RAINBOW SEAMSTRESS.flavorText: Is this card any good? It would seam sew.

SPYMISTRESS.name: Spymistress
SPYMISTRESS.flavorText: Spies in Outland must blend into the environment. That means hot-pink gear and bright green hair. It’s a weird place.

STARSHOOTER.name: Starshooter
STARSHOOTER.flavorText: Shoot for the stars! And if you miss, just don't hit me.

UMBERWING.name: Umberwing
UMBERWING.flavorText: Demon Hunters refer to these glaives as "the ol’ flappy-attackys."

BOULDERING BUDDY.name: Bouldering Buddy
BOULDERING BUDDY.flavorText: Why would you buy a walking stick when the forest is full of them!?

CARRIER.name: Carrier
CARRIER.flavorText: Yeah, my teammates always call me this.

GROTESQUE DRAGONHAWK.name: Grotesque Dragonhawk
GROTESQUE DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: They say that "grotesque is in the eye of the beholder," but that's just because they've never seen a Grotesque Dragonhawk. Yikes!

CONVOKE THE SPIRITS.name: Convoke the Spirits
CONVOKE THE SPIRITS.flavorText: The spirits prefer to convoke when there's some hot gossip to discuss.

TOMB SPIDER.name: Tomb Spider
TOMB SPIDER.flavorText: Less serious than its cousin, the Grave Spider.

PRIMALFIN LOOKOUT.name: Primalfin Lookout
PRIMALFIN LOOKOUT.flavorText: Lookout is a self-appointed title that's mostly an excuse to beat things up.

STRANDED SPACEMAN.name: Stranded Spaceman
STRANDED SPACEMAN.flavorText: Would you say you're floating in a most peculiar way?

SAFETY EXPERT.name: Safety Expert
SAFETY EXPERT.flavorText: Remember: Always wear your helmet when strapped to a bajillion explosives.

RAZA THE CHAINED.name: Raza the Chained
RAZA THE CHAINED.flavorText: "Could you do me a favor and get the keys from Kazakus?"

PET PARROT.name: Pet Parrot
PET PARROT.flavorText: You are REQUIRED to give it crackers. It's the Bird Law.

EMERALD SKYTALON.name: Emerald Skytalon
EMERALD SKYTALON.flavorText: Sworn protectors of Ysera at the Emerald Dragonshrine, these majestic owls have been touched by the powers of the Emerald Dream, taking on an almost crystalline appearance.

DRAIN SOUL.name: Drain Soul
DRAIN SOUL.flavorText: Cleans even the toughest clogs with just a flick of the wrist!

JIVE, INSECT!.name: JIVE, INSECT!
JIVE, INSECT!.flavorText: "WHY IS NO ONE JIVING? I SPECIFICALLY REQUESTED IT!"

RATS OF EXTRAORDINARY SIZE.name: Rats of Extraordinary Size
RATS OF EXTRAORDINARY SIZE.flavorText: They don't care if you believe they exist.

DIVINE STAR.name: Divine Star
DIVINE STAR.flavorText: I could really use a wish right now.

MURKWATER SCRIBE.name: Murkwater Scribe
MURKWATER SCRIBE.flavorText: The pen is mightier than the trident.

SUNSAPPER LYNESSA.name: Sunsapper Lynessa
SUNSAPPER LYNESSA.flavorText: Paladins are sooo lawful that they start feeling like a Rogue just by sitting on someone else's beach chair.

EVIL QUARTERMASTER.name: EVIL Quartermaster
EVIL QUARTERMASTER.flavorText: He trained for a whole year to become quarter-master. Three more, and he'll be a full-master.

KELI'DAN THE BREAKER.name: Keli'dan the Breaker
KELI'DAN THE BREAKER.flavorText: He calms down a lot if you just give him a turn.

V-07-TR-0N PRIME.name: V-07-TR-0N Prime
V-07-TR-0N PRIME.flavorText: Long after the titans' departure, Mimiron dreamed of creating something with an approximation of their power. He may have actually succeeded!

HOPE OF QUEL'THALAS.name: Hope of Quel'Thalas
HOPE OF QUEL'THALAS.flavorText: Hey, give me a minute. I just need to load my.... uh, hope.

WITCHWOOD GRIZZLY.name: Witchwood Grizzly
WITCHWOOD GRIZZLY.flavorText: You know what they say about people with big hands? Small bears.

METEOROLOGIST.name: Meteorologist
METEOROLOGIST.flavorText: Some say the world will end in fire. Some say in ice. Why not BOTH?

VRYGHOUL.name: Vryghoul
VRYGHOUL.flavorText: It's pronounced VERY GHOUL. Don't let anyone tell you different.

ROTTING NECROMANCER.name: Rotting Necromancer
ROTTING NECROMANCER.flavorText: You can't spell dredge without D-E-D.

CLAW.name: Claw
CLAW.flavorText: The claw decides who will stay and who will go.

FLIK SKYSHIV.name: Flik Skyshiv
FLIK SKYSHIV.flavorText: Junior explorers scan the night sky in fear of her candle’s flame!

FACELESS CORRUPTOR.name: Faceless Corruptor
FACELESS CORRUPTOR.flavorText: What does Madame Lazul have against faces?!

PRIMORDIAL EXPLORER.name: Primordial Explorer
PRIMORDIAL EXPLORER.flavorText: "We're letting the poisonous dude carry the bags?"

PROSPECTOR'S CARAVAN.name: Prospector's Caravan
PROSPECTOR'S CARAVAN.flavorText: Prospectors came from all around in the Golden Legendary Rush of '49.

QUEENSGUARD.name: Queensguard
QUEENSGUARD.flavorText: Archnemesis of the Guardian of Kings.

ARCHSPORE MSSHI'FN.name: Archspore Msshi'fn
ARCHSPORE MSSHI'FN.flavorText: Brave leader of the Sporeggar. Guided by the philosophy that one should not mssh with matters that are not one's msshiness.

VULPERA TOXINBLADE.name: Vulpera Toxinblade
VULPERA TOXINBLADE.flavorText: The blade works well enough on its own… but this is just in case.

RUNE DAGGER.name: Rune Dagger
RUNE DAGGER.flavorText: Turns out being stabbed makes you more vulnerable to magic.

LI'NA, SHOP MANAGER.name: Li'Na, Shop Manager
LI'NA, SHOP MANAGER.flavorText: Somebody has to do the paperwork around here.

POWER CHORD: SYNCHRONIZE.name: Power Chord: Synchronize
POWER CHORD: SYNCHRONIZE.flavorText: "It's all about you, girl On your 16,000th birthday"

COOL GHOUL.name: Cool Ghoul
COOL GHOUL.flavorText: He has disco fever! :D Because of the disco plague. :(

DRUM CIRCLE.name: Drum Circle
DRUM CIRCLE.flavorText: It's more of a drum pentagon, really.

SHIP'S CANNON.name: Ship's Cannon
SHIP'S CANNON.flavorText: If you hear someone yell, "Cannonball!" you're about to get wet. Or crushed.

MARK OF THE SPIKESHELL.name: Mark of the Spikeshell
MARK OF THE SPIKESHELL.flavorText: "I'm DEFINITELY turtle-y enough for the turtle club."

MOLTEN GIANT.name: Molten Giant
MOLTEN GIANT.flavorText: He gets terrible heartburn. BECAUSE HE IS FULL OF LAVA.

DR. MORRIGAN.name: Dr. Morrigan
DR. MORRIGAN.flavorText: She will NOT STOP until she gets tenure.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/2a/VO_BOT_433_Female_Banshee_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BOT_433_Female_Banshee_Play_01.wav Death is just the beginning.

RELIQUARY SEEKER.name: Reliquary Seeker
RELIQUARY SEEKER.flavorText: The Reliquary considers itself the equal of the League of Explorers. The League of Explorers doesn't.

RHYTHMDANCER RISA.name: Rhythmdancer Risa
RHYTHMDANCER RISA.flavorText: Shadowstep to the left! Double jump to the right! Class cross!

INNER RAGE.name: Inner Rage
INNER RAGE.flavorText: They're only smiling on the outside.

SHRINK RAY.name: Shrink Ray
SHRINK RAY.flavorText: Actually works by enlarging the rest of the world.

MORTAL COIL.name: Mortal Coil
MORTAL COIL.flavorText: If your spells look like horrifying skulls, let's be honest, you should get to draw some cards.

DJINNI OF ZEPHYRS.name: Djinni of Zephyrs
DJINNI OF ZEPHYRS.flavorText: If you want your wish granted, don't rub him the wrong way.

BAD LUCK ALBATROSS.name: Bad Luck Albatross
BAD LUCK ALBATROSS.flavorText: Legend holds that it's bad luck to harm it. So maybe just pat it on the head, okay?

WAVE OF NOSTALGIA.name: Wave of Nostalgia
WAVE OF NOSTALGIA.flavorText: Ja, please don't freeze my minions. No stall, ja????

SHIVERING SORCERESS.name: Shivering Sorceress
SHIVERING SORCERESS.flavorText: Remember to use your sick days wisely.

ON THE HUNT.name: On the Hunt
ON THE HUNT.flavorText: The mastiff giggles if you don't hit any ducks.

TORRENT.name: Torrent
TORRENT.flavorText: Weeks of underwater cross-training have really built up her fourarms.

HOLY GLOWSTICKS.name: Holy Glowsticks
HOLY GLOWSTICKS.flavorText: Somewhere there's a Naaru missing a couple of shards.

RENO THE RELICOLOGIST.name: Reno the Relicologist
RENO THE RELICOLOGIST.flavorText: All his life, Reno Jackson was only a gatling wand away from becoming the greatest and most terrifying mage who ever existed.

HARTH STONEBREW.name: Harth Stonebrew
HARTH STONEBREW.flavorText: "Grab a slice by the hearth and enjoy the festivities. This celebration is for all of us!" -Harth

NIGHTMARE FUEL.name: Nightmare Fuel
NIGHTMARE FUEL.flavorText: Every instance of "but not less than (1)" has been replaced with "but not more than (1)."

CAMOUFLAGED DIRIGIBLE.name: Camouflaged Dirigible
CAMOUFLAGED DIRIGIBLE.flavorText: "What does that cloud look like to you?" "Trouble."

DARKBISHOP BENEDICTUS.name: Darkbishop Benedictus
DARKBISHOP BENEDICTUS.flavorText: Dark Bishop takes Light Pawn, check.

SHALE SPIDER.name: Shale Spider
SHALE SPIDER.flavorText: The 2nd member of the VERY exclusive Is-Called-A-Spider-But-Isn't-A-Beast Club.

SPIRIT POACHER.name: Spirit Poacher
SPIRIT POACHER.flavorText: Always poach from your local spirit shelter.

NIGHTMARE LORD XAVIUS.name: Nightmare Lord Xavius
NIGHTMARE LORD XAVIUS.flavorText: Xavius will also be replacing Illidan as the Demon Hunter hero in an upcoming patch.

DWARVEN ARCHAEOLOGIST.name: Dwarven Archaeologist
DWARVEN ARCHAEOLOGIST.flavorText: She's making great progress on paying off that advanced degree.

BONECHEWER VANGUARD.name: Bonechewer Vanguard
BONECHEWER VANGUARD.flavorText: She came here to taunt you and chew on bones, and she's all outta bones.

BRAZEN ZEALOT.name: Brazen Zealot
BRAZEN ZEALOT.flavorText: Some paladins really Light it up.

GLUGG THE GULPER.name: Glugg the Gulper
GLUGG THE GULPER.flavorText: Food can be scarce in the Abyssal Depths, leading its top predators to pursue any potential source of sustenance. Even extra crunchy ones.

STARSCALE CONSTELLAR.name: Starscale Constellar
STARSCALE CONSTELLAR.flavorText: You'll understand how to best make use of its effect once you connect the dots.

ELWYNN BOAR.name: Elwynn Boar
ELWYNN BOAR.flavorText: Be grateful we lowered the requirement from 65,340,285.

JADE SPIRIT.name: Jade Spirit
JADE SPIRIT.flavorText: "He's so cute! I just want to squeeze him, then use him for Jade Golem parts!" - Aya Blackpaw

DEMONWRATH.name: Demonwrath
DEMONWRATH.flavorText: Demons are not angry most of the time. You have to play this card in order to really bring it out of them.

SCALERIDER.name: Scalerider
SCALERIDER.flavorText: Do Re Me Fa So La Spear Throw!

WATERCOLOR ARTIST.name: Watercolor Artist
WATERCOLOR ARTIST.flavorText: They've amassed a largely aquatic body of work, painting lakes, rivers and self portraits.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/1/14/TID_716_TidalRevenant_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ TID_716_TidalRevenant_Play.wav <summon sound>

IMPRISONED CELESTIAL.name: Imprisoned Celestial
IMPRISONED CELESTIAL.flavorText: "Look at your deck, now back to me, now back at your deck, now back to me. Who am I? None of your—I'm on a horse."

SCHOOLING.name: Schooling
SCHOOLING.flavorText: A group of Piranha are known as a Scholomance.

GALACTIC CRUSADER.name: Galactic Crusader
GALACTIC CRUSADER.flavorText: The will was very specific that in the event of the Crusader's death, you were to inherit these random spells. Very odd.

ANCIENT OF WAR.name: Ancient of War
ANCIENT OF WAR.flavorText: Young Night Elves love to play "Who can get the Ancient of War to Uproot?" You lose if you get crushed to death.

WILDFIRE.name: Wildfire
WILDFIRE.flavorText: The Barrens were a lush jungle. Then this happened.

IMPRISONED SCRAP IMP.name: Imprisoned Scrap Imp
IMPRISONED SCRAP IMP.flavorText: His impish imports imply impressively impetuous impropriety.

GOLDSHIRE GNOLL.name: Goldshire Gnoll
GOLDSHIRE GNOLL.flavorText: They're searching for one ring. They're pretty sure someone said Goldshire.

HELLFIRE.name: Hellfire
HELLFIRE.flavorText: It's spells like these that make it hard for Warlocks to get decent help.

SILVERMOON GUARDIAN.name: Silvermoon Guardian
SILVERMOON GUARDIAN.flavorText: The first time they tried to guard Silvermoon against the scourge, it didn’t go so well…

SHRIEK.name: Shriek
SHRIEK.flavorText: The first warning sign of an oncoming warlock temper tantrum.

STITCHED TRACKER.name: Stitched Tracker
STITCHED TRACKER.flavorText: He's just exercising his right to bear arms.

POZZIK, AUDIO ENGINEER.name: Pozzik, Audio Engineer
POZZIK, AUDIO ENGINEER.flavorText: "I'm down here, fixin' all the Gnomish tech that breaks down mid-set while that buffoon Fizzle is up there taking pictures of the sky. YOU tell ME who's the better engineer!"

GLIDE.name: Glide
GLIDE.flavorText: "Come with me, and you'll see, a whole new hand of possibly the same cards."

TYR.name: Tyr
TYR.flavorText: Brought me back to life, S Tyr card.

TINKERTOWN TECHNICIAN.name: Tinkertown Technician
TINKERTOWN TECHNICIAN.flavorText: Won't you take me to... Tinkertown?

PRISMATIC ELEMENTAL.name: Prismatic Elemental
PRISMATIC ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Disappointed they were rejected from the Magical Guardian tryouts.

CAGE HEAD.name: Cage Head
CAGE HEAD.flavorText: You get your head stuck in a cage ONCE, and all of a sudden you've got a new nickname.

OCTOSARI.name: Octosari
OCTOSARI.flavorText: Eight arms of sand-flinging, foe-wringing, card-slinging fury!

CAPTAIN GALVANGAR.name: Captain Galvangar
CAPTAIN GALVANGAR.flavorText: It wasn't the ravages of war that took Galvangar, it was hypothermia.

FLOECASTER.name: Floecaster
FLOECASTER.flavorText: His real name is Melvin, but he prefers his friends call him ... <sigh> ..."Floecaster."

RUSTSTEED RAIDER.name: Ruststeed Raider
RUSTSTEED RAIDER.flavorText: Three-time winner (and sole survivor) of the Crashes of Outland motocross!

JUDGMENT OF JUSTICE.name: Judgment of Justice
JUDGMENT OF JUSTICE.flavorText: Look, we don't need a jury. We've got a paladin right here!

CLIMBING HOOK.name: Climbing Hook
CLIMBING HOOK.flavorText: "It LOOKS like a grappling hook but it's actually a climbing hook. It's a really important distinction you just wouldn't get it."

IMPRISONED ANTAEN.name: Imprisoned Antaen
IMPRISONED ANTAEN.flavorText: Can I get a pair of size XXXXXL manacles?

DRAGONSLAYER.name: Dragonslayer
DRAGONSLAYER.flavorText: A pair of stout dwarves nearly averted the Cataclysm.

LOCK AND LOAD.name: Lock and Load
LOCK AND LOAD.flavorText: Rexxar narrowed his eyes, grabbed his machine gun, and said: "It's go time. Lock and load." This card pays homage to that special moment.

DEATHWING, MAD ASPECT.name: Deathwing, Mad Aspect
DEATHWING, MAD ASPECT.flavorText: Bite that one, bite that other one, claw this one, swallow that one whole....

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/8b/VO_DRG_026_Male_Dragon_Attack_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_DRG_026_Male_Dragon_Attack_03.wav CATACLYSM!

KOBOLD MINER.name: Kobold Miner
KOBOLD MINER.flavorText: A mining kobold that costs 2, has very low health, and gives you resources… what is this, Warcraft Rumble?

RENO, LONE RANGER.name: Reno, Lone Ranger
RENO, LONE RANGER.flavorText: With an uncertain past and a questionable future, Reno was lucky to find his home on the range.

FOREBODING FLAME.name: Foreboding Flame
FOREBODING FLAME.flavorText: "I am the harbinger of the end times! Soon, destruction will reign and chaos will ensue in the culmination of your demise: waking up 15 minutes before your alarm!"

ENVOY OF LAZUL.name: Envoy of Lazul
ENVOY OF LAZUL.flavorText: "Note to self: possess someone who's local and knows directions next time."

BLUBBER BARON.name: Blubber Baron
BLUBBER BARON.flavorText: When oil, railroad, steel, robber, and red are all already taken, your options are limited.

MOTION DENIED.name: Motion Denied
MOTION DENIED.flavorText: DO NOT PASS GO. DO NOT COLLECT 200 GOLD.

SOULFREEZE.name: Soulfreeze
SOULFREEZE.flavorText: An effective way to freeze someone's soul is to just freeze their body.

TERRORSCALE STALKER.name: Terrorscale Stalker
TERRORSCALE STALKER.flavorText: Likes to scare his friends half to death.

WORGEN INFILTRATOR.name: Worgen Infiltrator
WORGEN INFILTRATOR.flavorText: If you want to stop a worgen from infiltrating, just yell, "No! Bad boy!"

STONESKIN BASILISK.name: Stoneskin Basilisk
STONESKIN BASILISK.flavorText: He got that way from looking into a mirror.

CRAZED ALCHEMIST.name: Crazed Alchemist
CRAZED ALCHEMIST.flavorText: "You'll love my new recipe!" he says... especially if you're not happy with your current number of limbs.

LEPER GNOME.name: Leper Gnome
LEPER GNOME.flavorText: He really just wants to be your friend, but the constant rejection is starting to really get to him.

HORRENDOUS GROWTH.name: Horrendous Growth
HORRENDOUS GROWTH.flavorText: Stop picking at it! You’re only making it worse.

BOLA SHOT.name: Bola Shot
BOLA SHOT.flavorText: On second thought, bolas aren't very good against flying worms.

INSIGHT.name: Insight
INSIGHT.flavorText: Shouldn't the eyes be facing backwards for insight?

ACORNBEARER.name: Acornbearer
ACORNBEARER.flavorText: You’d be nuts to mess with the squirrel squad.

FLICKERING LIGHTBOT.name: Flickering Lightbot
FLICKERING LIGHTBOT.flavorText: These bots are sent out with nearly drained batteries, for dramatic effect.

HEMET, FOAM MARKSMAN.name: Hemet, Foam Marksman
HEMET, FOAM MARKSMAN.flavorText: So THIS is who's been lowering the power level of all those Hearthstone cards in a foamly fashion.

LIVEWIRE LANCE.name: Livewire Lance
LIVEWIRE LANCE.flavorText: The lance is heavy but it’s the battery pack that really does a number on the shoulders.

LESSER MITHRIL SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Mithril Spellstone
LESSER MITHRIL SPELLSTONE.flavorText: To dwarves of stone the demon called With promises of might, enthralled In grasping greed they found their doom Forever bound in mithril tombs.

DEHYDRATE.name: Dehydrate
DEHYDRATE.flavorText: JUST A LITTLE FURTHER LITTLE GUY, YOU CAN MAKE IT!!!

SOULSTEALER.name: Soulstealer
SOULSTEALER.flavorText: "Wanna see what destruction looks like? Here it is in undead form - it's your boy Soulstealer!"

FLOOP'S GLORIOUS GLOOP.name: Floop's Glorious Gloop
FLOOP'S GLORIOUS GLOOP.flavorText: How much gloop could Floop's Gloop gloop if Floop's Gloop could gloop gloop?

LYRA THE SUNSHARD.name: Lyra the Sunshard
LYRA THE SUNSHARD.flavorText: Arise, fair sun, and kill my envious foes. They don't have a legendary as beautiful as you.

DEEPMINER BRANN.name: Deepminer Brann
DEEPMINER BRANN.flavorText: This is a very on-brannd effect.

SHADOW WORD: PAIN.name: Shadow Word: Pain
SHADOW WORD: PAIN.flavorText: A step up from a spell cast by many beginning acolytes: "Shadow Word: Annoy".

SIGHTLESS WATCHER.name: Sightless Watcher
SIGHTLESS WATCHER.flavorText: What he lacks in sight, he makes up for in sleight-of-tentacle tricks.

SPIRIT ALPHA.name: Spirit Alpha
SPIRIT ALPHA.flavorText: Just like in the natural world, the alpha of the species is bright purple.

SHARKFIN FAN.name: Sharkfin Fan
SHARKFIN FAN.flavorText: His taste in soup is criminal.

WINDFURY.name: Windfury
WINDFURY.flavorText: Windfury is like Earthfury and Firefury, but more light and airy.

NORTHWATCH COMMANDER.name: Northwatch Commander
NORTHWATCH COMMANDER.flavorText: It was all going well until some Horde had the cunning idea of attacking from the south.

MEETING STONE.name: Meeting Stone
MEETING STONE.flavorText: "I'm clicking on it, but nothing's happening."

LICENSED ADVENTURER.name: Licensed Adventurer
LICENSED ADVENTURER.flavorText: "Just point me in the vague direction of the things you want smashed, and you got yourself a deal!"

ARGENT PROTECTOR.name: Argent Protector
ARGENT PROTECTOR.flavorText: "I'm not saying you can dodge fireballs. I'm saying with this shield, you won't have to."

MICRO MACHINE.name: Micro Machine
MICRO MACHINE.flavorText: This card is the real thing.

CHAR.name: Char
CHAR.flavorText: There's just no point trying to add flavor to this now.

SOUL INFUSION.name: Soul Infusion
SOUL INFUSION.flavorText: People called him a soulless monster. We're not sure this is better.

OGREMANCER.name: Ogremancer
OGREMANCER.flavorText: After their third attempt, Tharg began to suspect that Krul was summoning the skeletons on purpose.

CLOAK OF SHADOWS.name: Cloak of Shadows
CLOAK OF SHADOWS.flavorText: Only worthy emperors can see the cloak.

SANGUINE SOLDIER.name: Sanguine Soldier
SANGUINE SOLDIER.flavorText: They just need someone to ouch for them.

RAPTOR HATCHLING.name: Raptor Hatchling
RAPTOR HATCHLING.flavorText: They’re just baby teeth. Lots and lots of baby teeth.

CURSE OF AGONY.name: Curse of Agony
CURSE OF AGONY.flavorText: Now, fools, you shall all understand my back pain!

CONSUME MAGIC.name: Consume Magic
CONSUME MAGIC.flavorText: Please be mindful when consuming raw or undercooked magic.

MUCK PLUMBER.name: Muck Plumber
MUCK PLUMBER.flavorText: If you drink muck, you go to the Maw before you die.

TRAVELMASTER DUNGAR.name: Travelmaster Dungar
TRAVELMASTER DUNGAR.flavorText: Our travel options will take you to Paradise and beyond!

FOOD FIGHT.name: Food Fight
FOOD FIGHT.flavorText: Now THIS is the deadliest catch.

CORONER.name: Coroner
CORONER.flavorText: It was at this moment the Coroner decided to become a farmer instead.

LESSER ONYX SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Onyx Spellstone
LESSER ONYX SPELLSTONE.flavorText: The trolls of old embraced the gift A jewel of black for daggers swift No party lasts who finds the stone Those wielding it soon stand alone.

STUDENT OF THE STARS.name: Student of the Stars
STUDENT OF THE STARS.flavorText: She is getting her major in Ursa.

WICKED WITCHDOCTOR.name: Wicked Witchdoctor
WICKED WITCHDOCTOR.flavorText: You can easily defeat her by either dealing 4 damage, or dropping a house on her.

SHADOWTOUCHED KVALDIR.name: Shadowtouched Kvaldir
SHADOWTOUCHED KVALDIR.flavorText: Four out of five deck doctors say this works great with Reno Jackson!

JADE BEHEMOTH.name: Jade Behemoth
JADE BEHEMOTH.flavorText: I think we should talk about the jade elephant in the room.

AGGRAMAR, THE AVENGER.name: Aggramar, the Avenger
AGGRAMAR, THE AVENGER.flavorText: Formerly a trusted lieutenant of Sargeras, Aggramar helped him fight the demonic legions across many worlds before he was corrupted.

ROTGILL.name: Rotgill
ROTGILL.flavorText: In the summer: Hotgill. Mechanized: Botgill. Everyone else: Notgill.

SAND BREATH.name: Sand Breath
SAND BREATH.flavorText: After Uldum, EVERYONE had sand breath.

DURNHOLDE IMPOSTER.name: Durnholde Imposter
DURNHOLDE IMPOSTER.flavorText: Assassins of the Infinite Dragonflight waited for their moment to strike at Thrall before he ever became Warchief.

SHATTERED SUN CLERIC.name: Shattered Sun Cleric
SHATTERED SUN CLERIC.flavorText: They always have a spare flask of Sunwell Energy Drink™!

EFFICIENT OCTO-BOT.name: Efficient Octo-bot
EFFICIENT OCTO-BOT.flavorText: Pull the lever, Octo-bot... Wrong leverrrrr!

PEON.name: Peon
PEON.flavorText: Joke's on the peon: the job's never done.

GURUBASHI CHICKEN.name: Gurubashi Chicken
GURUBASHI CHICKEN.flavorText: “Ya hold it by da feet, mon. Den ya THROW.”

KANGOR'S ENDLESS ARMY.name: Kangor's Endless Army
KANGOR'S ENDLESS ARMY.flavorText: "That's three, Kangor. Three isn't endless." - Countess Ashmore

ANCIENT MAGE.name: Ancient Mage
ANCIENT MAGE.flavorText: Sometimes he forgets and just wanders into someone else's game.

LORD GODFREY.name: Lord Godfrey
LORD GODFREY.flavorText: Betrayed the Alliance. Betrayed the Horde. All for 200 achievement points and a sweet, sweet hat.

DRUM SOLOIST.name: Drum Soloist
DRUM SOLOIST.flavorText: "Was I rushin' or was I dragon?"

FEL CANNON.name: Fel Cannon
FEL CANNON.flavorText: The box says, "New and improved, with 200% more fel!"

EUREKA!.name: Eureka!
EUREKA!.flavorText: Genius is 1% inspiration, and 99% drawing your Deathwing.

PRIMORDIAL WAVE.name: Primordial Wave
PRIMORDIAL WAVE.flavorText: A primordial hello to you too!

DIRTY RAT.name: Dirty Rat
DIRTY RAT.flavorText: It's not his fault… Someone keeps stealing his soap!

PRESTOR'S PYROMANCER.name: Prestor's Pyromancer
PRESTOR'S PYROMANCER.flavorText: Ah, yeah. This guy. Definitely not an evil dragon in disguise either.

GOLGANNETH, THE THUNDERER.name: Golganneth, the Thunderer
GOLGANNETH, THE THUNDERER.flavorText: With dominion over the seas and skies, Golganneth fearlessly wields the power of nature to serve the Pantheon.

ZEREK, MASTER CLONER.name: Zerek, Master Cloner
ZEREK, MASTER CLONER.flavorText: His original name was Aerek. Then the first clone was Berek. They went evil around Merek.

BLACKWING CORRUPTOR.name: Blackwing Corruptor
BLACKWING CORRUPTOR.flavorText: He got his name when he gave Blackwing some comic books and rock & roll records.

BOON OF THE ASCENDED.name: Boon of the Ascended
BOON OF THE ASCENDED.flavorText: Ascension is not some external power granted to you, it is the power you find within yourself.

FROSTBOLT.name: Frostbolt
FROSTBOLT.flavorText: It is customary to yell "Chill out!" or "Freeze!" or "Ice ice, baby!" when you play this card.

SIEGEBREAKER.name: Siegebreaker
SIEGEBREAKER.flavorText: Has a side hustle as a siegebroker.

FORBIDDEN SHAPING.name: Forbidden Shaping
FORBIDDEN SHAPING.flavorText: But the minion arrives covered in goo.

ARCANE FLAKMAGE.name: Arcane Flakmage
ARCANE FLAKMAGE.flavorText: Ancient pandaren proverb: He who is without secrets lacks flak.

BIG BAD ARCHMAGE.name: Big Bad Archmage
BIG BAD ARCHMAGE.flavorText: "My, my, what big minions I have!"

DEATHCHILLER.name: Deathchiller
DEATHCHILLER.flavorText: Man, death is like the most chill state... you've got nothing to do but relax.

MAGMA RAGER.name: Magma Rager
MAGMA RAGER.flavorText: He likes to think he is powerful, but pretty much anyone can solo Molten Core now.

PELAGOS.name: Pelagos
PELAGOS.flavorText: He's a great judge of character.

ENCHANTER.name: Enchanter
ENCHANTER.flavorText: "I know Scourgebane! Your materials and tips appreciated!"

JUSTICAR TRUEHEART.name: Justicar Trueheart
JUSTICAR TRUEHEART.flavorText: It's like putting racing stripes and a giant spoiler on your hero power.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/4/49/VO_AT_132_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_132_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/4/49/VO_AT_132_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_132_ATTACK_02.wav Disqualified.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e8/VO_AT_132_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_132_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

SNUGGLE TEDDY.name: Snuggle Teddy
SNUGGLE TEDDY.flavorText: Someone really put their heart into making this.

SERRATED BONE SPIKE.name: Serrated Bone Spike
SERRATED BONE SPIKE.flavorText: Draka, in an attempt to help, threw them a bone.

R.C. RAMPAGE.name: R.C. Rampage
R.C. RAMPAGE.flavorText: This place has really gone to the dogs.

AGENCY ESPIONAGE.name: Agency Espionage
AGENCY ESPIONAGE.flavorText: What gnomish monitoring devices lack in subtlety, they make up for in robustness.

GNOMISH EXPERIMENTER.name: Gnomish Experimenter
GNOMISH EXPERIMENTER.flavorText: He's legitimately surprised every time he turns himself into a chicken.

DARKRIDER.name: Darkrider
DARKRIDER.flavorText: Before the corruption spread to the Emerald Dream, he was known only by this: Rider.

DRONE DECONSTRUCTOR.name: Drone Deconstructor
DRONE DECONSTRUCTOR.flavorText: You have to deconstruct to reconstruct.

SNOWED IN.name: Snowed In
SNOWED IN.flavorText: “What do you mean school isn’t cancelled?! It’s a snow day!”

CULT MASTER.name: Cult Master
CULT MASTER.flavorText: She may be an evil cult master, but she still calls her parents once a week.

ETHEREAL ARCANIST.name: Ethereal Arcanist
ETHEREAL ARCANIST.flavorText: The ethereals are wrapped in cloth to give form to their non-corporeal bodies. Also because it's nice and soft.

FIREWORK ELEMENTAL.name: Firework Elemental
FIREWORK ELEMENTAL.flavorText: The brightest spark can still go dark.

NECRIUM APOTHECARY.name: Necrium Apothecary
NECRIUM APOTHECARY.flavorText: Necrium: Get the afterlife without the aftertaste!

HOPEFUL DRYAD.name: Hopeful Dryad
HOPEFUL DRYAD.flavorText: "I hope this dragon doesn't eat me when it grows up."

KEYBOARD SOLOIST.name: Keyboard Soloist
KEYBOARD SOLOIST.flavorText: Give her a hand, everybody! Or maybe 4!

DRAKKARI EMBALMER.name: Drakkari Embalmer
DRAKKARI EMBALMER.flavorText: A troll in life, death, and online forums.

ARCANE SHOT.name: Arcane Shot
ARCANE SHOT.flavorText: Magi conjured arcane arrows to sell to hunters, until hunters learned just enough magic to do it themselves. The resulting loss of jobs sent Stormwind into a minor recession.

ENHANCED DREADLORD.name: Enhanced Dreadlord
ENHANCED DREADLORD.flavorText: Photo actually taken across the street in the reflection of a doorknob.

JEWELED MACAW.name: Jeweled Macaw
JEWELED MACAW.flavorText: It’s not LITERALLY jeweled. The goblins were terribly disappointed.

CLOCKWORK GIANT.name: Clockwork Giant
CLOCKWORK GIANT.flavorText: He and Mountain Giant don't get along.

EGGBASHER.name: Eggbasher
EGGBASHER.flavorText: We could do this the over-easy way or the over-hard way.

EXTRATERRESTRIAL EGG.name: Extraterrestrial Egg
EXTRATERRESTRIAL EGG.flavorText: I'll have mine starry-side up please.

MUTATING LIFEFORM.name: Mutating Lifeform
MUTATING LIFEFORM.flavorText: Who knows how many amazing discoveries are out there! ... Never mind, I'm going home.

NOZARI.name: Nozari
NOZARI.flavorText: In another timeline, she was called Yeszari.

FIRST FLAME.name: First Flame
FIRST FLAME.flavorText: You never forget your first love: fire.

EONAR, THE LIFE-BINDER.name: Eonar, the Life-Binder
EONAR, THE LIFE-BINDER.flavorText: Protector of all living things, she once saved the nascent world-soul of Azeroth from annihilation. It seems mercy was her greatest wisdom.

DRAIN LIFE.name: Drain Life
DRAIN LIFE.flavorText: "I've just sucked one year of your life away."

DALARAN MAGE.name: Dalaran Mage
DALARAN MAGE.flavorText: You don't see a lot of Dalaran warriors.

ADDLED GRIZZLY.name: Addled Grizzly
ADDLED GRIZZLY.flavorText: Druids who spend too long in bear form are more susceptible to the whispers of the Old Gods. Right now they are whispering the lyrics to "La Bamba".

WRETCHED TUTOR.name: Wretched Tutor
WRETCHED TUTOR.flavorText: "If you like my tutoring, you'll love my sister the art therapist, my father the driver, and my mother the housekeeper."

MALCHEZAAR'S IMP.name: Malchezaar's Imp
MALCHEZAAR'S IMP.flavorText: Malchezaar used to have an imp named Dobby working for him, but there was a tragic accident.

BARREL OF MONKEYS.name: Barrel of Monkeys
BARREL OF MONKEYS.flavorText: There used to be four monkeys, but then one fell off and bumped his head.

IRONBEAK OWL.name: Ironbeak Owl
IRONBEAK OWL.flavorText: Their wings are silent but their screech is... whatever the opposite of silent is.

MOORABI.name: Moorabi
MOORABI.flavorText: Most disturbing is how Moorabi covers all those frozen minions with flavored syrup.

NAZMANI BLOODWEAVER.name: Nazmani Bloodweaver
NAZMANI BLOODWEAVER.flavorText: Her first stage name, Ketchupweaver, failed to excite the audience.

UNSTABLE PORTAL.name: Unstable Portal
UNSTABLE PORTAL.flavorText: The denizens of Azeroth have no idea how much work goes into stabilizing portals. We spend like 30% of GDP on portal upkeep.

GRIMESTREET OUTFITTER.name: Grimestreet Outfitter
GRIMESTREET OUTFITTER.flavorText: If you bargain hard, he'll throw in the hat.

MUSEUM CURATOR.name: Museum Curator
MUSEUM CURATOR.flavorText: He is forever cursing the kids who climb on the rails and the evil archeologists who animate the exhibits.

ROBOCALLER.name: Robocaller
ROBOCALLER.flavorText: When I was your age, robocallers had to dial themselves!

NETHER BREATH.name: Nether Breath
NETHER BREATH.flavorText: "Whether the Nether is cold, whether the Nether is hot, we'll burn together, whatever the Nether, whether we like it or not."

HOLOGRAM OPERATOR.name: Hologram Operator
HOLOGRAM OPERATOR.flavorText: Help me, Temporary Draenei. You're my only hope!

FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL.name: First Day of School
FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL.flavorText: "Report to the bookstore to buy your books, the alchemist to buy your potions, and then get your wands at the… wandryroom?"

SHIMMER SHOT.name: Shimmer Shot
SHIMMER SHOT.flavorText: I hope I don't jinx the outcome.

GROOK FU MASTER.name: Grook Fu Master
GROOK FU MASTER.flavorText: Grook Fu, the ancient Hozen art of bashing heads with a stick.

NORGANNON.name: Norgannon
NORGANNON.flavorText: His tremendous arcane magic was strong enough to save all of the spirits of the titans after Sargeras destroyed their physical forms.

SIGIL OF TIME.name: Sigil of Time
SIGIL OF TIME.flavorText: Sigil of Right A Down Right A Down.

KEEPER OF ULDAMAN.name: Keeper of Uldaman
KEEPER OF ULDAMAN.flavorText: U da man! No, U da man!

SKYDIVING INSTRUCTOR.name: Skydiving Instructor
SKYDIVING INSTRUCTOR.flavorText: "Is it dangerous?" "For me? Not at all. Now jump!"

PRINCE TALDARAM.name: Prince Taldaram
PRINCE TALDARAM.flavorText: Three Princes stand before you. This one wants to copy others.

KRUL THE UNSHACKLED.name: Krul the Unshackled
KRUL THE UNSHACKLED.flavorText: Spicklefizz pondered his life choices as he looked at the chain around his neck. "Become a warlock," they said. "You get to enslave demons," they said.

NORTH SEA KRAKEN.name: North Sea Kraken
NORTH SEA KRAKEN.flavorText: You have no idea how tired this guy is of being released.

PHOTOSYNTHESIS.name: Photosynthesis
PHOTOSYNTHESIS.flavorText: Nothing beats some time relaxing in the sun with a pile of good mulch.

UNITE THE MURLOCS.name: Unite the Murlocs
UNITE THE MURLOCS.flavorText: Form feet and legs! Form arms and body! Oh. Sorry. I was thinking about Mechafin.

ARMAGEDILLO.name: Armagedillo
ARMAGEDILLO.flavorText: We may never know what provoked it, but we will never forget the consequences.

PETTY THEFT.name: Petty Theft
PETTY THEFT.flavorText: Room service at a pirate hotel really cleans house.

COLIFERO THE ARTIST.name: Colifero the Artist
COLIFERO THE ARTIST.flavorText: You are what you paint! And Colifero is paint.

NOURISH.name: Nourish
NOURISH.flavorText: Druids take nourishment from many things: the power of nature, the songbird's chirp, a chocolate cake.

MINDBENDER.name: Mindbender
MINDBENDER.flavorText: I like my brain unbent, thanks.

BLACK MORASS IMPOSTER.name: Black Morass Imposter
BLACK MORASS IMPOSTER.flavorText: Does something seem off about Medivh's apprentice to you?

RECONNAISSANCE.name: Reconnaissance
RECONNAISSANCE.flavorText: “But Commander, I already did the connaissance.”

SWIPE.name: Swipe
SWIPE.flavorText: When a bear rears back and extends his arms, he's about to Swipe! ... or hug.

AZSHARAN RITUAL.name: Azsharan Ritual
AZSHARAN RITUAL.flavorText: The harmonious silence surrounding the ritual was unceremoniously BROKEN when HAROLD began eating stale potato chips.

DARK TRANSFORMATION.name: Dark Transformation
DARK TRANSFORMATION.flavorText: The Northrend Arm Wrestling Championship just found its new champion.

POTION VENDOR.name: Potion Vendor
POTION VENDOR.flavorText: Everyone gets two because that’s all she can hold.

KIDNAP.name: Kidnap
KIDNAP.flavorText: Check your coat, but don't check the coat closet.

SHIFTING SCROLL.name: Shifting Scroll
SHIFTING SCROLL.flavorText: Next turn, this is going to be AMAZING.

EXOTIC HOUNDMASTER.name: Exotic Houndmaster
EXOTIC HOUNDMASTER.flavorText: "Hi lil guy! Have a bite of Green, it's good for you!"

CUTPURSE.name: Cutpurse
CUTPURSE.flavorText: He has a giant collection of purses now. One for every outfit!

SOOTHSAYER'S CARAVAN.name: Soothsayer's Caravan
SOOTHSAYER'S CARAVAN.flavorText: With tusks like those, you might call her a "Toothsayer."

LORD OF THE ARENA.name: Lord of the Arena
LORD OF THE ARENA.flavorText: He used to be a 2100+ rated arena player, but that was years ago and nobody can get him to shut up about it.

CLIFF DIVE.name: Cliff Dive
CLIFF DIVE.flavorText: "Is it safe?" "Sure, we have plenty of replacement pirates."

SWAMP KING DRED.name: Swamp King Dred
SWAMP KING DRED.flavorText: Swamp King Dred, more like Swamp King Dead, amiright?

CHALK ARTIST.name: Chalk Artist
CHALK ARTIST.flavorText: Well it's either a dragon or a dinosaur - chalk it up to art style.

SON OF HODIR.name: Son of Hodir
SON OF HODIR.flavorText: You look dehydrated, drink some water! Come on, chug! Chug! Chug! Chug!

MIND EATER.name: Mind Eater
MIND EATER.flavorText: Watch out brain, she'll chew you up! She's a Mind Eater!

TOY BOAT.name: Toy Boat
TOY BOAT.flavorText: Try playing seven of these in one turn fast.

BLOOD WARRIORS.name: Blood Warriors
BLOOD WARRIORS.flavorText: They have an uneasy rivalry with the Blood Paladins.

DEFENDER OF ARGUS.name: Defender of Argus
DEFENDER OF ARGUS.flavorText: You wouldn’t think that Argus would need this much defending. But it does.

SLITHERING DEATHSCALE.name: Slithering Deathscale
SLITHERING DEATHSCALE.flavorText: Colossal minions know her better as Slithering Damagescale.

SLIMESCALE DIVER.name: Slimescale Diver
SLIMESCALE DIVER.flavorText: You try putting on a wetsuit with scales.

CARNIVAL BARKER.name: Carnival Barker
CARNIVAL BARKER.flavorText: The barking initially confused faire-goers, so he switched to words.

MONKEY BUSINESS.name: Monkey Business
MONKEY BUSINESS.flavorText: Why aren't the bananas randomly split???

CALL TO ARMS.name: Call to Arms
CALL TO ARMS.flavorText: More personal than a text to arms.

EXPLORER'S HAT.name: Explorer's Hat
EXPLORER'S HAT.flavorText: Harrison Jones was disappointed that he didn't get to be part of the League of Explorers, but his hat did.

CORRUPTED SEER.name: Corrupted Seer
CORRUPTED SEER.flavorText: For seers, it's very handy to have your crystal ball hanging right in front of your face.

ANUBISATH DEFENDER.name: Anubisath Defender
ANUBISATH DEFENDER.flavorText: Also comes running when he hears a can opener.

SPIRITSINGER UMBRA.name: Spiritsinger Umbra
SPIRITSINGER UMBRA.flavorText: She sees the fate of anyone she meets, but it's always the same: dinosaur attack.

STEWARD OF SCROLLS.name: Steward of Scrolls
STEWARD OF SCROLLS.flavorText: Oh dang it, I spilled ink elemental all over my essay!

MAGEHUNTER.name: Magehunter
MAGEHUNTER.flavorText: Hates waiting. Abhors chit chat. Fond of the color purple.

LESSER OPAL SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Opal Spellstone
LESSER OPAL SPELLSTONE.flavorText: For those seeking glory and power Be not swayed by Azari the Devourer The opal grants victory to the weak But leaves your soul barren and bleak

SAFETY GOGGLES.name: Safety Goggles
SAFETY GOGGLES.flavorText: Remember, always be safe in the lab to mitigate injuries! *painfully snaps goggles onto face*

BOUNCING BLADE.name: Bouncing Blade
BOUNCING BLADE.flavorText: Only goblins would think this was a good idea. Even they are starting to have their doubts.

VEXALLUS.name: Vexallus
VEXALLUS.flavorText: He only casts the spells once - it's Shmexallus that casts the copy.

THE CURATOR.name: The Curator
THE CURATOR.flavorText: The Curator guards Azeroth’s deadliest creatures, but it’s secretly terrified of squirrels.

CENARION WARD.name: Cenarion Ward
CENARION WARD.flavorText: Don't ask about his right hand. He's still growing into it.

HEALING WAVE.name: Healing Wave
HEALING WAVE.flavorText: Favored by shaman who study the art of restoration and healing, this spell would feel smug, if it had feelings.

HYSTERIA.name: Hysteria
HYSTERIA.flavorText: "My mount and I share a special connection. Just not a good one."

SMOTHERING STARFISH.name: Smothering Starfish
SMOTHERING STARFISH.flavorText: Is a sucker for small talk.

CHARGED HAMMER.name: Charged Hammer
CHARGED HAMMER.flavorText: You can only pick it up if you are worthy.

HEMATURGE.name: Hematurge
HEMATURGE.flavorText: She's here to PUMP! YOU UP!

STEALER OF SOULS.name: Stealer of Souls
STEALER OF SOULS.flavorText: The tooth fairy gig didn't work out.

GHOULISH ALCHEMIST.name: Ghoulish Alchemist
GHOULISH ALCHEMIST.flavorText: AND I THREW IT ON THE GROUND!

TOAD OF THE WILDS.name: Toad of the Wilds
TOAD OF THE WILDS.flavorText: "Someday we'll find it. The Oasis Connection. The peons, the caravans, and me."

MO'ARG FORGEFIEND.name: Mo'arg Forgefiend
MO'ARG FORGEFIEND.flavorText: Enraged not by fel energies, but by an itchy nose he cannot scratch.

ANCIENT WATCHER.name: Ancient Watcher
ANCIENT WATCHER.flavorText: Why do its eyes seem to follow you as you walk by?

KARGAL BATTLESCAR.name: Kargal Battlescar
KARGAL BATTLESCAR.flavorText: One if by land, two if by tree.

RINGMASTER'S BATON.name: Ringmaster's Baton
RINGMASTER'S BATON.flavorText: A mech, a dragon, and a pirate walk into an Old God's gaping maw. The mech was too crunchy, the dragon was too hot, but the pirate was just right.

KIL'JAEDEN.name: Kil'jaeden
KIL'JAEDEN.flavorText: With complete control of the Burning Legion's forces, Kil'jaeden will stop at nothing until all of the traitorous Draenei have been squelched. *right clicks the enemy hero*

SUNFURY CHAMPION.name: Sunfury Champion
SUNFURY CHAMPION.flavorText: Champion of the Great Blood Elf Bake Off 12 years running.

STAR POWER.name: Star Power
STAR POWER.flavorText: Five of the spectators were star-struck.

CYCLE OF HATRED.name: Cycle of Hatred
CYCLE OF HATRED.flavorText: If you run 2 of these, would that make it the bi-cycle of hatred?

SASQUAWK.name: Sasquawk
SASQUAWK.flavorText: He makes your last turn this turn. But if you play him next turn, your next turn is this turn. Doing both would make this turn last turn and next turn this turn. Which turn is this next turn last turn?

ELVEN MINSTREL.name: Elven Minstrel
ELVEN MINSTREL.flavorText: "After that gig in Hamlin went south, I swore off rats."

COMMANDING SHOUT.name: Commanding Shout
COMMANDING SHOUT.flavorText: "Shout! Shout! Let it all out!" - Advice to warriors-in-training

RATCATCHER.name: Ratcatcher
RATCATCHER.flavorText: He's on the hunt for Togwaggle's missing rat.

SILK STITCHING.name: Silk Stitching
SILK STITCHING.flavorText: The slogan of their very exclusive sewing club is "You can't stitch with us."

AVALANCHE.name: Avalanche
AVALANCHE.flavorText: One of our more snowbally cards.

STALAGG.name: Stalagg
STALAGG.flavorText: Stalagg want to write own flavor text. "STALAGG AWESOME!"

PIT LORD.name: Pit Lord
PIT LORD.flavorText: Mannoroth, Magtheridon, and Brutallus may be dead, but it turns out there are a LOT of pit lords.

RECKLESS ROCKETEER.name: Reckless Rocketeer
RECKLESS ROCKETEER.flavorText: One Insane Rocketeer. One Rocket full of Explosives. Infinite Fun.

VAL'KYR SOULCLAIMER.name: Val'kyr Soulclaimer
VAL'KYR SOULCLAIMER.flavorText: My Ghoul friend is back and you're gonna be in trouble.

VICIOUS SLITHERSPEAR.name: Vicious Slitherspear
VICIOUS SLITHERSPEAR.flavorText: He goes by ‘Fun-Loving Slitherspear’ on his dating profile.

FELSABER.name: Felsaber
FELSABER.flavorText: Some drivers rev their engines. This one growls all on its own.

RAM TAMER.name: Ram Tamer
RAM TAMER.flavorText: Pump up the ram, pump it up. While your hooves are stompin’.

DALARAN ASPIRANT.name: Dalaran Aspirant
DALARAN ASPIRANT.flavorText: Is he aspiring or inspiring? Make up your mind!

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/a/a7/VO_AT_006_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_006_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/6c/VO_AT_006_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_006_ATTACK_02.wav So. Here's where you're wrong!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/73/VO_AT_006_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_006_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

PRINCE VALANAR.name: Prince Valanar
PRINCE VALANAR.flavorText: Three Princes stand before you. This one devours one after another.

MARK OF SCORN.name: Mark of Scorn
MARK OF SCORN.flavorText: Threat Level who? Mark of Scorn!

DARKGLARE.name: Darkglare
DARKGLARE.flavorText: He's got a dark glare, but he sees crystal clear!

PLAGIARIZE.name: Plagiarize
PLAGIARIZE.flavorText: Copying is just using your resources wisely.

LIFE SENTENCE.name: Life Sentence
LIFE SENTENCE.flavorText: Also sentenced to laugh and love.

TOOTH OF NEFARIAN.name: Tooth of Nefarian
TOOTH OF NEFARIAN.flavorText: Nefarian: Lord of Blackrock, creator of the chromatic dragonflight, victim of several root canals.

HARMONIC DISCO.name: Harmonic Disco
HARMONIC DISCO.flavorText: "Worry not, festival patrons! A disco is hardly any means for panic!"

LORD BAROV.name: Lord Barov
LORD BAROV.flavorText: Alexei Barov stayed at Scholomance despite leasing it to Kel’Thuzad. He says it’s for "supervision."

GORGONZORMU.name: Gorgonzormu
GORGONZORMU.flavorText: Don't remove this from your deck or else you'll be cutting the cheese.

BATTLEFIELD NECROMANCER.name: Battlefield Necromancer
BATTLEFIELD NECROMANCER.flavorText: Coming soon: the Hand Necromancer and the Deck Necromancer.

MOLTEN BLADE.name: Molten Blade
MOLTEN BLADE.flavorText: It’s a sword! It’s a knife! It’s a swizzle-stick!

GATHER YOUR PARTY.name: Gather Your Party
GATHER YOUR PARTY.flavorText: Thrilling adventure! Danger guaranteed! Loot uncertain! Death optional! Who’s with me?

AVIAN WATCHER.name: Avian Watcher
AVIAN WATCHER.flavorText: He mostly watches light romantic comedies.

IMP MASTER.name: Imp Master
IMP MASTER.flavorText: She would enjoy the job a lot more if she just could get the imps to QUIT BITING HER.

SEN'JIN SHIELDMASTA.name: Sen'jin Shieldmasta
SEN'JIN SHIELDMASTA.flavorText: Sen'jin Village is nice, if you like trolls and dust.

ANDUIN'S GIFT.name: Anduin's Gift
ANDUIN'S GIFT.flavorText: "My council assures me this is the perfect gift! Not that they needed to tell me. I know what's in there." -Anduin

FURIOUS ETTIN.name: Furious Ettin
FURIOUS ETTIN.flavorText: One head is a morning person. The other head hates morning people.

MUCK POOLS.name: Muck Pools
MUCK POOLS.flavorText: Making a dredger is easier than you'd think. You don't need to worry about mucking it up!

SPIRIT OF THE LYNX.name: Spirit of the Lynx
SPIRIT OF THE LYNX.flavorText: Much of this shrine’s power lies in the can-opener noise it makes.

MIND CONTROL TECH.name: Mind Control Tech
MIND CONTROL TECH.flavorText: Mind Control technology is getting better, but that's not saying much.

ARROGANT CRUSADER.name: Arrogant Crusader
ARROGANT CRUSADER.flavorText: To be honest, he was kind of a jerk even BEFORE he was bitten by that ghoul.

MERITHRA.name: Merithra
MERITHRA.flavorText: The green dragon flight was always a Merithracracy.

BETRAYAL.name: Betrayal
BETRAYAL.flavorText: Everyone has a price. Gnomes, for example, can be persuaded by stuffed animals and small amounts of chocolate.

EQUALITY.name: Equality
EQUALITY.flavorText: We are all special unique snowflakes... with 1 Health.

DEMONFIRE.name: Demonfire
DEMONFIRE.flavorText: Demonfire is like regular fire except for IT NEVER STOPS BURNING HELLLPPP

MISMATCHED FOSSILS.name: Mismatched Fossils
MISMATCHED FOSSILS.flavorText: Whoever put these fossils together must be really careless.

FEAST AND FAMINE.name: Feast and Famine
FEAST AND FAMINE.flavorText: Please sir, may I have some armor?

THE SKELETON KNIGHT.name: The Skeleton Knight
THE SKELETON KNIGHT.flavorText: Apparently it really was just a flesh wound.

STOWAWAY.name: Stowaway
STOWAWAY.flavorText: Cut him a break. Even economy class tickets are pretty expensive these days.

GOBLIN BOMB.name: Goblin Bomb
GOBLIN BOMB.flavorText: They're Dr. Boom's babies. His baby boomers.

UN'GORO BROCHURE.name: Un'Goro Brochure
UN'GORO BROCHURE.flavorText: Our Un'Goro package includes the Tortollan travel tour! Just don't mind the Devilsaurs.

SNEED'S OLD SHREDDER.name: Sneed's Old Shredder
SNEED'S OLD SHREDDER.flavorText: When Sneed was defeated in the Deadmines, his shredder was sold at auction to an anonymous buyer. (Probably Hogger.)

BURNING BLADE ACOLYTE.name: Burning Blade Acolyte
BURNING BLADE ACOLYTE.flavorText: Wields a disappointingly normal looking blade.

EXARCH OTHAAR.name: Exarch Othaar
EXARCH OTHAAR.flavorText: The temptation of limitless knowledge led some Eredar to join the Burning Legion. In the Sha’tari Draenei, the study of everything lives on.

GLINDA CROWSKIN.name: Glinda Crowskin
GLINDA CROWSKIN.flavorText: Summon an unlimited* number of minions!** *Six **Wisps

ARMORED GOON.name: Armored Goon
ARMORED GOON.flavorText: Armored except for non-critical areas, such as the head, torso, fists and thighs.

AZSHARAN MOONCATCHER.name: Azsharan Mooncatcher
AZSHARAN MOONCATCHER.flavorText: The light of Elune faded from the ruins of Zin-Azshari, but not its treasures.

SUDDEN BETRAYAL.name: Sudden Betrayal
SUDDEN BETRAYAL.flavorText: You thought he was your bro-bold, but turns out he's your foe-bold.

REMIXED TOTEMCARVER.name: Remixed Totemcarver
REMIXED TOTEMCARVER.flavorText: Music always sounds better on old, wooden speakers.

SERVANT OF YOGG-SARON.name: Servant of Yogg-Saron
SERVANT OF YOGG-SARON.flavorText: Yogg-Saron always likes to complain about how he has too many servants and there are too many mouths to feed.

FORBIDDEN WORDS.name: Forbidden Words
FORBIDDEN WORDS.flavorText: Please confirm your age before reading this flavor text.

NORTHERN NAVIGATION.name: Northern Navigation
NORTHERN NAVIGATION.flavorText: Leads directly to Greatfather Winter's workshop.

BOOMMASTER FLARK.name: Boommaster Flark
BOOMMASTER FLARK.flavorText: Every good plan requires a bit of patience. And a lot of explosives.

SLUDGE SLURPER.name: Sludge Slurper
SLUDGE SLURPER.flavorText: You can't stop slurping this delicious sludge!

HEAVY PLATE.name: Heavy Plate
HEAVY PLATE.flavorText: "You asked for unbendable, unwavering armor–I don't see why you're upset."

LESSER EMERALD SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Emerald Spellstone
LESSER EMERALD SPELLSTONE.flavorText: An emerald stone for Tauren hands Who sought its strength to save their lands Their tribes now lost, their rage released Who’s hunting now? And who’s the beast?

RECORD SCRATCHER.name: Record Scratcher
RECORD SCRATCHER.flavorText: A Rogue's favorite audio sample is an orchestral stab.

SILVERMOON ARCANIST.name: Silvermoon Arcanist
SILVERMOON ARCANIST.flavorText: This turn only, I'm something of an Arcanist myself.

SANCTUM SPELLBENDER.name: Sanctum Spellbender
SANCTUM SPELLBENDER.flavorText: "I'll take that... and that... aaand that."

ASPHYXIATE.name: Asphyxiate
ASPHYXIATE.flavorText: I find your abundance of Attack disturbing.

STOLEN GOODS.name: Stolen Goods
STOLEN GOODS.flavorText: It fell off a kodo, I promise!

PACK THE HOUSE.name: Pack the House
PACK THE HOUSE.flavorText: How many Pack the Houses would a pack house if a pack could house Pack the House?

HOLY WATER.name: Holy Water
HOLY WATER.flavorText: For a healthier option, try Holy Water: Zero.

EBON DRAGONSMITH.name: Ebon Dragonsmith
EBON DRAGONSMITH.flavorText: Having a furnace-mouth is really handy for a blacksmith.

COUNTESS ASHMORE.name: Countess Ashmore
COUNTESS ASHMORE.flavorText: "1 minion… ah, ah, ah! 2 minions… ah, ah, ah! 3 minions… ah, ah, ah!"

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/1/1c/VO_GIL_578_Female_BloodElf_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_GIL_578_Female_BloodElf_Play_01.wav My power over you grows stronger yet.

CULT NEOPHYTE.name: Cult Neophyte
CULT NEOPHYTE.flavorText: Make a new recruit's deficiencies your efficiencies.

CELESTIAL DREAMER.name: Celestial Dreamer
CELESTIAL DREAMER.flavorText: If you think her job is easy, YOU try falling asleep on cue.

COMMANDER SIVARA.name: Commander Sivara
COMMANDER SIVARA.flavorText: With six legs, gills, and an impressive array of magic, Sivara is an all-terrain-spellcaster.

FOAMRENDER.name: Foamrender
FOAMRENDER.flavorText: No honey, we have Shadowmourne at home.

PLAGUE SCIENTIST.name: Plague Scientist
PLAGUE SCIENTIST.flavorText: The excruciating pain means it's working!

BOLVAR FORDRAGON.name: Bolvar Fordragon
