BOLVAR FORDRAGON.flavorText: Spoiler alert: Bolvar gets melted and then sits on an ice throne and everyone forgets about him.

SANGUINE DEPTHS.name: Sanguine Depths
SANGUINE DEPTHS.flavorText: There may not be any skeletons in the closets at Castle Nathria, but there sure are souls in the basement.

WAXMANCY.name: Waxmancy
WAXMANCY.flavorText: The waxmancer works with flame and form, giving shape to figures warm. Some think he's a crazy creeper, but crafting minions is simply cheaper.

ARKONITE DEFENSE CRYSTAL.name: Arkonite Defense Crystal
ARKONITE DEFENSE CRYSTAL.flavorText: I was just asking if that's what you wanted your Starship to look like, there's no need to get defensive.

GLAIVEZOOKA.name: Glaivezooka
GLAIVEZOOKA.flavorText: For the times when a regular bazooka just isn't enough.

SUNBORNE VAL'KYR.name: Sunborne Val'kyr
SUNBORNE VAL'KYR.flavorText: Bring valor to Odyn's halls, Champion!

OVERPLANNER.name: Overplanner
OVERPLANNER.flavorText: "Hey kids, what do you call an arrogant skydiving pirate? A condescending con descending!"

TRAIL MIX.name: Trail Mix
TRAIL MIX.flavorText: You can tell this is an escapist fantasy game because there are no raisins.

JUNGLE PANTHER.name: Jungle Panther
JUNGLE PANTHER.flavorText: Stranglethorn is a beautiful place to visit, but you wouldn't want to live there.

GERMINATION.name: Germination
GERMINATION.flavorText: I regret asking how sporelings are made.

TYR'S TEARS.name: Tyr's Tears
TYR'S TEARS.flavorText: Liek this if u cri evertim

STAMPEDING KODO.name: Stampeding Kodo
STAMPEDING KODO.flavorText: This Kodo is so big that he can stampede by himself.

INKMASTER SOLIA.name: Inkmaster Solia
INKMASTER SOLIA.flavorText: Solia marks the Kabal with intricate tattoos that grant immense power. Also it makes it harder for other gangs to recruit from their numbers. BACK OFF, GOONS.

FABLE STABLEHAND.name: Fable Stablehand
FABLE STABLEHAND.flavorText: She took over the job when Feeble Steeblehand left.

BLOODMAGE THALNOS.name: Bloodmage Thalnos
BLOODMAGE THALNOS.flavorText: He's in charge of the Annual Scarlet Monastery Blood Drive!

SALTY DOG.name: Salty Dog
SALTY DOG.flavorText: He's recently recovered from being a "scurvy dog."

IMMOLATE.name: Immolate
IMMOLATE.flavorText: "Well if you cared about those cards so much, why didn't you play them?"

COUNTERFEIT BLADE.name: Counterfeit Blade
COUNTERFEIT BLADE.flavorText: Don't worry, the blade retracts into the handle!

UNEXPECTED RESULTS.name: Unexpected Results
UNEXPECTED RESULTS.flavorText: Sometimes science is more art than science. A lot of people don’t get that.

CRYSTALLIZER.name: Crystallizer
CRYSTALLIZER.flavorText: This elf's winning the arms race.

BUILD A SNOWMAN.name: Build a Snowman
BUILD A SNOWMAN.flavorText: This is the coolest spell once you get it rolling.

UNDERKING.name: Underking
UNDERKING.flavorText: "Behold, the Underking! I'm always beneath you, but nothing is beneath me! I hereby declare war on peace and happiness! Soon, all will tremble before me!"

BRAIN FREEZE.name: Brain Freeze
BRAIN FREEZE.flavorText: "The professor called on me, and I totally froze!"

CREATION PROTOCOL.name: Creation Protocol
CREATION PROTOCOL.flavorText: If you want the destruction protocol, just go in reverse.

RUSTSWORN INITIATE.name: Rustsworn Initiate
RUSTSWORN INITIATE.flavorText: The Rusted Legion's training leaves a little to be desired. He hasn't even had a tetanus shot yet!

DEATHMATCH PAVILION.name: Deathmatch Pavilion
DEATHMATCH PAVILION.flavorText: Worth it for the stuffed toy at the end.

OBSIDIAN SHARD.name: Obsidian Shard
OBSIDIAN SHARD.flavorText: You know you’re a Rogue when a sharp rock makes you go “Ooh! Dagger!”

Y'SHAARJ, RAGE UNBOUND.name: Y'Shaarj, Rage Unbound
Y'SHAARJ, RAGE UNBOUND.flavorText: When he's working out, he binds all that rage back into a ponytail.

DRAGON SOUL.name: Dragon Soul
DRAGON SOUL.flavorText: Crafted by Deathwing's goblin horde, but the dragon added the rainbow sparkles himself.

SPAWNPOOL FORAGER.name: Spawnpool Forager
SPAWNPOOL FORAGER.flavorText: Putting food on the table requires persistence, enthusiasm, and the finest murloc Gloves of Foraging.

FLIGHT OF THE BRONZE.name: Flight of the Bronze
FLIGHT OF THE BRONZE.flavorText: You're telling me Hearthstone will make a 1 Mana 5/5 with Taunt? Maybe when bronze flies!

IMPLOYEE OF THE MONTH.name: Imployee of the Month
IMPLOYEE OF THE MONTH.flavorText: Imployee of the Month, 666 months running.

SIR FINLEY OF THE SANDS.name: Sir Finley of the Sands
SIR FINLEY OF THE SANDS.flavorText: "The sands shall be my sea! And this scarab shall be my, er, strange and wriggly boat!"

SHADOWY FIGURE.name: Shadowy Figure
SHADOWY FIGURE.flavorText: Terrible at shadow puppets: “This is… a tentacle! And this is… two tentacles!”

DISCOVERY OF MAGIC.name: Discovery of Magic
DISCOVERY OF MAGIC.flavorText: It's in a book, just take a look!

STORMWIND KNIGHT.name: Stormwind Knight
STORMWIND KNIGHT.flavorText: They're still embarrassed about "The Deathwing Incident".

FROST NOVA.name: Frost Nova
FROST NOVA.flavorText: Hey man, that's cold. Literally and metaphorically.

AZSHARAN SCROLL.name: Azsharan Scroll
AZSHARAN SCROLL.flavorText: Kids these days are always scrolling on their tomes.

HOWLING BLAST.name: Howling Blast
HOWLING BLAST.flavorText: For Death Knights, yelling really loudly is a valid attack strategy.

THE RAT KING.name: The Rat King
THE RAT KING.flavorText: "I'm the giant rat that makes all of da rules!"

MAD BOMBER.name: Mad Bomber
MAD BOMBER.flavorText: He's not really all that crazy, he is just not as careful with explosives as he should be.

MALKOROK.name: Malkorok
MALKOROK.flavorText: Garrosh's best buddy. It's true. Look it up.

GIGAFIN.name: Gigafin
GIGAFIN.flavorText: How much storage does Gigafin's Maw have? About a giga bite.

RICOCHET SHOT.name: Ricochet Shot
RICOCHET SHOT.flavorText: Simple geometry? Actually, I find it's quite complex.

MARUUT STONEBINDER.name: Maruut Stonebinder
MARUUT STONEBINDER.flavorText: Savior of the World Pillar, Maruut valiantly fought the Twilight's Hammer to aid Therazane against the Cataclysm.

LIFEBINDER'S GIFT.name: Lifebinder's Gift
LIFEBINDER'S GIFT.flavorText: Everyone's investing in Nature spells these days, but that bubble is about to burst.

UNEARTHED RAPTOR.name: Unearthed Raptor
UNEARTHED RAPTOR.flavorText: Still hunting for the ones who earthed him.

RITE OF ATROCITY.name: Rite of Atrocity
RITE OF ATROCITY.flavorText: Turns out 2 Atrocities do make a Rite!

PIT FIGHTER.name: Pit Fighter
PIT FIGHTER.flavorText: What did the pits ever do to you?

WOLPERTINGER.name: Wolpertinger
WOLPERTINGER.flavorText: Scholomance student Brewfest prank gone awry.

ELISE, BADLANDS SAVIOR.name: Elise, Badlands Savior
ELISE, BADLANDS SAVIOR.flavorText: From the library to the field, she's proved herself to be a leading intellectual.

KODOHIDE DRUMKIT.name: Kodohide Drumkit
KODOHIDE DRUMKIT.flavorText: Stolen from a druidic drum circle, now destined to make music that is actually good.

RAGNAROS, LIGHTLORD.name: Ragnaros, Lightlord
RAGNAROS, LIGHTLORD.flavorText: What happens when you try and corrupt a corrupted firelord? DOUBLE NEGATIVE, INSECT!

DEADLINE.name: Deadline
DEADLINE.flavorText: For all you procrastinators out there, don't worry. That's why we added Tradeable.

FRAMESTER.name: Framester
FRAMESTER.flavorText: "Who put these beans in my pocket?!" -Man With Beans in Pocket

TWISTING NETHER.name: Twisting Nether
TWISTING NETHER.flavorText: The Twisting Nether is a formless place of magic and illusion and destroyed minions.

SHARD OF THE NAARU.name: Shard of the Naaru
SHARD OF THE NAARU.flavorText: Fell from the sky, huh? I'll give you ten gold.

SUNFIRE SMITHING.name: Sunfire Smithing
SUNFIRE SMITHING.flavorText: It's simple, just throw it into the sun.

CRYSTAL POWER.name: Crystal Power
CRYSTAL POWER.flavorText: Often used as healing crystals, but also good for throwing at people.

SERENA BLOODFEATHER.name: Serena Bloodfeather
SERENA BLOODFEATHER.flavorText: She’s really into networking! After all, she’s introduced countless low-level Horde players to the Spirit Healer.

MIMIRON'S HEAD.name: Mimiron's Head
MIMIRON'S HEAD.flavorText: Do not push the big red button!

SUSPICIOUS PEDDLER.name: Suspicious Peddler
SUSPICIOUS PEDDLER.flavorText: The best snake oil this side of Azeroth.

THE LIGHT! IT BURNS!.name: The Light! It Burns!
THE LIGHT! IT BURNS!.flavorText: Wait, if you're over there, then who's messing with the lights?!

BACKROOM BOUNCER.name: Backroom Bouncer
BACKROOM BOUNCER.flavorText: "WHY ARE YOU IN THE BACK ROOM? WHO IS WATCHING THE FRONT?!"

AMBASSADOR FAELIN.name: Ambassador Faelin
AMBASSADOR FAELIN.flavorText: For thousands of years, Faelin has longed to return to his homeland. Will Zin-Azshari be as he hopes, or are the secrets of the deep better left forgotten?

FROSTFIN CHOMPER.name: Frostfin Chomper
FROSTFIN CHOMPER.flavorText: If you want good sushi, it is important to always keep your murlocs on ice.

MIRROR IMAGE.name: Mirror Image
MIRROR IMAGE.flavorText: Oh hey it's Mirror Image! !egamI rorriM s'ti yeh hO

VALDRIS FELGORGE.name: Valdris Felgorge
VALDRIS FELGORGE.flavorText: I don't mean to pry, but you don't by chance happen to have six fingers on both of your hands?

ANONYMOUS INFORMANT.name: Anonymous Informant
ANONYMOUS INFORMANT.flavorText: It turns out she wasn't so great at keeping secrets after all.

WANDMAKER.name: Wandmaker
WANDMAKER.flavorText: She creates incredibly affordable wands of all shapes and sizes. But not owls. The owl is all-natural.

USHER OF SOULS.name: Usher of Souls
USHER OF SOULS.flavorText: Nothing unburdens your soul like a good ushing!

STAMPEDE.name: Stampede
STAMPEDE.flavorText: Many hunters long for the pitter-patter of enormous feet.

ARCANE MISSILES.name: Arcane Missiles
ARCANE MISSILES.flavorText: You'd think you'd be able to control your missiles a little better since you're a powerful mage and all.

SUNREAVER WARMAGE.name: Sunreaver Warmage
SUNREAVER WARMAGE.flavorText: What, did you expect the Sunreavers to be coldages?

NAGA GIANT.name: Naga Giant
NAGA GIANT.flavorText: He might be giant, but he’s still a couple thousand protein shakes away from competing in the Colossal Wrestling Championship.

DEAFEN.name: Deafen
DEAFEN.flavorText: Hey, Volsat, we can't hear you. You're on mute.

DISRUPTIVE SPELLBREAKER.name: Disruptive Spellbreaker
DISRUPTIVE SPELLBREAKER.flavorText: WHO IS THE BLOOD ELVES' DENTIST?

ALDOR PEACEKEEPER.name: Aldor Peacekeeper
ALDOR PEACEKEEPER.flavorText: The Aldor hate two things: the Scryers and smooth jazz.

DEVOURER OF SOULS.name: Devourer of Souls
DEVOURER OF SOULS.flavorText: Winner of the Scourge's annual funnel cake devouring contest 12 years running.

SHADOW VISIONS.name: Shadow Visions
SHADOW VISIONS.flavorText: This one’s a bird. And here’s a bunny!

CRABATOA.name: Crabatoa
CRABATOA.flavorText: This giant crab loves to sink entire naval fleets, but it'll settle for a single dinghy in a pinch.

SEA REAVER.name: Sea Reaver
SEA REAVER.flavorText: A little better than Sea Minus Reaver.

FIENDISH RITES.name: Fiendish Rites
FIENDISH RITES.flavorText: "You have the right to sacrifice an ally. If you do not have an ally, then one will be sacrificed for you."

PINT-SIZED SUMMONER.name: Pint-Sized Summoner
PINT-SIZED SUMMONER.flavorText: She's quite jealous of the Gallon-Sized Summoner.

LIGHTMAW NETHERDRAKE.name: Lightmaw Netherdrake
LIGHTMAW NETHERDRAKE.flavorText: Do you think it's a glass half full kind of Netherdrake, or a glass half empty, inescapable void kind of Netherdrake?

BARON GEDDON.name: Baron Geddon
BARON GEDDON.flavorText: Baron Geddon was Ragnaros's foremost lieutenant, until he got FIRED.

ACADEMIC ESPIONAGE.name: Academic Espionage
ACADEMIC ESPIONAGE.flavorText: The tenth Pyroblast really felt like overkill.

TRAINING SESSION.name: Training Session
TRAINING SESSION.flavorText: Instructor Razuvious's training turns the Scourge's Death Knights into hardened killing machines. His merciless routines focus on breaking down his underlings until they build up a resistance to his strength.

LIGHTNING BREATH.name: Lightning Breath
LIGHTNING BREATH.flavorText: Recipe: One dragon, four wool socks, thick shag carpet.

RUNIC ADORNMENT.name: Runic Adornment
RUNIC ADORNMENT.flavorText: Rune, rune on the wall, who's the greenest of them all?

CLOAKSCALE CHEMIST.name: Cloakscale Chemist
CLOAKSCALE CHEMIST.flavorText: Her suit was fitted using a scale model.

JAINA'S GIFT.name: Jaina's Gift
JAINA'S GIFT.flavorText: "On this day, my magic will bring us together." -Jaina

GIANT MASTODON.name: Giant Mastodon
GIANT MASTODON.flavorText: Still salty about it not being the "Year of the Mastodon."

LIGHT'S JUSTICE.name: Light's Justice
LIGHT'S JUSTICE.flavorText: Prince Malchezaar was a collector of rare weapons. He'd animate them and have them dance for him.

DECK OF LUNACY.name: Deck of Lunacy
DECK OF LUNACY.flavorText: Voted "Most Lunacy" in Madness Monthly magazine.

BARREL ROLL.name: Barrel Roll
BARREL ROLL.flavorText: "We're not even close to Draenor, just do the trick! It'll be fiiiine!"

SNAKEBITE.name: Snakebite
SNAKEBITE.flavorText: Don't look her in the eyes or you'll turn to ROCK!

DARK PHARAOH TEKAHN.name: Dark Pharaoh Tekahn
DARK PHARAOH TEKAHN.flavorText: He'll get that League of Explorers and their little murloc too!

SANITIZE.name: Sanitize
SANITIZE.flavorText: We were originally going to make a joke about a popular streamer, but one of our designers is a total germaphobe.

EARTHQUAKE.name: Earthquake
EARTHQUAKE.flavorText: Shake it, sh-sh-sh-shake it like a Kalimdor fissure.

SPIRIT OF THE TIDES.name: Spirit of the Tides
SPIRIT OF THE TIDES.flavorText: Cleans the ocean better than any store-brand competitor - guaranteed or your Mana back!

BEACHED WHALE.name: Beached Whale
BEACHED WHALE.flavorText: Call me Illidan. Some years ago — never mind how long precisely — having little or no gold in my purse, and nothing particular to interest me on Azeroth, I thought I would fly about a little and see the demony part of the world…

MINECART CRUISER.name: Minecart Cruiser
MINECART CRUISER.flavorText: Where are you drivin', Minecart Cruiser? Where is your bounty, fortune, and fame?

SCRAPBOOKING STUDENT.name: Scrapbooking Student
SCRAPBOOKING STUDENT.flavorText: "…and this is the time I rode a dinosaur, and this is the time that I helped solve a murder, and this is the time I got corrupted by the Old Gods..."

GIFTS OF AZSHARA.name: Gifts of Azshara
GIFTS OF AZSHARA.flavorText: Barber: What do you want? Naga: You ever have a thirst for arcane power? Barber: Say no more.

VIVID SPORES.name: Vivid Spores
VIVID SPORES.flavorText: Hey man, I just feel like... death is just a construct of our imaginations, ya know?

MALEVOLENT STRIKE.name: Malevolent Strike
MALEVOLENT STRIKE.flavorText: "I don't know how those got in there, but I'm blaming you two."

STAMPEDING ROAR.name: Stampeding Roar
STAMPEDING ROAR.flavorText: The Gurubashi Arena has an extremely permissive policy on pets in the workplace.

BARRICADE.name: Barricade
BARRICADE.flavorText: The Alliance and Horde join forces to enforce the fire safety capacity.

GAME MASTER.name: Game Master
GAME MASTER.flavorText: "You hear the mrgrgls of angry murlocs approaching. Roll initiative!"

OVERDRAFT.name: Overdraft
OVERDRAFT.flavorText: Wait. It costs mana to be out of mana?!

WHIRLING COMBATANT.name: Whirling Combatant
WHIRLING COMBATANT.flavorText: It's called capoeira! And yes, it is dangerous!

INFINITIZE THE MAXITUDE.name: Infinitize the Maxitude
INFINITIZE THE MAXITUDE.flavorText: When your music is instrumental, it doesn't matter if the words make no sense.

BARNES.name: Barnes
BARNES.flavorText: He used to play every part, until Moroes confiscated his Orb of Deception.

DUN BALDAR BRIDGE.name: Dun Baldar Bridge
DUN BALDAR BRIDGE.flavorText: At least there's no fall damage in Hearthstone.

HOLY CHAMPION.name: Holy Champion
HOLY CHAMPION.flavorText: She really likes seeing people get better. That's why she hurts them in the first place.

GOREHOWL.name: Gorehowl
GOREHOWL.flavorText: Grommash Hellscream's famous axe. Somehow this ended up in Prince Malchezaar's possession. Quite the mystery!

PARTNER IN CRIME.name: Partner in Crime
PARTNER IN CRIME.flavorText: "You know what we need? Some rope." "That's stupid. Name one thing you'd need a rope for."

RUNED MITHRIL ROD.name: Runed Mithril Rod
RUNED MITHRIL ROD.flavorText: "Please, I need these greens to disenchant them." —Every Enchanter Ever

ALL YOU CAN EAT.name: All You Can Eat
ALL YOU CAN EAT.flavorText: Never design cards when you're hungry.

TOTEMIC SURGE.name: Totemic Surge
TOTEMIC SURGE.flavorText: It's not really advanced shamanic magic, you just draw nasty eyebrows on them.

BELLOWING FLAMES.name: Bellowing Flames
BELLOWING FLAMES.flavorText: Too much bellowing. Not enough flames.

BARKSHIELD SENTINEL.name: Barkshield Sentinel
BARKSHIELD SENTINEL.flavorText: His bite is worse than his bark.

SHIMMERFLY.name: Shimmerfly
SHIMMERFLY.flavorText: Plenty of buzz around this card.

FIND THE IMPOSTER.name: Find the Imposter
FIND THE IMPOSTER.flavorText: My money is on the evil advisor to the king.

THE LEVIATHAN.name: The Leviathan
THE LEVIATHAN.flavorText: Built by Ini Stormcoil, this massive vessel can withstand almost anything you put it through... although she would prefer you didn't!

IMPFERNO.name: Impferno
IMPFERNO.flavorText: Imps don't get mad when you set them on fire. They think it's cozy.

FORLORN STALKER.name: Forlorn Stalker
FORLORN STALKER.flavorText: He's going to leave the dying up to you, if that's cool.

VOID VIRTUOSO.name: Void Virtuoso
VOID VIRTUOSO.flavorText: That is one interesting dress code.

LURKER.name: Lurker
LURKER.flavorText: Never typed in chat. Subscribed for 40 months. The perfect viewer.

CURSE OF RAFAAM.name: Curse of Rafaam
CURSE OF RAFAAM.flavorText: This is what happens when Rafaam stubs his toe unexpectedly.

HARMONIC MOOD.name: Harmonic Mood
HARMONIC MOOD.flavorText: ROYGBive your hero +2 Attack this turn.

THE BEAST.name: The Beast
THE BEAST.flavorText: He lives in Blackrock Mountain. He eats Gnomes. That's pretty much it.

KABAL LACKEY.name: Kabal Lackey
KABAL LACKEY.flavorText: I'll tell you one thing he doesn't lack: GUMPTION.

WILD GROWTH.name: Wild Growth
WILD GROWTH.flavorText: Grow your own mana crystals with this Mana Crystal Growth Kit, only 39.99!

NERUBIAN EGG.name: Nerubian Egg
NERUBIAN EGG.flavorText: Eggs are a good source of protein and Nerubians.

A LIGHT IN THE DARKNESS.name: A Light in the Darkness
A LIGHT IN THE DARKNESS.flavorText: Wait, how can you have a light in the dark? If you turn on a light while it’s dark, doesn’t that mean it’s no longer dark?

RAZORSCALE.name: Razorscale
RAZORSCALE.flavorText: A razorscale, razormane, and razorclaw walk into the tavern.

ASTALOR BLOODSWORN.name: Astalor Bloodsworn
ASTALOR BLOODSWORN.flavorText: I hear his third phase is even more intense.

CARELESS CRAFTER.name: Careless Crafter
CARELESS CRAFTER.flavorText: How about YOU try folding paper with only three fingers!?

OASIS OUTLAWS.name: Oasis Outlaws
OASIS OUTLAWS.flavorText: With their oasis polluted by the Bloodrock Mining Company, Snake Eyes has set aside her differences with the outlaws of the Badlands to put an end to Bloodrock's operation.

LIFEWEAVER.name: Lifeweaver
LIFEWEAVER.flavorText: Lifeweaving is all well and good until it's time to cut the thread.

MORTUARY MACHINE.name: Mortuary Machine
MORTUARY MACHINE.flavorText: The ankle bone's connected to the shin bone. The knuckle bone's connected to the... eh, it'll be fine.

MASS DISPEL.name: Mass Dispel
MASS DISPEL.flavorText: It dispels buffs, powers, hopes, and dreams.

PRESSURE PLATE.name: Pressure Plate
PRESSURE PLATE.flavorText: The appropriate dishware for stressful situations.

IREBOUND BRUTE.name: Irebound Brute
IREBOUND BRUTE.flavorText: "You don't understand… ogres are an untapped market for vengeance and hatred!"

FEL FISSURE.name: Fel Fissure
FEL FISSURE.flavorText: This will clear the board, I'm fisSURE of it!

COSMIC PHENOMENON.name: Cosmic Phenomenon
COSMIC PHENOMENON.flavorText: Which one you ask? Uhh, all of them.

RODENT NEST.name: Rodent Nest
RODENT NEST.flavorText: Pig sty? No, this is a rat's nest.

LESSER PEARL SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Pearl Spellstone
LESSER PEARL SPELLSTONE.flavorText: In ages old, when Ancients broke Azari of the Legion spoke To tempt the mortals: gems of power The weak succumbed, their souls devoured.

NAJAK HEXXEN.name: Najak Hexxen
NAJAK HEXXEN.flavorText: "I've got friends on the other side... of the battlefield."

RIFTCLEAVER.name: Riftcleaver
RIFTCLEAVER.flavorText: Brings you face to face with your destructive impulses.

ZOLA THE GORGON.name: Zola the Gorgon
ZOLA THE GORGON.flavorText: Her name seems a bit cheesy.

BOUNTY BOARD.name: Bounty Board
BOUNTY BOARD.flavorText: Reno's desire to be a face known around the Badlands might have backfired a little bit.

SHADOW WORD: DEVOUR.name: Shadow Word: Devour
SHADOW WORD: DEVOUR.flavorText: Devouring souls is like a buffet. You have to take a little bit of everything.

FORBIDDEN SHRINE.name: Forbidden Shrine
FORBIDDEN SHRINE.flavorText: Telling me not to use something just makes me want to use it more.

TEACHER'S PET.name: Teacher's Pet
TEACHER'S PET.flavorText: Really goes the extra mile to get the Hay+.

PRIDE'S FURY.name: Pride's Fury
PRIDE'S FURY.flavorText: Day 4: I think they're starting to suspect.

GARDEN GNOME.name: Garden Gnome
GARDEN GNOME.flavorText: "Greetings, my little shrubs... It's whittlin' time."

STONESPLINTER TROGG.name: Stonesplinter Trogg
STONESPLINTER TROGG.flavorText: The only thing worse than smelling troggs is listening to their poetry.

STONE SENTINEL.name: Stone Sentinel
STONE SENTINEL.flavorText: He and his friends just want to rock out.

GRUUL.name: Gruul
GRUUL.flavorText: He's Gruul "the Dragonkiller". He just wanted to cuddle them… he never meant to…

TIDE POOLS.name: Tide Pools
TIDE POOLS.flavorText: I know they look delicious but do NOT eat them.

PETTING ZOO.name: Petting Zoo
PETTING ZOO.flavorText: Welcome to the petting zoo. DO NOT TOUCH THE ANIMALS.

NEFERSET RITUALIST.name: Neferset Ritualist
NEFERSET RITUALIST.flavorText: The Neferset are great—they'll always make sure their friends are feline fine.

LOST IN THE PARK.name: Lost in the Park
LOST IN THE PARK.flavorText: Mister, have you seen my Archdruid?

FAR SIGHT.name: Far Sight
FAR SIGHT.flavorText: Drek'thar can't see, but he can see. You know what I mean? It's ok if you don't.

VOL'JIN.name: Vol'jin
VOL'JIN.flavorText: Vol'jin is a shadow hunter, which is like a shadow priest except more voodoo.

SPORE HALLUCINATION.name: Spore Hallucination
SPORE HALLUCINATION.flavorText: It's the good kind of hallucination.

HARROWING OX.name: Harrowing Ox
HARROWING OX.flavorText: Dead or alive, you're pulling that plow.

WAVE POOL THRASHER.name: Wave Pool Thrasher
WAVE POOL THRASHER.flavorText: Used to be called Wave Pool Splasher until 'The Incident'.

RAVEN IDOL.name: Raven Idol
RAVEN IDOL.flavorText: Was petrified when it found out it didn't make the cut for Azerothian Idol.

TROGG GEMTOSSER.name: Trogg Gemtosser
TROGG GEMTOSSER.flavorText: Oh no! You're throwing valuable gems at me! Please stop!

SCARLET WEBWEAVER.name: Scarlet Webweaver
SCARLET WEBWEAVER.flavorText: Isn't that nice? The spider made the explorer a sleeping bag!

MAGTHERIDON, UNRELEASED.name: Magtheridon, Unreleased
MAGTHERIDON, UNRELEASED.flavorText: Playing with this card can be penalized with up to a two-year suspension. Please wait until the card is officially released.

GRIMSCALE ORACLE.name: Grimscale Oracle
GRIMSCALE ORACLE.flavorText: These are the brainy murlocs. It turns out that doesn’t mean much.

WOODLAND WONDERS.name: Woodland Wonders
WOODLAND WONDERS.flavorText: Is this a standup fight or another bug hunt?

OGRE MAGI.name: Ogre Magi
OGRE MAGI.flavorText: Training Ogres in the art of spellcasting is a questionable decision.

YOUNG PRIESTESS.name: Young Priestess
YOUNG PRIESTESS.flavorText: She can't wait to learn Power Word: Fortitude Rank 2.

SNOWFALL GUARDIAN.name: Snowfall Guardian
SNOWFALL GUARDIAN.flavorText: You’re finally awake! That fall looked really bad. Demon Hunters? Mercenaries? What are you talking about? Come on, I just unpacked a Golden Moorabi, let’s go build a Freeze Shaman deck.

LOKEN, JAILER OF YOGG-SARON.name: Loken, Jailer of Yogg-Saron
LOKEN, JAILER OF YOGG-SARON.flavorText: Really great at his job! - Yogg-Saron

BRASS ELEMENTAL.name: Brass Elemental
BRASS ELEMENTAL.flavorText: You handle the water spells. It's got the earth, wind, and fire covered.

ZEREK'S CLONING GALLERY.name: Zerek's Cloning Gallery
ZEREK'S CLONING GALLERY.flavorText: Cloning can be a jarring experience.

ARCHMAGE.name: Archmage
ARCHMAGE.flavorText: You earn the title of Archmage when you can destroy anyone who calls you on it.

REINFORCED PLATING.name: Reinforced Plating
REINFORCED PLATING.flavorText: I am become death, destroyer of azerite.

TORTOLLAN TRAVELER.name: Tortollan Traveler
TORTOLLAN TRAVELER.flavorText: Tortolla, preserve my energy for this hike!

SKELETAL SIDEKICK.name: Skeletal Sidekick
SKELETAL SIDEKICK.flavorText: He's got your back. And your arm.

TAR LORD.name: Tar Lord
TAR LORD.flavorText: Tar Lord, man... legendary monster? Aw, forget it.

BLOOD CRUSADER.name: Blood Crusader
BLOOD CRUSADER.flavorText: Defending Silvermoon takes a lot of blood, sweat, tears, and blood.

INKVEIL AMBUSHER.name: Inkveil Ambusher
INKVEIL AMBUSHER.flavorText: You’ve got it wrong. She releases ink when you’re scared.

SPECTRAL KNIGHT.name: Spectral Knight
SPECTRAL KNIGHT.flavorText: What do Faerie Dragons and Spectral Knights have in common? They both love pasta!

SPICE BREAD BAKER.name: Spice Bread Baker
SPICE BREAD BAKER.flavorText: The secret ingredient is love. And a LOT of butter.

OLD MURK-EYE.name: Old Murk-Eye
OLD MURK-EYE.flavorText: He's a legend among murlocs. "Mrghllghghllghg!", they say.

TOURNAMENT MEDIC.name: Tournament Medic
TOURNAMENT MEDIC.flavorText: The medic tournament is less entertaining than the Grand Tournament.

MELTED MAKER.name: Melted Maker
MELTED MAKER.flavorText: Melts what he makes (cheese) and makes a mean melt (grilled cheese).

DAY AT THE FAIRE.name: Day at the Faire
DAY AT THE FAIRE.flavorText: Karl knew he would someday regret that turkey leg.

STAND AGAINST DARKNESS.name: Stand Against Darkness
STAND AGAINST DARKNESS.flavorText: Or if you're too tired, you can just kind of lean against the darkness.

NIGHTBLADE.name: Nightblade
NIGHTBLADE.flavorText: Your face is the place you'd probably least like a dagger, and where rogues are most likely to deliver them.

ILLIDARI FELBLADE.name: Illidari Felblade
ILLIDARI FELBLADE.flavorText: A whirling dervish of demonic devastation.

VOLCANIC LUMBERER.name: Volcanic Lumberer
VOLCANIC LUMBERER.flavorText: The roots, the roots, the roots is on fire!

EXPLODINEER.name: Explodineer
EXPLODINEER.flavorText: Explodineeeer... explodifaaaar... explode whereeeever you aaaaare...

SNEAKY SNAKES.name: Sneaky Snakes
SNEAKY SNAKES.flavorText: You're a sneaky lil snake, aren'tcha?

RELENTLESS PURSUIT.name: Relentless Pursuit
RELENTLESS PURSUIT.flavorText: If you steal a Demon Hunter's corn dog, you'll get what's coming.

BURROW BUSTER.name: Burrow Buster
BURROW BUSTER.flavorText: We almost went with the name "Giant Drill", but then it would've HAD to be an 8/8.

SI:7 INFORMANT.name: SI:7 Informant
SI:7 INFORMANT.flavorText: Sitting in a tavern all day and looking scary is hard work, but somebody has to do it.

SHAN'DO WILDCLAW.name: Shan'do Wildclaw
SHAN'DO WILDCLAW.flavorText: She holds both an academic post and a scratching post.

FLAME JUGGLER.name: Flame Juggler
FLAME JUGGLER.flavorText: At first he liked juggling chain saws, but then he thought, "Flames are better! Because FIRE!"

CHAOTIC TENDRIL.name: Chaotic Tendril
CHAOTIC TENDRIL.flavorText: "So are you good, evil, or neutral?" "Just chaotic."

MALORNE THE WAYWATCHER.name: Malorne the Waywatcher
MALORNE THE WAYWATCHER.flavorText: A figure of legend and myth, Malorne is one of the oldest of the Wild Gods and father to Cenarius himself.

ASTROBIOLOGIST.name: Astrobiologist
ASTROBIOLOGIST.flavorText: Biologists spend a semester abroad. Astrobiologists spend a semester aboard.

SCAVENGING SHIVARRA.name: Scavenging Shivarra
SCAVENGING SHIVARRA.flavorText: Say what you want but finding a matching set of six swords takes commitment.

DEMONIC DYNAMICS.name: Demonic Dynamics
DEMONIC DYNAMICS.flavorText: The Blue Imp Group sure knows how to put on a show!

SNOWBLIND HARPY.name: Snowblind Harpy
SNOWBLIND HARPY.flavorText: Not snowblind; she can spot a level 51 noob over 40 yards away.

BLADED LADY.name: Bladed Lady
BLADED LADY.flavorText: While you were busy learning magic, she studied the blade.

SANCTUM CHANDLER.name: Sanctum Chandler
SANCTUM CHANDLER.flavorText: Has been burning at both ends to keep the place illuminated.

BATTLEPICKAXE.name: Battlepickaxe
BATTLEPICKAXE.flavorText: You can pick your battles, and you can pick your axes, but you can't uh… pick your friends' battlepickaxes?

GRIM HARVEST.name: Grim Harvest
GRIM HARVEST.flavorText: "Muahaha… This year's harvest was quite grim… just how I like it! Because I'm EVIL!"

THIRSTY DRIFTER.name: Thirsty Drifter
THIRSTY DRIFTER.flavorText: Quick! Someone bring her a Manathirst card!

RAID THE DOCKS.name: Raid the Docks
RAID THE DOCKS.flavorText: Winning the annual Ratchet Regatta really went to their heads.

RECOMBOBULATOR.name: Recombobulator
RECOMBOBULATOR.flavorText: For when you didn’t combobulate quite right the first time around.

FLOATING WATCHER.name: Floating Watcher
FLOATING WATCHER.flavorText: "Evil Eye Watcher of Doom" was the original name, but marketing felt it was a bit too aggressive.

CORE RAGER.name: Core Rager
CORE RAGER.flavorText: It takes a special kind of hunter to venture deep into a firey lava pit and convince a monster who lives there to come home and be a cuddly housepet.

TERRORGUARD ESCAPEE.name: Terrorguard Escapee
TERRORGUARD ESCAPEE.flavorText: Poor guy is terrified, look at his faces.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/a/a8/VO_BT_159_Male_Terrorguard_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BT_159_Male_Terrorguard_Play_01.wav I will not be tamed!

WING COMMANDER ICHMAN.name: Wing Commander Ichman
WING COMMANDER ICHMAN.flavorText: “Mulverick, it’s not your flying, it’s your faction.”

CONVICTION (RANK 1).name: Conviction (Rank 1)
CONVICTION (RANK 1).flavorText: It was the strength of Cariel's faith that emboldened the defenders of Northwatch that day. Although the strength of her giant hammer didn’t exactly hurt either.

FACELESS RAGER.name: Faceless Rager
FACELESS RAGER.flavorText: When you need to rage anonymously.

THE BOOMSHIP.name: The Boomship
THE BOOMSHIP.flavorText: Dr. Boom ends his motivational speeches by dropping the mechs.

SILVERLEAF POISON.name: Silverleaf Poison
SILVERLEAF POISON.flavorText: Kazakus has taken to a more direct approach in recent times.

FACELESS BEHEMOTH.name: Faceless Behemoth
FACELESS BEHEMOTH.flavorText: Rejected names: Forty-Foot Faceless, Big ol' No-face, Huge Creature Sans Face, Teddy.

KURTRUS ASHFALLEN.name: Kurtrus Ashfallen
KURTRUS ASHFALLEN.flavorText: Kurtrus fled the Black Temple, abandoning Illidan's cause, to seek revenge against the Dreadlord Anetheron.

Y'SHAARJ, THE DEFILER.name: Y'Shaarj, the Defiler
Y'SHAARJ, THE DEFILER.flavorText: Y'Shaarj made an excellent office intern, doing the copying AND defiling.

CAVALRY HORN.name: Cavalry Horn
CAVALRY HORN.flavorText: The clarion call of the Alliance skipping every objective and going straight to Drek’Thar.

WISP.name: Wisp
WISP.flavorText: If you hit an Eredar Lord with enough Wisps, it will explode. But why?

SAND DRUDGE.name: Sand Drudge
SAND DRUDGE.flavorText: Loves long walks on the beach, raising the dead, and chocolates.

HIGH PRIEST AMET.name: High Priest Amet
HIGH PRIEST AMET.flavorText: All minions are equal, but some minions are more equal than others.

COUNTERSPELL.name: Counterspell
COUNTERSPELL.flavorText: What's the difference between a mage playing with Counterspell and a mage who isn't? The mage who isn't is getting Pyroblasted in the face.

GAHZ'RILLA.name: Gahz'rilla
GAHZ'RILLA.flavorText: The Sen'jin High football team is The Gahz'rillas.

BALL HOG.name: Ball Hog
BALL HOG.flavorText: "There's no hog in team... ANYMORE! I QUIT!"

BATTERHEAD.name: Batterhead
BATTERHEAD.flavorText: When it comes to problem-solving, he always uses his head.

RED CARD.name: Red Card
RED CARD.flavorText: Finally, Demon Hunter has expanded its color palette to TWO colors!

STEGODON.name: Stegodon
STEGODON.flavorText: Level 40 Tortollan Paladins quest to tame a Stegodon. There are no level 41 Tortollan Paladins.

VOLATILE ELEMENTAL.name: Volatile Elemental
VOLATILE ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Currently in an anger management class with Raging Worgen, Grommash Hellscream, and The Angry Chicken. It isn't helping.

SQUALLHUNTER.name: Squallhunter
SQUALLHUNTER.flavorText: "Oh, the weather outside is frightful… But Squallhunter's so delightful! And since we've gone down this road--overload, overload, overload!"

DISPATCH KODO.name: Dispatch Kodo
DISPATCH KODO.flavorText: "Crime reported at First Bank of Gadgetzan. Huge quantities of Jade being carried away by what looks like a bunch of Hozen. Kodo 77 can you make it over there now?"

WAR MASTER VOONE.name: War Master Voone
WAR MASTER VOONE.flavorText: War Master sounds cooler than Dragon Sitter.

SKULKING GEIST.name: Skulking Geist
SKULKING GEIST.flavorText: It's as though a million Jade Idols cried out, and were suddenly silenced.

SPECTRAL CUTLASS.name: Spectral Cutlass
SPECTRAL CUTLASS.flavorText: So sharp it can cut through a spectral tomato!

INFILTRATOR LILIAN.name: Infiltrator Lilian
INFILTRATOR LILIAN.flavorText: She'll get to the bottom of this even if it kills her. Twice!

ARGUNITE GOLEM.name: Argunite Golem
ARGUNITE GOLEM.flavorText: Golem Bling never really caught on - the fad crumbled after the Cataclysm.

SPIRIT GATHERER.name: Spirit Gatherer
SPIRIT GATHERER.flavorText: They call him the Wisp Whisperer.

WHACK-A-GNOLL.name: Whack-A-Gnoll
WHACK-A-GNOLL.flavorText: Need closure on your Hardcore WoW character dying in Westfall? Step right up!

CUTTHROAT BUCCANEER.name: Cutthroat Buccaneer
CUTTHROAT BUCCANEER.flavorText: In life he worked as a sword swallower.

ONCE UPON A TIME....name: Once Upon a Time...
ONCE UPON A TIME....flavorText: ...There was a humble little squirrel on a quest to defeat an evil dragon. With the help of its earthen friend, it saved the murloc princess from danger. The end.

CATHEDRAL OF ATONEMENT.name: Cathedral of Atonement
CATHEDRAL OF ATONEMENT.flavorText: You'll actually find more than one tonement here.

ANNOY-O-TRON.name: Annoy-o-Tron
ANNOY-O-TRON.flavorText: The inventor of the Annoy-o-Tron was immediately expelled from Tinkerschool, Tinkertown, and was eventually exiled from the Eastern Kingdoms altogether.

ACOLYTE OF PAIN.name: Acolyte of Pain
ACOLYTE OF PAIN.flavorText: He trained when he was younger to be an acolyte of joy, but things didn’t work out like he thought they would.

SPELLBOOK BINDER.name: Spellbook Binder
SPELLBOOK BINDER.flavorText: You're bound to love his work!

ALLEY ARMORSMITH.name: Alley Armorsmith
ALLEY ARMORSMITH.flavorText: The rent is cheap and she passes the savings onto YOU!

CHENVAALA.name: Chenvaala
CHENVAALA.flavorText: Like the Dragon Soul. If dragons had souls of ice.

MOONWELL.name: Moonwell
MOONWELL.flavorText: Everyone always asks what the moonwell is but how come no one ever asks how well the moon is?

MOGOR THE OGRE.name: Mogor the Ogre
MOGOR THE OGRE.flavorText: Mogor helped reopen the Dark Portal once. You know you're in trouble when you have to rely on an ogre.

HOARDING DRAGON.name: Hoarding Dragon
HOARDING DRAGON.flavorText: Keeps his two cents to himself.

DIVINE RAGER.name: Divine Rager
DIVINE RAGER.flavorText: For when you need to rage, rage against the dying of the Light.

AZSHARAN VESSEL.name: Azsharan Vessel
AZSHARAN VESSEL.flavorText: Not even the sturdiest Highborne ship could survive the churning waters of the Sundering.

PARTY FAVOR TOTEM.name: Party Favor Totem
PARTY FAVOR TOTEM.flavorText: It's the gift (totem) that keeps on giving (totems)!

BAKU THE MOONEATER.name: Baku the Mooneater
BAKU THE MOONEATER.flavorText: In her defense, it did look like a cookie.

VEREESA WINDRUNNER.name: Vereesa Windrunner
VEREESA WINDRUNNER.flavorText: Good things come in threes: Windrunner sisters and arrows of Thori'dal.

RECKLESS FLURRY.name: Reckless Flurry
RECKLESS FLURRY.flavorText: Look. Cautious Flurries will only get you so far in life.

MOUNT HYJAL IMPOSTER.name: Mount Hyjal Imposter
MOUNT HYJAL IMPOSTER.flavorText: Among Tyrande's forces, Murozond had planted agents to ensure Archimonde's victory.

SLAM.name: Slam
SLAM.flavorText: "Dun da dun, dun da dun": if you've heard an ogre sing this, it's too late.

MORTAL ERADICATION.name: Mortal Eradication
MORTAL ERADICATION.flavorText: Clearly anything with 6 or more health is immortal. Such as Street Trickster. We are nerfing Street Trickster for lore accuracy.

FARSEER NOBUNDO.name: Farseer Nobundo
FARSEER NOBUNDO.flavorText: "Someone help me! I'm stuck in a net!"

ANIMATED MOONWELL.name: Animated Moonwell
ANIMATED MOONWELL.flavorText: Your spells are sure to make a splash!

MES'ADUNE THE FRACTURED.name: Mes'Adune the Fractured
MES'ADUNE THE FRACTURED.flavorText: Cracking open an elemental with the boys.

BRUTAL ANNIHILAN.name: Brutal Annihilan
BRUTAL ANNIHILAN.flavorText: Sometimes, problems can be solved by throwing everything you've got at it. This is not one of those times.

SYLVANAS WINDRUNNER.name: Sylvanas Windrunner
SYLVANAS WINDRUNNER.flavorText: Sylvanas was turned into the Banshee Queen by Arthas, but he probably should have just killed her because it just pissed her off.

TREACHEROUS TORMENTOR.name: Treacherous Tormentor
TREACHEROUS TORMENTOR.flavorText: He's so mean, he leaves you on red.

BUTTONS.name: Buttons
BUTTONS.flavorText: "I'll give you an arm and a leg for your Flametongue Pin."

DIVINE STRENGTH.name: Divine Strength
DIVINE STRENGTH.flavorText: Every year a few paladins get disqualified from the Westfall weight lifting championship for using Divine Strength.

DISCIPLINARIAN GANDLING.name: Disciplinarian Gandling
DISCIPLINARIAN GANDLING.flavorText: "He doesn’t grade on a curve, but on a sharp spike instead."

SCAVENGING HYENA.name: Scavenging Hyena
SCAVENGING HYENA.flavorText: Hyenas prefer the bones of kodos or windserpents, but they'll eat pretty much anything. Even Brussels sprouts.

THE GLASS KNIGHT.name: The Glass Knight
THE GLASS KNIGHT.flavorText: She seems scary, but she's got a glass jaw.

TORMENTED DREADWING.name: Tormented Dreadwing
TORMENTED DREADWING.flavorText: People say you can't see clearly through corruption, but you have more eyes than ever!

MURLOC TIDECALLER.name: Murloc Tidecaller
MURLOC TIDECALLER.flavorText: This guy gets crazy strong at family reunions.

FRAZZLED FRESHMAN.name: Frazzled Freshman
FRAZZLED FRESHMAN.flavorText: "Late to bed, early to rise, makes a student unable to open her eyes."

CRABRIDER.name: Crabrider
CRABRIDER.flavorText: "Now I'm falling asleep and she's calling a crab…"

PACKAGE DEALER.name: Package Dealer
PACKAGE DEALER.flavorText: I'm always getting my neighbor's mail. And my other neighbor. And my other neighbor. I'm stealing their packages.

ULTRASAUR.name: Ultrasaur
ULTRASAUR.flavorText: Evolved the really long neck to spy on its neighbors.

CROSSROADS GOSSIPER.name: Crossroads Gossiper
CROSSROADS GOSSIPER.flavorText: Not afraid to spill the tea.

HOLLOW ABOMINATION.name: Hollow Abomination
HOLLOW ABOMINATION.flavorText: As soon as you land your first Honorable Kill, trust me, you'll be hooked!

OPERA SOLOIST.name: Opera Soloist
OPERA SOLOIST.flavorText: It ain't over until the imp mother sings.

MUCKBORN SERVANT.name: Muckborn Servant
MUCKBORN SERVANT.flavorText: Party guests never tip as well as the patrons in Bob's tavern.

THE BEAST WITHIN.name: The Beast Within
THE BEAST WITHIN.flavorText: Undoes years of obedience school training.

HALLUCINATION.name: Hallucination
HALLUCINATION.flavorText: "Protoss? In our base? I think you're seeing things."

SHARP-EYED SEEKER.name: Sharp-Eyed Seeker
SHARP-EYED SEEKER.flavorText: If you give it treats, it will give you shiny objects!

WILDWALKER.name: Wildwalker
WILDWALKER.flavorText: She was born to be something. She is just not quite sure what yet...

QUARTZITE CRUSHER.name: Quartzite Crusher
QUARTZITE CRUSHER.flavorText: It's not just a weapon… it's a rock!

MIRACLE SALESMAN.name: Miracle Salesman
MIRACLE SALESMAN.flavorText: "Hey! Hope you’re well. Have you ever wanted to be your own boss?"

ARCANE GIANT.name: Arcane Giant
ARCANE GIANT.flavorText: Claims to be drawn to Karazhan because of the ley lines. Actually, just loves Moroes’ cooking.

WILDPAW GNOLL.name: Wildpaw Gnoll
WILDPAW GNOLL.flavorText: A big fan of four-claw discounts.

SEAL OF LIGHT.name: Seal of Light
SEAL OF LIGHT.flavorText: The walrus of Light restores EIGHT Health.

STONEHEARTH VINDICATOR.name: Stonehearth Vindicator
STONEHEARTH VINDICATOR.flavorText: “True strength comes from within your deck” is a whole lot less inspiring.

DRAGON ROAR.name: Dragon Roar
DRAGON ROAR.flavorText: Not to be confused with Dragon Yodel.

WARDRUID LOTI.name: Wardruid Loti
WARDRUID LOTI.flavorText: “Ravasaur!” “Pretty scary” “…Blammodax!” “Is that a thing?” “SMAXODON!” “….now you’re just making those up.”

GRAVE DEFILER.name: Grave Defiler
GRAVE DEFILER.flavorText: She keeps her Fel spells nice and organized in her defiling cabinet.

VOODOO DOLL.name: Voodoo Doll
VOODOO DOLL.flavorText: "Aww, I love it! It even kinda looks like me."

E.T.C., GOD OF METAL.name: E.T.C., God of Metal
E.T.C., GOD OF METAL.flavorText: There are Old Gods and then there are Rock Gods.

ALARA'SHI.name: Alara'shi
ALARA'SHI.flavorText: It's a bird! It's a plane! It's a bear! It's a felstalker! It's a doomguard! It's an imp!

SWEETENED SNOWFLURRY.name: Sweetened Snowflurry
SWEETENED SNOWFLURRY.flavorText: "You want a piece of me!? Will that be one scoop or two?"

BLOOD KNIGHT.name: Blood Knight
BLOOD KNIGHT.flavorText: The Blood Knights get their holy powers from the Sunwell, which you should NOT bathe in.

PRIESTESS OF FURY.name: Priestess of Fury
PRIESTESS OF FURY.flavorText: Furious that she only has six warglaives. The Sightless Watcher has eight! The fel is always greener on the other side.

FORBIDDEN ANCIENT.name: Forbidden Ancient
FORBIDDEN ANCIENT.flavorText: This Ancient was banned from the local tavern after tucking a 'Dr. Boom' up its sleeve.

BAITED ARROW.name: Baited Arrow
BAITED ARROW.flavorText: The card is common, but the steak is rare.

DUNE SCULPTOR.name: Dune Sculptor
DUNE SCULPTOR.flavorText: Come for the magic show, stay for the sand castles.

FACELESS MANIPULATOR.name: Faceless Manipulator
FACELESS MANIPULATOR.flavorText: The Faceless Ones are servants of Yogg-Saron, and they feed on fear. Right now they are feeding on your fear of accidentally disenchanting all your good cards.

GRAVE RUNE.name: Grave Rune
GRAVE RUNE.flavorText: I'm gravely sorry to rune this.

MAGICAL DOLLHOUSE.name: Magical Dollhouse
MAGICAL DOLLHOUSE.flavorText: Build your own dollhouse in 3 easy steps! 1. Build a castle. 2. Miniaturize it. 3. GLITTER!

FAIRGROUND FOOL.name: Fairground Fool
FAIRGROUND FOOL.flavorText: "What did Illidan say when his rocketeer broke down on the Darkmoon racetrack? YOU ARE NOT REPAIRED!"

SOULCIOLOGIST MALICIA.name: Soulciologist Malicia
SOULCIOLOGIST MALICIA.flavorText: If you value your life, don't call it a "soft science."

PURIFY.name: Purify
PURIFY.flavorText: Even better than a hot shower with vigorous scrubbing!

MADAM GOYA.name: Madam Goya
MADAM GOYA.flavorText: She has set up her Black Market here in Gadgetzan for one purpose, to make a KILLING when Beanie Babies make their inevitable comeback.

SIRE DENATHRIUS.name: Sire Denathrius
SIRE DENATHRIUS.flavorText: History has a way of altering villains so that we can no longer see ourselves in them. Unfortunately for the Venthyr, they all look like Sire Denathrius.

MASTER SWORDSMITH.name: Master Swordsmith
MASTER SWORDSMITH.flavorText: He's currently trying to craft a "flail-axe", but all the other swordsmiths say it can't be done.

INCANTER'S FLOW.name: Incanter's Flow
INCANTER'S FLOW.flavorText: "Gettin' them discounts in bulk amounts, spells can come, and spells can go, castin' costs drop with my sweet, sweet flow."

WOECLEAVER.name: Woecleaver
WOECLEAVER.flavorText: Turn that frown into TWO frowns!

MIRACLE GROWTH.name: Miracle Growth
MIRACLE GROWTH.flavorText: I’ve got NO idea what’s in that fertilizer.

BEARON GLA'SHEAR.name: Bearon Gla'shear
BEARON GLA'SHEAR.flavorText: When you get hit by a royally bad pun, you just have to grin and bear it.

CURSED SOUVENIR.name: Cursed Souvenir
CURSED SOUVENIR.flavorText: Most souvenirs are considered tacky and soulless. This one is certainly not one of those things!

STRENGTH IN NUMBERS.name: Strength in Numbers
STRENGTH IN NUMBERS.flavorText: One minion, two minions... tree minions!

DARKMOON MAGICIAN.name: Darkmoon Magician
DARKMOON MAGICIAN.flavorText: Darkmoon Magicians pull rabbits out of their hats, and wins out of their... hats.

RIN, ORCHESTRATOR OF DOOM.name: Rin, Orchestrator of Doom
RIN, ORCHESTRATOR OF DOOM.flavorText: Rin's orchestra is the best of the best. When your replacement is just one summoning away, you have to play perfectly.

MUTANUS THE DEVOURER.name: Mutanus the Devourer
MUTANUS THE DEVOURER.flavorText: As long as Naralex stays under the blanket, Mutanus can't get him.

POLLUTED HOARDER.name: Polluted Hoarder
POLLUTED HOARDER.flavorText: Roll ‘greed’ OR THIS COULD HAPPEN TO YOU.

SHADOWHOOF SLAYER.name: Shadowhoof Slayer
SHADOWHOOF SLAYER.flavorText: Was a humble Elven Archer before Sargeras got to him.

SWIFTSCALE TRICKSTER.name: Swiftscale Trickster
SWIFTSCALE TRICKSTER.flavorText: If you play your cards fast enough, who's to say how much they cost?

AUCHENAI PHANTASM.name: Auchenai Phantasm
AUCHENAI PHANTASM.flavorText: “Okay kids did everyone remember to heal before we left?”

MIGHT OF MENETHIL.name: Might of Menethil
MIGHT OF MENETHIL.flavorText: Menethil's Might, at night, fights the light, not quite the blight, right?

BLADEMASTER SAMURO.name: Blademaster Samuro
BLADEMASTER SAMURO.flavorText: Artists paint their visions meticulously on canvas. Blademasters paint with, uh, broader strokes.

SPECIMEN CLAW.name: Specimen Claw
SPECIMEN CLAW.flavorText: Great at catching alien species. Not so much their plushies.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/5c/GDB_107_SpecimenClaw_PLay.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ GDB_107_SpecimenClaw_PLay.wav

NERUB'AR WEBLORD.name: Nerub'ar Weblord
NERUB'AR WEBLORD.flavorText: Weblords spend all day making giant trampoline parks.

BOLNER HAMMERBEAK.name: Bolner Hammerbeak
BOLNER HAMMERBEAK.flavorText: Show him how to do something once, and he can do it a thousand times. This turn.

C'THUN.name: C'Thun
C'THUN.flavorText: C'Thun's least favorite Hearthstone card: Eye for an Eye.

voicelines.death:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/4/41/VO_OG_280_Male_OldGod_InPlay_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_OG_280_Male_OldGod_InPlay_01.wav Your minions will abandon you.
  • ▶️ VO_OG_280_Male_OldGod_InPlay_02.wav Death is close.

GNASH.name: Gnash
GNASH.flavorText: It's rude to gnash with your mouth open.

THE BOOGEYMONSTER.name: The Boogeymonster
THE BOOGEYMONSTER.flavorText: Has 20 years of training in classical ballet, but ALLLLLL he ever gets asked to do is boogie.

DISPOSAL ASSISTANT.name: Disposal Assistant
DISPOSAL ASSISTANT.flavorText: A bright green liquid that people say is bad for you... That's either hazardous waste OR a new popular brand of soft drink.

HEARTBREAKER HEDANIS.name: Heartbreaker Hedanis
HEARTBREAKER HEDANIS.flavorText: Hedanis has won over the hearts and minds of millions of fans all over Azeroth! Shadow magic had nothing to do with it - not that you asked or anything.

UNIDENTIFIED MAUL.name: Unidentified Maul
UNIDENTIFIED MAUL.flavorText: When all you have is an unidentified maul, everything else looks like an unidentified nail.

PIP THE POTENT.name: Pip the Potent
PIP THE POTENT.flavorText: One time, I was trying to get Pip's attention to warn her that the dangerous outlaw Cheery Ollie, who also goes by just 'O', was headed her way. "Pip! Pip! Cheery O!", I shouted.

EVOLUTION CHAMBER.name: Evolution Chamber
EVOLUTION CHAMBER.flavorText: "Survival of Swarm dependent on evolution, iteration. Trust process, trust sequences. Swarm will not fail." - Abathur

DWARVEN SHARPSHOOTER.name: Dwarven Sharpshooter
DWARVEN SHARPSHOOTER.flavorText: Scissors, knives, needles, you name it! He'll shoot it.

TIMEWINDER ZARIMI.name: Timewinder Zarimi
TIMEWINDER ZARIMI.flavorText: With how generous Whizbang's return policy is, Zarimi has never been busier.

SEAL FATE.name: Seal Fate
SEAL FATE.flavorText: Firmly press the seal of your fates instead of leaving the flap open.

PARCHED DESPERADO.name: Parched Desperado
PARCHED DESPERADO.flavorText: I'm green And I'm about to die Da ba dee da ba di

SPECTRAL SIGHT.name: Spectral Sight
SPECTRAL SIGHT.flavorText: "Pick a card, any card! Preferably the left- or right-most card."

NATURAL TALENT.name: Natural Talent
NATURAL TALENT.flavorText: Unfortunately, they got 2nd place at the talent show with their synchronized swimming routine.

THE FIST OF RA-DEN.name: The Fist of Ra-den
THE FIST OF RA-DEN.flavorText: The mighty Ra-den was known as the Keeper of Storms. Unfortunately, he could not keep his fist.

DELIVERANCE.name: Deliverance
DELIVERANCE.flavorText: In 30 minutes or less, or else it’s free!

ULTRA-CAPACITOR.name: Ultra-Capacitor
ULTRA-CAPACITOR.flavorText: If my calculations are correct, when this baby hits 88 miles per hour...

WALKING MOUNTAIN.name: Walking Mountain
WALKING MOUNTAIN.flavorText: The hills are alive with the sound of YEEEEHAAAWWWW!

DEPUTIZATION AURA.name: Deputization Aura
DEPUTIZATION AURA.flavorText: You're my favorite deput- oh. You died… Ok just kidding, THAT guy is my favorite deputy.

SELECTIVE BREEDER.name: Selective Breeder
SELECTIVE BREEDER.flavorText: His ethics are top notch. Just look at that smiling kitty!

SOUTH COAST CHIEFTAIN.name: South Coast Chieftain
SOUTH COAST CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: It got the conch. You let it speak!

EARTH SHOCK.name: Earth Shock
EARTH SHOCK.flavorText: Earth Shock? Shouldn't it be "Azeroth Shock"?

EVIL CONSCRIPTER.name: EVIL Conscripter
EVIL CONSCRIPTER.flavorText: Kobold! There’s a place you can handle I said kobold! When you’re short in the candle Cast a spell with the E! V! I! L!

MINDGAMES.name: Mindgames
MINDGAMES.flavorText: Sometimes it feels like this is all a game.

CRAZED WORSHIPPER.name: Crazed Worshipper
CRAZED WORSHIPPER.flavorText: Every month they share a pancake breakfast with the Perfectly Rational Worshippers.

FAIRE ARBORIST.name: Faire Arborist
FAIRE ARBORIST.flavorText: The bad apple never falls far from the treant.

DRAGON SPEAKER.name: Dragon Speaker
DRAGON SPEAKER.flavorText: All of his speeches really drag on.

GOLIATH, SNEED'S MASTERPIECE.name: Goliath, Sneed's Masterpiece
GOLIATH, SNEED'S MASTERPIECE.flavorText: “Listen, this baby has blades, rockets, and rocket blades. Only thing it doesn’t have is good gas mileage.”

DOOMMAIDEN.name: Doommaiden
DOOMMAIDEN.flavorText: You merely adopted the doom. I was maiden it.

BLIND BOX.name: Blind Box
BLIND BOX.flavorText: THREE Flame Imps?? C'mon, where's my pity timer?!

BUFFET BIGGUN.name: Buffet Biggun
BUFFET BIGGUN.flavorText: "Look, I just want to know what kind of monster put raisins in this."

KAZAKUS, GOLEM SHAPER.name: Kazakus, Golem Shaper
KAZAKUS, GOLEM SHAPER.flavorText: With a little love and some tenderness, we’ll CRUSH OUR FOES!

BONEMARE.name: Bonemare
BONEMARE.flavorText: Attacks her job with unbridled enthusiasm.

FORGOTTEN TORCH.name: Forgotten Torch
FORGOTTEN TORCH.flavorText: Why does a forgotten torch turn into a roaring torch with no provocation? It's one of life's many mysteries.

HYDRATION TOTEM.name: Hydration Totem
HYDRATION TOTEM.flavorText: This filtered water really cleanses the spirit.

EDWIN VANCLEEF.name: Edwin VanCleef
EDWIN VANCLEEF.flavorText: He led the Stonemasons in the reconstruction of Stormwind, and when the nobles refused to pay, he founded the Defias Brotherhood to, well, deconstruct Stormwind.

DREADSOUL CORRUPTER.name: Dreadsoul Corrupter
DREADSOUL CORRUPTER.flavorText: Believe it or not, Dreadsouls aren't already corrupted.

LANDSLIDE.name: Landslide
LANDSLIDE.flavorText: "And they win it by a landslide! Wait, where did all the other racers go?"

MAD HATTER.name: Mad Hatter
MAD HATTER.flavorText: He's entirely bonkers. All the best goblins are.

PIRANHA LAUNCHER.name: Piranha Launcher
PIRANHA LAUNCHER.flavorText: A great improvement over the guppy launcher.

CONE OF COLD.name: Cone of Cold
CONE OF COLD.flavorText: Magi of the Kirin Tor were casting Cubes of Cold for many years before Cones came into fashion some 90 years ago.

WOUND PREY.name: Wound Prey
WOUND PREY.flavorText: You steal the cranberry juice, you pay the price.

HIDDEN MEANING.name: Hidden Meaning
HIDDEN MEANING.flavorText: I'm telling you, if you play the song backwards at triple speed I SWEAR Mukla sings about the Burning Legion.

BARRENS SCAVENGER.name: Barrens Scavenger
BARRENS SCAVENGER.flavorText: When the hundredth centaur dropped, so did her bracers.

UNYIELDING VINDICATOR.name: Unyielding Vindicator
UNYIELDING VINDICATOR.flavorText: Strike and smash, until it is done.

DIVINE HYMN.name: Divine Hymn
DIVINE HYMN.flavorText: Taken up an octave, it's highly effective against stained glass golems.

IGNITE.name: Ignite
IGNITE.flavorText: "So there I was in the Deadmines, I had VanCleef by the throat, and I was just about to let him have it when... <sniff> What's that smell?"

RIMETONGUE.name: Rimetongue
RIMETONGUE.flavorText: Warriors are red, Frost spells are blue, If you're being hit by a weapon, Rimetongue's got you.

BLOOD OF THE ANCIENT ONE.name: Blood of The Ancient One
BLOOD OF THE ANCIENT ONE.flavorText: Add two cups of Blood of the Ancient One to one cup of lemon juice. Add just a dash of sugar and stir. Delicious!

PLATED BEETLE.name: Plated Beetle
PLATED BEETLE.flavorText: "Ok, your party has defeated the beetle." "I put it on my head." "What?" "I put it on my head. Like a hat."

FROSTWOLF GRUNT.name: Frostwolf Grunt
FROSTWOLF GRUNT.flavorText: Grunting is what his father did and his father before that. It's more than just a job.

NITROBOOST POISON.name: Nitroboost Poison
NITROBOOST POISON.flavorText: Pouring iced milk into your vehicle's fuel tank does NOT provide a Nitro boost, but it does go great with your victory cookies.

MASS PRODUCTION.name: Mass Production
MASS PRODUCTION.flavorText: Whenever you cast this, we make a new Nemsy portrait.

BALLOON MERCHANT.name: Balloon Merchant
BALLOON MERCHANT.flavorText: It's a shiny yellow balloon! But it can be popped with a single point of damage.

MANA TIDE TOTEM.name: Mana Tide Totem
MANA TIDE TOTEM.flavorText: It is said that some shaman can say "Floatin' totem" 10 times, fast.

BLACKSCALE BRUTE.name: Blackscale Brute
BLACKSCALE BRUTE.flavorText: Black, the scales of angry Naga! Red, the flames of Azshari's past!

VILESPINE SLAYER.name: Vilespine Slayer
VILESPINE SLAYER.flavorText: 'Cause slayers gonna slay, slay, slay, slay, slay.

ICEBLOOD GARRISON.name: Iceblood Garrison
ICEBLOOD GARRISON.flavorText: On weekends, it hosts the local community theater rehearsals.

EMBRACE DARKNESS.name: Embrace Darkness
EMBRACE DARKNESS.flavorText: Once you both get comfortable, darkness is actually pretty snuggly.

LIGHTNING STORM.name: Lightning Storm
LIGHTNING STORM.flavorText: An umbrella won't be effective, I'm afraid.

SHATTERSKIN GARGOYLE.name: Shatterskin Gargoyle
SHATTERSKIN GARGOYLE.flavorText: Don't worry, this one's just a statue.

SHRIEKING SHROOM.name: Shrieking Shroom
SHRIEKING SHROOM.flavorText: Auditioning for the next Fungal Idol.

SELENIC DRAKE.name: Selenic Drake
SELENIC DRAKE.flavorText: Shouldn't this have like, a thousand times more attack?

FROST STRIKE.name: Frost Strike
FROST STRIKE.flavorText: Anyone up for some frost bowling?

TWISTED PACK.name: Twisted Pack
TWISTED PACK.flavorText: Twist it! Rip it! Play it!

GYROCOPTER.name: Gyrocopter
GYROCOPTER.flavorText: The hula doll is still absolutely required.

PRIMAL DUNGEONEER.name: Primal Dungeoneer
PRIMAL DUNGEONEER.flavorText: They wanted a Mature Dungeoneer. Instead they got this.

SLUMBERING SPRITE.name: Slumbering Sprite
SLUMBERING SPRITE.flavorText: Careful, sometimes he punches and screams when he wakes up.

HENCH-CLAN HAG.name: Hench-Clan Hag
HENCH-CLAN HAG.flavorText: The Hench Clan is an equal opportunity employer, no matter which parts of you came from where.

HAILBRINGER.name: Hailbringer
HAILBRINGER.flavorText: Knows every way to greet someone.

DARK ARAKKOA.name: Dark Arakkoa
DARK ARAKKOA.flavorText: There's a whole gradient of Arakkoa! This one is on the darker side.

SECRET PLAN.name: Secret Plan
SECRET PLAN.flavorText: The secret is... There is no plan!

HUNTSMAN ALTIMOR.name: Huntsman Altimor
HUNTSMAN ALTIMOR.flavorText: He loves all his Gargons equally. (Hecutis is his favorite and it's not close.)

LUNAR VISIONS.name: Lunar Visions
LUNAR VISIONS.flavorText: The true mystery of lunar visions is how there is nothing to watch when there are so many channels.

KNIGHT OF THE WILD.name: Knight of the Wild
KNIGHT OF THE WILD.flavorText: He gets a discount on the tournament entry fee because he is his own horse.

ACROBATICS.name: Acrobatics
ACROBATICS.flavorText: He soars through the air with the greatest of fleas.

ARCANITE RIPPER.name: Arcanite Ripper
ARCANITE RIPPER.flavorText: A guitar with a skull - perfect for headbanging.

MISDIRECTION.name: Misdirection
MISDIRECTION.flavorText: Sometimes it's as simple as putting on a fake mustache and pointing at someone else.

FIRETREE WITCHDOCTOR.name: Firetree Witchdoctor
FIRETREE WITCHDOCTOR.flavorText: If your tree is on fire - stop, drop, and troll.

ELEMENTAL DESTRUCTION.name: Elemental Destruction
ELEMENTAL DESTRUCTION.flavorText: I'm not a shaman or anything, but isn't Elemental Destruction the opposite of what they want to do?

PRINCE LIAM.name: Prince Liam
PRINCE LIAM.flavorText: "I have a very particular set of skills. Skills that make me a nightmare for witches like you."

HUNGERING ANCIENT.name: Hungering Ancient
HUNGERING ANCIENT.flavorText: This guy puts the horror in horrorticulture.

AZURE DRAKE.name: Azure Drake
AZURE DRAKE.flavorText: They initially planned to be the Beryl or Cerulean drakes, but those felt a tad too pretentious.

SPIRIT PEDDLER.name: Spirit Peddler
SPIRIT PEDDLER.flavorText: *facepalm* I asked for an art piece of a ghost on a bicycle...

MECHANICAL YETI.name: Mechanical Yeti
MECHANICAL YETI.flavorText: The yetis of Chillwind Point are a source of both inspiration and savage beatings.

MUKLA, TYRANT OF THE VALE.name: Mukla, Tyrant of the Vale
MUKLA, TYRANT OF THE VALE.flavorText: Pro tip: DO NOT BOGART THE BANANAS.

UNBOUND ELEMENTAL.name: Unbound Elemental
UNBOUND ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Unlike bound elementals, Unbound ones really enjoy a night on the town.

LINECRACKER.name: Linecracker
LINECRACKER.flavorText: "Tell me if you’ve heard this one!"

ARGENT SQUIRE.name: Argent Squire
ARGENT SQUIRE.flavorText: "I solemnly swear to uphold the Light, purge the world of darkness, and to eat only burritos." - The Argent Dawn Oath

CONDEMN (RANK 1).name: Condemn (Rank 1)
CONDEMN (RANK 1).flavorText: "I wished you no harm, but for your cruelty, by the light, I condemn you all!" Xyrella shouted, unaware that irony was not her strong suit.

DRAGGED BELOW.name: Dragged Below
DRAGGED BELOW.flavorText: I know this is a frustrating situation you’re in, Captain, but there’s no need to curse.

GRIMESTREET ENFORCER.name: Grimestreet Enforcer
GRIMESTREET ENFORCER.flavorText: "Sir, you don't have a permit to park your mount here."

ONE HIT WONDER.name: One Hit Wonder
ONE HIT WONDER.flavorText: They're trying to get a second hit in with their next single, "Divine Shield".

VOIDLORD.name: Voidlord
VOIDLORD.flavorText: Never let it hold your checkbook.

SLEEPY RESIDENT.name: Sleepy Resident
SLEEPY RESIDENT.flavorText: Shouldn’t this be a Priest card?

EXOTIC MOUNTSELLER.name: Exotic Mountseller
EXOTIC MOUNTSELLER.flavorText: *Taps roof of mammoth* “You can fit so many squirrels in this thing!”

INSTRUCTOR FIREHEART.name: Instructor Fireheart
INSTRUCTOR FIREHEART.flavorText: When you have fire in your heart, even death can't stop you.

HEADMASTER KEL'THUZAD.name: Headmaster Kel'Thuzad
HEADMASTER KEL'THUZAD.flavorText: "You wish to know my secrets, hmm? I carry little bits of tuna in the sleeves of my robe, he loves that. Oh, you meant the risen dead? That was trivial, trivial."

SWINDLE.name: Swindle
SWINDLE.flavorText: You know, it's probably just cheaper to find a place that sells the plushie…

WIND-UP ENFORCER.name: Wind-Up Enforcer
WIND-UP ENFORCER.flavorText: Code 6404.5 clearly states that all Enforcers remain in their packaging until told by authorized personnel.

STAGE HAND.name: Stage Hand
STAGE HAND.flavorText: Holds everything himself because people wouldn't stop touching the prop table.

TWIN EMPEROR VEK'LOR.name: Twin Emperor Vek'lor
TWIN EMPEROR VEK'LOR.flavorText: Do they make decisions based on age? "I'm two minutes older therefore we burn this village."

WIDOWBLOOM SEEDSMAN.name: Widowbloom Seedsman
WIDOWBLOOM SEEDSMAN.flavorText: Sometimes a blue thumb is better than a green one.

VIOLET HAZE.name: Violet Haze
VIOLET HAZE.flavorText: Elite Tauren Chieftain's next hit single.

SOULEATER'S SCYTHE.name: Souleater's Scythe
SOULEATER'S SCYTHE.flavorText: Would you like those souls for here or to-go?

LILYPAD LURKER.name: Lilypad Lurker
LILYPAD LURKER.flavorText: Honestly, the frog did nothing wrong.

SHADOWSTEP.name: Shadowstep
SHADOWSTEP.flavorText: Rogue dance troops will sometimes Shadowstep away at the end of a performance. Crowds love it.

HARMONIC POP.name: Harmonic Pop
HARMONIC POP.flavorText: Here with supporting vocals: Snap and Crackle!

PRESCIENCE.name: Prescience
PRESCIENCE.flavorText: Wait don't change the channel! I love this vision.

VOLLEY MAUL.name: Volley Maul
VOLLEY MAUL.flavorText: "It's all fun and games until someone gets hurt." - LAME PARTY POOPERS

SUDDEN GENESIS.name: Sudden Genesis
SUDDEN GENESIS.flavorText: Being hurt can make you another person.

POWER WORD: TENTACLES.name: Power Word: Tentacles
POWER WORD: TENTACLES.flavorText: Because you're wrapped in a protective layer of… tentacles?

THE ONE-AMALGAM BAND.name: The One-Amalgam Band
THE ONE-AMALGAM BAND.flavorText: Why be good with ONE instrument when you can be terrible with ALL of them!!!

UR'ZUL RAGER.name: Ur'zul Rager
UR'ZUL RAGER.flavorText: The Burning Legion is host to many horrors, but a 3 Mana 5/1 is the worst of all!

SNOWFLIPPER PENGUIN.name: Snowflipper Penguin
SNOWFLIPPER PENGUIN.flavorText: On land, a group of penguins is called a "waddle."

SPOTLIGHT.name: Spotlight
SPOTLIGHT.flavorText: Everyone's eyes are on you! Well, they're also looking at the giant Elemental that we're using as a spotlight, but mainly at you!

SPIRIT CLAWS.name: Spirit Claws
SPIRIT CLAWS.flavorText: They'll be MUCH easier to use once they add the spiritthumb.

MURLOCULA.name: Murlocula
MURLOCULA.flavorText: The best part of Murlocula is when he said "IT'S MRRGLIN' TIME" and totally mrrgled those guys.

HORSESHOE SLINGER.name: Horseshoe Slinger
HORSESHOE SLINGER.flavorText: Some people think this card is broken, but I think it's farrier than that.

KVALDIR RAIDER.name: Kvaldir Raider
KVALDIR RAIDER.flavorText: Coming soon... to a tuskarr village near you!

FISHFLINGER.name: Fishflinger
FISHFLINGER.flavorText: The scent of fish lingers on the fishflinger's fish fingers.

CORPSE FLOWER.name: Corpse Flower
CORPSE FLOWER.flavorText: Sometimes it's better not to stop and smell the flowers.

ICEBLOOD TOWER.name: Iceblood Tower
ICEBLOOD TOWER.flavorText: “Why is it called Iceblood Tower?” “Not really sure. Anyways, try not to lose your footing on any of the frozen bodies as you make your way in.”

ANIMATED ARMOR.name: Animated Armor
ANIMATED ARMOR.flavorText: Try putting it on. Wait, let me get my camera.

QUEEN AZSHARA.name: Queen Azshara
QUEEN AZSHARA.flavorText: Hobbies include: Ordering subjects around, making deals with old gods, and taking long walks under the beach.

HAMMER OF THE NAARU.name: Hammer of the Naaru
HAMMER OF THE NAARU.flavorText: The naaru wasn't using it. It doesn't have arms.

CRUD CARETAKER.name: Crud Caretaker
CRUD CARETAKER.flavorText: All it takes is a little love and a LOT of junk!

SHADOW CHORD: DISTORT.name: Shadow Chord: Distort
SHADOW CHORD: DISTORT.flavorText: For some unknown reason, using distortion intentionally in your music will attract hundreds of geckos to your location.

ADORABLE INFESTATION.name: Adorable Infestation
ADORABLE INFESTATION.flavorText: Some cards are strong by sheer power; others draw strength from love.

SUPREME ARCHAEOLOGY.name: Supreme Archaeology
SUPREME ARCHAEOLOGY.flavorText: Archaeology is the discovery of rare and powerful artifacts. Supreme Archaeology is TAKING THEM!

UNIDENTIFIED CONTRACT.name: Unidentified Contract
UNIDENTIFIED CONTRACT.flavorText: The terms of service are constantly changing.

RADAR DETECTOR.name: Radar Detector
RADAR DETECTOR.flavorText: "Yup! I definitely don't know how to read radar."

MR. SMITE.name: Mr. Smite
MR. SMITE.flavorText: “Please, Mr. Smite was my father. Call me Yorik.”

CURIOUS GLIMMERROOT.name: Curious Glimmerroot
CURIOUS GLIMMERROOT.flavorText: George promised to be good. But it's easy for little Glimmerroots to forget.

MOLTEN RUNE.name: Molten Rune
MOLTEN RUNE.flavorText: It's post-ancient modern realist neoclassical impressionist art. No idea what it means though.

LAKE THRESHER.name: Lake Thresher
LAKE THRESHER.flavorText: "There’s a monster in the lake?!" "That’s not a monster, that’s Gary."

HENCH-CLAN BURGLAR.name: Hench-Clan Burglar
HENCH-CLAN BURGLAR.flavorText: She’s more of a rat burglar.

COSMIC ANOMALY.name: Cosmic Anomaly
COSMIC ANOMALY.flavorText: INGREDIENTS: STAR-STUFF, BLUE 1, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS.

CONCERT PROMO-DRAKE.name: Concert Promo-Drake
CONCERT PROMO-DRAKE.flavorText: There's a reason why it's promoting the festival instead of playing in it - it's a rhyme-lost protodrake.

JACE DARKWEAVER.name: Jace Darkweaver
JACE DARKWEAVER.flavorText: As a former mage, making the transition from fire to felfire was quite easy.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e5/VO_SW_044_Male_NightElf_Attack_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_SW_044_Male_NightElf_Attack_01.wav Death to the Legion!

ABOMINABLE BOWMAN.name: Abominable Bowman
ABOMINABLE BOWMAN.flavorText: Frosty the Bowman... was an angry hateful soul... with a fresh hewn bow and a missing nose...

SKULL OF GUL'DAN.name: Skull of Gul'dan
SKULL OF GUL'DAN.flavorText: A fellow of evil possessed, of most devious shadow. He hath turned on his kin a thousand times, and now, how abhorred in all imagination he is!

INI STORMCOIL.name: Ini Stormcoil
INI STORMCOIL.flavorText: Before setting her sights on exploration, Ini was known for many inventions, such as the airborne breadmaking dirigible, the hypersprocket 200X zoom binoculars, and jobes (jean robes).

DANCE FLOOR.name: Dance Floor
DANCE FLOOR.flavorText: I don't think Rush would ever be here.

DRAGONKIN SORCERER.name: Dragonkin Sorcerer
DRAGONKIN SORCERER.flavorText: Dragonkin Sorcerers be all "I'm a wizard" and everyone else be all "daaaaang".

AVIANA.name: Aviana
AVIANA.flavorText: Call her "Tweety". She'll find it real funny. I PROMISE.

THE LICH KING.name: The Lich King
THE LICH KING.flavorText: "All that I am: anger, cruelty, vengeance, 8 attack - I bestow upon you, my chosen knight."

ANCESTRAL HEALING.name: Ancestral Healing
ANCESTRAL HEALING.flavorText: I personally prefer some non-ancestral right-the-heck-now healing, but maybe that is just me.

BIG-TIME RACKETEER.name: Big-Time Racketeer
BIG-TIME RACKETEER.flavorText: "It'd be a shame if someone disenchanted those Legendaries."

MIXTAPE.name: Mixtape
MIXTAPE.flavorText: That tape has got poetry and clarinet on it, Garona. POETRY. AND CLARINET.

MASTER OF EVOLUTION.name: Master of Evolution
MASTER OF EVOLUTION.flavorText: Will be really useful in the new "Hearthémon" game.

CHAIN LIGHTNING (RANK 1).name: Chain Lightning (Rank 1)
CHAIN LIGHTNING (RANK 1).flavorText: Still better than receiving a chain letter.

GREEDY PARTNER.name: Greedy Partner
GREEDY PARTNER.flavorText: "Don't worry, we'll evenly split the bounty. Then I'll have two evenly sized piles of gold!"

PRODUCT 9.name: Product 9
PRODUCT 9.flavorText: We're fresh out of Toyrantus right now but lemme show you something we have that's just as good!

BANANA VENDOR.name: Banana Vendor
BANANA VENDOR.flavorText: There's always money in the banana stand.

VEX CROW.name: Vex Crow
VEX CROW.flavorText: As birds of ill omen, these crows often summon Doomsayers.

SINISTER DEAL.name: Sinister Deal
SINISTER DEAL.flavorText: "So, what's in the sack?" "Something... sinister." "Okay, it's a deal."

INCRIMINATING PSYCHIC.name: Incriminating Psychic
INCRIMINATING PSYCHIC.flavorText: Good news: He knows Kazakus's secret identity! Bad news: Now he's here.

GHOST WRITER.name: Ghost Writer
GHOST WRITER.flavorText: This eccentric scribe was cursed to an afterlife of never being recognized for his talents! Muahaha!

FELFIN NAVIGATOR.name: Felfin Navigator
FELFIN NAVIGATOR.flavorText: Return my fishes to me, and I myself shall carry you to the gates of Mrrhalla!

ESCAPED MANASABER.name: Escaped Manasaber
ESCAPED MANASABER.flavorText: Captive manasabers don't behave much better--they're always scratching your furniture and coughing up mana balls.

AGAMAGGAN.name: Agamaggan
AGAMAGGAN.flavorText: Though he fell during the War of the Ancients, his legacy on Azeroth can be seen in the flourishing quilboar tribes who still worship him.

WIND-UP BURGLEBOT.name: Wind-up Burglebot
WIND-UP BURGLEBOT.flavorText: Don't blame the bot for his crimes... Blame whoever keeps winding him up!

INJURED HAULER.name: Injured Hauler
INJURED HAULER.flavorText: With how many cacti are all over the Badlands, this job has to be some sort of sick joke.

SONYA SHADOWDANCER.name: Sonya Shadowdancer
SONYA SHADOWDANCER.flavorText: Love like you've never been hurt. Dance like a 1/1 is watching.

HACK THE SYSTEM.name: Hack the System
HACK THE SYSTEM.flavorText: Anything can be hacked, if you're holding an axe.

TIMEWARDEN.name: Timewarden
TIMEWARDEN.flavorText: When are we getting the Silver, Gold, and Diamond dragonflight?

COLD CASE.name: Cold Case
COLD CASE.flavorText: And that's why you keep your skeletons in your closet instead of your freezer.

FROSTWOLF WARMASTER.name: Frostwolf Warmaster
FROSTWOLF WARMASTER.flavorText: “The spoils of war ain’t free… Unless you’re me!”

ANIMA GOLEM.name: Anima Golem
ANIMA GOLEM.flavorText: The Dark Animus is evil and mysterious and huge and unable to write sentences that utilize proper grammar.

FRANTIC HIPPOGRYPH.name: Frantic Hippogryph
FRANTIC HIPPOGRYPH.flavorText: It's killed and it'll kill again!

OASIS THRASHER.name: Oasis Thrasher
OASIS THRASHER.flavorText: Didn't get tickets for E.T.C.'s show.

FROZEN TOUCH.name: Frozen Touch
FROZEN TOUCH.flavorText: Is this what Bob was talking about when he said he served a drink to a Death Knight once?

ARCANE QUIVER.name: Arcane Quiver
ARCANE QUIVER.flavorText: "Quiver in fear!" - The Lich King "Ok." - Me

SKETCH ARTIST.name: Sketch Artist
SKETCH ARTIST.flavorText: Never ask an artist how many pieces they've finished.

LOAD THE CHAMBER.name: Load the Chamber
LOAD THE CHAMBER.flavorText: Wait! Before we duel, I gotta install these shaders.

DEATH'S BITE.name: Death's Bite
DEATH'S BITE.flavorText: "Take a bite outta Death." - McScruff the Deathlord

GHOSTLY CHARGER.name: Ghostly Charger
GHOSTLY CHARGER.flavorText: Maybe we should have called him Ghostly Rusher.

DISCIPLE OF EONAR.name: Disciple of Eonar
DISCIPLE OF EONAR.flavorText: If you do not receive his rose, you will have to pack your bags and leave Ulduar immediately.

GRIMESTREET PAWNBROKER.name: Grimestreet Pawnbroker
GRIMESTREET PAWNBROKER.flavorText: "I don't know a lot about used GvG cards, so I'm going to have to call in an expert."

GROUNDSKEEPER.name: Groundskeeper
GROUNDSKEEPER.flavorText: It’s tricky for dryads to tend the garden without trampling the flowers.

HOT STREAK.name: Hot Streak
HOT STREAK.flavorText: It's easy to catch fire when you're on fire.

CATCH OF THE DAY.name: Catch of the Day
CATCH OF THE DAY.flavorText: Only its fish mother thinks it's a catch.

K'THIR RITUALIST.name: K'thir Ritualist
K'THIR RITUALIST.flavorText: Something evil this way comes… and it's bringing friends over!

FEARSOME DOOMGUARD.name: Fearsome Doomguard
FEARSOME DOOMGUARD.flavorText: They were originally called Cuddleguards, but they were not inspiring the proper amount of fear.

IGNEOUS LAVAGORGER.name: Igneous Lavagorger
IGNEOUS LAVAGORGER.flavorText: Lava shark, doo doo doo doo doo doo.

FYE, THE SETTING SUN.name: Fye, the Setting Sun
FYE, THE SETTING SUN.flavorText: There is a dragon way down in Bloodrock They call the Setting Sun

ILLIDAN STORMRAGE.name: Illidan Stormrage
ILLIDAN STORMRAGE.flavorText: Illidan's brother, Malfurion, imprisoned him beneath Hyjal for 10,000 years. Stormrages are not good at letting go of grudges.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/b3/VO_Hero_10_Male_NightElf_TRIGGER_Metamorphosis_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️Now I am complete!
