GRAND EMPRESS SHEK'ZARA.name: Grand Empress Shek'zara
GRAND EMPRESS SHEK'ZARA.flavorText: So is a Grand Empress an empress that's grand or an empress's empress?

VIOLET WARDEN.name: Violet Warden
VIOLET WARDEN.flavorText: He's got magic, a shield, and an unwavering obsession with the color purple.

VORACIOUS READER.name: Voracious Reader
VORACIOUS READER.flavorText: But how much of it is skimming?

TROUBLED MECHANIC.name: Troubled Mechanic
TROUBLED MECHANIC.flavorText: In space, no one can hear you talk about your troubles.

TAK NOZWHISKER.name: Tak Nozwhisker
TAK NOZWHISKER.flavorText: "One for me and one for future me!"

SHIELDMAIDEN.name: Shieldmaiden
SHIELDMAIDEN.flavorText: She has three shieldbearers in her party to supply her with back ups when she gets low on durability.

SHOWDOWN!.name: Showdown!
SHOWDOWN!.flavorText: An epic confrontation between the outlaws and the in-laws.

DILIGENT NOTETAKER.name: Diligent Notetaker
DILIGENT NOTETAKER.flavorText: You never know what cards are going to be on the test.

THE HEADLESS HORSEMAN.name: The Headless Horseman
THE HEADLESS HORSEMAN.flavorText: This flavor text, you would expect to rhyme and reference, to great effect! It starts out strong, but as you can tell it doesn't end very good.

POWER SLIDER.name: Power Slider
POWER SLIDER.flavorText: There's a huge difference between a battle-axe and an axe-guitar. One is for combat, and the other is for combat AND rocking out.

COSMONAUT.name: Cosmonaut
COSMONAUT.flavorText: It might look like they're underwater, but they're cosmo-not!

SN1P-SN4P.name: SN1P-SN4P
SN1P-SN4P.flavorText: "It's gonna be snip this, snap that. Bada-snip, bada-snap!"

THRALL, DEATHSEER.name: Thrall, Deathseer
THRALL, DEATHSEER.flavorText: "Do not be afraid. Approach. The dead will sleep… for now."

VARIAN WRYNN.name: Varian Wrynn
VARIAN WRYNN.flavorText: Leader of the Alliance! Father of Anduin! Also he likes to play Arena, and he averages 12 wins.

FUNNEL CAKE.name: Funnel Cake
FUNNEL CAKE.flavorText: After all this time…. I thought it'd be bigger!

ERODED SEDIMENT.name: Eroded Sediment
ERODED SEDIMENT.flavorText: A perfect minion for those feeling sedimental about their past.

PYROTECHNICIAN.name: Pyrotechnician
PYROTECHNICIAN.flavorText: The difference between a pyrotechnician and a pyromaniac is a paycheck.

ONYX MAGESCRIBE.name: Onyx Magescribe
ONYX MAGESCRIBE.flavorText: Sometimes you gotta spend spells to earn spells.

FIERCE OUTSIDER.name: Fierce Outsider
FIERCE OUTSIDER.flavorText: Look, if you stopped breaking stuff you wouldn't have to stay outside.

HARDCORE CULTIST.name: Hardcore Cultist
HARDCORE CULTIST.flavorText: Thumb in = devil horns. Thumb out = I love you. A VERY important distinction when you're at a metal concert.

PRINCESS HUHURAN.name: Princess Huhuran
PRINCESS HUHURAN.flavorText: She flitters around Ahn'Qiraj dreaming of the day she will meet a sweet prince, whom she can lay thousands of eggs with.

OH MY YOGG!.name: Oh My Yogg!
OH MY YOGG!.flavorText: Many wonders lie within, but they are not mere toys when your mind is their plaything.

FROZEN MAMMOTH.name: Frozen Mammoth
FROZEN MAMMOTH.flavorText: *record scratch* "So, you may be wondering how I got here."

BULWARK OF AZZINOTH.name: Bulwark of Azzinoth
BULWARK OF AZZINOTH.flavorText: This plate turned shield you shall wield, praying its powers fel will serve you well.

NAGA SEA WITCH.name: Naga Sea Witch
NAGA SEA WITCH.flavorText: If she had studied harder, she would have been a C+ witch.

CRUSH.name: Crush
CRUSH.flavorText: Using this card on your enemies is one of the best things in life, according to some barbarians.

DARK INQUISITOR XANESH.name: Dark Inquisitor Xanesh
DARK INQUISITOR XANESH.flavorText: Fear is the mind-killer, and also the name of my wurm.

BEST IN SHELL.name: Best in Shell
BEST IN SHELL.flavorText: The agility course takes a while.

GREEN-THUMB GARDENER.name: Green-Thumb Gardener
GREEN-THUMB GARDENER.flavorText: Sometimes all a plant needs is, like, A LOT of water.

THE HARVESTER OF ENVY.name: The Harvester of Envy
THE HARVESTER OF ENVY.flavorText: "Ah, permission shmermission! You can borrow anything you want, anytime, as long as if you give it back before it's missed. Everyone knows that! Right?"

KEZAN MYSTIC.name: Kezan Mystic
KEZAN MYSTIC.flavorText: They pretend to be wise and enlightened, but they mostly just hate to be left out of a secret.

ENTITLED CUSTOMER.name: Entitled Customer
ENTITLED CUSTOMER.flavorText: "Do you have any idea how much mana I've spent at your store? 6."

REMIXED MUSICIAN.name: Remixed Musician
REMIXED MUSICIAN.flavorText: Like every bard I know, he's a chaotic Neutral jack of all trades.

INVIGORATING SERMON.name: Invigorating Sermon
INVIGORATING SERMON.flavorText: Every underdog sports coach knows this one.

SI:7 ASSASSIN.name: SI:7 Assassin
SI:7 ASSASSIN.flavorText: You can't keep the streets clean if you're afraid to get your hands dirty.

LOOSE SPECIMEN.name: Loose Specimen
LOOSE SPECIMEN.flavorText: You leave Deathstalker Rexxar alone in the lab for TWO minutes…

FURNACEFIRE COLOSSUS.name: Furnacefire Colossus
FURNACEFIRE COLOSSUS.flavorText: Smelts in his mouth, not in your hand.

AUTODEFENSE MATRIX.name: Autodefense Matrix
AUTODEFENSE MATRIX.flavorText: We call it the bubble machine.

PILOTED SHREDDER.name: Piloted Shredder
PILOTED SHREDDER.flavorText: Once upon a time, only goblins piloted shredders. These days, everyone from Doomsayer to Lorewalker Cho seems to ride one.

SCHOOL TEACHER.name: School Teacher
SCHOOL TEACHER.flavorText: She also tutors 3 Piranha Swarmers on her off hours.

SHADOWFORM.name: Shadowform
SHADOWFORM.flavorText: If a bright light shines on a priest in Shadowform… do they cast a shadow?

COGMASTER'S WRENCH.name: Cogmaster's Wrench
COGMASTER'S WRENCH.flavorText: For tightening cogs and smashin' troggs!

REPULSIVE GARGANTUAN.name: Repulsive Gargantuan
REPULSIVE GARGANTUAN.flavorText: "EW, YUCK, GROSS, ICKY-" "Stop, you're hurting my feelings!"

GALAKROND, THE NIGHTMARE.name: Galakrond, the Nightmare
GALAKROND, THE NIGHTMARE.flavorText: The enormous creature unfurled terrifying claws dripping with poisonous ichor. King Togwaggle was pleased, but inwardly disappointed the great Nightmare refused to wear the candle.

STAFF OF THE PRIMUS.name: Staff of the Primus
STAFF OF THE PRIMUS.flavorText: THE PRIMUS, RULER OF MALDRAXXUS, MASTER STRATEGIST, AND wielder of toothpicks!

DERANGED DOCTOR.name: Deranged Doctor
DERANGED DOCTOR.flavorText: Unfortunately, his doctorate is in Murloc Literature.

DA UNDATAKAH.name: Da Undatakah
DA UNDATAKAH.flavorText: First Deathrattle: Draw a card. Second: Draw 2 cards. Third: Throw Mon'kind off a steel cage and plummet sixteen feet through an announcer’s table.

DEATH SPEAKER BLACKTHORN.name: Death Speaker Blackthorn
DEATH SPEAKER BLACKTHORN.flavorText: He can speak death but has a hard time reading it.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/3d/VO_BAR_329_Male_Quilboar_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BAR_329_Male_Quilboar_Play_01.wav You struggle against the inevitable!

AIR RAID.name: Air Raid
AIR RAID.flavorText: It's difficult to get an air raid together. You have to get twenty-five people, and they all want to play a paladin!

CORE HOUND.name: Core Hound
CORE HOUND.flavorText: You don’t tame a Core Hound. You just train it to eat someone else before it eats you.

CLOCKWORK GNOME.name: Clockwork Gnome
CLOCKWORK GNOME.flavorText: Clockwork gnomes are always asking what time it is.

POISON SEEDS.name: Poison Seeds
POISON SEEDS.flavorText: "Poisonseed Bagel" is the least popular bagel at McTiggin's Druidic Bagel Emporium.

SOUL BARRAGE.name: Soul Barrage
SOUL BARRAGE.flavorText: Works especially well on jazz musicians.

ARGUS, THE EMERALD STAR.name: Argus, the Emerald Star
ARGUS, THE EMERALD STAR.flavorText: Once a proud titan, Argus was fated to meet a darker end. Sargeras and his demons would later corrupt and shatter Argus to use his power for themselves.

SCALEWORM.name: Scaleworm
SCALEWORM.flavorText: A popular local alternative to bananas.

SUNWELL INITIATE.name: Sunwell Initiate
SUNWELL INITIATE.flavorText: Initiates don’t study pronunciation until level 20.

TIDAL SURGE.name: Tidal Surge
TIDAL SURGE.flavorText: Also good for removing pesky stains.

TOMB WARDEN.name: Tomb Warden
TOMB WARDEN.flavorText: Also known as an ancient copy machine.

LIGHT'S CHAMPION.name: Light's Champion
LIGHT'S CHAMPION.flavorText: When there's something strange (say, a gibbering demon) in your neighborhood, who are you going to call?

BUCCANEER.name: Buccaneer
BUCCANEER.flavorText: The best part of buccaneering is the pants.

SILVERBACK PATRIARCH.name: Silverback Patriarch
SILVERBACK PATRIARCH.flavorText: He likes to act like he's in charge, but the silverback matriarch actually runs things.

TAME BEAST (RANK 1).name: Tame Beast (Rank 1)
TAME BEAST (RANK 1).flavorText: "Trust me laddie, I never eat seafood!"

ARCANE GOLEM.name: Arcane Golem
ARCANE GOLEM.flavorText: Having Arcane golems at home really classes up the place, and as a bonus they are great conversation pieces.

FINJA, THE FLYING STAR.name: Finja, the Flying Star
FINJA, THE FLYING STAR.flavorText: The last true master of Finjitsu.

BARRENS TRAPPER.name: Barrens Trapper
BARRENS TRAPPER.flavorText: Just add a bit of murloc meat for bait. Beasts can’t resist that special seasoning…

DUPLICATE.name: Duplicate
DUPLICATE.flavorText: The one time when duping cards won't get your account banned!

FERAL RAGE.name: Feral Rage
FERAL RAGE.flavorText: Let's be honest. One option is a lot ragier than the other.

LION'S GUARD.name: Lion's Guard
LION'S GUARD.flavorText: She takes the lion's share of the credit, too.

MASS RESURRECTION.name: Mass Resurrection
MASS RESURRECTION.flavorText: One's company, two's a crowd, and three's a “mass” resurrection, apparently.

TOME TAMPERING.name: Tome Tampering
TOME TAMPERING.flavorText: An overdue book calls for a do-over.

GREATER ARCANE MISSILES.name: Greater Arcane Missiles
GREATER ARCANE MISSILES.flavorText: Wow, and I thought Arcane Missiles was great!

ENTOMB.name: Entomb
ENTOMB.flavorText: It's perfectly safe as long as you remember to put in air holes.

BATTLEFIEND.name: Battlefiend
BATTLEFIEND.flavorText: Say what you like about my hatchet-headed hooligan, he’s my battle-friend.

SI:7 SMUGGLER.name: SI:7 Smuggler
SI:7 SMUGGLER.flavorText: After a while, Onyxia's regurgitated rats start to taste pretty good.

THING FROM BELOW.name: Thing from Below
THING FROM BELOW.flavorText: Just can't resist the opportunity to hang around with a bunch of totems.

CUSTOMS ENFORCER.name: Customs Enforcer
CUSTOMS ENFORCER.flavorText: Anything to declare? "yes... CHAMPION! Azeroth cries out..."

STORMPIKE QUARTERMASTER.name: Stormpike Quartermaster
STORMPIKE QUARTERMASTER.flavorText: Frozen funnel cakes taste just like ice cream, if you pretend real hard.

MENACING NIMBUS.name: Menacing Nimbus
MENACING NIMBUS.flavorText: Electra stores her elementals in the cloud.

STILTSTEPPER.name: Stiltstepper
STILTSTEPPER.flavorText: Circus school was tough, sometimes you had to step on people to make it to the top.

BOOK OF SPECTERS.name: Book of Specters
BOOK OF SPECTERS.flavorText: Known throughout the land as the Spooky-nomicon.

WYVERN'S SLUMBER.name: Wyvern's Slumber
WYVERN'S SLUMBER.flavorText: But watch, as soon as you try to go to sleep it'll be running all around the house making a bunch of noise.

MARIN THE MANAGER.name: Marin the Manager
MARIN THE MANAGER.flavorText: Mawin! Mawin is what bwings us togethaaa... today.

PERSISTENT PEDDLER.name: Persistent Peddler
PERSISTENT PEDDLER.flavorText: Loves pyramid schemes and bike rides.

SHIELD SLAM.name: Shield Slam
SHIELD SLAM.flavorText: "What is a better weapon? The sharp one your enemies expect, or the blunt one they ignore?" - The Art of Warrior, Chapter 9

RUNEFORGING.name: Runeforging
RUNEFORGING.flavorText: I swear the runes are genuine!

CHAOS STRIKE.name: Chaos Strike
CHAOS STRIKE.flavorText: "What do we want?" "CHAOS!" "When do we want it?" "WHEN LEAST EXPECTED!"

SIREN SONG.name: Siren Song
SIREN SONG.flavorText: "Sing along if you know the lyrics! -- WEEWOOWEEWOO!"

MYSTIFIED TO'CHA.name: Mystified To'cha
MYSTIFIED TO'CHA.flavorText: We hired your elementary school math teacher to make this card.

CONSECRATION.name: Consecration
CONSECRATION.flavorText: Consecrated ground glows with Holy energy. But it smells a little, too.

LUSHWATER SCOUT.name: Lushwater Scout
LUSHWATER SCOUT.flavorText: Only knows how to play "Careless Murgl" and "Mrgl Mrgl Little Star."

DARING REPORTER.name: Daring Reporter
DARING REPORTER.flavorText: She's working on a story! While skydiving!

SERPENT WIG.name: Serpent Wig
SERPENT WIG.flavorText: Legends say that all those who look into her eyes are turned to plush.

G'HUUN THE BLOOD GOD.name: G'huun the Blood God
G'HUUN THE BLOOD GOD.flavorText: All of the other Old Gods used to laugh and call him names. They never let poor G'huun join in any Old God games.

ILLIDARI INQUISITOR.name: Illidari Inquisitor
ILLIDARI INQUISITOR.flavorText: Armed with fear, big eyes, ruthless efficiency, almost fanatical devotion to your hero, and nice brown robes.

CATTLE RUSTLER.name: Cattle Rustler
CATTLE RUSTLER.flavorText: What once started as a small-time cat burglary gig has turned into a life of cattle rustling. What a shame.

RHYME SPINNER.name: Rhyme Spinner
RHYME SPINNER.flavorText: For ONCE we're not talking about ice!

TORETH THE UNBREAKING.name: Toreth the Unbreaking
TORETH THE UNBREAKING.flavorText: Toreth took Bubble Hearth extra seriously.

SINFUELED GOLEM.name: Sinfueled Golem
SINFUELED GOLEM.flavorText: That poor golem is going to be stuck as a guard forever. He can never get a head!

BLOODIED KNIGHT.name: Bloodied Knight
BLOODIED KNIGHT.flavorText: Chillwind Yeti would NEVER betray you like this.

TAMSIN ROAME.name: Tamsin Roame
TAMSIN ROAME.flavorText: In life, Tamsin Roame was one of the Alliance's most promising mages; now she is the Horde's most dangerous warlock.

C'THUN'S CHOSEN.name: C'Thun's Chosen
C'THUN'S CHOSEN.flavorText: He gave her a promise ring and everything.

WALLOW, THE WRETCHED.name: Wallow, the Wretched
WALLOW, THE WRETCHED.flavorText: Their hairdo is anything BUT wretched.

NIGHTMARE AMALGAM.name: Nightmare Amalgam
NIGHTMARE AMALGAM.flavorText: Be all that you can be.

UNDERBELLY FENCE.name: Underbelly Fence
UNDERBELLY FENCE.flavorText: She’ll take anything you have—except scruples and a good work ethic.

SWORDFISH.name: Swordfish
SWORDFISH.flavorText: While you were partying, I studied the fish.

HORN OF WINTER.name: Horn of Winter
HORN OF WINTER.flavorText: Much better than the Horn of Loseter.

DREK'THAR.name: Drek'Thar
DREK'THAR.flavorText: Inside your deck there are two wolves. One is a frostwolf. The other is a frostwolf. You are a Frostwolf.

EAT! THE! IMP!.name: Eat! The! Imp!
EAT! THE! IMP!.flavorText: No need for flavor text, it's seasoned perfectly!

REVERBERATIONS.name: Reverberations
REVERBERATIONS.flavorText: This sounds much louder in the void.

SKY RAIDER.name: Sky Raider
SKY RAIDER.flavorText: Maybe he should've hatched a plan that could actually carry booty back too.

WHIRLWEAVER.name: Whirlweaver
WHIRLWEAVER.flavorText: Of all the creations from the Construct Quarter, a naga combined with water is the most intuitive.

DREADSCALE.name: Dreadscale
DREADSCALE.flavorText: Let's be clear about this: ACIDMAW is the sidekick.

CINDERSTORM.name: Cinderstorm
CINDERSTORM.flavorText: Forecast: "Cloudy with a chance of fireballs."

BATTLE VICAR.name: Battle Vicar
BATTLE VICAR.flavorText: She's the most down-to-earth paladin you'll ever meet... until she stands up.

DISCIPLE OF C'THUN.name: Disciple of C'Thun
DISCIPLE OF C'THUN.flavorText: C’Thun’s recruiting pitch involves cookies, which is why it’s the most popular Old God.

RAVENCALLER.name: Ravencaller
RAVENCALLER.flavorText: That Friends and Familiars Plan is really paying off!

PYROBLAST.name: Pyroblast
PYROBLAST.flavorText: Take the time for an evil laugh after you draw this card.

NAGA'S PRIDE.name: Naga's Pride
NAGA'S PRIDE.flavorText: Lionfish, Naga, and Spears, oh my!

BLADE OF C'THUN.name: Blade of C'Thun
BLADE OF C'THUN.flavorText: C'Thun demands a sacrifice! Preferably a Deathwing.

FRIGHTENED FLUNKY.name: Frightened Flunky
FRIGHTENED FLUNKY.flavorText: Some people just aren't cut out to be supervillain material.

FELSOUL JAILER.name: Felsoul Jailer
FELSOUL JAILER.flavorText: He can lock 'em up, but he just can't keep 'em.

ENCHANTED RAVEN.name: Enchanted Raven
ENCHANTED RAVEN.flavorText: Once upon a midnight restive, Medivh pondered, feeling festive!

FLAMEREAPER.name: Flamereaper
FLAMEREAPER.flavorText: Honestly it sows more flame than it reaps.

URSOC.name: Ursoc
URSOC.flavorText: The great bear lord was so mighty that the Nightmare could only corrupt his spirit, not his strength.

RIVENDARE, WARRIDER.name: Rivendare, Warrider
RIVENDARE, WARRIDER.flavorText: More like the 4 Horsemen of the "Can't Get Here On Time."

ROTNEST DRAKE.name: Rotnest Drake
ROTNEST DRAKE.flavorText: Clean your room, or I'm taking your favorite minion away!

METEOR.name: Meteor
METEOR.flavorText: When you absolutely, positively have to kill all the dinosaurs.

PATCHES THE PILOT.name: Patches the Pilot
PATCHES THE PILOT.flavorText: Finally, a Patches you want to draw on turn 1!

SQUASHLING.name: Squashling
SQUASHLING.flavorText: Everyone hail to the squashling song!

DOOMERANG.name: Doomerang
DOOMERANG.flavorText: Guaranteed to return your weapon directly to your hand! (Wear gloves. Thick ones.)

EVERGREEN STAG.name: Evergreen Stag
EVERGREEN STAG.flavorText: Nevergreen Stag has Enrage, Overkill, and Honorable Kill.

THE CRYSTAL COVE.name: The Crystal Cove
THE CRYSTAL COVE.flavorText: For some strange reason, everyone that hangs out at the Crystal Cove has the same name...

HOOKED SCIMITAR.name: Hooked Scimitar
HOOKED SCIMITAR.flavorText: Oooooooooooow. I'm hooked on a scimitar!

SIR FINLEY, SEA GUIDE.name: Sir Finley, Sea Guide
SIR FINLEY, SEA GUIDE.flavorText: "No need to worry, ol' chums, I have the map right here. It says to continue going straight down!"

DRUID OF THE FANG.name: Druid of the Fang
DRUID OF THE FANG.flavorText: The Druids of the Fang live in the Wailing Caverns. They wear cool snake shirts and tell snake jokes and say "bro" a lot.

REPLICAT-O-TRON.name: Replicat-o-tron
REPLICAT-O-TRON.flavorText: According to the Boom Labs sales brochure, it "impractically makes itself!"

SUFFOCATING SHADOWS.name: Suffocating Shadows
SUFFOCATING SHADOWS.flavorText: "Reading is good for you," they said.

TIME-LOST PROTODRAKE.name: Time-Lost Protodrake
TIME-LOST PROTODRAKE.flavorText: Weird way to say "late" but ok.

SABOTAGE.name: Sabotage
SABOTAGE.flavorText: Rogues can't stand it. They know you planned it! They are going to set you straight!

FROST GIANT.name: Frost Giant
FROST GIANT.flavorText: Don't ask him about the beard. JUST DON'T.

SPLISH-SPLASH WHELP.name: Splish-Splash Whelp
SPLISH-SPLASH WHELP.flavorText: Little Whelpy, you're the one You make Mana lots of fun

LAVA BURST.name: Lava Burst
LAVA BURST.flavorText: It's like an ocean of liquid magma in your mouth!

COPYCAT.name: Copycat
COPYCAT.flavorText: Whatever you do, DON’T let two of them meet.

FACE COLLECTOR.name: Face Collector
FACE COLLECTOR.flavorText: “I’ll trade you a Malfurion for an Anduin.”

PRIZE VENDOR.name: Prize Vendor
PRIZE VENDOR.flavorText: He's just making sure they're real. Authentic tickets taste like strawberry.

VENTURE CO. MERCENARY.name: Venture Co. Mercenary
VENTURE CO. MERCENARY.flavorText: No Job is too big. No fee is too big.

EXARCH AKAMA.name: Exarch Akama
EXARCH AKAMA.flavorText: Akama fiercely led the Vindicators in the Draenei's quest to find a new home. If only he knew what would await him on the planet of Draenor…

ORIGAMI FROG.name: Origami Frog
ORIGAMI FROG.flavorText: For extra-realistic fly-snatching action, use tape!

LESSER DIAMOND SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Diamond Spellstone
LESSER DIAMOND SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A diamond, white, this stone the eighth A precious jewel for those of faith A whispered prayer restores the lost But none among them know the cost.

SKYCAP'N KRAGG.name: Skycap'n Kragg
SKYCAP'N KRAGG.flavorText: What's more boss than riding a parrot with a jawbone for a shoulderpad while wielding a giant hook-lance-thing and wearing a pirate hat? NOTHING.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/f2/VO_AT_070_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_070_PLAY_01.wav

ANCIENT OF BLOSSOMS.name: Ancient of Blossoms
ANCIENT OF BLOSSOMS.flavorText: His new shampoo is really working!

IDOL OF Y'SHAARJ.name: Idol of Y'Shaarj
IDOL OF Y'SHAARJ.flavorText: Without a tongue, it speaks in seven. Without a voice, its echo lingers forever.

CLEAR THE WAY.name: Clear the Way
CLEAR THE WAY.flavorText: The terrifying part is the gryphons' squeaky voices afterward.

SUBMERGED SPACEROCK.name: Submerged Spacerock
SUBMERGED SPACEROCK.flavorText: Time for some out of this world RNG.

SKARR, THE CATASTROPHE.name: Skarr, the Catastrophe
SKARR, THE CATASTROPHE.flavorText: We're not in Karazhan anymore, Reno.

SI:7 SKULKER.name: SI:7 Skulker
SI:7 SKULKER.flavorText: Burying bones and calling it skullduggery.

MILITIA COMMANDER.name: Militia Commander
MILITIA COMMANDER.flavorText: She only needs two commands: "Heel" and "Sic 'em!"

TRICKY SATYR.name: Tricky Satyr
TRICKY SATYR.flavorText: Silly Satyr, tricks are for whelps!

METEOR STORM.name: Meteor Storm
METEOR STORM.flavorText: "Sir, the possibility of successfully drawing all of your Asteroids in a row are approximately 3,720:1!" "Never tell me the odds!"

AMPHIBIOUS ELIXIR.name: Amphibious Elixir
AMPHIBIOUS ELIXIR.flavorText: Made by frogs, for frogs, from frogs.

CAGEMATCH CUSTODIAN.name: Cagematch Custodian
CAGEMATCH CUSTODIAN.flavorText: Cleans up after a dust up.

OVERWHELM.name: Overwhelm
OVERWHELM.flavorText: Scholomance student Brewfest prank gone terribly, terribly awry.

BLIGHTBLOOD BERSERKER.name: Blightblood Berserker
BLIGHTBLOOD BERSERKER.flavorText: He should really go see a dentist about that tusk. And a dermatologist. And a therapist.

VELAROK WINDBLADE.name: Velarok Windblade
VELAROK WINDBLADE.flavorText: His deceptive manipulations have dug the Bloodrock Company into a hole they can't get out of.

KEL'THUZAD, THE INEVITABLE.name: Kel'Thuzad, the Inevitable
KEL'THUZAD, THE INEVITABLE.flavorText: Looks like Kel'Thuzad is borrowing some of Mr. Bigglesworth's nine lives.

BLOOD RAZOR.name: Blood Razor
BLOOD RAZOR.flavorText: For the close shave that you've always wanted. Caution: Very sharp.

DEMONIC STUDIES.name: Demonic Studies
DEMONIC STUDIES.flavorText: "Do you wanna summon a demon? I wanna summon a demon!"

MAGATHA, BANE OF MUSIC.name: Magatha, Bane of Music
MAGATHA, BANE OF MUSIC.flavorText: Not to be confused with that one other "-agatha" that likes when you play minions.

HIGH INQUISITOR WHITEMANE.name: High Inquisitor Whitemane
HIGH INQUISITOR WHITEMANE.flavorText: No one told her that champions want to sleep in.

VICIOUS BLOODWORM.name: Vicious Bloodworm
VICIOUS BLOODWORM.flavorText: Not to be confused with the Viscous Bloodworm.

TOXIC SEWER OOZE.name: Toxic Sewer Ooze
TOXIC SEWER OOZE.flavorText: When Sergeant Sally shows up unexpectedly, DO NOT FLUSH YOUR MANA CRYSTALS DOWN THE TOILET.

SIEGE TANK.name: Siege Tank
SIEGE TANK.flavorText: Pretty decent as an off tank, but incredible as a main tank.

TROGGZOR THE EARTHINATOR.name: Troggzor the Earthinator
TROGGZOR THE EARTHINATOR.flavorText: He keeps earthinating the countryside despite attempts to stop him.

TICKING ABOMINATION.name: Ticking Abomination
TICKING ABOMINATION.flavorText: Abomination. Emphasis on the second syllable.

SECRETKEEPER.name: Secretkeeper
SECRETKEEPER.flavorText: Where is Mankrik’s wife? She’ll never tell.

FROSTMOURNE.name: Frostmourne
FROSTMOURNE.flavorText: Death Nights, Frost Morn, what's next - Blood Noon?

WRATHSPIKE BRUTE.name: Wrathspike Brute
WRATHSPIKE BRUTE.flavorText: You scratch her back, her back scratches back.

UNDYING DISCIPLE.name: Undying Disciple
UNDYING DISCIPLE.flavorText: We get it, you're undead. But jumping out of a grave? That's a bit much.

YMIRJAR DEATHBRINGER.name: Ymirjar Deathbringer
YMIRJAR DEATHBRINGER.flavorText: Purple cotton candy is the snack of choice in Ymirheim.

RED HERRING.name: Red Herring
RED HERRING.flavorText: He's got gill-ty written all over him!

VEILED WORSHIPPER.name: Veiled Worshipper
VEILED WORSHIPPER.flavorText: If you’re not wearing your regulation cultist clothing, how will Galakrond know to devour you last?

PURSUIT OF JUSTICE.name: Pursuit of Justice
PURSUIT OF JUSTICE.flavorText: "Is this about justice or just us?"

OMEGA MEDIC.name: Omega Medic
OMEGA MEDIC.flavorText: She feels waiting for healing makes you appreciate it more.

SHENANIGANS.name: Shenanigans
SHENANIGANS.flavorText: It's not personal, it's just monkey business.

STREET TRICKSTER.name: Street Trickster
STREET TRICKSTER.flavorText: His first trick: making your wallet disappear!

DARKBOMB.name: Darkbomb
DARKBOMB.flavorText: If you're looking to make an "Emo" deck, this card is perfect!

CONVINCING DISGUISE.name: Convincing Disguise
CONVINCING DISGUISE.flavorText: Okay gang, let's see who's really under the mask… *gasp* Old Man Bru'kan!?

VULGAR HOMUNCULUS.name: Vulgar Homunculus
VULGAR HOMUNCULUS.flavorText: Fortunately he has an even number of fingers.

voicelines.attack:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/87/VO_LOOT_013_Male_Demon_Play_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_LOOT_013_Male_Demon_Play_02.wav Hey, twerp! Go away.
  • ▶️ VO_LOOT_013_Male_Demon_Play_03.wav Phew, you stink!

TROLL BATRIDER.name: Troll Batrider
TROLL BATRIDER.flavorText: "Quiet! The bat can't hear where he's goin'!"

CLOCKWORK KNIGHT.name: Clockwork Knight
CLOCKWORK KNIGHT.flavorText: It takes a lot to wind him up.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/eb/VO_AT_096_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_096_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c3/VO_AT_096_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_096_ATTACK_02.wav Time. To. Die.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/b8/VO_AT_096_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_096_DEATH_03.wav My. Time's. Up.

REBUKE.name: Rebuke
REBUKE.flavorText: When one buke just isn’t enough.

FACELESS SUMMONER.name: Faceless Summoner
FACELESS SUMMONER.flavorText: They never get the recognition they deserve.

PRINCE MALCHEZAAR.name: Prince Malchezaar
PRINCE MALCHEZAAR.flavorText: He was super excited to acquire Gorehowl at a garage sale! Then super disappointed to find out it was a foam reproduction.

SALVAGE THE BUNKER.name: Salvage the Bunker
SALVAGE THE BUNKER.flavorText: You just HAD to go with the cheap sheet metal didn't you?

DRAKONID CRUSHER.name: Drakonid Crusher
DRAKONID CRUSHER.flavorText: Drakonids were created to have all the bad parts of a dragon in the form of a humanoid. But, like, why?

SARONITE TASKMASTER.name: Saronite Taskmaster
SARONITE TASKMASTER.flavorText: Don't even think of asking for time off.

BURROWING SCORPID.name: Burrowing Scorpid
BURROWING SCORPID.flavorText: It's a game of hide and go sting.

FORTUNE TELLER.name: Fortune Teller
FORTUNE TELLER.flavorText: "I see a giant piano in your future."

SNATCH AND GRAB.name: Snatch and Grab
SNATCH AND GRAB.flavorText: Snatch grabbed the snacks and Grab snatched the grub. The perfect crime.

BLOOD TO ICHOR.name: Blood To Ichor
BLOOD TO ICHOR.flavorText: For his next trick, he turns the ichor back to blood and stuffs it back in you.

TWILIGHT RUNNER.name: Twilight Runner
TWILIGHT RUNNER.flavorText: Every morning you find two dead cards at your doorstep.

RENOWNED PERFORMER.name: Renowned Performer
RENOWNED PERFORMER.flavorText: Cutting the assistant in half is the easy part.

HULKING OVERFIEND.name: Hulking Overfiend
HULKING OVERFIEND.flavorText: To hulk, perhaps, to fiend: ay, there's the rub.

VITALITY TOTEM.name: Vitality Totem
VITALITY TOTEM.flavorText: You can usually find these at the totemist's market on Saturdays.

STEELDANCER.name: Steeldancer
STEELDANCER.flavorText: Pretty powerful if you blade your cards right.

THISTLE TEA.name: Thistle Tea
THISTLE TEA.flavorText: Aren't Thistles prickly? Why would you drink them? I don't get Rogues.

EVASIVE DRAKONID.name: Evasive Drakonid
EVASIVE DRAKONID.flavorText: Doesn't respond to spells, hero powers, calls, or text messages.

ULTIMATE INFESTATION.name: Ultimate Infestation
ULTIMATE INFESTATION.flavorText: Ghouls in the pipe, five by five.

STORMWIND PIPER.name: Stormwind Piper
STORMWIND PIPER.flavorText: Throws crazy parties with the Rat King—except when it's raining.

BOOMKIN.name: Boomkin
BOOMKIN.flavorText: Some Druids consider balance to be a state of harmony between the Natural and the Arcane. Others are more focused on the balance of the opponent’s life total versus their own.

ACTIVATE THE OBELISK.name: Activate the Obelisk
ACTIVATE THE OBELISK.flavorText: A one-eyed, one stone, towering purple minion healer.

SHADOWLIGHT SCHOLAR.name: Shadowlight Scholar
SHADOWLIGHT SCHOLAR.flavorText: Imagine having the power of soul magic and using it as a reading light.

XOR'TOTH, BREAKER OF STARS.name: Xor'toth, Breaker of Stars
XOR'TOTH, BREAKER OF STARS.flavorText: We started his stats at 50,000,000,000/50,000,000,000 to be lore-accurate, but it was just a nudge too powerful.

MYSTERIOUS CHALLENGER.name: Mysterious Challenger
MYSTERIOUS CHALLENGER.flavorText: He may sound surly and antisocial, but he's actually just really shy.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/53/VO_AT_079_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_079_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/ec/VO_AT_079_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_079_ATTACK_02.wav Stop asking questions!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c1/VO_AT_079_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_079_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

DRAGON CONSORT.name: Dragon Consort
DRAGON CONSORT.flavorText: Everybody wants someone to snuggle with. Even giant armored scaly draconic beasts of destruction.

INSTRUMENT TECH.name: Instrument Tech
INSTRUMENT TECH.flavorText: A tech card without Tradeable? CRINGE.

SAVAGE ROAR.name: Savage Roar
SAVAGE ROAR.flavorText: What do they roar? Nobody can quite tell, but it sounds like "Elephant Macho Breeze". It's probably not that, though.

RAID NEGOTIATOR.name: Raid Negotiator
RAID NEGOTIATOR.flavorText: "What do you mean by aggressive negotiation tactics?" "Negotiations in bear form."

POCKET SAND.name: Pocket Sand
POCKET SAND.flavorText: I was only trying to get it in your eyes, man. YOU didn't need to open your mouth like that!

SUPERCOLLIDER.name: Supercollider
SUPERCOLLIDER.flavorText: Boom's Second Law of Motion: HIT IT VERY HARD!

COMMENCEMENT.name: Commencement
COMMENCEMENT.flavorText: "Remember, graduates—you carry a heavy weight on your shoulders now."

ARCANE AMPLIFIER.name: Arcane Amplifier
ARCANE AMPLIFIER.flavorText: Not on good terms with warlocks.

DEMOLITION RENOVATOR.name: Demolition Renovator
DEMOLITION RENOVATOR.flavorText: "Look, the Sire said he wanted something more open concept..."

THE STORM BRINGER.name: The Storm Bringer
THE STORM BRINGER.flavorText: Finally, Electra can work from home.

MAGISTER'S APPRENTICE.name: Magister's Apprentice
MAGISTER'S APPRENTICE.flavorText: "If this is the work I'll be doing, maybe I don't want to be just like you someday..."

KRAG'WA, THE FROG.name: Krag'wa, the Frog
KRAG'WA, THE FROG.flavorText: Krag'wa has a ritual to honor his friends and a ritual to devour his enemies. No one can tell them apart.

FORSAKEN LIEUTENANT.name: Forsaken Lieutenant
FORSAKEN LIEUTENANT.flavorText: WE didn’t forsake him. He CHOSE to defend a tower against the entire Alliance front line by himself.

COLDLIGHT SEER.name: Coldlight Seer
COLDLIGHT SEER.flavorText: The Coldlight murlocs reside in the darkest pits of the Abyssal Depths. So no, there's no getting away from murlocs.

MALORNE.name: Malorne
MALORNE.flavorText: When Malorne isn't mauling hordes of demons, he enjoys attending parties, though he prefers to go stag.

MORDRESH FIRE EYE.name: Mordresh Fire Eye
MORDRESH FIRE EYE.flavorText: You're not hardcore unless you died hardcore.

MUSTER FOR BATTLE.name: Muster for Battle
MUSTER FOR BATTLE.flavorText: "I'm bringing the guacamole!" – One of the most successful (yet rare) Silver Hand rallying cries

TEMPORUS.name: Temporus
TEMPORUS.flavorText: Follows adventurers, seeking the ultimate time magic: the ability to reload.

MIC DROP.name: Mic Drop
MIC DROP.flavorText: The perfect card to play after emoting.

ALDRACHI WARBLADES.name: Aldrachi Warblades
ALDRACHI WARBLADES.flavorText: The ancient Aldrachi were the greatest warriors in the universe. Imagine their power if they'd put the handle at the END of the blade.

AMBIENT LIGHTSPAWN.name: Ambient Lightspawn
AMBIENT LIGHTSPAWN.flavorText: Make sure it's smaller than your other lightspawns for the best fill lighting.

DR. BOOM'S SCHEME.name: Dr. Boom's Scheme
DR. BOOM'S SCHEME.flavorText: “We did it! We blew up the vault!” “You mean the vault door?” “Oh. The doooor…”

MYRA ROTSPRING.name: Myra Rotspring
MYRA ROTSPRING.flavorText: On her first day on the job, Myra removed the smoke detectors.

SHADOW COUNCIL.name: Shadow Council
SHADOW COUNCIL.flavorText: Why is everybody in Outland replacing their hands?!

GOLDRINN.name: Goldrinn
GOLDRINN.flavorText: His relentless ferocity has made him well known among many peoples and by many names, including Lo’Gosh and the Great Wolf.

ARENA TREASURE CHEST.name: Arena Treasure Chest
ARENA TREASURE CHEST.flavorText: Yeah it's great, but did you see the Arena Treasure Arms?!

ROKARA, THE VALOROUS.name: Rokara, the Valorous
ROKARA, THE VALOROUS.flavorText: As strong-willed and stubborn as her first day in the Horde, Rokara now wielded a weapon that rivaled even her tenacity.

WICKED SKELETON.name: Wicked Skeleton
WICKED SKELETON.flavorText: It's minions like these that give normal, law-abiding skeletons a bad rap.

EVERSONG PORTAL.name: Eversong Portal
EVERSONG PORTAL.flavorText: In retrospect, it's pretty impressive that they had the Lynxes just ready to go.

IMPRISONED SUNGILL.name: Imprisoned Sungill
IMPRISONED SUNGILL.flavorText: Imprisoned for ten thousand years! Not because it's a demon. Because of the dancing.

MAYOR NOGGENFOGGER.name: Mayor Noggenfogger
MAYOR NOGGENFOGGER.flavorText: This flavor text was randomly generated. If it happens to form words and make sense, that is purely by chance.

GELBIN MEKKATORQUE.name: Gelbin Mekkatorque
GELBIN MEKKATORQUE.flavorText: He's the leader of the gnomes, and an incredible inventor. He's getting better, too; He turns things into chickens WAY less than he used to.

CURSED CASTAWAY.name: Cursed Castaway
CURSED CASTAWAY.flavorText: She was an ordinary castaway... until she found that cursed volleyball.

ASTRAL TIGER.name: Astral Tiger
ASTRAL TIGER.flavorText: Astral kitty litter is surprisingly hard to find.

DRAGON'S PACK.name: Dragon's Pack
DRAGON'S PACK.flavorText: Each dragon's pack is guaranteed to have at least one rare.

KABAL CRYSTAL RUNNER.name: Kabal Crystal Runner
KABAL CRYSTAL RUNNER.flavorText: "Listen, I can cut you in on a little of this premium mana, but you can't tell my boss."

BLAZING TRANSMUTATION.name: Blazing Transmutation
BLAZING TRANSMUTATION.flavorText: Congratulations! Your minion evolved into a Fire type!

BOOTSTRAP SUNKENEER.name: Bootstrap Sunkeneer
BOOTSTRAP SUNKENEER.flavorText: Part of the deck, part of the crew.

GRIMESTREET SMUGGLER.name: Grimestreet Smuggler
GRIMESTREET SMUGGLER.flavorText: She's got anything you want. Need the latest derpinger? No problem!

EDUCATED ELEKK.name: Educated Elekk
EDUCATED ELEKK.flavorText: "This reminds me of a saying. 'An elekk never…' something. I can't remember."

LOTUS ASSASSIN.name: Lotus Assassin
LOTUS ASSASSIN.flavorText: For 5000g, you can just give the Jade Lotus any name and they will assassinate and/or embarrass them.

SHADOWBLADE SLINGER.name: Shadowblade Slinger
SHADOWBLADE SLINGER.flavorText: Throwing knives isn’t easy for a warlock. It’s quite painful, in fact.

CROWD SURFER.name: Crowd Surfer
CROWD SURFER.flavorText: I'm pretty sure it's the band that's supposed to be crowd surfing, but you do you little dude.

COMMAND THE ELEMENTS.name: Command the Elements
COMMAND THE ELEMENTS.flavorText: What, you expected a shaman to have trouble with a place called STORMWIND?

FREYA, KEEPER OF NATURE.name: Freya, Keeper of Nature
FREYA, KEEPER OF NATURE.flavorText: Good things come in pairs. Good things come in pairs.

TWISTED WORGEN.name: Twisted Worgen
TWISTED WORGEN.flavorText: Sometimes the Old Gods' corruptions gives you power untold, sometimes you get +1 Attack. We can’t all be winners in the Eldritch lottery.

ASHTONGUE SLAYER.name: Ashtongue Slayer
ASHTONGUE SLAYER.flavorText: Her other hand attachments include a corkscrew and a bottle opener.

ROACH.name: Roach
ROACH.flavorText: These still aren't as bad as the ones in my old apartment complex.

SAVAGE COMBATANT.name: Savage Combatant
SAVAGE COMBATANT.flavorText: Maybe if you whistle a tune it will soothe him. Yeah... Try that.

WHISPERS OF EVIL.name: Whispers of EVIL
WHISPERS OF EVIL.flavorText: Madame Lazul’s ASMR program is off to a promising start!

ARCANE BREATH.name: Arcane Breath
ARCANE BREATH.flavorText: One of many side effects from eating mana cookies.

CRUSHING HAND.name: Crushing Hand
CRUSHING HAND.flavorText: Shamans always have the firmest handshakes.

RAYLLA, SAND SCULPTOR.name: Raylla, Sand Sculptor
RAYLLA, SAND SCULPTOR.flavorText: Is this flavor text raylla the best we can do?

CI'CIGI.name: Ci'Cigi
CI'CIGI.flavorText: She once bought a 1of1 Golden Skull of Gul'dan written entirely in Thalassian for 2,000,000 Gold.

INVITATION COURIER.name: Invitation Courier
INVITATION COURIER.flavorText: Sending mail via steward is soooo old school.

ICEHOWL.name: Icehowl
ICEHOWL.flavorText: This massive yeti just closes his eyes and charges at the nearest target. The nearest Target is a couple blocks away and has sick deals on skateboards.

CRYSTALWEAVER.name: Crystalweaver
CRYSTALWEAVER.flavorText: The trick is soaking the crystals in warm milk to soften them up.

CHAOTIC CONSUMPTION.name: Chaotic Consumption
CHAOTIC CONSUMPTION.flavorText: You're not you when you're hungry.

RUNI, TIME EXPLORER.name: Runi, Time Explorer
RUNI, TIME EXPLORER.flavorText: In the future, Xyrella's daughter would become a hero of time, but Nozdormu needed her now, for this moment.

GEOSCULPTOR YIP.name: Geosculptor Yip
GEOSCULPTOR YIP.flavorText: Once crafted a gauntlet out of earwax and pure ambition.

WYRMREST AGENT.name: Wyrmrest Agent
WYRMREST AGENT.flavorText: Keeping tabs on the Grand Tournament is priority 1 for the five mighty Dragonflights!

ARCANE LUMINARY.name: Arcane Luminary
ARCANE LUMINARY.flavorText: They say true value is the cards you find along the way.

HENCH-CLAN HOGSTEED.name: Hench-Clan Hogsteed
HENCH-CLAN HOGSTEED.flavorText: This is CLEARLY their first rodeo.

DRUID OF THE SABER.name: Druid of the Saber
DRUID OF THE SABER.flavorText: That's saberTEETH, not like curved pirate blades. That's a different kind of druid. Druid of the Curved Pirate Blades.

PRISMATIC BEAM.name: Prismatic Beam
PRISMATIC BEAM.flavorText: Seven colors of the rainbow, one for each enemy minion.

ANUBISATH SENTINEL.name: Anubisath Sentinel
ANUBISATH SENTINEL.flavorText: He's actually a 1/1 who picked up the hammer from the last guy.

VENOMIZER.name: Venomizer
VENOMIZER.flavorText: Keeps getting banned for toxic behavior.

IRONCLAD.name: Ironclad
IRONCLAD.flavorText: With one inch of clearance, Ironclad proved ineffective against speedbumps.

BRU'KAN.name: Bru'kan
BRU'KAN.flavorText: Bru'kan, his body weathered and weary, felt his time nearing its end. Teaching brave champions like Rokara gives him hope for a greater future.

WARGLAIVES OF AZZINOTH.name: Warglaives of Azzinoth
WARGLAIVES OF AZZINOTH.flavorText: The blades glow green from things unseen, dark dreams whirling in the felfire gleam.

PARALLAX CANNON.name: Parallax Cannon
PARALLAX CANNON.flavorText: Math is now cannon in the Warcraft universe.

CRAM SESSION.name: Cram Session
CRAM SESSION.flavorText: The font of the arcane gives nearly limitless access to power and energy! But it can't keep you awake, for that we still use coffee.

DEATH GROWL.name: Death Growl
DEATH GROWL.flavorText: GRRRRR I'M SO ANGRY BECAUSE I'M DEAD!

IXLID, FUNGAL LORD.name: Ixlid, Fungal Lord
IXLID, FUNGAL LORD.flavorText: We suggest crafting Ixlid; he'll grow on you. Literally.

FINE PRINT.name: Fine Print
FINE PRINT.flavorText: Text in italics can't hurt you. (Yes it can.)

COGHAMMER.name: Coghammer
COGHAMMER.flavorText: So you ripped this out of a machine, carved some runes on it, stuck it on a handle, and now it's a weapon of great divine power? Seems legit.

AZSHARAN SWEEPER.name: Azsharan Sweeper
AZSHARAN SWEEPER.flavorText: The enchanted objects of Zin-Azshari have extremely long warranties.

DARKMIRE MOONKIN.name: Darkmire Moonkin
DARKMIRE MOONKIN.flavorText: Birds of a feather Moonfire together.

CHAOS CREATION.name: Chaos Creation
CHAOS CREATION.flavorText: So THIS is who's been Greening everything!

LIVING PRAIRIE.name: Living Prairie
LIVING PRAIRIE.flavorText: Whoooooa, we're half way there Whooa-oh, -

DOUBLING IMP.name: Doubling Imp
DOUBLING IMP.flavorText: What's worse than finding two imps in your lab? Only finding one of them.

FROSTY D\u00c9COR.name: Frosty Décor
FROSTY D\u00c9COR.flavorText: "Yeah, Nature magic pays the bills, but my passion lies elsewhere."

URSINE MAUL.name: Ursine Maul
URSINE MAUL.flavorText: Buy all the bears at the Ursine Mall!

PILFERED POWER.name: Pilfered Power
PILFERED POWER.flavorText: The Hozen don't get paid much, but at least they get to keep any excess mana.

HIGH TEMPLAR.name: High Templar
HIGH TEMPLAR.flavorText: If this job doesn't work out, I can always fall back on being a Psionic Storm Chaser.

MAN'ARI MOSHER.name: Man'ari Mosher
MAN'ARI MOSHER.flavorText: "E.T.C. is sooo mainstream. Have you heard of Blight Boar?"

FIRE ELEMENTAL.name: Fire Elemental
FIRE ELEMENTAL.flavorText: He can never take a bath. Ewww.

SLUDGE BELCHER.name: Sludge Belcher
SLUDGE BELCHER.flavorText: DO NOT GIVE HIM A ROOT BEER.

COVER ARTIST.name: Cover Artist
COVER ARTIST.flavorText: The Faceless Ones are servants of Yogg-Saron, and they feed on fear. Right now they are feeding on our fear of you realizing we copied this flavor text.

POWER OF CREATION.name: Power of Creation
POWER OF CREATION.flavorText: Mostly used for party tricks, to be honest.

INJURED MARAUDER.name: Injured Marauder
INJURED MARAUDER.flavorText: He’ll keep going despite the neighsayers.

GLOOP SPRAYER.name: Gloop Sprayer
GLOOP SPRAYER.flavorText: "Are you sure that's enough gloop?" "Hold on."

BOG SLOSHER.name: Bog Slosher
BOG SLOSHER.flavorText: It's the bane of freshly mopped floors everywhere.

ARGENT BRAGGART.name: Argent Braggart
ARGENT BRAGGART.flavorText: Not sure why he's bragging, he's got the same stats as the next guy.

PEN FLINGER.name: Pen Flinger
PEN FLINGER.flavorText: The pen is also a more aerodynamic short-range projectile than the sword.

UNPOPULAR HAS-BEEN.name: Unpopular Has-Been
UNPOPULAR HAS-BEEN.flavorText: Oh man, she used to rock more than ANYONE back in the Year of the Kraken. I wish I could've seen her perform back then…

VOODOO HEXXER.name: Voodoo Hexxer
VOODOO HEXXER.flavorText: The Silver Hand recruits shuddered in terror when they saw the dreaded totem of the Hexxer: A tiny little snowman, impaled with pins.

DRAGONBLIGHT CULTIST.name: Dragonblight Cultist
DRAGONBLIGHT CULTIST.flavorText: Galakrond would be extra mad if he was resurrected with gnaw marks on his bones.

SHAKU, THE COLLECTOR.name: Shaku, the Collector
SHAKU, THE COLLECTOR.flavorText: Aya even staged an intervention once, but Shaku still insists that he is not a hoarder.

BRITTLEBONE DESTROYER.name: Brittlebone Destroyer
BRITTLEBONE DESTROYER.flavorText: Broke many a leg in drama class.

AUCHENAI SOULPRIEST.name: Auchenai Soulpriest
AUCHENAI SOULPRIEST.flavorText: The Auchenai know the end is coming, but they're not sure when.

COCONUT CANNONEER.name: Coconut Cannoneer
COCONUT CANNONEER.flavorText: You think these just fell out of a coconut tree?

SHIMMERING COURSER.name: Shimmering Courser
SHIMMERING COURSER.flavorText: A courser is a courser of course, of course, she's more of a unicorn than a horse...

SNIPE.name: Snipe
SNIPE.flavorText: A great sniper hits the spot. Just like a delicious flank of boar. Mmmmm.

LUMIA.name: Lumia
LUMIA.flavorText: "What's a world soul?" "Only the most sophisticated form of life ever protected by Titans. AND it's spherical! SPHERICAL!"

DOZING MARKSMAN.name: Dozing Marksman
DOZING MARKSMAN.flavorText: It's the sleeper of the set.

BOISTEROUS BARD.name: Boisterous Bard
BOISTEROUS BARD.flavorText: As a kid, she fought with rocks. Now she fights with ROCK!

IMPRISONED HOMUNCULUS.name: Imprisoned Homunculus
IMPRISONED HOMUNCULUS.flavorText: He got a time out for excessive vulgarity.

SCARLET PURIFIER.name: Scarlet Purifier
SCARLET PURIFIER.flavorText: The Scarlet Crusade is doing market research to find out if the "Mauve Crusade" would be better received.

TRICK TOTEM.name: Trick Totem
TRICK TOTEM.flavorText: It knows how to sit still and do tricks. Still working on rolling over, though.

MARK OF THE LOTUS.name: Mark of the Lotus
MARK OF THE LOTUS.flavorText: The mark of the Lotus is a little flower drawn in permanent marker on the ankle.

MOGU FLESHSHAPER.name: Mogu Fleshshaper
MOGU FLESHSHAPER.flavorText: He's here to shape *clap* you up!

THE RUNESPEAR.name: The Runespear
THE RUNESPEAR.flavorText: When asked what the runes do, the tauren smith smiled: "A little of this, a little of that..."

LIGHTBOMB.name: Lightbomb
LIGHTBOMB.flavorText: This is what happens when you allow goblins to be priests.

AMITUS, THE PEACEKEEPER.name: Amitus, the Peacekeeper
AMITUS, THE PEACEKEEPER.flavorText: As a champion of harmony, Amitus abstained from the Pantheon's many conflicts until one day, shortly after the corruption of Sargeras, she vanished altogether.

LONE CHAMPION.name: Lone Champion
LONE CHAMPION.flavorText: He is a champion, with no friends. He'll keep on fighting, til the end!

DREADLORD'S BITE.name: Dreadlord's Bite
DREADLORD'S BITE.flavorText: When it gets too dull, it's more of a nibble.

MOR'SHAN WATCH POST.name: Mor'shan Watch Post
MOR'SHAN WATCH POST.flavorText: Pushing into Ashenvale made this post uneventful.

FIRE PLUME PHOENIX.name: Fire Plume Phoenix
FIRE PLUME PHOENIX.flavorText: This is what happens when you use a volcano as a bird bath.

REINCARNATE.name: Reincarnate
REINCARNATE.flavorText: It's like birth, except you're an adult and you were just dead a second ago.

SHIELDBREAKER.name: Shieldbreaker
SHIELDBREAKER.flavorText: Can also break up fights, relationships, and unions.

TOPIOR THE SHRUBBAGAZZOR.name: Topior the Shrubbagazzor
TOPIOR THE SHRUBBAGAZZOR.flavorText: They got a dragon that burns 1000 gallons of anima a week.

SCALELORD.name: Scalelord
SCALELORD.flavorText: It's about what they have in common, not what makes them different.

SADDLEMASTER.name: Saddlemaster
SADDLEMASTER.flavorText: Seat covers. Check. Racing stripes. Check. Cupholder. Check.

DAR'KHAN DRATHIR.name: Dar'Khan Drathir
DAR'KHAN DRATHIR.flavorText: You're telling me that you didn't suspect him of being evil, even though the first four letters of his name are D-A-R-K?

EMBERSCALE DRAKE.name: Emberscale Drake
EMBERSCALE DRAKE.flavorText: The third little dragon made his armor out of adamantite.

RAZORBOAR.name: Razorboar
RAZORBOAR.flavorText: And this little pig built his house out of VENGEANCE.

DEVOURING ECTOPLASM.name: Devouring Ectoplasm
DEVOURING ECTOPLASM.flavorText: When it's on keto, it only devours tauren.

TWIN-FIN FIN TWIN.name: Twin-fin Fin Twin
TWIN-FIN FIN TWIN.flavorText: They call him Murloc Joe, winner of the Big M Memorial Surf Off Competition.

CULT SORCERER.name: Cult Sorcerer
CULT SORCERER.flavorText: No matter how many times we tell her not to, she keeps feeding C'Thun scraps under the table.

PHARAOH'S BLESSING.name: Pharaoh's Blessing
PHARAOH'S BLESSING.flavorText: Life hack: Sneeze near a pharaoh.

ELDER LONGNECK.name: Elder Longneck
ELDER LONGNECK.flavorText: And so the bartender says, “Why the long neck?”

STONE DRAKE.name: Stone Drake
STONE DRAKE.flavorText: "I am the great Stone Drake - good morning!"

KAJA'MITE CREATION.name: Kaja'mite Creation
KAJA'MITE CREATION.flavorText: You made this? I made this.

VOID SCRIPTURE.name: Void Scripture
VOID SCRIPTURE.flavorText: The Old Gods like to think of them as "Addendums."

STORMPIKE COMMANDO.name: Stormpike Commando
STORMPIKE COMMANDO.flavorText: The Stormpike Commandos are demolition experts. They also bake a mean cupcake.

ALL FEL BREAKS LOOSE.name: All Fel Breaks Loose
ALL FEL BREAKS LOOSE.flavorText: Maybe we should have made the bars closer together…

SPELLBENDER.name: Spellbender
SPELLBENDER.flavorText: While it's fun to intercept enemy lightning bolts, a spellbender much prefers to intercept opposing Marks of the Wild. It just feels meaner. And blood elves... well, they're a little mean.

THOUGHTSTEAL.name: Thoughtsteal
THOUGHTSTEAL.flavorText: "What do you get when you cast Thoughtsteal on an Orc? Nothing!" - Tauren joke

PHOTON CANNON.name: Photon Cannon
PHOTON CANNON.flavorText: If this card were a minion, it would have Rush.

RISING WINDS.name: Rising Winds
RISING WINDS.flavorText: Do not talk to me or my chick ever again.

TENTACLE TENDER.name: Tentacle Tender
TENTACLE TENDER.flavorText: It's a messy job but somebody's got to do it. Well, actually, nobody should do this.

MURLOC HOLMES.name: Murloc Holmes
MURLOC HOLMES.flavorText: When you have eliminated the imfroggable, whatever remains, however uncroakable, must be the truth.

WHEEL OF DEATH!!!.name: Wheel of DEATH!!!
WHEEL OF DEATH!!!.flavorText: Why don't the good guys ever get a wheel?

FROZEN CLONE.name: Frozen Clone
FROZEN CLONE.flavorText: It's like déjà vu, times two.

WITCHWOOD PIPER.name: Witchwood Piper
WITCHWOOD PIPER.flavorText: She rids villages of annoying pests, like rats and children.

MYRMIDON.name: Myrmidon
MYRMIDON.flavorText: He didn't have time to Myrmidon the other half of his armor before combat started.

WEIGHT OF THE WORLD.name: Weight of the World
WEIGHT OF THE WORLD.flavorText: Unluckily for him, Azeroth has a tendency to get bigger every 2 years or so.

HEROIC STRIKE.name: Heroic Strike
HEROIC STRIKE.flavorText: Really, if you're a hero, this is every strike.

CRANE GAME.name: Crane Game
CRANE GAME.flavorText: This claw machine is RIGGED! I keep getting demons that bite me!

SOLDIER'S CARAVAN.name: Soldier's Caravan
SOLDIER'S CARAVAN.flavorText: It’s a clown car… for JUSTICE!

THUNDERBRINGER.name: Thunderbringer
THUNDERBRINGER.flavorText: You can lead a horse to water, but you can't stop it from electrocuting everything in the water.

CONSERVATOR NYMPH.name: Conservator Nymph
CONSERVATOR NYMPH.flavorText: Whatever you do, don't water your Treants after midnight!

FROSTWOLF WARLORD.name: Frostwolf Warlord
FROSTWOLF WARLORD.flavorText: The Frostwolves are locked in combat with the Stormpike Expedition over control of Alterac Valley. Every attempt at peace-talks has ended with Captain Galvangar killing the mediator.

SHADE OF NAXXRAMAS.name: Shade of Naxxramas
SHADE OF NAXXRAMAS.flavorText: I would've thought the giant, floating necropolis that is Naxxramas would cast a bigger shadow.

CRYSTALLINE GREATMACE.name: Crystalline Greatmace
CRYSTALLINE GREATMACE.flavorText: The only difference between a mace and a greatmace is... PRESENTATION!

SPIKED WHEEL.name: Spiked Wheel
SPIKED WHEEL.flavorText: Great for driving, terrible for steering.

TOPSY TURVY.name: Topsy Turvy
TOPSY TURVY.flavorText: "Help! I've fallen and I can't get down!"

ICE CREAM PEDDLER.name: Ice Cream Peddler
ICE CREAM PEDDLER.flavorText: I scream, you scream, we all scream when we see a Freeze Mage.

SPITTING CAMEL.name: Spitting Camel
SPITTING CAMEL.flavorText: Were you expectorating another bad pun?

CLIMACTIC NECROTIC EXPLOSION.name: Climactic Necrotic Explosion
CLIMACTIC NECROTIC EXPLOSION.flavorText: The less legible the band's logo, the more hardcore it is.

WRATHGUARD.name: Wrathguard
WRATHGUARD.flavorText: After playing against 5 Annoy-O-Trons, any normal guard will become a Wrathguard.

SCOURGE TROLL.name: Scourge Troll
SCOURGE TROLL.flavorText: This is where I'd put my Deathrattle - IF I HAD ONE!

TORTOLLAN FORAGER.name: Tortollan Forager
TORTOLLAN FORAGER.flavorText: In the Tortollan tongue, Un’goro is known as the “Land of the Lost and Found.”

DISPOSSESSED SOUL.name: Dispossessed Soul
DISPOSSESSED SOUL.flavorText: I'm afraid it came as a great shock to her when she died.

FIGHT OVER ME.name: Fight Over Me
FIGHT OVER ME.flavorText: And you thought the battles between the Alliance and Horde got ugly…

TROGG BEASTRAGER.name: Trogg Beastrager
TROGG BEASTRAGER.flavorText: Still angry that the Gadgetzan Rager Club wouldn't accept him as a member.

BLOODSAIL CORSAIR.name: Bloodsail Corsair
BLOODSAIL CORSAIR.flavorText: Every pirate uses the same four digits to access Automated Gold Dispensers. It's called the "Pirate's Code".

KODORIDER.name: Kodorider
KODORIDER.flavorText: Someone called her a Rhinorider, and she's NOT HAPPY.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/b3/VO_AT_099_ATTACK_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_099_ATTACK_04.wav Stampede!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/cb/VO_AT_099_DEATH_05.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_099_DEATH_05.wav <death sound>

THRALLMAR FARSEER.name: Thrallmar Farseer
THRALLMAR FARSEER.flavorText: He's stationed in the Hellfire Peninsula, but he's hoping for a reassignment closer to Orgrimmar, or really anywhere the ground is less on fire.

KING PLUSH.name: King Plush
KING PLUSH.flavorText: He's so fluffy you're gonna DIE!

STORM CHASER.name: Storm Chaser
STORM CHASER.flavorText: Best drank after a stiff gale.

WEB OF DECEPTION.name: Web of Deception
WEB OF DECEPTION.flavorText: You sit on a web of LIES!

AVENGE.name: Avenge
AVENGE.flavorText: Several paladins have joined together to deliver justice under the name "Justice Force". Their lawyer talked them out of calling themselves the Justice League.

PHANTOM FREEBOOTER.name: Phantom Freebooter
PHANTOM FREEBOOTER.flavorText: There's no such thing as a free boot.

PRAISE GALAKROND!.name: Praise Galakrond!
PRAISE GALAKROND!.flavorText: "Turn to Galakrond, Chapter 3 Verse 12. 'SNARL! ROAR! GRAAAAGH!' Let us reflect on this wisdom."

HEADCRACK.name: Headcrack
HEADCRACK.flavorText: When all else fails, nothing beats a swift whack upside the head.

POWER WORD: FEAST.name: Power Word: Feast
POWER WORD: FEAST.flavorText: Some people are here for the stellar, world-renowned academic program. Others are here for the buffet.

THORNMANTLE MUSICIAN.name: Thornmantle Musician
THORNMANTLE MUSICIAN.flavorText: She calls the hyena her "little chef". Not sure what that's about.

SHOCKSPITTER.name: Shockspitter
SHOCKSPITTER.flavorText: That blue raspberry candy was very sour.

THORIGNIR DRAKE.name: Thorignir Drake
THORIGNIR DRAKE.flavorText: Throwing your children at enemies qualifies you for Worst Mother of the Year.

ETHEREAL CONJURER.name: Ethereal Conjurer
ETHEREAL CONJURER.flavorText: Despite the name, he's a solid conjurer.

TWISTED WEBWEAVER.name: Twisted Webweaver
TWISTED WEBWEAVER.flavorText: This spider is so evil that it catches things in its web and EATS them!

WISH OF THE NEW MOON.name: Wish of the New Moon
WISH OF THE NEW MOON.flavorText: Because wishing upon a star was soooo last expansion.

STELLAR BALANCE.name: Stellar Balance
STELLAR BALANCE.flavorText: Famously, Moonfire and Starfire are about equal in power.

QUASAR.name: Quasar
QUASAR.flavorText: No one is going to believe that quasars are a real thing, Durg'tash the Sorcerer.

NEPTULON.name: Neptulon
NEPTULON.flavorText: Neptulon is "The Tidehunter". He’s one of the four elemental lords. And he and Ragnaros get together and make really amazing saunas.

EXPLOSIVE SHEEP.name: Explosive Sheep
EXPLOSIVE SHEEP.flavorText: How is this supposed to work? Your enemies think, "Hey! Cute sheep!" and run over to cuddle it?

PATCHWORK PALS.name: Patchwork Pals
PATCHWORK PALS.flavorText: "I'll name you Misha, you Huffer, and you can be the third one."

DUSKBOAR.name: Duskboar
DUSKBOAR.flavorText: Often excluded from dinner parties. To be fair, he is very boaring.

TUSKARR TOTEMIC.name: Tuskarr Totemic
TUSKARR TOTEMIC.flavorText: Turns out the tuskarr aren't real choosy about their totems.

FROSTBITTEN FREEBOOTER.name: Frostbitten Freebooter
FROSTBITTEN FREEBOOTER.flavorText: Alongside Eliza Goreblade and Peggy Brittlebone, the three Pirate Sisters terrorize the sea.

TRANSLOCATION INSTRUCTOR.name: Translocation Instructor
TRANSLOCATION INSTRUCTOR.flavorText: *Translocates behind you* psssh... nothin personnel, kid.

TUSKARR JOUSTER.name: Tuskarr Jouster
TUSKARR JOUSTER.flavorText: Just could not be talked out of using his turtle for the joust...

SOCK PUPPET SLITHERSPEAR.name: Sock Puppet Slitherspear
SOCK PUPPET SLITHERSPEAR.flavorText: The right hand of Queen Azshara is Lady Vashj. This is her left hand.

VILE CALL.name: Vile Call
VILE CALL.flavorText: "We're calling to inform you that your vehicle's insurance is about to expire."

CHROMAGGUS.name: Chromaggus
CHROMAGGUS.flavorText: Left head and right head can never agree about what to eat for dinner, so they always end up just eating ramen again.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/52/BRM_031_Chromaggus_EnterPlay_1.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ BRM_031_Chromaggus_EnterPlay_1.wav <summon sound>

EVIL TOTEM.name: EVIL Totem
EVIL TOTEM.flavorText: A lot of people blame the parents when a totem goes bad.

FELSTRING HARP.name: Felstring Harp
FELSTRING HARP.flavorText: Playing it will singe your fingers and wither your soul, but at least it never needs restringing!

ANCHORITE.name: Anchorite
ANCHORITE.flavorText: A Priest is nothing without their anchor. Wait, what?

SPOT THE DIFFERENCE.name: Spot the Difference
SPOT THE DIFFERENCE.flavorText: Ah, I see now! One of them is a picture of a Chillwind Yeti, and the other is a Blood Elf.

COLDLIGHT ORACLE.name: Coldlight Oracle
COLDLIGHT ORACLE.flavorText: They can see the future. In that future both players draw more cards. Spoooky.

DIRTY TRICKS.name: Dirty Tricks
DIRTY TRICKS.flavorText: "Ahh sand in my eyes! Also, I'm being stabbed."

BARGAIN BIN.name: Bargain Bin
BARGAIN BIN.flavorText: Used to contain Worgen Greaser until SOMEONE started buffing it.

UNDERCITY VALIANT.name: Undercity Valiant
UNDERCITY VALIANT.flavorText: Almost went to play for Stormwind before signing with Undercity.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/d/d9/VO_AT_030_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_030_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e2/VO_AT_030_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_030_ATTACK_02.wav Join us in death!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/1/1d/VO_AT_030_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_030_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

YSERA, EMERALD ASPECT.name: Ysera, Emerald Aspect
YSERA, EMERALD ASPECT.flavorText: She was previously Yuhsera, with a ‘yuh’.

SUSPICIOUS ALCHEMIST.name: Suspicious Alchemist
SUSPICIOUS ALCHEMIST.flavorText: Side effects may include feeling totally fine! Don't even worry about it.

TOTEM GOLIATH.name: Totem Goliath
TOTEM GOLIATH.flavorText: It was an art project, and nobody knew when to stop.

CARICATURE ARTIST.name: Caricature Artist
CARICATURE ARTIST.flavorText: "Pfffft…. You look RIDICULOUS! And I haven't even drawn the mustache yet!"

ANUB'ARAK.name: Anub'arak
ANUB'ARAK.flavorText: Was actually a pretty nice guy before, you know, the whole Lich King thing.

COBRA SHOT.name: Cobra Shot
COBRA SHOT.flavorText: "Cobra Shot" hurts way, way, way more than "Cobra Cuddle."

JITTERBUG.name: Jitterbug
JITTERBUG.flavorText: The only bug that was intentional.

STARSHIP SCHEMATIC.name: Starship Schematic
STARSHIP SCHEMATIC.flavorText: It's not plagiarism if you blow up the original ship with lasers.

FOREST GUIDE.name: Forest Guide
FOREST GUIDE.flavorText: "Just sign this waiver, and we'll be on our way."

VOID RAY.name: Void Ray
VOID RAY.flavorText: Raymond just had this empty feeling.

NOBLE MINIBOT.name: Noble Minibot
NOBLE MINIBOT.flavorText: I always get the minibot with the wobbly wheel.

BATTLEWORN FACELESS.name: Battleworn Faceless
BATTLEWORN FACELESS.flavorText: "I shall hug him and squeeze him and call him Earthen George."

NERUBIAN SWARMGUARD.name: Nerubian Swarmguard
NERUBIAN SWARMGUARD.flavorText: How long can this go on? Apparently even in death.

K'URE, THE LIGHT BEYOND.name: K'ure, the Light Beyond
K'URE, THE LIGHT BEYOND.flavorText: The Draenei's story of survival should instill hope in you that anything is possible!! As long as you have the aid of an interdimensional manifestation of holy energy.

INFEST.name: Infest
INFEST.flavorText: The best part is the look on their face when you jump out of the cake! Err… corpse.

FATESPINNER.name: Fatespinner
FATESPINNER.flavorText: Her clothing? Pure silk, of course.

HARBINGER CELESTIA.name: Harbinger Celestia
HARBINGER CELESTIA.flavorText: She wanders realities, taking on many forms. One was a unicorn princess.

CROP ROTATION.name: Crop Rotation
CROP ROTATION.flavorText: "Dave, you're never gunna believe this! The plants ARE the zombies!"

OMEGA AGENT.name: Omega Agent
OMEGA AGENT.flavorText: They don't just find the truth. They give it a ten second head start, then hunt it down.

IN FORMATION!.name: In Formation!
IN FORMATION!.flavorText: None can doubt the strength of the Scholomance student body.

MUENSTEROSITY.name: Muensterosity
MUENSTEROSITY.flavorText: We were going to put some cheesy joke here, but we goudan't come up with anything.

QUALITY ASSURANCE.name: Quality Assurance
QUALITY ASSURANCE.flavorText: I assure you this card is quality.

EVERYFIN IS AWESOME.name: Everyfin is Awesome
EVERYFIN IS AWESOME.flavorText: Everyfin is cool when you're part of a murloc team!

DEMONIC PROJECT.name: Demonic Project
DEMONIC PROJECT.flavorText: Another group project where Jaraxxus doesn't do any work.

CHILLWIND YETI.name: Chillwind Yeti
CHILLWIND YETI.flavorText: He always dreamed of coming down from the mountains and opening a noodle shop, but he never got the nerve.

SWARM OF LIGHTBUGS.name: Swarm of Lightbugs
SWARM OF LIGHTBUGS.flavorText: No, I asked for 'lightNING in a bottle'!

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c2/VO_ULD_184_Male_Kobold_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_ULD_184_Male_Kobold_Play_01.wav EVIL get you!

SCOURGE RAGER.name: Scourge Rager
SCOURGE RAGER.flavorText: Why's he so mad? Well you'd be mad too if you were created as a joke!

CHILL VIBES.name: Chill Vibes
CHILL VIBES.flavorText: "You're listening to 47.7 Shaman FM radio. It's time to kick back, relax, and take in the music."

SWARTHY SWORDSHINER.name: Swarthy Swordshiner
SWARTHY SWORDSHINER.flavorText: Everyone knows swords are slashier when they're shiny!

voicelines.death:
https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/65/VO_VAC_701_Male_Goblin_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_VAC_701_Male_Goblin_Play_01.wav Set it down, and I'll shine it up!
  • ▶️ Swarthy_Swordshiner_Underlay_Play.wav <underlay sound>

BAZAAR MUGGER.name: Bazaar Mugger
BAZAAR MUGGER.flavorText: Premium muggings at a discount price.

TWILIGHT DARKMENDER.name: Twilight Darkmender
TWILIGHT DARKMENDER.flavorText: First she separates them from the lights, washes them in cold water, and hang-dries.

LADY LIADRIN.name: Lady Liadrin
LADY LIADRIN.flavorText: When it comes to spells, she loves 'em then she librams.

GRAVE HORROR.name: Grave Horror
GRAVE HORROR.flavorText: Trolls can regenerate lost limbs, but this is what they do with the leftovers.

ASVEDON, THE GRANDSHIELD.name: Asvedon, the Grandshield
ASVEDON, THE GRANDSHIELD.flavorText: If you think that's strong, you should see his Great Great Grandshield.

BLOOD IN THE WATER.name: Blood in the Water
BLOOD IN THE WATER.flavorText: Fish are friends, not food! Gilgoblins on the other hand…

CALL IN THE FINISHERS.name: Call in the Finishers
CALL IN THE FINISHERS.flavorText: When you really need a job done… but you don't really care if it gets done right.

RIN, THE FIRST DISCIPLE.name: Rin, the First Disciple
RIN, THE FIRST DISCIPLE.flavorText: Signed and sealed, she delivers oblivion.

TRACKING.name: Tracking
TRACKING.flavorText: For the person who just cannot decide what card to put into a deck!

MARSH HYDRA.name: Marsh Hydra
MARSH HYDRA.flavorText: Three heads of marsh-mashing, bog-bashing, swamp-stomping fury!

BLOODBLOOM.name: Bloodbloom
BLOODBLOOM.flavorText: Help save mana. Donate blood today!

CHITTERING TUNNELER.name: Chittering Tunneler
CHITTERING TUNNELER.flavorText: Ear to the ground, he carefully interpreted the chittering noises: “You wanna cast a spell? I wanna cast a spell!”

CULTIVATION.name: Cultivation
CULTIVATION.flavorText: Calling this an 8 mana card is missing the forest for the trees.

DEFILE.name: Defile
DEFILE.flavorText: This spell was originally designed to help warlocks clean up their hard drives.

MYTHICAL RUNEBEAR.name: Mythical Runebear
MYTHICAL RUNEBEAR.flavorText: The eyes have it: that's a Runebear.

HORN OF PLENTY.name: Horn of Plenty
HORN OF PLENTY.flavorText: Don't be silly, there's never been a cornucopia in the art.

STICK UP.name: Stick Up
STICK UP.flavorText: Dude, Velarok, give me a minute to play my turn, the rope's burning!

COILFANG CONSTRICTOR.name: Coilfang Constrictor
COILFANG CONSTRICTOR.flavorText: How do you know when someone has a crush on you? They take your breath away.

NEPTULON THE TIDEHUNTER.name: Neptulon the Tidehunter
NEPTULON THE TIDEHUNTER.flavorText: Neptulon, tired of filling hands, is now throwing hands.

PSYCHOPOMP.name: Psychopomp
PSYCHOPOMP.flavorText: "Come with me if you want to re-live."

THE FOREST'S AID.name: The Forest's Aid
THE FOREST'S AID.flavorText: Delicious Forest’s Aid! Made from real forests.

CAROUSEL GRYPHON.name: Carousel Gryphon
CAROUSEL GRYPHON.flavorText: "When does this bird land in Stormwind? I've been flying for hours!"

ANTIQUE HEALBOT.name: Antique Healbot
ANTIQUE HEALBOT.flavorText: They don't make 'em like they used to! (Because of explosions, mostly.)

NOVICE ZAPPER.name: Novice Zapper
NOVICE ZAPPER.flavorText: The novices would prefer that he did not.

POGO-HOPPER.name: Pogo-Hopper
POGO-HOPPER.flavorText: Once you hop, you just can't stop!

ARBOR UP.name: Arbor Up
ARBOR UP.flavorText: If you can’t outrun a tree, you really shouldn’t be here anyway.

REVENGE.name: Revenge
REVENGE.flavorText: This is better than Arcane Explosion, so I guess warriors are finally getting revenge on mages for Mortal Strike being worse than Fireball.

COMBUSTION.name: Combustion
COMBUSTION.flavorText: Sally is friends with three Silverhand Recruits conveniently standing in a line. After casting this spell, how many friends does she have left? (Show your work.)

OPTIMISTIC OGRE.name: Optimistic Ogre
OPTIMISTIC OGRE.flavorText: "What if this goes wrong?" "But what if this goes right?"

WICKERFLAME BURNBRISTLE.name: Wickerflame Burnbristle
WICKERFLAME BURNBRISTLE.flavorText: Wickerflame spent years as a recruit for the Goons, never making the big-time because he always fired his chest-cannon too slowly. "Hey," he thought, "maybe if I keep my beard lit on fire, I can do this faster." BOOM, promoted.

THE DARK PORTAL.name: The Dark Portal
THE DARK PORTAL.flavorText: Some say it's the source of Azeroth's greatest problems—aside from the gnomes.

RETURN POLICY.name: Return Policy
RETURN POLICY.flavorText: Sorry, the Workshop has a strict 'no-takesies-backsies' policy.

SPELLWEAVER.name: Spellweaver
SPELLWEAVER.flavorText: Spells offer twice the moisture wicking of cotton.

ANNOY-O-TROUPE.name: Annoy-o-Troupe
ANNOY-O-TROUPE.flavorText: Some classes get Void Lords, other classes get Annoyed Lords.

SATYR OVERSEER.name: Satyr Overseer
SATYR OVERSEER.flavorText: What he lacks in communication skills, he makes up for with highly responsive staffing allocations.

RING OF COURAGE.name: Ring of Courage
RING OF COURAGE.flavorText: Now to find the Ring of Wisdom and Ring of Power.

DRUID OF THE REEF.name: Druid of the Reef
DRUID OF THE REEF.flavorText: “Wow, there’s a whole sunken city down here!”

LIGHTFORGED CRUSADER.name: Lightforged Crusader
LIGHTFORGED CRUSADER.flavorText: Self-appointed president of the Paladins Only Paladin Club.

GRIFTAH, TRUSTED VENDOR.name: Griftah, Trusted Vendor
GRIFTAH, TRUSTED VENDOR.flavorText: "Tiki mugs will match any kind of home décor! They're timeless!"

MAGICFIN.name: Magicfin
MAGICFIN.flavorText: The best part is when he pulls Deathwing out of a top hat!

RISE TO THE OCCASION.name: Rise to the Occasion
RISE TO THE OCCASION.flavorText: Faith is never lost, only repurposed.

DIREWOLF COMMANDER.name: Direwolf Commander
DIREWOLF COMMANDER.flavorText: When you’re riding a wolf, it’s in charge and you're allowed to make suggestions.

DARKMOON RABBIT.name: Darkmoon Rabbit
DARKMOON RABBIT.flavorText: That's no ordinary rabbit! That's the most foul, cruel, and bad-tempered rodent you ever set eyes on!

EXTRA ARMS.name: Extra Arms
EXTRA ARMS.flavorText: All the better to hug you with!

MEANSTREET MARSHAL.name: Meanstreet Marshal
MEANSTREET MARSHAL.flavorText: Remember, submit your bribes directly to the Marshal - it's the law!

AQUA ARCHIVIST.name: Aqua Archivist
AQUA ARCHIVIST.flavorText: Do not summon! I JUST had to put all my scrolls in rice.

FLORIST.name: Florist
FLORIST.flavorText: Trade district. Trade district a shop. Color Legendary. Color Legendary golden. Rose is a rose is a rose is a rose.

INITIATION.name: Initiation
INITIATION.flavorText: The things a murloc's gotta go through to graduate from Scholomance…

LESSER SAPPHIRE SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Sapphire Spellstone
LESSER SAPPHIRE SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A stone of blue, embraced with glee By murloc lords beneath the sea Soon numberless they swarmed the shore First two, then four, then more...and more...

KIRI, CHOSEN OF ELUNE.name: Kiri, Chosen of Elune
KIRI, CHOSEN OF ELUNE.flavorText: Now, when the Sun is between the Moon and the Azeroth... that's when you've got a problem.

NERUBIAN VIZIER.name: Nerubian Vizier
NERUBIAN VIZIER.flavorText: One of the essential constructors of the Northrend wide web.

SNACK RUN.name: Snack Run
SNACK RUN.flavorText: "I'll have two monster churros, a combo box of Yogg-Saron, and one of those turkey legs that ate the Silver Hand Recruit."

ORGRIMMAR ASPIRANT.name: Orgrimmar Aspirant
ORGRIMMAR ASPIRANT.flavorText: "Four out of three orcs struggle with math." - Angry Zurge

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/62/VO_AT_066_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_066_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/2b/VO_AT_066_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_066_ATTACK_02.wav Defend yourself!

ASTRAL RIFT.name: Astral Rift
ASTRAL RIFT.flavorText: Let's see what's behind rift number one!

WEAPONS EXPERT.name: Weapons Expert
WEAPONS EXPERT.flavorText: "Yes, Your Honor, this appears to be some sort of blade."

MOZAKI, MASTER DUELIST.name: Mozaki, Master Duelist
MOZAKI, MASTER DUELIST.flavorText: Treats her students like her peers, which means defeating them in one-sided duels all day long.

EADRIC THE PURE.name: Eadric the Pure
EADRIC THE PURE.flavorText: Nobody rocks a monocle like Eadric.

FIRE FLY.name: Fire Fly
FIRE FLY.flavorText: Archnemeses: small children with glass jars.

SHADY BARTENDER.name: Shady Bartender
SHADY BARTENDER.flavorText: One sin and tonic, coming right up.

LIGHTFORGED BLESSING.name: Lightforged Blessing
LIGHTFORGED BLESSING.flavorText: Some might call this a lightforgery.

CREEPY PAINTING.name: Creepy Painting
CREEPY PAINTING.flavorText: I do not like this painting, Harth. Its smug aura mocks me.

REWIND.name: Rewind
REWIND.flavorText: If you don't find the spell you want, just cast this one more time and see if you get lucky.

PATHMAKER.name: Pathmaker
PATHMAKER.flavorText: You can never choose the wrong path if you make your own.

JADE SWARMER.name: Jade Swarmer
JADE SWARMER.flavorText: He's so good at swarming, he can swarm all by himself!

BLOOD IMP.name: Blood Imp
BLOOD IMP.flavorText: Imps are content to hide and viciously taunt everyone nearby.

ALUNETH.name: Aluneth
ALUNETH.flavorText: PHENOMENAL ARCANE POWER…itty bitty living space.

ELITIST SNOB.name: Elitist Snob
ELITIST SNOB.flavorText: "I heard the Sire invited a Murloc! How dreadful!"

UNWILLING SACRIFICE.name: Unwilling Sacrifice
UNWILLING SACRIFICE.flavorText: Stand right... there. Perfect, perfect! Now don't move.

HEISTBARON TOGWAGGLE.name: Heistbaron Togwaggle
HEISTBARON TOGWAGGLE.flavorText: A staunch ally of Rafaam, at least while the shinies keep flowing.

TWILIGHT FLAMECALLER.name: Twilight Flamecaller
TWILIGHT FLAMECALLER.flavorText: Make sure you summon a Twilight Marshmallowcaller too! Mmmm Mmm Mmm!!

SECRET PASSAGE.name: Secret Passage
SECRET PASSAGE.flavorText: I use this to sneak out at night and do some villainous baking in the kitchen.

PRIVATE EYE.name: Private Eye
PRIVATE EYE.flavorText: Eye see what you did there.

DEADSCALE KNIGHT.name: Deadscale Knight
DEADSCALE KNIGHT.flavorText: His favorite spell is Chum Explosion.

RAVEN FAMILIAR.name: Raven Familiar
RAVEN FAMILIAR.flavorText: Quoth the raven, 'Does yours cost more?'

\"HEALTH\" DRINK.name: "Health" Drink
\"HEALTH\" DRINK.flavorText: Do not exceed recommend daily serving size of 0 grams.

OMEGA DEVASTATOR.name: Omega Devastator
OMEGA DEVASTATOR.flavorText: The Alpha Devastator didn’t devastate enough. The Beta Devastator devastated too much. But the Omega was just right!

SUNSCALE RAPTOR.name: Sunscale Raptor
SUNSCALE RAPTOR.flavorText: And they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they don't stop coming and they—

SUNWING SQUAWKER.name: Sunwing Squawker
SUNWING SQUAWKER.flavorText: Most parrots repeat curses, not blessings.

BRONZE EXPLORER.name: Bronze Explorer
BRONZE EXPLORER.flavorText: Always ready to explore new friendships! Except with Deathwing.

GRACE OF THE HIGHFATHER.name: Grace of the Highfather
GRACE OF THE HIGHFATHER.flavorText: The fish was thiiiiis big, can you believe it?

DR. BOOM, MAD GENIUS.name: Dr. Boom, Mad Genius
DR. BOOM, MAD GENIUS.flavorText: "Of course I've gone mad with power. Ever try going mad without it?"

WILDERNESS PACK.name: Wilderness Pack
WILDERNESS PACK.flavorText: Don't bother asking, "Can we keep them?" The answer is no.

KALECGOS.name: Kalecgos
KALECGOS.flavorText: He was once the Aspect of Magic but gave it up to focus on cheap tricks.

WRATHSCALE NAGA.name: Wrathscale Naga
WRATHSCALE NAGA.flavorText: If throwing glaives is what you crave; summon tokens and make 'em broken.

GHOULS' NIGHT.name: Ghouls' Night
GHOULS' NIGHT.flavorText: "Ohmygosh, did you hear what Jessicorpse said to Deathanny??"

DARKFALLEN SHADOW.name: Darkfallen Shadow
DARKFALLEN SHADOW.flavorText: Manathirst AND Reborn?! Pick a side!

CARNIVOROUS CUBE.name: Carnivorous Cube
CARNIVOROUS CUBE.flavorText: He's always grumpy until he's eaten his first barista of the morning.

BATTLEWORN VANGUARD.name: Battleworn Vanguard
BATTLEWORN VANGUARD.flavorText: "Welcome to Dun Baldar Felwings! Do you want 'em mild, spicy, or BURNING Legion?"

HELLION.name: Hellion
HELLION.flavorText: Let's upgrade to the non-flammable tires next time.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/82/VO_SC_412_Male_Human_Attack_01.wav?38e419" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_SC_412_Male_Human_Attack_01.wav Death rides with me!

ARCHMAGE ANTONIDAS.name: Archmage Antonidas
ARCHMAGE ANTONIDAS.flavorText: Antonidas was the Grand Magus of the Kirin Tor, and Jaina's mentor. This was a big step up from being Grand Magus of Jelly Donuts.

CRAZED CHEMIST.name: Crazed Chemist
CRAZED CHEMIST.flavorText: You don't have to be crazy to work here, but it helps.

BLOOD BOIL.name: Blood Boil
BLOOD BOIL.flavorText: And once your blood is at a boil, throw in the plaguetti.

TOTEM CRUNCHER.name: Totem Cruncher
TOTEM CRUNCHER.flavorText: When regular totem hours won't cut it.

SAVANNAH HIGHMANE.name: Savannah Highmane
SAVANNAH HIGHMANE.flavorText: In the jungle, the mighty jungle, the lion gets slowly consumed by hyenas.

COORDINATED STRIKE.name: Coordinated Strike
COORDINATED STRIKE.flavorText: Undisputed champions of "Dancing with the Satyrs."

AMAN'THUL.name: Aman'Thul
AMAN'THUL.flavorText: The leader of the titans was the first to awaken. In his loneliness, he sought out other titans across many different worlds, and together, they formed the Pantheon.

AEROSOILIZER.name: Aerosoilizer
AEROSOILIZER.flavorText: Banned in Wild for opening a hole in the ozone layer.

TOWN CRIER.name: Town Crier
TOWN CRIER.flavorText: When he was younger, he was the town crybaby.

SHADOWCLOTH NEEDLE.name: Shadowcloth Needle
SHADOWCLOTH NEEDLE.flavorText: Makes light of the darkest repair jobs.

ONYXIA.name: Onyxia
ONYXIA.flavorText: Onyxia long manipulated the Stormwind Court by disguising herself as Lady Katrana Prestor. You would have thought that the giant wings and scales would have been a giveaway.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/1/1a/VO_EX1_562_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_EX1_562_Play_01.wav You dare challenge the daughter of Deathwing?

RITUAL OF THE NEW MOON.name: Ritual of the New Moon
RITUAL OF THE NEW MOON.flavorText: This ritual does nothing, but they do it anyway for the social connection.

MUROZOND THE INFINITE.name: Murozond the Infinite
MUROZOND THE INFINITE.flavorText: "Well, I'm glad YOU knew what I should be doing this turn."

FAL'DOREI STRIDER.name: Fal'dorei Strider
FAL'DOREI STRIDER.flavorText: What’s worse? Seeing the spider, or NOT seeing the spider, but knowing it’s somewhere in your deck?

TAR CREEPER.name: Tar Creeper
TAR CREEPER.flavorText: If you won't come to the tar pits, we'll bring them to you!

ANGRY HELHOUND.name: Angry Helhound
ANGRY HELHOUND.flavorText: When you wake up on the all 3 wrong sides of the bed.

FLAME BEHEMOTH.name: Flame Behemoth
FLAME BEHEMOTH.flavorText: Always look both ways before crossing the Formation Grounds.

CORRUPTING MIST.name: Corrupting Mist
CORRUPTING MIST.flavorText: The most terrifying of Un’goro magics is both silent… AND deadly.

INFESTOR.name: Infestor
INFESTOR.flavorText: Even if you survive its neural parasite, you will never live it down.

ROCKET BOOTS.name: Rocket Boots
ROCKET BOOTS.flavorText: This is the happiest moment of Grik's life. We'll miss him.

GLACIATE.name: Glaciate
GLACIATE.flavorText: We now have a more accurate answer to the age-old question "What's cooler than being cool?"

RAM COMMANDER.name: Ram Commander
RAM COMMANDER.flavorText: Get your RAM in pairs for better performance.

CRYSTAL WELDER.name: Crystal Welder
CRYSTAL WELDER.flavorText: For all you weld-heads out there, this flavor text is a deep cut.

XYRELLA, THE DEVOUT.name: Xyrella, the Devout
XYRELLA, THE DEVOUT.flavorText: Xyrella thought she was only saving her daughter. Her actions may very well have saved the entire world.

AZERITE GIANT.name: Azerite Giant
AZERITE GIANT.flavorText: Either that giant isn't really giant, or that doorway is HUGE!

OCCULT CONJURER.name: Occult Conjurer
OCCULT CONJURER.flavorText: Like mirror image, but more secretive and angsty.
