HOLOTECHNICIAN.name: Holotechnician
HOLOTECHNICIAN.flavorText: Ironically, operating the spotlight comes with very little recognition.

STUBBORN SUSPECT.name: Stubborn Suspect
STUBBORN SUSPECT.flavorText: He keeps saying "I'll never talk," but no one has actually asked him anything.

STORMCOIL MOTHERSHIP.name: Stormcoil Mothership
STORMCOIL MOTHERSHIP.flavorText: Has been known to abduct sea cows and leave kelp circles.

ABYSSAL WAVE.name: Abyssal Wave
ABYSSAL WAVE.flavorText: Often followed up with a chasmic handshake.

SORCERER'S GAMBIT.name: Sorcerer's Gambit
SORCERER'S GAMBIT.flavorText: After "the incident," the Stockades really had to reevaluate their anti-mage protocols.

TWILIGHT ACOLYTE.name: Twilight Acolyte
TWILIGHT ACOLYTE.flavorText: The dragons mostly keep him around as a snack.

WARTBRINGER.name: Wartbringer
WARTBRINGER.flavorText: “Does she cause them with magic, or just…like have a bucket she brings with her?”

OBSIDIANSMITH.name: Obsidiansmith
OBSIDIANSMITH.flavorText: Was able to produce more effective weapons than his predecessor, Kelpsmith.

CAPTURE COLDTOOTH MINE.name: Capture Coldtooth Mine
CAPTURE COLDTOOTH MINE.flavorText: We hit a huge haul! Or wait… no, it's just a coin.

DREAMPETAL FLORIST.name: Dreampetal Florist
DREAMPETAL FLORIST.flavorText: Unlike gnomes, dreampetals grow more than 3 feet tall.

SEEK GUIDANCE.name: Seek Guidance
SEEK GUIDANCE.flavorText: Xyrella was looking for spiritual guidance but found deck-building tips instead.

UMBRACLAW.name: Umbraclaw
UMBRACLAW.flavorText: Umbraclaws of a feather hibernate together.

STUBBORN GASTROPOD.name: Stubborn Gastropod
STUBBORN GASTROPOD.flavorText: Stubbornly pursuing its dream to become Azeroth's fastest animal!

BUILDING-BLOCK GOLEM.name: Building-Block Golem
BUILDING-BLOCK GOLEM.flavorText: I HOPE YOU STEP ON A 1-COST MINION!

POLYMORPH: JELLYFISH.name: Polymorph: Jellyfish
POLYMORPH: JELLYFISH.flavorText: While Ini’s first use of the Spontaneous Gelatin Transmalgamizer may have gotten her banned from the Gnomish Cooking Convention, she’s never one to throw away a new invention.

ANUB'AR AMBUSHER.name: Anub'ar Ambusher
ANUB'AR AMBUSHER.flavorText: Originally he was called "Anub'ar Guy who bounces a guy back to your hand", but it lacked a certain zing.

GREAT HALL.name: Great Hall
GREAT HALL.flavorText: It's fabulous! It's grand! It's, well it's really very nice.

GOLDEN SCARAB.name: Golden Scarab
GOLDEN SCARAB.flavorText: Who actually puts all the gold plating on these things, and why?

DRAGONHAWK RIDER.name: Dragonhawk Rider
DRAGONHAWK RIDER.flavorText: Check it out. You can do barrel rolls on this thing.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/86/VO_AT_083_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_083_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/27/VO_AT_083_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_083_ATTACK_02.wav Seriously!?
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/6f/VO_AT_083_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_083_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

ANCIENT TOTEM.name: Ancient Totem
ANCIENT TOTEM.flavorText: This is SO much cuter than Tinyfin.

BOTTOMLESS TOY CHEST.name: Bottomless Toy Chest
BOTTOMLESS TOY CHEST.flavorText: That's right, it goes in the toy chest.

FUNGALMANCER.name: Fungalmancer
FUNGALMANCER.flavorText: Fungalmancy is the easy major for those who can't cut it at Waxmancy.

EMERGENCY MEETING.name: Emergency Meeting
EMERGENCY MEETING.flavorText: You installed a big flashing red button on the ship and expected me NOT to press it?

HOG RANCHER.name: Hog Rancher
HOG RANCHER.flavorText: Suspiciously close to a Quilboar village.

KROLUSK BARKSTRIPPER.name: Krolusk Barkstripper
KROLUSK BARKSTRIPPER.flavorText: My friend went krolusk tipping once… once!

WINDCHILL.name: Windchill
WINDCHILL.flavorText: The thermometer says it’s 0° right now, but with the windchill it feels like -25°.

GREEN JELLY.name: Green Jelly
GREEN JELLY.flavorText: This card really breaks out of the mold.

QUARTERMASTER.name: Quartermaster
QUARTERMASTER.flavorText: His specialty? Dividing things into four pieces.

REMORNIA, LIVING BLADE.name: Remornia, Living Blade
REMORNIA, LIVING BLADE.flavorText: Was it the lead pipe... the candlestick... or the unhinged, sentient, bloodthirsty sword?

DEFROST.name: Defrost
DEFROST.flavorText: Shouldn't this NOT be a Frost spell?

SCALED NIGHTMARE.name: Scaled Nightmare
SCALED NIGHTMARE.flavorText: I like it because it scales.

NESTING GOLEM.name: Nesting Golem
NESTING GOLEM.flavorText: NESTING GOLEEEEEEEEEEEEM!!!!!!! Eh… It just doesn't feel the same.

TRAVEL AGENT.name: Travel Agent
TRAVEL AGENT.flavorText: I could've hired her or some Dodo.

FOR QUEL'THALAS!.name: For Quel'Thalas!
FOR QUEL'THALAS!.flavorText: For kwell-kell.. for kell… for kwee- for the city!

CARVING CHISEL.name: Carving Chisel
CARVING CHISEL.flavorText: Look at your stone. Visualize the totem within. Then gently...

CROW'S NEST LOOKOUT.name: Crow's Nest Lookout
CROW'S NEST LOOKOUT.flavorText: The extra eyes means he sees extra good.

IDOL'S ADORATION.name: Idol's Adoration
IDOL'S ADORATION.flavorText: That is a mic, not a door.

GOLAKKA CRAWLER.name: Golakka Crawler
GOLAKKA CRAWLER.flavorText: Universally adored by both control decks and ninjas.

SANCTUARY.name: Sanctuary
SANCTUARY.flavorText: Few quests are completed by cowering under a table.

CHAMPION OF STORMS.name: Champion of Storms
CHAMPION OF STORMS.flavorText: Has some grievances it just can't wait to air out.

CLEARANCE PROMOTER.name: Clearance Promoter
CLEARANCE PROMOTER.flavorText: "Sorry, we just sold our last Worgen Greaser figure."

ARTIFICER XY'MOX.name: Artificer Xy'mox
ARTIFICER XY'MOX.flavorText: "The anticipation to use this relic is killing me! Though, it will more likely kill you."

LIFEGUARD.name: Lifeguard
LIFEGUARD.flavorText: Hey, no aggro in the pool!

FELRATTLER.name: Felrattler
FELRATTLER.flavorText: It only rattles when YOU'RE in danger.

NEW HEIGHTS.name: New Heights
NEW HEIGHTS.flavorText: The sky's the limit (or at least 99 is).

ASSASSINATE.name: Assassinate
ASSASSINATE.flavorText: If you don't want to be assassinated, move to the Barrens and change your name. Good luck!

WEAPONS ATTENDANT.name: Weapons Attendant
WEAPONS ATTENDANT.flavorText: Hotel policy states that you must leave your weapons at the front desk. But GOOD NEWS! You can also buy weapons at the back desk!!

MAL'GANIS.name: Mal'Ganis
MAL'GANIS.flavorText: Mal'Ganis doesn't like being betrayed, so if you discard him, watch out.

OBLITERATE.name: Obliterate
OBLITERATE.flavorText: Why is 6 afraid of 7? Because Obliterate 9!

SHIFTER ZERUS.name: Shifter Zerus
SHIFTER ZERUS.flavorText: It's like being able to play with THREE angry chickens!

SUMMONING STONE.name: Summoning Stone
SUMMONING STONE.flavorText: Sometimes it feels like it's always the same slackers that are waiting for a summon.

IMPBALMING.name: Impbalming
IMPBALMING.flavorText: With your complexion, Imp Balm is a great demonizer.

CREEP TUMOR.name: Creep Tumor
CREEP TUMOR.flavorText: "If you spot one of these, back away or burn it to hell. Never fight on their turf."

HAUNTING VISIONS.name: Haunting Visions
HAUNTING VISIONS.flavorText: When you're awake at 3 AM and can't stop thinking about that time you called your teacher "mom."

DEATHBORNE.name: Deathborne
DEATHBORNE.flavorText: Kel'Thuzad thinks adding a silent 'e' at the end of words makes them sound cooler.

VOID RIPPER.name: Void Ripper
VOID RIPPER.flavorText: You had to put the portable hole inside the bag of holding, didn't you?!

JOB SHADOWER.name: Job Shadower
JOB SHADOWER.flavorText: "Our prosperity… is beyond… a shadow of… a doubt! Ok, got it!"

BOVINE SKELETON.name: Bovine Skeleton
BOVINE SKELETON.flavorText: The secret cow level has been unearthed.

MOLTEN BREATH.name: Molten Breath
MOLTEN BREATH.flavorText: Pizza so hot it burns OTHER PEOPLE’S MOUTHS.

INFESTED BREATH.name: Infested Breath
INFESTED BREATH.flavorText: Remember to brush your tongue as well as your teeth.

TRADE PRINCE GALLYWIX.name: Trade Prince Gallywix
TRADE PRINCE GALLYWIX.flavorText: Gallywix believes in supply and demand. He supplies the beatings and demands you pay up!

CORSAIR CACHE.name: Corsair Cache
CORSAIR CACHE.flavorText: Where's a corsair's favorite place to hide treasure? Under their deck!

ALEXSTRASZA.name: Alexstrasza
ALEXSTRASZA.flavorText: Alexstrasza the Life-Binder brings life and hope to everyone. Except Deathwing. And Malygos. And Nekros.

SPAMMY ARCANIST.name: Spammy Arcanist
SPAMMY ARCANIST.flavorText: You don't have to jump while spamming, but it’s more fun that way.

GRIMTOTEM BUZZKILL.name: Grimtotem Buzzkill
GRIMTOTEM BUZZKILL.flavorText: I'd be mad too if you called me a 'buzzkill'.

ARMORSMITH.name: Armorsmith
ARMORSMITH.flavorText: She accepts guild funds for repairs!

MAIDEN OF THE LAKE.name: Maiden of the Lake
MAIDEN OF THE LAKE.flavorText: Not a good basis for a system of government.

VECTUS.name: Vectus
VECTUS.flavorText: Don’t let that dark magic worry you. He’ll ensure they hatch without a scratch.

RING MATRON.name: Ring Matron
RING MATRON.flavorText: But where does she keep them?

HIDDEN WISDOM.name: Hidden Wisdom
HIDDEN WISDOM.flavorText: Find your own wisdom. Perhaps behind the couch.

POMPOUS THESPIAN.name: Pompous Thespian
POMPOUS THESPIAN.flavorText: Alas poor Annoy-o-Tron! A fellow of infinite jest, of most excellent fancy!

RELIC OF PHANTASMS.name: Relic of Phantasms
RELIC OF PHANTASMS.flavorText: Xy'mox chuckled. "You mean the Chaos Emerald?"

STICKY SITUATION.name: Sticky Situation
STICKY SITUATION.flavorText: "Now this is what I'd call..." "...just shut up."

SEEPING OOZELING.name: Seeping Oozeling
SEEPING OOZELING.flavorText: Uh, you might want to get that looked at.

MALTED MAGMA.name: Malted Magma
MALTED MAGMA.flavorText: Most celebrities nope out at this one.

SIRA'KESS CULTIST.name: Sira'kess Cultist
SIRA'KESS CULTIST.flavorText: "Sira'kess, she's the best! Puts her followers to the test.

HENCH-CLAN SNEAK.name: Hench-Clan Sneak
HENCH-CLAN SNEAK.flavorText: He’d be a lot sneakier if he wasn’t trailing 300 yards of power cable…

GADGETZAN JOUSTER.name: Gadgetzan Jouster
GADGETZAN JOUSTER.flavorText: It's not HER fault you didn't put a spinning saw blade on your horse.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/5b/VO_AT_133_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_133_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/8e/VO_AT_133_ATTACK_ALT1_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_133_ATTACK_ALT1_03.wav Full speed!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/31/VO_AT_133_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_133_DEATH_04.wav <death sound>

CHILLMAW.name: Chillmaw
CHILLMAW.flavorText: Chillmaw keeps trying to ruin the Grand Tournament, and she would've done it too, if it weren't for those dang kids!

IMPRISONED PHOENIX.name: Imprisoned Phoenix
IMPRISONED PHOENIX.flavorText: It's actually pretty easy to escape chains when you can burst into flames.

DRAKKARI ENCHANTER.name: Drakkari Enchanter
DRAKKARI ENCHANTER.flavorText: Drakkari sorceresses have the irritating habit of repeating themselves at the end of every sentence. Every sentence.

CORPSE FARM.name: Corpse Farm
CORPSE FARM.flavorText: It ain't much, but it's dishonest work.

FRACKING.name: Fracking
FRACKING.flavorText: For fhe person who jusf cannof decide whaf card fo puf info a deck!

HULLBREAKER.name: Hullbreaker
HULLBREAKER.flavorText: Breaks through the hard shell to reach the ship's gooey interior.

LIVING MONUMENT.name: Living Monument
LIVING MONUMENT.flavorText: This is not the greatest card in the world. This is just a monument.

BLOATED PYTHON.name: Bloated Python
BLOATED PYTHON.flavorText: This is why Scholomance engineering students prefer C++.

HYENA ALPHA.name: Hyena Alpha
HYENA ALPHA.flavorText: Everything the sun touches is ours—so long as it's already dead.

KOBOLD APPRENTICE.name: Kobold Apprentice
KOBOLD APPRENTICE.flavorText: Horrible secret: The Darkness is immune to Arcane Missiles.

THE CAVERNS BELOW.name: The Caverns Below
THE CAVERNS BELOW.flavorText: Why can't it ever be The Taverns Below?

GLOWFLY SWARM.name: Glowfly Swarm
GLOWFLY SWARM.flavorText: Glowflies are distant relations to spelling bees.

DEATHWEAVER AURA.name: Deathweaver Aura
DEATHWEAVER AURA.flavorText: Knitting is a harmless hobby. Weaving, though...

IDENTITY THEFT.name: Identity Theft
IDENTITY THEFT.flavorText: Identity theft is not a joke, Jim!

PINT-SIZE POTION.name: Pint-Size Potion
PINT-SIZE POTION.flavorText: I hope you didn't disenchant your Shadow Word: Horror!

PSYCH-O-TRON.name: Psych-o-Tron
PSYCH-O-TRON.flavorText: "Annoyinger-o-Tron" was just too unwieldy. And accurate.

ETERNAL SENTINEL.name: Eternal Sentinel
ETERNAL SENTINEL.flavorText: Just try to avoid eye contact.

BRONZE HERALD.name: Bronze Herald
BRONZE HERALD.flavorText: This is why you shouldn’t shoot the messenger.

LION'S FRENZY.name: Lion's Frenzy
LION'S FRENZY.flavorText: Only as sharp as your draw.

NITHOGG.name: Nithogg
NITHOGG.flavorText: Not to be confused with Nithogger.

SPELLZERKER.name: Spellzerker
SPELLZERKER.flavorText: But don’t ask her to use it in a sentence.

HOLLOW HOUND.name: Hollow Hound
HOLLOW HOUND.flavorText: Uh oh, the hollow hound is coming out of its cage! Don't worry though, it's doing just fine.

BURGLY BULLY.name: Burgly Bully
BURGLY BULLY.flavorText: He only burgles to pay the bills. He is really just a bully at heart.

COMMAND THE ILLIDARI.name: Command the Illidari
COMMAND THE ILLIDARI.flavorText: Give me an R! Give me a U! Give me an S! Give me an H! You two, you’re exclamation points!

CORRUPTED ASHBRINGER.name: Corrupted Ashbringer
CORRUPTED ASHBRINGER.flavorText: Put your faith in the blight!

FORENSIC DUSTER.name: Forensic Duster
FORENSIC DUSTER.flavorText: He had plenty of experience with dusting things from his time as a butler, so when a murder was committed he saw a real job opportunity!

RUNIC CARVINGS.name: Runic Carvings
RUNIC CARVINGS.flavorText: "That totem was beautiful… and you runed it!"

FOCUSED WILL.name: Focused Will
FOCUSED WILL.flavorText: Extreme focus is almost as effective as a really flashy distraction.

DRUID OF THE SCYTHE.name: Druid of the Scythe
DRUID OF THE SCYTHE.flavorText: She's a scythe for sore eyes.

ABUSIVE SERGEANT.name: Abusive Sergeant
ABUSIVE SERGEANT.flavorText: ADD ME TO YOUR DECK, MAGGOT!

SCALDING GEYSER.name: Scalding Geyser
SCALDING GEYSER.flavorText: ”Wow, what’s that land formation called?” “It s’cald a Geyser.”

BONE GLAIVE.name: Bone Glaive
BONE GLAIVE.flavorText: Resourceful Demon Hunters find a use for every part of the Demon.

AKALI, THE RHINO.name: Akali, the Rhino
AKALI, THE RHINO.flavorText: Most trolls only get to “AAAAHHH!” and don’t make it to the “kali” part.

PLOT TWIST.name: Plot Twist
PLOT TWIST.flavorText: It’s coming from inside the deck!

VIOLET WURM.name: Violet Wurm
VIOLET WURM.flavorText: It's wurms all the way down.

KAEL'THAS SINSTRIDER.name: Kael'thas Sinstrider
KAEL'THAS SINSTRIDER.flavorText: You heard about Kael'thas? That's messed up, right?

TRAMPLING RHINO.name: Trampling Rhino
TRAMPLING RHINO.flavorText: "Whew. I thought you said 'Trampoline Rhino.' Now that would have been scary."

SILVER VANGUARD.name: Silver Vanguard
SILVER VANGUARD.flavorText: Float like a Faerie Dragon, sting like a Hivequeen.

RINGMASTER WHATLEY.name: Ringmaster Whatley
RINGMASTER WHATLEY.flavorText: His main qualification is that he'll work with anyone. Or anything.

OBSERVER OF MYSTERIES.name: Observer of Mysteries
OBSERVER OF MYSTERIES.flavorText: Nobody tell him, but he still has his Secrets set to the "Try Me" mode.

XYRELLA.name: Xyrella
XYRELLA.flavorText: On the Night of Falling Stars, Xyrella had a vision of a shattered naaru. "Go to the Barrens," the being said. "Seek the shards of my broken body. Restore me, and I will restore your daughter."

LUCKYDO BUCCANEER.name: Luckydo Buccaneer
LUCKYDO BUCCANEER.flavorText: You can't just leave a Luckydo somewhere. You gotta keep 'em with you! Especially in Gadgetzan!

SHA'TARI CLOAKFIELD.name: Sha'tari Cloakfield
SHA'TARI CLOAKFIELD.flavorText: The Sha'tari are the reigning champions of interdimensional hide-and-go-seek.

DOZING DRAGON.name: Dozing Dragon
DOZING DRAGON.flavorText: Emerald dreams can become emerald realities.

PLAYMAKER.name: Playmaker
PLAYMAKER.flavorText: "Here's the plan: you go left, I go right, and the wounded guy takes the hit."

ELITE TAUREN CHAMPION.name: Elite Tauren Champion
ELITE TAUREN CHAMPION.flavorText: Strumming his guitar with a molten ember from the first fire of Azeroth, E.T.C.'s ear-splitting, heart-wrenching, head-banging solo held back Magatha and her forces of evil, single-handedly saving music for centuries to come.

THROW GLAIVE.name: Throw Glaive
THROW GLAIVE.flavorText: "No, no, I said SHOW me the glaive!"

FROSTBITE.name: Frostbite
FROSTBITE.flavorText: The sad reality of a raging toothpaste addiction.

MALFURION'S GIFT.name: Malfurion's Gift
MALFURION'S GIFT.flavorText: "May this imbue you with the life of the party!" -Malfurion

SKYFIN.name: Skyfin
SKYFIN.flavorText: "Do you want to be a murloc or a dragon?" "Yes."

OUTRIDER'S AXE.name: Outrider's Axe
OUTRIDER'S AXE.flavorText: "I only have to get 4 Zhevra hooves? How hard could that be?"

VAPORIZE.name: Vaporize
VAPORIZE.flavorText: Rumor has it that Deathwing brought about the Cataclysm after losing a game to this card. We may never know the truth.

COSPLAY CONTESTANT.name: Cosplay Contestant
COSPLAY CONTESTANT.flavorText: She's the winner of the Valeera Cosplay Contest! Second place was Valeera.

PLAGUED PROTODRAKE.name: Plagued Protodrake
PLAGUED PROTODRAKE.flavorText: "What’s in the drake?! WHAT’S IN THE DRAKE?"

KLAXXI AMBER-WEAVER.name: Klaxxi Amber-Weaver
KLAXXI AMBER-WEAVER.flavorText: Amberweaving is a specialty course at the local trade school.

GALLOPING SAVIOR.name: Galloping Savior
GALLOPING SAVIOR.flavorText: "Look to my coming on the first light of the third card."

APEXIS SMUGGLER.name: Apexis Smuggler
APEXIS SMUGGLER.flavorText: "S-secrets? I don't have any! Whoa, look, a spell!"

BLACK CAT.name: Black Cat
BLACK CAT.flavorText: She's so odd, you can't even.

ETERNIUM ROVER.name: Eternium Rover
ETERNIUM ROVER.flavorText: He's all beeps and smiles but you're just a walking pile of armor to him.

COSTUMED ENTERTAINER.name: Costumed Entertainer
COSTUMED ENTERTAINER.flavorText: Just remember not to talk. It breaks character.

SHIELD SHATTER.name: Shield Shatter
SHIELD SHATTER.flavorText: "Is the shield being shattered or doing the shattering?" "Yes."

FIREBRAND.name: Firebrand
FIREBRAND.flavorText: Too cool for school, too hot for thought.

COERCE.name: Coerce
COERCE.flavorText: "Give me your lunch money, or the sandwich gets it!"

PUPPETMASTER DORIAN.name: Puppetmaster Dorian
PUPPETMASTER DORIAN.flavorText: Though Dorian may officially be working under Dr. Boom, we all know who's really pulling the strings...

MERCH SELLER.name: Merch Seller
MERCH SELLER.flavorText: "Sorry, we're all out of Mediums. All we've got left are Gnome, Extra Large, and Annihilan."

SORCEROUS SUBSTITUTE.name: Sorcerous Substitute
SORCEROUS SUBSTITUTE.flavorText: This substitute's substitution is a dangerous institution.

CRYSTALLINE ORACLE.name: Crystalline Oracle
CRYSTALLINE ORACLE.flavorText: Being made of light has its disadvantages, but at least it's always looking on the bright side.

SURVIVAL OF THE FITTEST.name: Survival of the Fittest
SURVIVAL OF THE FITTEST.flavorText: Sometimes the fittest is the one smart enough to not start a fight with seven 6/6 Treants.

DEVIATE DREADFANG.name: Deviate Dreadfang
DEVIATE DREADFANG.flavorText: Even with wings, snakes STILL don't have legs.

GUARD THE CITY.name: Guard the City
GUARD THE CITY.flavorText: At thousands of feet below the surface, it's a pretty high-pressure job.

AEGIS OF LIGHT.name: Aegis of Light
AEGIS OF LIGHT.flavorText: "Try scooching together! The arrows are getting through!"

NOZDORMU.name: Nozdormu
NOZDORMU.flavorText: Time to write some flavor text.

FLOPPY HYDRA.name: Floppy Hydra
FLOPPY HYDRA.flavorText: If you cut one of its heads off, it'll grow back twice as cute!

FREE SPIRIT.name: Free Spirit
FREE SPIRIT.flavorText: His soul was supposed to go to Ardenweald, but you can't chain a free spirit down.

UTGARDE GRAPPLESNIPER.name: Utgarde Grapplesniper
UTGARDE GRAPPLESNIPER.flavorText: Note: The dragon may be a little cranky upon arrival.

MASKED REVELER.name: Masked Reveler
MASKED REVELER.flavorText: "It's party time! P-A-R-T-Why? Because I gotta!"

PARTY CRASHER.name: Party Crasher
PARTY CRASHER.flavorText: "Do you ever wonder why you don't get invited anywhere?" "… no, not really."

FROST LICH JAINA.name: Frost Lich Jaina
FROST LICH JAINA.flavorText: "Arthas was a spoiled child, playing with toys he could neither control nor understand. Come into the cold. I will show you the true power of the Frozen Throne."

CONSUME.name: Consume
CONSUME.flavorText: What are you looking at? This isn't a mukbang.

CONJURER'S CALLING.name: Conjurer's Calling
CONJURER'S CALLING.flavorText: If only you’d let it go to voicemail…

NOSTALGIC GNOME.name: Nostalgic Gnome
NOSTALGIC GNOME.flavorText: She remembers Alterac Valley like it was 833 days ago.

HELYA.name: Helya
HELYA.flavorText: Named after the first thing Odyn said after landing a sick kickflip.

HEAVY METAL!.name: Heavy Metal!
HEAVY METAL!.flavorText: This metal is so heavy it will satisfy your iron requirements for the next year.

COLAQUE.name: Colaque
COLAQUE.flavorText: Ten thousand years ago, the city of Zin-Azshari fell to the bottom of the sea... and partially onto Colaque's shell.

HEDGE MAZE.name: Hedge Maze
HEDGE MAZE.flavorText: If you keep seeing a statue of the Sire, you’re not going in circles. There’s just so many of them.

VERDANT DREAMSABER.name: Verdant Dreamsaber
VERDANT DREAMSABER.flavorText: Hey, at least the card frame is verdant.

THEOTAR, THE MAD DUKE.name: Theotar, the Mad Duke
THEOTAR, THE MAD DUKE.flavorText: "I'm afraid you've gone mad! You're entirely bonkers. But I'll tell you a secret. All the best souls are."

BULL DOZER.name: Bull Dozer
BULL DOZER.flavorText: Leave them alone for two minutes and they go right into sleep mode.

FELFIRE DEADEYE.name: Felfire Deadeye
FELFIRE DEADEYE.flavorText: She only shoots people who pet her cat without asking first.

HEROIC INNKEEPER.name: Heroic Innkeeper
HEROIC INNKEEPER.flavorText: We reserve the right to refuse service to any 1/1.

ALL TERRAIN VOIDHOUND.name: All Terrain Voidhound
ALL TERRAIN VOIDHOUND.flavorText: 4 claw drive, independent joint suspension AND a 7 mana warranty? Where do I sign?

PREDATION.name: Predation
PREDATION.flavorText: No need to worry! The squid is actually being sent to a nice kelp farm upstate.

SHADOW SUFFUSION.name: Shadow Suffusion
SHADOW SUFFUSION.flavorText: Be honest - you had to look up what that means.

SOULFIRE.name: Soulfire
SOULFIRE.flavorText: Are you lighting a soul on fire? Or burning someone with your OWN soul? This seems like an important distinction.

SOUTHSEA DECKHAND.name: Southsea Deckhand
SOUTHSEA DECKHAND.flavorText: Pirates are into this new fad called "Planking".

JUICY PSYCHMELON.name: Juicy Psychmelon
JUICY PSYCHMELON.flavorText: It's not juicy at all. IT'S JUST MESSING WITH YOUR HEAD.

EERIE STATUE.name: Eerie Statue
EERIE STATUE.flavorText: Don't blink! Don't turn your back, don't look away, and DON'T BLINK.

GIANT WASP.name: Giant Wasp
GIANT WASP.flavorText: Float like a butterfly, sting like a giant wasp!

TUNNEL TROGG.name: Tunnel Trogg
TUNNEL TROGG.flavorText: Sure, they're ugly, but they live in tunnels. You try your beauty routine without natural light.

LOST IN THE JUNGLE.name: Lost in the Jungle
LOST IN THE JUNGLE.flavorText: George and Karl were never heard from again.

DRAGONRIDER TALRITHA.name: Dragonrider Talritha
DRAGONRIDER TALRITHA.flavorText: You can't just run away from your problems. Unless you have another dragon to jump to.

HENCH-CLAN THUG.name: Hench-Clan Thug
HENCH-CLAN THUG.flavorText: Hard time making ends meet? Hate the League of Explorers? Get a job henching!

SUMMONER DARKMARROW.name: Summoner Darkmarrow
SUMMONER DARKMARROW.flavorText: Some people say your name can influence what career you go into. Summoner Darkmarrow is not one of those people.

MANKRIK.name: Mankrik
MANKRIK.flavorText: Relives his nightmare every day a new Horde player is created.

DARKSPEAR BERSERKER.name: Darkspear Berserker
DARKSPEAR BERSERKER.flavorText: "If I die, I'm taking my hero down with me."

ANYFIN CAN HAPPEN.name: Anyfin Can Happen
ANYFIN CAN HAPPEN.flavorText: Theme song by Ellie Goldfin and Blagghghlrlrl Harris.

PTERRORDAX HATCHLING.name: Pterrordax Hatchling
PTERRORDAX HATCHLING.flavorText: Aww. So cute. Want to feed him another finger?

CONQUEROR'S BANNER.name: Conqueror's Banner
CONQUEROR'S BANNER.flavorText: Olgra, I love your new tapestry! Where did you get it?

ZAI, THE INCREDIBLE.name: Zai, the Incredible
ZAI, THE INCREDIBLE.flavorText: Following this act will be her younger brother, Frank the Mediocre.

STEAM SURGER.name: Steam Surger
STEAM SURGER.flavorText: Explorers nicknamed him the Teapot Elemental.

STONESKIN ARMORER.name: Stoneskin Armorer
STONESKIN ARMORER.flavorText: Pretty sensitive for someone made of thick skin.

SPIDER TANK.name: Spider Tank
SPIDER TANK.flavorText: "What if we put guns on it?" -Fizzblitz, staring at the spider-transportation-machine

DEFENSE ATTORNEY NATHANOS.name: Defense Attorney Nathanos
DEFENSE ATTORNEY NATHANOS.flavorText: "Your Honor, my client was simply trying a new tree trimming technique!"

BOOM WRENCH.name: Boom Wrench
BOOM WRENCH.flavorText: Boom, the Inventor; Can he fix it? Boom, the Inventor; No he can't!

GHASTLY CONJURER.name: Ghastly Conjurer
GHASTLY CONJURER.flavorText: Wearing purple after the holidays? GHASTLY!

GENEROUS MUMMY.name: Generous Mummy
GENEROUS MUMMY.flavorText: Yeah, she's mummified, but her money hasn’t dried up!

BRASSWING.name: Brasswing
BRASSWING.flavorText: I’ve seen this before. You just have to time it right to avoid the dragon.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/75/AV_340_Brasswing_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ AV_340_Brasswing_Play.wav <summon sound>

DEVOUT DUNGEONEER.name: Devout Dungeoneer
DEVOUT DUNGEONEER.flavorText: "Please do smaller pulls, this is my first time healing."

INTERSTELLAR STARSLICER.name: Interstellar Starslicer
INTERSTELLAR STARSLICER.flavorText: The universe is infinite. Ever-expanding, its sheer size is something that even the ancestors of our ancestors can only dream of knowing. And even still, across every single pocket of the galaxy, every one thing is unique. So, no, we've never made the same flavor-text twice, IDK what you're talking about.

TWISTED TETHER.name: Twisted Tether
TWISTED TETHER.flavorText: First, convince your opponent that you just want to play tetherball. Then, you GET 'EM!

DEMONHEART.name: Demonheart
DEMONHEART.flavorText: Virtually every member of the pro demon lobby is a warlock. Weird.

SILAS DARKMOON.name: Silas Darkmoon
SILAS DARKMOON.flavorText: "You might remember me from such attractions as 'Being Shot out of a Cannon' or 'That Carousel Ate My Friend.'"

GLOOM STAG.name: Gloom Stag
GLOOM STAG.flavorText: Majestic. Ethereal. Still pretty down in the dumps, though.

WICKED WHISPERS.name: Wicked Whispers
WICKED WHISPERS.flavorText: When the Old Ones whisper, others will scream.

COLD STORAGE.name: Cold Storage
COLD STORAGE.flavorText: Sapphiron's favorite treat always was popsicles.

MURGUR MURGURGLE.name: Murgur Murgurgle
MURGUR MURGURGLE.flavorText: Murlocs are not native to Outland. When the Sungills arrived, one among them rose to the challenge of this dark world. They call him... Murgurgle. Murgur Murgurgle.

DEATHWING.name: Deathwing
DEATHWING.flavorText: Once a noble dragon known as Neltharion, Deathwing lost his mind and shattered Azeroth before finally being defeated. Daddy issues?

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/4/4b/VO_NEW1_030_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_NEW1_030_Play_01.wav I am power incarnate!

INVINCIBLE.name: Invincible
INVINCIBLE.flavorText: No it's not, I can see it right there.

CORRUPTION.name: Corruption
CORRUPTION.flavorText: It starts with stealing a pen from work, and before you know it, BOOOM! Corrupted!

TANGLEFUR MYSTIC.name: Tanglefur Mystic
TANGLEFUR MYSTIC.flavorText: Doom! Only doom for you! But pay good tip, maybe less doom.

PLAGUE OF DEATH.name: Plague of Death
PLAGUE OF DEATH.flavorText: Don't worry, there's a happy little funhouse right under that sand pit.

IMPRISONED FELMAW.name: Imprisoned Felmaw
IMPRISONED FELMAW.flavorText: It doesn't care who woke it up, someone's getting bitten.

SOULSHARD LAPIDARY.name: Soulshard Lapidary
SOULSHARD LAPIDARY.flavorText: Also known as a soul sequincer.

GORMOK THE IMPALER.name: Gormok the Impaler
GORMOK THE IMPALER.flavorText: Gormok has been giving impaling lessons in a small tent near the tournament grounds. For only 25g you too could learn the fine art of impaling!

SADDLE UP!.name: Saddle Up!
SADDLE UP!.flavorText: And then they rode off into the sunset, not knowing they left their stove on.

HIPPOGRYPH.name: Hippogryph
HIPPOGRYPH.flavorText: Known for its ferocious grace, the hippogryph is a truly majestic creature. Except when molting.

ENSLAVED FEL LORD.name: Enslaved Fel Lord
ENSLAVED FEL LORD.flavorText: He's not really chained up. He just wears that to scare the imps when they get too unruly.

COLDARRA DRAKE.name: Coldarra Drake
COLDARRA DRAKE.flavorText: The Grand Tournament has a "No dragons allowed" policy, but it's rarely enforced.

ENCUMBERED PACK MULE.name: Encumbered Pack Mule
ENCUMBERED PACK MULE.flavorText: "Now I can pick up EVERY knick-knack."

NELLIE, THE GREAT THRESHER.name: Nellie, the Great Thresher
NELLIE, THE GREAT THRESHER.flavorText: Not to be mistaken for her freshwater cousin, Nessie, this massive creature was harnessed to carry Hooktusk's favorite ship.

ARCANE WATCHER.name: Arcane Watcher
ARCANE WATCHER.flavorText: Now his watch has ended… until you have Spell Damage.

EAGLEHORN BOW.name: Eaglehorn Bow
EAGLEHORN BOW.flavorText: First Lesson: Put the pointy end in the other guy.

PLAGUEMAW THE ROTTING.name: Plaguemaw the Rotting
PLAGUEMAW THE ROTTING.flavorText: This is why you should brush your teeth three times a day!

PRIMAL FUSION.name: Primal Fusion
PRIMAL FUSION.flavorText: Golce and Dabbana have a new line of Earth Totems available at vendors everywhere this holiday season.

GRIMESTREET PROTECTOR.name: Grimestreet Protector
GRIMESTREET PROTECTOR.flavorText: Some new asphalt should do the trick.

MENAGERIE JUG.name: Menagerie Jug
MENAGERIE JUG.flavorText: It's art imitating Battlegrounds imitating life.

TENTACLES FOR ARMS.name: Tentacles for Arms
TENTACLES FOR ARMS.flavorText: That's right. Garrosh just slapped you to death with a tentacle.

POWER INFUSION.name: Power Infusion
POWER INFUSION.flavorText: It infuses, it enthuses, it amuses!

BLOODBOUND IMP.name: Bloodbound Imp
BLOODBOUND IMP.flavorText: ALWAYS read the terms and conditions.

VOLCANIC DRAKE.name: Volcanic Drake
VOLCANIC DRAKE.flavorText: Volcanic Drakes breathe lava instead of fire. The antacid vendor at Thorium Point does a brisk business with them.

BARBED THORN.name: Barbed Thorn
BARBED THORN.flavorText: Comes with a pack of bandages.

CAULDRON ELEMENTAL.name: Cauldron Elemental
CAULDRON ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Decorating tip: Unused cauldrons can make a lovely elemental display.

REFLECTO ENGINEER.name: Reflecto Engineer
REFLECTO ENGINEER.flavorText: The whole thing's based on the Rubber-Glue Phenomenon.

ALTAR OF FIRE.name: Altar of Fire
ALTAR OF FIRE.flavorText: "I now pronounce you, Crispy and Fried."

MADDEST BOMBER.name: Maddest Bomber
MADDEST BOMBER.flavorText: Talk about a name that limits design space.

MAJORDOMO EXECUTUS.name: Majordomo Executus
MAJORDOMO EXECUTUS.flavorText: You thought Executus turned you into Ragnaros, but really Ragnaros was in you the whole time.

RESIZING POUCH.name: Resizing Pouch
RESIZING POUCH.flavorText: Just don't put a Resizing Pouch inside the Resizing Pouch.

DISCIPLE OF AMITUS.name: Disciple of Amitus
DISCIPLE OF AMITUS.flavorText: "Oh great Amitus, I took your style advice on the poncho, but pray tell - one or two golden gloves?"

SNEAKY DELINQUENT.name: Sneaky Delinquent
SNEAKY DELINQUENT.flavorText: All right, now open your lid and say "Ahh!"

WORTHY EXPEDITION.name: Worthy Expedition
WORTHY EXPEDITION.flavorText: This isn't where I parked my mount.

CALL TO THE STAND.name: Call to the Stand
CALL TO THE STAND.flavorText: Don't worry, there is a chair for you to sit in. It's very misleading.

WEAPONS PROJECT.name: Weapons Project
WEAPONS PROJECT.flavorText: Harrison Jones was kicked off this project.

WASTELAND ASSASSIN.name: Wasteland Assassin
WASTELAND ASSASSIN.flavorText: They'll never see me coming, what with my glowing body, eyes and daggers.

EVOCATION.name: Evocation
EVOCATION.flavorText: You too could be the winner of the national spelling spree!

LESSER SPINEL SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Spinel Spellstone
LESSER SPINEL SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A story concluded, the kobolds had fought Yet here is a spellstone Azari forgot Pawned off to shops, considered a trinket Dark powers contained, none would think it

LIVING MANA.name: Living Mana
LIVING MANA.flavorText: If you truly love your mana, set it free.

MALFURION THE PESTILENT.name: Malfurion the Pestilent
MALFURION THE PESTILENT.flavorText: "Cenarius once taught me about the precarious balance between life and death. I have come to understand: there IS no balance. Death always wins."

ONYX BISHOP.name: Onyx Bishop
ONYX BISHOP.flavorText: B4 is a nice place to visit, but he wouldn't want to live there.

HANDMAIDEN.name: Handmaiden
HANDMAIDEN.flavorText: Why did she unspool the last roll of royal toilet paper?!

BENEATH THE GROUNDS.name: Beneath the Grounds
BENEATH THE GROUNDS.flavorText: Can you hold these eggs for just a second? I promise they're not full of giant enraged undead spider things.

FLARK'S BOOM-ZOOKA.name: Flark's Boom-Zooka
FLARK'S BOOM-ZOOKA.flavorText: It used to be a Ba-zooka but we ran out of sheep.

UNDERTAKER.name: Undertaker
UNDERTAKER.flavorText: In a world where you can run to a spirit healer and resurrect yourself, Undertakers do pretty light business.

BLACKWING TECHNICIAN.name: Blackwing Technician
BLACKWING TECHNICIAN.flavorText: This is who you go to when your Blackwing needs a tune up. Don't go to a cut rate Blackwing tune up shop!

HIVE QUEEN.name: Hive Queen
HIVE QUEEN.flavorText: Her favorite game is "The Floor is Larva."

SUNSPOT DRAGON.name: Sunspot Dragon
SUNSPOT DRAGON.flavorText: THIS is why you shouldn't look directly at the sun.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/28/BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav <summon sound>

ANETHERON.name: Anetheron
ANETHERON.flavorText: Leads every demonic invasion. Hopefully this one turns out better than the World Tree.

SKYBARGE.name: Skybarge
SKYBARGE.flavorText: It's more of a ship-gun than a gunship.

UNENDING SWARM.name: Unending Swarm
UNENDING SWARM.flavorText: swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm swarm -

MISCHIEF MAKER.name: Mischief Maker
MISCHIEF MAKER.flavorText: Fair trade is for noble-minded suckers with dignity and honor.

RELIC OF DIMENSIONS.name: Relic of Dimensions
RELIC OF DIMENSIONS.flavorText: A glaive is a glaive, but a mystery box could be anything! It could even be a glaive!

TAINTED ZEALOT.name: Tainted Zealot
TAINTED ZEALOT.flavorText: The love she shares seems to go nowhere. Now she's lost her Light, tosses and turns, she can't sleep at night...

ASHAMANE.name: Ashamane
ASHAMANE.flavorText: In ancient times, Ashamane sacrificed herself to save night elves from the Legion’s wrath. Her name is still honored among their descendants.

GUILD TRADER.name: Guild Trader
GUILD TRADER.flavorText: Somehow, she manages six different professions.

I KNOW A GUY.name: I Know a Guy
I KNOW A GUY.flavorText: Well… a guy who knows a guy.

CRIMSON HOTHEAD.name: Crimson Hothead
CRIMSON HOTHEAD.flavorText: Has a real passion for spelling.

STRONGMAN.name: Strongman
STRONGMAN.flavorText: Sure, it looks impressive until you realize it's a barrel of helium.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/be/VO_DMF_078_Male_Orc_Play_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_DMF_078_Male_Orc_Play_02.wav Feat of strength? Pfft, arms of strength!

DISTRESS SIGNAL.name: Distress Signal
DISTRESS SIGNAL.flavorText: HELP! HEEELP! MY OPPONENT PLAYED CARDS!

FAIRY TALE FOREST.name: Fairy Tale Forest
FAIRY TALE FOREST.flavorText: Man, I wish fairy tales were real, Durg'tash the Sorcerer.

SANDWASP QUEEN.name: Sandwasp Queen
SANDWASP QUEEN.flavorText: Oooh, see that wasp! Watch that sting! Dig in the Sandwasp Queen!

SANC'AZEL.name: Sanc'Azel
SANC'AZEL.flavorText: That castle has some serious drip.

RAGING FELSCREAMER.name: Raging Felscreamer
RAGING FELSCREAMER.flavorText: Screaming loudly will not reduce the cost of non-demonic goods.

RAT PACK.name: Rat Pack
RAT PACK.flavorText: He's gonna do it his way.

LOST TALLSTRIDER.name: Lost Tallstrider
LOST TALLSTRIDER.flavorText: The message, "If found, please return to Mulgore," is tattooed on his rear.

SHERIFF BARRELBRIM.name: Sheriff Barrelbrim
SHERIFF BARRELBRIM.flavorText: Is that Sheriff Barrelbrim, owner of the Badlands Barrelbuilding?

THOR.name: Thor
THOR.flavorText: "I need your clothes, your boots and your chitinous exoskeleton."

HARMONIC METAL.name: Harmonic Metal
HARMONIC METAL.flavorText: I have bashed together plenty of pieces of metal in my day and not ONCE has it sounded harmonic.

BLIGHTNOZZLE CRAWLER.name: Blightnozzle Crawler
BLIGHTNOZZLE CRAWLER.flavorText: "Well we HAD it contained. Then you went and gave it legs!"

KOBOLD HERMIT.name: Kobold Hermit
KOBOLD HERMIT.flavorText: To truly understand candles, it takes YEARS of quiet contemplation.

MECHA'THUN.name: Mecha'thun
MECHA'THUN.flavorText: "Your software will fail. Your users will abandon you. You are already obsolete."

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/8/83/VO_BOT_424_Male_OldGod_Attack_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BOT_424_Male_OldGod_Attack_01.wav Death is close.

ARCANE DYNAMO.name: Arcane Dynamo
ARCANE DYNAMO.flavorText: We ran out of jars, so we started putting brains in other stuff.

GRIMSCALE CHUM.name: Grimscale Chum
GRIMSCALE CHUM.flavorText: Listen, see? We'll take 'em to the docks, see? And throw 'em in the sea, see?

FLAMEWAKER.name: Flamewaker
FLAMEWAKER.flavorText: Flamewakers HATE being confused for Flamewalkers. They just wake up fire, they don’t walk on it. Walking on fire is CRAZY.

DOWN WITH THE SHIP.name: Down with the Ship
DOWN WITH THE SHIP.flavorText: It has been a privilege playing with you tonight.

TAR SLICK.name: Tar Slick
TAR SLICK.flavorText: Has +2 Attack on its opponent's turn.

CELESTIAL INK SET.name: Celestial Ink Set
CELESTIAL INK SET.flavorText: "Dear Mother, I have a lot of spells and burst in my hand. You should maybe run more armor and healing next time. Cordially, Your child"

REND BLACKHAND.name: Rend Blackhand
REND BLACKHAND.flavorText: Rend believes he is the True Warchief of the Horde and he keeps editing the wikipedia page for "Warchief of the Horde" to include his picture.

BLOODWORM.name: Bloodworm
BLOODWORM.flavorText: Queen Lana'thel insists on one of these, fried, every morning for breakfast.

CEREMONIAL MAUL.name: Ceremonial Maul
CEREMONIAL MAUL.flavorText: For the most discerning of hall monitors.

SERENITY.name: Serenity
SERENITY.flavorText: Ra-den loves teaching yoga on his off-hours.

ARCH-THIEF RAFAAM.name: Arch-Thief Rafaam
ARCH-THIEF RAFAAM.flavorText: He's very good at retrieving artifacts. From other people's museums.

SILVERFURY STALWART.name: Silverfury Stalwart
SILVERFURY STALWART.flavorText: Don't strike until you see the whites of their teeth.

OH, MANAGER!.name: Oh, Manager!
OH, MANAGER!.flavorText: "I'd like to speak with your admiral."

JIM RAYNOR.name: Jim Raynor
JIM RAYNOR.flavorText: He’s lost his faith, his friends, and his beloved, but he still believes that one day, he can make things right again.

STALWART AVENGER.name: Stalwart Avenger
STALWART AVENGER.flavorText: A good defense is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense which is a good defense which is a good offense!

MAN THE CANNONS.name: Man the Cannons
MAN THE CANNONS.flavorText: Now THAT’S a lotta splash damage!

JUKEBOX TOTEM.name: Jukebox Totem
JUKEBOX TOTEM.flavorText: If you really love Hearthstone, put another coin in the Totem baby!

IRONFORGE PORTAL.name: Ironforge Portal
IRONFORGE PORTAL.flavorText: Come to beautiful Ironforge! Where irons are forged and the forges are iron!

SNEAKY SCOUT.name: Sneaky Scout
SNEAKY SCOUT.flavorText: Do you know what they call Scouts that aren't sneaky? Target practice.

SPIRIT LASH.name: Spirit Lash
SPIRIT LASH.flavorText: We've got spirit, yes we do! We've got spirit, stolen from you!

SERPENT EGG.name: Serpent Egg
SERPENT EGG.flavorText: These things go from "adorable danger noodle!" to "MY FACE IS MELTING!" all too quickly.

LIBRAM OF HOPE.name: Libram of Hope
LIBRAM OF HOPE.flavorText: "Think you got lethal? Libram of NOPE!"

DRAGONLING MECHANIC.name: Dragonling Mechanic
DRAGONLING MECHANIC.flavorText: She is still working on installing the rocket launcher add-on for Mr. Bitey.

ANIMATED BERSERKER.name: Animated Berserker
ANIMATED BERSERKER.flavorText: He'd be a lot easier to animate if he would just stand still.

TRUSTY FISHING ROD.name: Trusty Fishing Rod
TRUSTY FISHING ROD.flavorText: That's weird… I can only catch magic carps with this old fishing rod.

POWER SPIKE.name: Power Spike
POWER SPIKE.flavorText: Jeff, when I said this deck needs a power spike I did not mean it like that.

CHARGE.name: Charge
CHARGE.flavorText: "Guys! Guys! Slow down!" - some kind of non-warrior minion

SENSORY DEPRIVATION.name: Sensory Deprivation
SENSORY DEPRIVATION.flavorText: You'll come out a new person.

WILD SPIRITS.name: Wild Spirits
WILD SPIRITS.flavorText: Wait, this card just released! It should be Standard Spirits!

BLESSING OF KINGS.name: Blessing of Kings
BLESSING OF KINGS.flavorText: Given the number of kings who have been assassinated, are you sure you want their blessing?

EXPENDABLE PERFORMERS.name: Expendable Performers
EXPENDABLE PERFORMERS.flavorText: When someone gets injured, it's considered performance art.

THE DARKNESS.name: The Darkness
THE DARKNESS.flavorText: I would rather light a single candle than curse the darkness. But I'm willing to do both.

DEMON COMPANION.name: Demon Companion
DEMON COMPANION.flavorText: Owning a pet can be real hell at times.

SPRINGPAW.name: Springpaw
SPRINGPAW.flavorText: The terrible thing about lynxes is lynxes are terrible things. Their teeth are made out of biting, their paws are made out of springs!

INFINITE AMALGAM.name: Infinite Amalgam
INFINITE AMALGAM.flavorText: The Infinite Amalgam sought Gammy, the greatest among them, though it feared the queen of the amalgams would never be found.

CROWD ROASTER.name: Crowd Roaster
CROWD ROASTER.flavorText: Every major show has an opening act to warm up the crowd.

ANODIZED ROBO CUB.name: Anodized Robo Cub
ANODIZED ROBO CUB.flavorText: It's adorable! AND OH MY GOODNESS WHY IS IT EATING MY FACE

ARCANE KEYSMITH.name: Arcane Keysmith
ARCANE KEYSMITH.flavorText: She sells all manner of keys: from A flat to G sharp.

WILD BLOODSTINGER.name: Wild Bloodstinger
WILD BLOODSTINGER.flavorText: Tame Bloodstingers would politely invite your minion to tea.

ANACHRONOS.name: Anachronos
ANACHRONOS.flavorText: "That's it, you're all in time out!"

SCARGIL.name: Scargil
SCARGIL.flavorText: Wanna know how he got those scars? So does he.

OVERGROWTH.name: Overgrowth
OVERGROWTH.flavorText: Zangarmarsh: it's a fungal out there!

POTIONMASTER PUTRICIDE.name: Potionmaster Putricide
POTIONMASTER PUTRICIDE.flavorText: "Good news everyone! I'm a Rogue card now!"

DEFIAS LEPER.name: Defias Leper
DEFIAS LEPER.flavorText: Do NOT eat Cookie’s Seafood Surprise.

SLAGMAW THE SLUMBERING.name: Slagmaw the Slumbering
SLAGMAW THE SLUMBERING.flavorText: You delved too greedily and too deep. You know what they awoke in the darkness of the Badlands: Rush and Taunt.

EXPLODING BLOATBAT.name: Exploding Bloatbat
EXPLODING BLOATBAT.flavorText: We've all been there after a night of one-too-many funnel cakes.

PANDAREN IMPORTER.name: Pandaren Importer
PANDAREN IMPORTER.flavorText: She carries everything you didn't want and more!

TWILIGHT'S CALL.name: Twilight's Call
TWILIGHT'S CALL.flavorText: If you’re experiencing resurrection sickness, press 1.

OVERCONFIDENT ORC.name: Overconfident Orc
OVERCONFIDENT ORC.flavorText: "I am da powerful! You are da poop!"

CRYOSTASIS.name: Cryostasis
CRYOSTASIS.flavorText: We'll thaw you out when we find a cure!

VERDANT LONGNECK.name: Verdant Longneck
VERDANT LONGNECK.flavorText: Always sticking its neck into other people’s business.

GARROTE.name: Garrote
GARROTE.flavorText: "I don't have money… but what I do have is a particular set of skills."

TUSKARRRR TRAWLER.name: Tuskarrrr Trawler
TUSKARRRR TRAWLER.flavorText: "Fish scales? Junk. A gravestone? Junk. This weird looking puzzle box? Junk. AHA! An Ancharrr!"

PURIFYING POWER.name: Purifying Power
PURIFYING POWER.flavorText: I sure do love making my minions better!

HOBART GRAPPLEHAMMER.name: Hobart Grapplehammer
HOBART GRAPPLEHAMMER.flavorText: Grapplehammer is the horrible mind behind the Automatic Piranha Launcher (banned in 7 districts)!

MULTI-STRIKE.name: Multi-Strike
MULTI-STRIKE.flavorText: “I said you get two attack, not two attacks!”

GURUBASHI HYPEMON.name: Gurubashi Hypemon
GURUBASHI HYPEMON.flavorText: Throw your hands in the air! They cost (1).

SPAWN OF N'ZOTH.name: Spawn of N'Zoth
SPAWN OF N'ZOTH.flavorText: Who's a cute widdle N'Zoth? You are! Yes you are! Yes you're the cutest widdle N'Zoth in the whole world!!!

NEEDLEROCK TOTEM.name: Needlerock Totem
NEEDLEROCK TOTEM.flavorText: You put the Needlerock in to get the Bloodrock out.

KALIMOS, PRIMAL LORD.name: Kalimos, Primal Lord
KALIMOS, PRIMAL LORD.flavorText: All that's missing is a little heart.

DREADLICH TAMSIN.name: Dreadlich Tamsin
DREADLICH TAMSIN.flavorText: At a certain point, you stop mocking death and start becoming it.

SMELT.name: Smelt
SMELT.flavorText: Due to his heightened olfactory system, Kha'zgoroth is cursed with always being the one that dealt it.

MOGOR'S CHAMPION.name: Mogor's Champion
MOGOR'S CHAMPION.flavorText: This champion has learned from the best. Except for his target selection.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/c2/VO_AT_088_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_088_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e4/VO_AT_088_ATTACK_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_088_ATTACK_03.wav Gimme trophy!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/71/VO_AT_088_DEATH_05.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_088_DEATH_05.wav <death sound>

CHOPSHOP COPTER.name: Chopshop Copter
CHOPSHOP COPTER.flavorText: Invention is the mother of entropy.

UNDERBELLY OOZE.name: Underbelly Ooze
UNDERBELLY OOZE.flavorText: It's always accepting of the less successful adventurers.

ASTRAL AUTOMATON.name: Astral Automaton
ASTRAL AUTOMATON.flavorText: You'll want to summon an automaTON of these.

MANA ADDICT.name: Mana Addict
MANA ADDICT.flavorText: She’s trying to kick the habit, but still takes some mana whenever she has a stressful day.

BIBLIOMITE.name: Bibliomite
BIBLIOMITE.flavorText: He did NOT want to cast a spell.

TWILIGHT TORRENT.name: Twilight Torrent
TWILIGHT TORRENT.flavorText: I hope it’s the first one.

SCARAB KEYCHAIN.name: Scarab Keychain
SCARAB KEYCHAIN.flavorText: "How do you keep losing your keys!? They couldn't have just gotten up and walked away!"

WARSONG OUTRIDER.name: Warsong Outrider
WARSONG OUTRIDER.flavorText: When it comes to the Warsong clan, outriders are the insiders.

BLOODSAIL RECRUITER.name: Bloodsail Recruiter
BLOODSAIL RECRUITER.flavorText: I want YOU! To plunder from the innocent!

FIGHT PROMOTER.name: Fight Promoter
FIGHT PROMOTER.flavorText: "Yeah, I can get you Knuckles. No, no, he's been clean for *weeks*."

NYDUS WORM.name: Nydus Worm
NYDUS WORM.flavorText: How did they fit an ultralisk in there!?

STEAMWHEEDLE SNIPER.name: Steamwheedle Sniper
STEAMWHEEDLE SNIPER.flavorText: Goblins seldom have the patience for sniping. Most prefer lobbing explosives.

FANDRAL STAGHELM.name: Fandral Staghelm
FANDRAL STAGHELM.flavorText: Always manages to mention "Back when I was creating the World Tree…" in EVERY conversation. Sheesh! Enough already.

SINRUNNER.name: Sinrunner
SINRUNNER.flavorText: Blanchy was said to be an affectionate and well-behaved horse in life. How she ended up in Revendreth? We're too afraid to ask.

MULCH.name: Mulch
MULCH.flavorText: Is this a noun or a verb? We will never know.

HEX LORD MALACRASS.name: Hex Lord Malacrass
HEX LORD MALACRASS.flavorText: Extremely awkward cousin of Hex Lord Malaclass.

LIGHTFUSED STEGODON.name: Lightfused Stegodon
LIGHTFUSED STEGODON.flavorText: “Come now, Johnston. I think those horns are quite fetching on you.”

HORN OF WRATHION.name: Horn of Wrathion
HORN OF WRATHION.flavorText: You can count the rings and find out Wrathion's true age.

TABLETOP ROLEPLAYER.name: Tabletop Roleplayer
TABLETOP ROLEPLAYER.flavorText: "And then I uh... I curse them with... uh... OH! I got it! They have to speak in rhymes or they turn into a crab!"

PRIMORDIAL PROTECTOR.name: Primordial Protector
PRIMORDIAL PROTECTOR.flavorText: I thought the "shape of water" meant something else.

CABAL SHADOW PRIEST.name: Cabal Shadow Priest
CABAL SHADOW PRIEST.flavorText: You never know who may be secretly working for the Cabal....

CRYOMANCER.name: Cryomancer
CRYOMANCER.flavorText: She loves Frozen. I mean who doesn't?

FAE TRICKSTER.name: Fae Trickster
FAE TRICKSTER.flavorText: Muahaha they'll never see this spell that costs (5) or more coming!!

IMPRISONED VILEFIEND.name: Imprisoned Vilefiend
IMPRISONED VILEFIEND.flavorText: If you do the time, you gotta make up the time.

CAPTAIN'S LOG.name: Captain's Log
CAPTAIN'S LOG.flavorText: Akama loves a nice comfy log to captain on.

RANGER GILLY.name: Ranger Gilly
RANGER GILLY.flavorText: Get you someone who looks at you the way Ranger Gilly looks at that Crocolisk.

SPIRIT OF THE RHINO.name: Spirit of the Rhino
SPIRIT OF THE RHINO.flavorText: Where did they get this preposterous hypothesis?

FANCY PACKAGING.name: Fancy Packaging
FANCY PACKAGING.flavorText: Wow, this card is great value! Until you open it.

VENGEFUL SPIRIT.name: Vengeful Spirit
VENGEFUL SPIRIT.flavorText: Sheesh, even the spirits are edgy when it comes to Demon Hunters.

WRETCHED RECLAIMER.name: Wretched Reclaimer
WRETCHED RECLAIMER.flavorText: "Ok, here's the plan. We kill you, then bring you back." "Stronger?" "No, about the same."

JEEVES.name: Jeeves
JEEVES.flavorText: This robot is a lean, mean, butlerin' machine.

LIBRAM OF JUSTICE.name: Libram of Justice
LIBRAM OF JUSTICE.flavorText: Proper justice. Throw the book at him!

GROOVY CAT.name: Groovy Cat
GROOVY CAT.flavorText: "Like, what if we're all just cards living in this box called Hearthstone, man?"

FIRE PLUME HARBINGER.name: Fire Plume Harbinger
FIRE PLUME HARBINGER.flavorText: Good for summoning elementals. Great for making s'mores.

HECKLEFANG HYENA.name: Hecklefang Hyena
HECKLEFANG HYENA.flavorText: Even their teeth are laughing at you.

MYSTERIOUS BLADE.name: Mysterious Blade
MYSTERIOUS BLADE.flavorText: It knows every secret you have left.

MOSH PIT.name: Mosh Pit
MOSH PIT.flavorText: Let the Corpses hit the floor!

LIVING ROOTS.name: Living Roots
LIVING ROOTS.flavorText: 2 out of 2 saplings recommend that you summon the saplings.

ARCHMAGE VARGOTH.name: Archmage Vargoth
ARCHMAGE VARGOTH.flavorText: He's an archmage, but he might want to brush up on the basics... like aiming.

STONEMAUL ANCHORMAN.name: Stonemaul Anchorman
STONEMAUL ANCHORMAN.flavorText: "Brug will read anything you put on the parchment prompter. Anything."

BURNING HEART.name: Burning Heart
BURNING HEART.flavorText: A 100% ethically sourced fire elemental heart is very hard to come by. This one definitely wasn't.

EXPLODINATOR.name: Explodinator
EXPLODINATOR.flavorText: When it absolutely, positively, has to blow up overnight.

WRENCHCALIBUR.name: Wrenchcalibur
WRENCHCALIBUR.flavorText: Whoso pulleth out this wrench from the toolbox is rightwise king of the lab.

BUCKET OF SOLDIERS.name: Bucket of Soldiers
BUCKET OF SOLDIERS.flavorText: Life is like a bucket of soldiers. You never know what bonus effects you're gonna get.

TRANQUIL TREANT.name: Tranquil Treant
TRANQUIL TREANT.flavorText: "Cut down my trunk and make a Mana Crystal," said the tree. "Then you can ramp away... and be happy."

PHARAOH CAT.name: Pharaoh Cat
PHARAOH CAT.flavorText: Mightiest of mousers, enduring in kingship of the upper and lower cat tree, conqueror of the red dot, the all-wise Catshepsut.

GUARDIAN ANIMALS.name: Guardian Animals
GUARDIAN ANIMALS.flavorText: The guidelines specifically state: "Students may also bring an ironbeak owl OR an alleycat OR a toad." They never said how big.

SHELL GAME.name: Shell Game
SHELL GAME.flavorText: I thiiink… It's under all three of 'em!

DRAGON EGG.name: Dragon Egg
DRAGON EGG.flavorText: Think of them as bullets for your dragon gun.

SOUL REND.name: Soul Rend
SOUL REND.flavorText: About as close to feeling guilt as a warlock's ever going to get.

EMBALMING RITUAL.name: Embalming Ritual
EMBALMING RITUAL.flavorText: "Guess what! We're getting a new cat."

STATIC WAVEFORM.name: Static Waveform
STATIC WAVEFORM.flavorText: LET ME SEE YOU MAKE SOME NOISE!!!

SOOT SPEWER.name: Soot Spewer
SOOT SPEWER.flavorText: The inventor of the goblin shredder is involved in several patent disputes with the inventor of the soot spewer.

LOR'THEMAR THERON.name: Lor'themar Theron
LOR'THEMAR THERON.flavorText: Out of all his life accomplishments, making a 2/2 Tinyfin is his finest.

OMINOUS NIGHTMARES.name: Ominous Nightmares
OMINOUS NIGHTMARES.flavorText: Everyone keeps talking about nightmares, but I don't see any horses?

MURMY.name: Murmy
MURMY.flavorText: Unlike other mummies, they rolled him up with rice, sliced cucumbers, and soy sauce on the side.

BONE WRAITH.name: Bone Wraith
BONE WRAITH.flavorText: It uses only the eco-friendly bones from free-range humanoids.

NECROLORD DRAKA.name: Necrolord Draka
NECROLORD DRAKA.flavorText: We originally planned on giving Rogue a Legendary minion called "The Moon", but SOMEONE jumped in the frame.

STARGAZING.name: Stargazing
STARGAZING.flavorText: See those dots up there? Those are called "stars." Except for that one. That's called an "airplane."

VIOLET ILLUSIONIST.name: Violet Illusionist
VIOLET ILLUSIONIST.flavorText: She’s much more cheerful after losing the ‘n’ in her name.

DINOSIZE.name: Dinosize
DINOSIZE.flavorText: Comes with fries and a drink.

STEAMCLEANER.name: Steamcleaner
STEAMCLEANER.flavorText: Business is slow since the anima shortage began. Things just don't get stained like they used to!

DIMENSIONAL RIPPER.name: Dimensional Ripper
DIMENSIONAL RIPPER.flavorText: The first dimensional ripper had a point. The second fell flat. The THIRD one really started to take shape!

WATERCANNON.name: Watercannon
WATERCANNON.flavorText: There's a teeny tiny pirate trapped in each of the water balloons. Free them!

EYESTALK OF C'THUN.name: Eyestalk of C'Thun
EYESTALK OF C'THUN.flavorText: C'Thun sees all...even next week's lottery numbers.

MANA RESERVOIR.name: Mana Reservoir
MANA RESERVOIR.flavorText: If it soaks too long, it becomes a reservoir hog.

COWBELL SOLOIST.name: Cowbell Soloist
COWBELL SOLOIST.flavorText: Hot take: We need LESS cowbell. Much, much less.

SHIELDED MINIBOT.name: Shielded Minibot
SHIELDED MINIBOT.flavorText: He chooses to believe what he is programmed to believe!

SILVERMOON SENTINEL.name: Silvermoon Sentinel
SILVERMOON SENTINEL.flavorText: I spent 8 mana polishing this shield, PLEASE don't make me bash you with it.

SWAMPQUEEN HAGATHA.name: Swampqueen Hagatha
SWAMPQUEEN HAGATHA.flavorText: Rafaam mainly enjoys working with Hagatha because she never laughs at Dr. Boom's jokes.

PROFESSOR PUTRICIDE.name: Professor Putricide
PROFESSOR PUTRICIDE.flavorText: Among his more notable inventions: A tentacle-groomer, a plague that would wipe out all life on Azeroth, and a fidget spinner.

INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY.name: Investment Opportunity
INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY.flavorText: "It's a real fixer-upper. I mean a REAL fixer upper."

RAT SENSEI.name: Rat Sensei
RAT SENSEI.flavorText: The old teacher needed to find some tokens with attitude.

CUTTING CLASS.name: Cutting Class
CUTTING CLASS.flavorText: When you actually are the sharpest tool in the shed.

BIG OL' WHELP.name: Big Ol' Whelp
BIG OL' WHELP.flavorText: A chonker, a real absolute unit.

MEDDLESOME SERVANT.name: Meddlesome Servant
MEDDLESOME SERVANT.flavorText: Has successfully gotten away with it too.

WEBWEAVE.name: Webweave
WEBWEAVE.flavorText: O, what a tangled web we weave, hoping spiders dodge the cleave.

BRING IT ON!.name: Bring It On!
BRING IT ON!.flavorText: Brrr, it's cold in here. Let's hope she doesn't have an Auctioneer!

NECROMECHANIC.name: Necromechanic
NECROMECHANIC.flavorText: If at first you don't succeed, die, die again.

WITHER.name: Wither
WITHER.flavorText: The opponent's minion can't live wither without you.

THADDIUS, MONSTROSITY.name: Thaddius, Monstrosity
THADDIUS, MONSTROSITY.flavorText: Feugen is positive that Thaddius will see play, but Stalagg seems negative about it.

FAMISHED FOOL.name: Famished Fool
FAMISHED FOOL.flavorText: He's not hungry for food, he's starving for attention!

LIGHTMENDER.name: Lightmender
LIGHTMENDER.flavorText: How many lightmenders does it take to mend a lightorb?

INVENTOR BOOM.name: Inventor Boom
INVENTOR BOOM.flavorText: The best part of inventing stuff is blowing it up!

ARCHMAGE ARUGAL.name: Archmage Arugal
ARCHMAGE ARUGAL.flavorText: His worgen children call him Archmage AROO-OO-OO-OO-gal.

MECHANO-EGG.name: Mechano-Egg
MECHANO-EGG.flavorText: When you need more iron in your diet.

HOBGOBLIN.name: Hobgoblin
HOBGOBLIN.flavorText: Hobgoblins are meeting next week to discuss union benefits. First on the list: dental plan.

MYSTERIOUS VISITOR.name: Mysterious Visitor
MYSTERIOUS VISITOR.flavorText: Dave, we can tell this letter is fake - it's in your handwriting. And take off that stupid hood, you're embarrassing us.

VELEN, LEADER OF THE EXILED.name: Velen, Leader of the Exiled
VELEN, LEADER OF THE EXILED.flavorText: For an exiled dude, he's pretty popular!

BABA NAGA.name: Baba Naga
BABA NAGA.flavorText: A folktale told to Naga children to scare them from swimming too close to the surface.

MOONFIRE.name: Moonfire
MOONFIRE.flavorText: "Cast Moonfire, and never stop." - How to Be a Druid, Chapter 5, Section 3

NEFERSET THRASHER.name: Neferset Thrasher
NEFERSET THRASHER.flavorText: Tough to do skateboard tricks with four legs.

CORPSE WIDOW.name: Corpse Widow
CORPSE WIDOW.flavorText: Her marriage survived death, but it decayed pretty quickly after that.

ANCIENT HARBINGER.name: Ancient Harbinger
ANCIENT HARBINGER.flavorText: "honey, can u run down to the store and pick up some 10 cost minions? thx"

FLOWRIDER.name: Flowrider
FLOWRIDER.flavorText: Her music sounds a lot better underwater where you can't hear it at all.

GLAIVEBOUND ADEPT.name: Glaivebound Adept
GLAIVEBOUND ADEPT.flavorText: "Initiate, this is your glaive. Think of it as an extension of yourself... Did you just throw it?!"

WRIGGLING HORROR.name: Wriggling Horror
WRIGGLING HORROR.flavorText: Created to scare. Born to wriggle.

NARAIN SOOTHFANCY.name: Narain Soothfancy
NARAIN SOOTHFANCY.flavorText: I predict... that you will be very happy with your reading!

AMULET OF UNDYING.name: Amulet of Undying
AMULET OF UNDYING.flavorText: Didn't seem to work out too well for this guy.

COPPERTAIL IMPOSTER.name: Coppertail Imposter
COPPERTAIL IMPOSTER.flavorText: It was fitting in fine until it gathered nuts and bolts.

DARKSHIRE LIBRARIAN.name: Darkshire Librarian
DARKSHIRE LIBRARIAN.flavorText: Do NOT be late with your overdue fines.

SHADOW CLONE.name: Shadow Clone
SHADOW CLONE.flavorText: "You thought you were attacking face, but it was me! You!"

MANA GIANT.name: Mana Giant
MANA GIANT.flavorText: Spell more and save more with a GIANT discount!

DIVINE BREW.name: Divine Brew
DIVINE BREW.flavorText: I'm on a cleanse, do you have any Light drinks?

MORBID SWARM.name: Morbid Swarm
MORBID SWARM.flavorText: Death Knights are masters of death who use shadow magic to control swarms of... ants?

KUN THE FORGOTTEN KING.name: Kun the Forgotten King
KUN THE FORGOTTEN KING.flavorText: Aya siphons a bit of Kun's soul to animate each golem in her Jade army. To his credit, he's being a great sport about it.

NEXUS-PRINCE SHAFFAR.name: Nexus-Prince Shaffar
NEXUS-PRINCE SHAFFAR.flavorText: Whatever you do, do not give him OR his ethereal parrot a magical lamp.

SHADOW WORD: DEATH.name: Shadow Word: Death
SHADOW WORD: DEATH.flavorText: If you miss, it leaves a lightning-bolt-shaped scar on your target.

FLIPPER FRIENDS.name: Flipper Friends
FLIPPER FRIENDS.flavorText: Despite the harsh conditions, friends can still be found under the sea.

CHAMPIONS OF AZEROTH.name: Champions of Azeroth
CHAMPIONS OF AZEROTH.flavorText: Weeee are the champions of the Wooorld… of Warcraft!

BLOODSAIL FLYBOOTER.name: Bloodsail Flybooter
BLOODSAIL FLYBOOTER.flavorText: They’re pretty fly for some pirate guys.

AESSINA.name: Aessina
AESSINA.flavorText: The Mother Wisp is a mysterious figure to most mortals, but to Ysera, she is a dear friend and companion.

WILFRED FIZZLEBANG.name: Wilfred Fizzlebang
WILFRED FIZZLEBANG.flavorText: He can summon anything, even a FEARSOME DOOMGUARD*. *He's pretty sure this is going to work out.

WRETCHED TILLER.name: Wretched Tiller
WRETCHED TILLER.flavorText: If you ever tried to plow permafrost, you’d be wretched, too.

CACTUS RAGER.name: Cactus Rager
CACTUS RAGER.flavorText: What doesn't kill ya makes you deader.

STREET SWEEPER.name: Street Sweeper
STREET SWEEPER.flavorText: The sweeper hit of the set.

SNEAKY DEVIL.name: Sneaky Devil
SNEAKY DEVIL.flavorText: The result of a tragic accident involving a Defias Thug, a Wand of Polymorph, and a bundle of Fel Lotus.

GALAKROND, THE TEMPEST.name: Galakrond, the Tempest
GALAKROND, THE TEMPEST.flavorText: Hagatha cried out over the winds: "Truly, you are as powerful as the Maelstrom!" To which the Tempest answered: "I AM THE MAELSTROM."

MAGIC DART FROG.name: Magic Dart Frog
MAGIC DART FROG.flavorText: There's a powerful throat in this frog.

HALVERIA DARKRAVEN.name: Halveria Darkraven
HALVERIA DARKRAVEN.flavorText: You know someone's cool when their name sounds like a font.

VENDETTA.name: Vendetta
VENDETTA.flavorText: A vengeful and vicarious vanguard against violent villains or vexed victims.

DESERT CAMEL.name: Desert Camel
DESERT CAMEL.flavorText: Dang. This card is sweet. Almost as sweet as Dessert Camel.

TORTOLLAN PILGRIM.name: Tortollan Pilgrim
TORTOLLAN PILGRIM.flavorText: A tortollan made it to the desert!

KABAL TRAFFICKER.name: Kabal Trafficker
KABAL TRAFFICKER.flavorText: She ships illicit mana crystals around the world in packages marked: FUNNEL CAKE.

ARROW SMITH.name: Arrow Smith
ARROW SMITH.flavorText: "What do you mean it's a violin bow!?!"

MOLTEN BLAST.name: Molten Blast
MOLTEN BLAST.flavorText: Well, how would YOU celebrate after finals week?!

DISGUISED K'THIR.name: Disguised K'thir
DISGUISED K'THIR.flavorText: That is not a very good disguise, dude.

WINGS OF HATE (RANK 1).name: Wings of Hate (Rank 1)
WINGS OF HATE (RANK 1).flavorText: For one day each February, they become the Wings of Love.

AUCHENAI DEATH-SPEAKER.name: Auchenai Death-Speaker
AUCHENAI DEATH-SPEAKER.flavorText: He sees no evil. He hears no evil. Eh, he speaks a little evil.

CHAINED GUARDIAN.name: Chained Guardian
CHAINED GUARDIAN.flavorText: Eternally jealous of the Unchained Gladiator.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/9/9f/VO_TTN_459_Male_Vrykul_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_TTN_459_Male_Vrykul_Play_01.wav Death cannot be bound.

TIDELOST BURROWER.name: Tidelost Burrower
TIDELOST BURROWER.flavorText: Burrowing may not be for everyone, but I dig it.

WIND-UP MUSICIAN.name: Wind-Up Musician
WIND-UP MUSICIAN.flavorText: Sure to wind up your opponents.

FALLEN SUN CLERIC.name: Fallen Sun Cleric
FALLEN SUN CLERIC.flavorText: It's hard to keep a Shattered Sun Cleric down.

HIGH EXARCH YREL.name: High Exarch Yrel
HIGH EXARCH YREL.flavorText: There can be no neutrality in the fight against darkness.

SPITEFUL SMITH.name: Spiteful Smith
SPITEFUL SMITH.flavorText: She'll craft you a sword, but you'll need to bring her 5 Steel Ingots, 3 Motes of Earth, and the scalp of her last customer.

ABSORBENT PARASITE.name: Absorbent Parasite
ABSORBENT PARASITE.flavorText: Your beasts' iron levels are high, what have you been feeding them?

FLOBBIDINOUS FLOOP.name: Flobbidinous Floop
FLOBBIDINOUS FLOOP.flavorText: Of all the scientists, he has the most knowledge (when measured in volume).

BRITTLESKIN ZOMBIE.name: Brittleskin Zombie
BRITTLESKIN ZOMBIE.flavorText: I was born with glass bones and paper skin.

JOYMANCER JEPETTO.name: Joymancer Jepetto
JOYMANCER JEPETTO.flavorText: Joymancy (noun): The practice of bringing joy to others through the use of magic. (see also: ethics)

UTHER OF THE EBON BLADE.name: Uther of the Ebon Blade
UTHER OF THE EBON BLADE.flavorText: "Step forward. Confess! Once I was a mere servant of the Light. Now I alone stand in judgement."

VESSINA.name: Vessina
VESSINA.flavorText: She wasn't happy when Hagatha sent her back to Uldum. But her "angry" hiss sounds like her "happy" hiss, so no one knew the difference.

DYN-O-MATIC.name: Dyn-o-matic
DYN-O-MATIC.flavorText: Star player on the inter-office Boomball team.

HARBOR SCAMP.name: Harbor Scamp
HARBOR SCAMP.flavorText: Hey, that gnome looks awfully fishy…

KING OF BEASTS.name: King of Beasts
KING OF BEASTS.flavorText: He never sleeps. Not even in the mighty jungle.

DON HAN'CHO.name: Don Han'Cho
DON HAN'CHO.flavorText: The brilliant mastermind of the Grimy Goons, Han sometimes thinks about ditching the idiot Cho, but that would just tear him apart.

RECKLESS APPRENTICE.name: Reckless Apprentice
RECKLESS APPRENTICE.flavorText: It’s all a great learning experience until someone accidentally aggros the boss.

SATED THRESHADON.name: Sated Threshadon
SATED THRESHADON.flavorText: Bet you can't eat just one murloc!

WITCH'S APPRENTICE.name: Witch's Apprentice
WITCH'S APPRENTICE.flavorText: Is she a frog that became a witch, or a witch that became a frog?

VICIOUS SCALEHIDE.name: Vicious Scalehide
VICIOUS SCALEHIDE.flavorText: They make wonderful pets if you're not allergic to blood loss.

SILVERWARE GOLEM.name: Silverware Golem
SILVERWARE GOLEM.flavorText: From the secret research labs of the Swiss Army.

DOUBLE CROSS.name: Double Cross
DOUBLE CROSS.flavorText: Valeera revealed herself to be a double agent. At which point Maiev felt comfortable revealing that she also was a double agent. And then Scabbs announced to everybody that - get this - he was a double agent.

SHADY DEALER.name: Shady Dealer
SHADY DEALER.flavorText: I have great deal for you... for 4 damage to your face!

STORMPIKE AID STATION.name: Stormpike Aid Station
STORMPIKE AID STATION.flavorText: Known by some as the “Stormpike Naptime Lounge.”

GIGANTOTEM.name: Gigantotem
GIGANTOTEM.flavorText: Totem Golem's uncle, gone too soon.

DECK OF CHAOS.name: Deck of Chaos
DECK OF CHAOS.flavorText: Yeah, it's chaos, but it's organized chaos.

ENCROACHING INSANITY.name: Encroaching Insanity
ENCROACHING INSANITY.flavorText: Pictured here is Loken stuck at his 20th hour on Diamond 5.

SNOW SHREDDER.name: Snow Shredder
SNOW SHREDDER.flavorText: "Yeah dude, snowboarding is like, totally safe. I've only ever been injured once."

SESSELIE OF THE FAE COURT.name: Sesselie of the Fae Court
SESSELIE OF THE FAE COURT.flavorText: They claim they're from the Fae Court, but that might be a Fae Kout.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/4/4c/VO_REV_319_Female_Tirnenn_Attack_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_REV_319_Female_Tirnenn_Attack_01.wav Death begets life.

MAW AND PAW.name: Maw and Paw
MAW AND PAW.flavorText: Home is where the disfigured, rotten heart is.

ELDER NADOX.name: Elder Nadox
ELDER NADOX.flavorText: For an Undead, is an elder the least or most dead?

EMERALD HIVE QUEEN.name: Emerald Hive Queen
EMERALD HIVE QUEEN.flavorText: She rules the emerald hive at the end of the yellow brick trail.

RUNEFORGE HAUNTER.name: Runeforge Haunter
RUNEFORGE HAUNTER.flavorText: Don't worry, he'll keep an eye on that for you.

IRON JUGGERNAUT.name: Iron Juggernaut
IRON JUGGERNAUT.flavorText: The Iron Juggernaut guards Orgrimmar and has just earned the "Employee of the Month" award!

KARA KAZHAM!.name: Kara Kazham!
KARA KAZHAM!.flavorText: This is what happens when you tell Khadgar to set the table.

POTION OF MADNESS.name: Potion of Madness
POTION OF MADNESS.flavorText: You'd be insane NOT to drink it!

NIGHTBANE TEMPLAR.name: Nightbane Templar
NIGHTBANE TEMPLAR.flavorText: Originally joined to be Arcanagos’ Templar, but has to admit that ordering pizza has become waaaay easier.

ARCHIVIST ELYSIANA.name: Archivist Elysiana
ARCHIVIST ELYSIANA.flavorText: Your deck is just another organizational challenge to her.

DRAGONHATCHER.name: Dragonhatcher
DRAGONHATCHER.flavorText: Which came first? The dragon or the dragonhatcher?

OBSIDIAN DESTROYER.name: Obsidian Destroyer
OBSIDIAN DESTROYER.flavorText: No obsidian is safe around the Obsidian Destroyer!

CERA'THINE FLEETRUNNER.name: Cera'thine Fleetrunner
CERA'THINE FLEETRUNNER.flavorText: World Record CTF Champion 16 years running.

FESTIVAL SECURITY.name: Festival Security
FESTIVAL SECURITY.flavorText: "Incident in the mosh pit? Copy that, be there in a year."

SUNFURY CLERGY.name: Sunfury Clergy
SUNFURY CLERGY.flavorText: Why is the sun so mad? Won't anyone ask about its feelings?

WRATHION.name: Wrathion
WRATHION.flavorText: Wrathion, son of Deathwing, is a dragon. Why isn't he tagged as a dragon, you ask? WHAT, ARE YOU TRYING TO BLOW HIS COVER??

TOTEMIC EVIDENCE.name: Totemic Evidence
TOTEMIC EVIDENCE.flavorText: Every totem is evidence of a tree's murder.

APOTHEOSIS.name: Apotheosis
APOTHEOSIS.flavorText: Defined as the absolute pinnacle of existence. Plus Lifesteal.

PROSTHETIC HAND.name: Prosthetic Hand
PROSTHETIC HAND.flavorText: It's creaky and it's rusty! It's spooky and it's dusty!

VILEFIEND.name: Vilefiend
VILEFIEND.flavorText: Dreamed of becoming a Stylefiend, but fel was never in season.

INFECTIOUS SPORELING.name: Infectious Sporeling
INFECTIOUS SPORELING.flavorText: "The best thing about being me—there’s so many 'me's."

REMIXED TUNING FORK.name: Remixed Tuning Fork
REMIXED TUNING FORK.flavorText: You can tune a fork, but you can't tune a fish.

AUCTIONHOUSE GAVEL.name: Auctionhouse Gavel
AUCTIONHOUSE GAVEL.flavorText: "I want to be a judge! Or an auctioneer! Look, all I want is one of those sweet, tiny hammers."

ORBITAL SATELLITE.name: Orbital Satellite
ORBITAL SATELLITE.flavorText: Picks up all the buzz in space.

BARTEND-O-BOT.name: Bartend-O-Bot
BARTEND-O-BOT.flavorText: Bartend-O-Bot! Make my Outcast card DO SOMETHING!

BLACKGUARD.name: Blackguard
BLACKGUARD.flavorText: "Did I ever tell you the story of when I single-handedly took down a 29/29 C'thun?" - Reno Jackson

TOME OF INTELLECT.name: Tome of Intellect
TOME OF INTELLECT.flavorText: Just a compilation of napkins of intellect.

ARCANE SERVANT.name: Arcane Servant
ARCANE SERVANT.flavorText: "Would sir like me to punch something?"

CONDUCTIVITY.name: Conductivity
CONDUCTIVITY.flavorText: That faceless sure didn't put up a lot of (length/cross-sectional area).

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/28/BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ BT_726_DragonmawSkyStalker_Play.wav <summon sound>

UPGRADED REPAIR BOT.name: Upgraded Repair Bot
UPGRADED REPAIR BOT.flavorText: It's the same as the previous generation but they slapped the word "upgraded" on it to sell it for double.

DOCTOR KRASTINOV.name: Doctor Krastinov
DOCTOR KRASTINOV.flavorText: He is not a medical doctor.

XB-931 HOUSEKEEPER.name: XB-931 Housekeeper
XB-931 HOUSEKEEPER.flavorText: "WHAT IS MY PURPOSE?" "You gain Armor." "OH GOD."

BLACKWATER PIRATE.name: Blackwater Pirate
BLACKWATER PIRATE.flavorText: "Look, they fell off the back of a ship, do you want them or not? I have a meeting with Y'Shaarj in like ten minutes."

LAWFUL LONGARM.name: Lawful Longarm
LAWFUL LONGARM.flavorText: Loves to lob law bombs from his law blog.

ROTHEART DRYAD.name: Rotheart Dryad
ROTHEART DRYAD.flavorText: Rot through the heart and Xavius is to blame!

HUMILITY.name: Humility
HUMILITY.flavorText: This card makes something really damp. Oh wait. That's "Humidity."

CHILLIN' VOL'JIN.name: Chillin' Vol'jin
CHILLIN' VOL'JIN.flavorText: After one visit to the cryopractor, YOU TOO can be chillin' like a Vol'jin!

SCOURGE TAMER.name: Scourge Tamer
SCOURGE TAMER.flavorText: He's a hunter AND a gatherer.

FLIGHT MASTER.name: Flight Master
FLIGHT MASTER.flavorText: Your gryphon will be summoned following a brief safety demonstration.

IRON SENSEI.name: Iron Sensei
IRON SENSEI.flavorText: Mechs like learning from him because he really speaks their language. 0110100001101001

TAMSIN'S PHYLACTERY.name: Tamsin's Phylactery
TAMSIN'S PHYLACTERY.flavorText: Eau de Morte. Guaranteed to take your date’s breath away

THE PURATOR.name: The Purator
THE PURATOR.flavorText: With the rise of the undead, the Curator sees it as his duty to take care of them.

REDEMPTION.name: Redemption
REDEMPTION.flavorText: I am not sure how you get demptioned the first time. It’s a mystery!

NIGHT PROWLER.name: Night Prowler
NIGHT PROWLER.flavorText: Listen to the mew-sic of the night.

PROFESSOR SLATE.name: Professor Slate
PROFESSOR SLATE.flavorText: "Don’t worry, this will be over in a second. It might FEEL like an eternity, but I assure you, it’s quite quick!"

ORDER IN THE COURT.name: Order in the Court
ORDER IN THE COURT.flavorText: "I have nothing BUT contempt for this court!"

WHELP WRANGLER.name: Whelp Wrangler
WHELP WRANGLER.flavorText: "Gosh darn it! How did these winged, airborne creatures manage to escape my knee-high, fenced enclosure AGAIN!?"

SIGHTLESS MAGISTRATE.name: Sightless Magistrate
SIGHTLESS MAGISTRATE.flavorText: Does "Justice is Blind" still apply with Spectral Sight?

PACKAGE RUNNER.name: Package Runner
PACKAGE RUNNER.flavorText: He could go... all... the... way!

CANDLERAISER.name: Candleraiser
CANDLERAISER.flavorText: You would not believe your eyes If ten million kobold guys Lit up the world to this ogre beat

UNLEASH FEL.name: Unleash Fel
UNLEASH FEL.flavorText: Why'd you put it on a leash in the first place?

IRONBARK.name: Ironbark
IRONBARK.flavorText: "The important thing, son, is to protect your spores! I have spoken!"

UMBRAL OWL.name: Umbral Owl
UMBRAL OWL.flavorText: It sleeps with one eye open.

TOYRANTUS.name: Toyrantus
TOYRANTUS.flavorText: Dr. Boom was definitely a dinosaur kid.

WASTELAND SCORPID.name: Wasteland Scorpid
WASTELAND SCORPID.flavorText: After they get to a certain size, it doesn't matter if they're poisonous or not.

COILSKAR COMMANDER.name: Coilskar Commander
COILSKAR COMMANDER.flavorText: Then thou shalt count to three, no more, no less. Three shall be the number thou shalt count, and the number of the counting shall be three. Four shalt thou not count, neither count thou two, excepting that thou then proceed to three. Five is right out.

TOXFIN.name: Toxfin
TOXFIN.flavorText: I'm addicted to him, but I know that he's Toxfin.

SPECTRAL TRAINEE.name: Spectral Trainee
SPECTRAL TRAINEE.flavorText: After graduating at the top of her class from Scholomance, she was granted an eternal scholarship to study abroad in Naxxramas.

VENGEFUL WALLOPER.name: Vengeful Walloper
VENGEFUL WALLOPER.flavorText: If you can't beat 'em, beat WITH 'em!

LESSER AMETHYST SPELLSTONE.name: Lesser Amethyst Spellstone
LESSER AMETHYST SPELLSTONE.flavorText: A purple stone Azari carved For dark hearts, craving, power-starved. The first to bow, the warlock Rin, Embraced the darkness, slew her kin.

CASCADING DISASTER.name: Cascading Disaster
CASCADING DISASTER.flavorText: Please keep all hands, arms, feet and legs inside the ride until the monster comes to a complete stop.

GRIMTOTEM BOUNTY HUNTER.name: Grimtotem Bounty Hunter
GRIMTOTEM BOUNTY HUNTER.flavorText: He’ll take a big weight off your shoulders.

OWLONIUS.name: Owlonius
OWLONIUS.flavorText: They said you sound like an owl.

DEMOLISHER.name: Demolisher
DEMOLISHER.flavorText: Laying siege isn't fun for anyone. It's not even all that effective, now that everyone has a flying mount.

WORKHORSE.name: Workhorse
WORKHORSE.flavorText: Give me ONE reason why a horse shouldn’t be allowed in the travel agency.

FACELESS SHAMBLER.name: Faceless Shambler
FACELESS SHAMBLER.flavorText: "What is that thing?!" "I'm not sure, but it seems to be sort of Ysera shaped."

ASTRAL PHASER.name: Astral Phaser
ASTRAL PHASER.flavorText: Ok, Mom, in this ONE instance it IS a phase.

EMERISS.name: Emeriss
EMERISS.flavorText: Taste your world's corruption! It tastes like chicken.

TOUGH CROWD.name: Tough Crowd
TOUGH CROWD.flavorText: "Your music's bad and you should feel bad."

MECHA-SHARK.name: Mecha-Shark
MECHA-SHARK.flavorText: "Why didn't you just build a normal submarine. Only you can fit inside" "WhY DiDn'T YoU JuSt BuIlD anormalsub-WHY DO YOU THINK WREZIG!! If you can build a freaking Mecha-Shark, then you build a freaking Mecha-Shark!"

SIGIL OF SUMMONING.name: Sigil of Summoning
SIGIL OF SUMMONING.flavorText: Look, summoning ain’t exactly a science. Sometimes it takes a turn.

SLEEP PARALYSIS.name: Sleep Paralysis
SLEEP PARALYSIS.flavorText: The wild SPRITE is paralyzed! It can't sleep!

TAINTHEART TORMENTER.name: Taintheart Tormenter
TAINTHEART TORMENTER.flavorText: Oh boo hoo, did someone's World Tree burn down?

BLASTCRYSTAL POTION.name: Blastcrystal Potion
BLASTCRYSTAL POTION.flavorText: There's a fine line between "potion" and "grenade". Wait. Actually, there's not.

SHIFTY SOPHOMORE.name: Shifty Sophomore
SHIFTY SOPHOMORE.flavorText: Experienced enough to do crimes, inexperienced enough to be super obvious about it.

TREESPEAKER.name: Treespeaker
TREESPEAKER.flavorText: Honestly, his delivery is a little wooden.

SNOWFURY GIANT.name: Snowfury Giant
SNOWFURY GIANT.flavorText: This minion goes all the way to 11!

GILDED GARGOYLE.name: Gilded Gargoyle
GILDED GARGOYLE.flavorText: You hear a coin rattling inside the slotted gargoyle...What could it mean?

FELFIRE POTION.name: Felfire Potion
FELFIRE POTION.flavorText: Kazakus has a squad of imps bottling Felfire round-the-clock and he *still* can't keep up with demand.

NESTING ROC.name: Nesting Roc
NESTING ROC.flavorText: Roc eggs are great in omelettes, sandwiches, and as bait to turn poachers into bird food.

TWO-FACED INVESTOR.name: Two-Faced Investor
