TWO-FACED INVESTOR.flavorText: Should never have opened that joint account...

FIREBALL.name: Fireball
FIREBALL.flavorText: This spell is useful for burning things. If you're looking for spells that toast things, or just warm them a little, you're in the wrong place.

SHADOW HUNTER VOL'JIN.name: Shadow Hunter Vol'jin
SHADOW HUNTER VOL'JIN.flavorText: You wouldn’t see this swap-meet on the Zandalari Roadshow.

GUNSLINGER KURTRUS.name: Gunslinger Kurtrus
GUNSLINGER KURTRUS.flavorText: "I have given up (a single copy of) EVERYTHING! What have YOU sacrificed?"

FEL BARRAGE.name: Fel Barrage
FEL BARRAGE.flavorText: Kurtrus leapt over a tombstone towards the demonic invaders, yelling "PEW! PEW!" as he shot them down with fel magic.

PERDITION'S BLADE.name: Perdition's Blade
PERDITION'S BLADE.flavorText: Perdition's Blade is Ragnaros's back-up weapon while Sulfuras is in the shop.

HEMET NESINGWARY.name: Hemet Nesingwary
HEMET NESINGWARY.flavorText: It's hard to make a living as a hunter in a world where beasts instantly reappear minutes after you kill them.

SCORCHING OBSERVER.name: Scorching Observer
SCORCHING OBSERVER.flavorText: We get it, you're mad that you only have one eye. But that's no excuse to burn down the entire Emerald Dream.

WORGEN ROADIE.name: Worgen Roadie
WORGEN ROADIE.flavorText: "I asked for an instrument, and you give me a CURSED BLADE!?"

BLOODHOOF BRAVE.name: Bloodhoof Brave
BLOODHOOF BRAVE.flavorText: He thought the set was called "Flippers of the Old Cods" and hungrily volunteered to be in it. He is definitely going to get his hearing checked.

MOSH'OGG ENFORCER.name: Mosh'Ogg Enforcer
MOSH'OGG ENFORCER.flavorText: Can’t break the rules if you can’t read ‘em.

SHARP SHIPMENT.name: Sharp Shipment
SHARP SHIPMENT.flavorText: Pre-check is amazing these days. New rules say you don't have to take off your shoes, helmet, or daggers!

ROCK MASTER VOONE.name: Rock Master Voone
ROCK MASTER VOONE.flavorText: After several audience members were burnt to a crisp, Voone's band became a lot less all-in on Dragons.

VANNDAR STORMPIKE.name: Vanndar Stormpike
VANNDAR STORMPIKE.flavorText: His favorite modes of transportation? Van, car, board, bike.

UNSTABLE GHOUL.name: Unstable Ghoul
UNSTABLE GHOUL.flavorText: Filling your Ghouls with Rocket Fuel is all the rage at Necromancer school.

LUCENTBARK.name: Lucentbark
LUCENTBARK.flavorText: Always feels refreshed after a little dirt nap.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/75/VO_DAL_357_Male_Ancient_Trigger-Resurrected_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_DAL_357_Male_Ancient_Trigger-Resurrected_01.wav Nature calls.

RECKLESS EXPERIMENTER.name: Reckless Experimenter
RECKLESS EXPERIMENTER.flavorText: It's hard to call her reckless when it's clear she knows what she's doing.

SINSTONE TOTEM.name: Sinstone Totem
SINSTONE TOTEM.flavorText: This one's heavier than the wooden totems. Mostly from the weight of your sins.

FLESHEATING GHOUL.name: Flesheating Ghoul
FLESHEATING GHOUL.flavorText: 'Flesheating' is an unfair name. It's just that there's not really much else for him to eat.

BONE BREAKER.name: Bone Breaker
BONE BREAKER.flavorText: Many weapons are bone breakers if you swing hard enough.

THE EXODAR.name: The Exodar
THE EXODAR.flavorText: Limitless potential! Boundless hope! Fourth rate space insurance.

BLAST WAVE.name: Blast Wave
BLAST WAVE.flavorText: If you’re burning and you know it, wave your hands!

LOST SPIRIT.name: Lost Spirit
LOST SPIRIT.flavorText: She simply refuses to ask for directions.

MURLOC TINYFIN.name: Murloc Tinyfin
MURLOC TINYFIN.flavorText: High mortality rate, from often being hugged to death.

NEFARIAN.name: Nefarian
NEFARIAN.flavorText: They call him "Blackwing" because he's a black dragon...... and he's got wings.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/20/VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/2/20/VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BRMA13_1_HP_GENERIC_18.wav Your magic is mine!

LAMPLIGHTER.name: Lamplighter
LAMPLIGHTER.flavorText: The elemental licked the oil and everybody laughed.

DEMONIC DEAL.name: Demonic Deal
DEMONIC DEAL.flavorText: The Burning Legion upped their efforts to sell Argus Timeshares.

ANIMA EXTRACTOR.name: Anima Extractor
ANIMA EXTRACTOR.flavorText: After we are done you're welcome to help yourself to cookies and apple juice. Thank you for your donation!

MOAT LURKER.name: Moat Lurker
MOAT LURKER.flavorText: He really enjoys lurking and gets a lot of job satisfaction out of it.

ENVOY OF PROSPERITY.name: Envoy of Prosperity
ENVOY OF PROSPERITY.flavorText: "Our prosperity is beyond a shadow of a doubt!"

FINAL GASP.name: Final Gasp
FINAL GASP.flavorText: And with a raspy whisper, he uttered his final words, "rez plz."

FOSSILIZED KALEIDOSAUR.name: Fossilized Kaleidosaur
FOSSILIZED KALEIDOSAUR.flavorText: He's not that bad if you don't die turn 4.

BLACKHOWL GUNSPIRE.name: Blackhowl Gunspire
BLACKHOWL GUNSPIRE.flavorText: The upper windows used to be for aiming. Then we thought: "Hey! MORE cannons!"

GADGETZAN FERRYMAN.name: Gadgetzan Ferryman
GADGETZAN FERRYMAN.flavorText: Is it just me, or is there something fishy about that ferryman?

VENOMSTRIKE BOW.name: Venomstrike Bow
VENOMSTRIKE BOW.flavorText: "You know you only have to coat the arrowhead in poison and not the entire bow, right?"

INGENIOUS ARTIFICER.name: Ingenious Artificer
INGENIOUS ARTIFICER.flavorText: He always brags that he's at the top of the bell curve.

SCV.name: SCV
SCV.flavorText: They're called SCVs because they're Super Cool (Very).

BURLY ROCKJAW TROGG.name: Burly Rockjaw Trogg
BURLY ROCKJAW TROGG.flavorText: He's burly because he does CrossFit.

CRUEL TASKMASTER.name: Cruel Taskmaster
CRUEL TASKMASTER.flavorText: "I'm going to need you to come in on Sunday." - Cruel Taskmaster

METALTOOTH LEAPER.name: Metaltooth Leaper
METALTOOTH LEAPER.flavorText: Don't leave them out in the rain. In Un'Goro Crater there is a whole colony of rust-tooth leapers.

RIVER CROCOLISK.name: River Crocolisk
RIVER CROCOLISK.flavorText: Edward "Lefty" Smith tried to make luggage out of a river crocolisk once.

DOOMCALLER.name: Doomcaller
DOOMCALLER.flavorText: "Hello, is Doom there? No? Can I leave a message?"

CONCIERGE.name: Concierge
CONCIERGE.flavorText: So THAT'S who's making all those keys for my Arena runs.

KEENEYE SPOTTER.name: Keeneye Spotter
KEENEYE SPOTTER.flavorText: "No Rexxar, not the face, the minion right there. Yep that one righ-- Rexxar no!"

RELIQUARY RESEARCHER.name: Reliquary Researcher
RELIQUARY RESEARCHER.flavorText: What good is a researcher if they're just gunna keep it all a secret?

YSERA THE DREAMER.name: Ysera the Dreamer
YSERA THE DREAMER.flavorText: Quick! Quick! Write it down before you forget them all!

REFRESHMENT VENDOR.name: Refreshment Vendor
REFRESHMENT VENDOR.flavorText: Menu: Funnel cakes, carrots, popcorn, jormungar steaks. It's hard serving a diverse clientele.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/7d/VO_AT_111_PLAY_ALT1_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_111_PLAY_ALT1_02.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/74/VO_AT_111_ATTACK_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_111_ATTACK_03.wav Grrr, pay up!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/cd/VO_AT_111_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_111_DEATH_04.wav But I have... more... cakes...

IMMOLATION AURA.name: Immolation Aura
IMMOLATION AURA.flavorText: If you can't take the heat, stop standing in the fire.

OMEGA MIND.name: Omega Mind
OMEGA MIND.flavorText: Has a side-business selling her lipstick shade, "Omega Red."

SELFISH SHELLFISH.name: Selfish Shellfish
SELFISH SHELLFISH.flavorText: Keeps any ancient book it finds all to its shelf.

RAKE.name: Rake
RAKE.flavorText: When you're done shredding through your enemies, use it on your leaves!

ARATHI WEAPONSMITH.name: Arathi Weaponsmith
ARATHI WEAPONSMITH.flavorText: 50% off fist weapons, limited time only!

THE MISTCALLER.name: The Mistcaller
THE MISTCALLER.flavorText: Calling the mist doesn't sound all that great. "Ooooh, it is slightly damp now!"

DREADED MOUNT.name: Dreaded Mount
DREADED MOUNT.flavorText: This is the summoning that never ends, and it goes on and on my friends...

FANGBOUND DRUID.name: Fangbound Druid
FANGBOUND DRUID.flavorText: Bound by the law of the fang, these druid floss their teeth twice a day.

VALIDATED DOOMSAYER.name: Validated Doomsayer
VALIDATED DOOMSAYER.flavorText: Really feels good about himself and is in a much better place now. But… he sure does miss piloting those shredders.

KAEL'THAS SUNSTRIDER.name: Kael'thas Sunstrider
KAEL'THAS SUNSTRIDER.flavorText: “Descent of Dragons was merely a set back!”

GOLAKKA GLUTTON.name: Golakka Glutton
GOLAKKA GLUTTON.flavorText: We lost our last cook to one of these.

EARTHEN RING FARSEER.name: Earthen Ring Farseer
EARTHEN RING FARSEER.flavorText: He can see really far, and he doesn't use a telescope like those filthy pirates.

OPEN THE CAGES.name: Open the Cages
OPEN THE CAGES.flavorText: "Coming out of my cage, and I'm dead by turn nine..."

POPSICOOLER.name: Popsicooler
POPSICOOLER.flavorText: Just passing through Alterac on its way to apply for a job at the Ice Cream Citadel.

UNSEEN SABOTEUR.name: Unseen Saboteur
UNSEEN SABOTEUR.flavorText: Far more effective than the flamboyant saboteur.

KOBOLD TASKMASTER.name: Kobold Taskmaster
KOBOLD TASKMASTER.flavorText: Fabled questgiver of the “Get me candle”, “Get me another candle”, and “Get me 11 more candle” questline.

UMBRAL GEIST.name: Umbral Geist
UMBRAL GEIST.flavorText: “After all, one can't leave his shadow lying about and not miss it sooner or later, don't you agree?”

FOXY FRAUD.name: Foxy Fraud
FOXY FRAUD.flavorText: His other street con involves a druid. He can't pull it off without a plant.

CORNERED SENTRY.name: Cornered Sentry
CORNERED SENTRY.flavorText: The Draenei are seriously considering cancelling "Bring Your Murderous Pet to Work Day."

HUNGRY ETTIN.name: Hungry Ettin
HUNGRY ETTIN.flavorText: How can he be hungry… if he's Ettin!?

BLACK HOLE.name: Black Hole
BLACK HOLE.flavorText: That's right! The square goes in the black hole.

FLY OFF THE SHELVES.name: Fly Off the Shelves
FLY OFF THE SHELVES.flavorText: No, Whizbang, you can't pass off a poorly made shelf as a cool Priest spell.

JADE BLOSSOM.name: Jade Blossom
JADE BLOSSOM.flavorText: Meditating under a jade blossom is said to grant you wisdom, unless you have a pollen allergy.

OGRE NINJA.name: Ogre Ninja
OGRE NINJA.flavorText: He didn't have the grades to get into ninja school, but his dad pulled some strings.

DARIUS CROWLEY.name: Darius Crowley
DARIUS CROWLEY.flavorText: You either die a villain, or live long enough to see yourself become the hero.

WING COMMANDER MULVERICK.name: Wing Commander Mulverick
WING COMMANDER MULVERICK.flavorText: “A board full of 2-Health minions? This is what I call a target rich environment.”

SHADOWBORN.name: Shadowborn
SHADOWBORN.flavorText: You merely adopted the shadows; I was born in them!

RENO JACKSON.name: Reno Jackson
RENO JACKSON.flavorText: Reno is a four-time winner of the 'Best Accessorized Explorer' award.

AZERITE CHAIN GANG.name: Azerite Chain Gang
AZERITE CHAIN GANG.flavorText: How long can this go on? For 6 years at least!

BOB THE BARTENDER.name: Bob the Bartender
BOB THE BARTENDER.flavorText: A good bartender always knows how to stir up the conversation.

BERYLLIUM NULLIFIER.name: Beryllium Nullifier
BERYLLIUM NULLIFIER.flavorText: Why Beryllium? Because it's hard to spell.

FUNGAL FORTUNES.name: Fungal Fortunes
FUNGAL FORTUNES.flavorText: Far superior to a beanstalk boondoggle.

HEARTTHROB.name: Heartthrob
HEARTTHROB.flavorText: Oh no, Harth! Look out! He's here to rob you!

WAYWARD SAGE.name: Wayward Sage
WAYWARD SAGE.flavorText: Carry on my wayward sage. There'll be peace and no more rage.

SNAKE TRAP.name: Snake Trap
SNAKE TRAP.flavorText: Why did it have to be snakes?

EVASIVE FEYWING.name: Evasive Feywing
EVASIVE FEYWING.flavorText: I've never heard of this fey-dragon called "Brightwing," but if I HAD, I’d say we’d be best friends.

IVORY ROOK.name: Ivory Rook
IVORY ROOK.flavorText: Bringing back this cycle was risky, but the Ivory Queen thought it was worth the gambit.

HELM OF HUMILIATION.name: Helm of Humiliation
HELM OF HUMILIATION.flavorText: <whispers> "...and your father was a Murloc too."

LIGHTBRINGER'S HAMMER.name: Lightbringer's Hammer
LIGHTBRINGER'S HAMMER.flavorText: This entire city must be purged. Or at least just the minions.

BEANSTALK BRUTE.name: Beanstalk Brute
BEANSTALK BRUTE.flavorText: I know a guy who might be able to handle this for us. He's kind of a specialist.

AXE FLINGER.name: Axe Flinger
AXE FLINGER.flavorText: Once a lowly "Stick Flinger", he's been relentless on the path to his ultimate dream: "Tauren Flinger".

MESSMAKER.name: Messmaker
MESSMAKER.flavorText: The most painful 1 damage of your life.

BLAZING INVOCATION.name: Blazing Invocation
BLAZING INVOCATION.flavorText: A lot of shaman have started vaping their invocations.

OCTO-MASSEUSE.name: Octo-masseuse
OCTO-MASSEUSE.flavorText: Oh yeah, all of those are the spots.

COPPERTAIL SNOOP.name: Coppertail Snoop
COPPERTAIL SNOOP.flavorText: Scavenges both nuts and bolts for the winter.

TWILIGHT GUARDIAN.name: Twilight Guardian
TWILIGHT GUARDIAN.flavorText: A result of magical experiments carried out by the Black Dragonflight, it's not his fault that he's a vicious killer.

NEXUS-CHAMPION SARAAD.name: Nexus-Champion Saraad
NEXUS-CHAMPION SARAAD.flavorText: The ethereals have their own jousting tournament, and Saraad is the reigning champion. Also he won the ethereal hot dog eating contest.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/b/bd/VO_AT_127_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_127_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/c/ca/VO_AT_127_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_127_ATTACK_02.wav You had your chance.
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/64/VO_AT_127_DEATH_04.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_127_DEATH_04.wav <death sound>

CONVINCING INFILTRATOR.name: Convincing Infiltrator
CONVINCING INFILTRATOR.flavorText: It’s always nice to steal a familiar face.

FROM DE OTHER SIDE.name: From De Other Side
FROM DE OTHER SIDE.flavorText: Why did Drakuru cross the road?

GIBBERING REJECT.name: Gibbering Reject
GIBBERING REJECT.flavorText: Don't get it wet or feed it after midnight.

FIREWORKER.name: Fireworker
FIREWORKER.flavorText: The one job where a spark of creativity is unwanted.

BOOTY BAY BOOKIE.name: Booty Bay Bookie
BOOTY BAY BOOKIE.flavorText: Also makes a great librarian. She's really good at fixing books!

HARMONICA SOLOIST.name: Harmonica Soloist
HARMONICA SOLOIST.flavorText: A magician never reveals their Secrets. A musician on the other hand...

PROMOTION.name: Promotion
PROMOTION.flavorText: And with the new title of 'Golden Hand Recruit', you also get a pay raise!

CLERIC OF AN'SHE.name: Cleric of An'she
CLERIC OF AN'SHE.flavorText: When it's her turn to cook, she'll always go for a Light sear.

SILTFIN SPIRITWALKER.name: Siltfin Spiritwalker
SILTFIN SPIRITWALKER.flavorText: The elements respond to anyone who calls them for a worthy cause, even if you call them by yelling, "MRGHRGLGLGL!"

ARANNA, THRILL SEEKER.name: Aranna, Thrill Seeker
ARANNA, THRILL SEEKER.flavorText: "Aranna, I feel like you only came to this island so you could use the zipline."

VENOMANCER.name: Venomancer
VENOMANCER.flavorText: Eight times the death of regular-mancers.

CHATTY BARTENDER.name: Chatty Bartender
CHATTY BARTENDER.flavorText: "So a Venthyr, an Old God, and a Tauren walk into a bar…"

SWORD AND BOARD.name: Sword and Board
SWORD AND BOARD.flavorText: Stab and Slab. Charge and Targe. Slash and Bash. You get the idea.

GRAVE DIGGING.name: Grave Digging
GRAVE DIGGING.flavorText: Grave digging as a profession has high turnover; it's important to maintain headcount.

SANGUINE REVELER.name: Sanguine Reveler
SANGUINE REVELER.flavorText: Have some! This drink is to die for!

DRAGONCALLER ALANNA.name: Dragoncaller Alanna
DRAGONCALLER ALANNA.flavorText: Her secret is using a gentle voice and carrying a baggie of hotdogs.

KEYWARDEN IVORY.name: Keywarden Ivory
KEYWARDEN IVORY.flavorText: She learned exactly one thing from her old man: copying.

HIPSTER.name: Hipster
HIPSTER.flavorText: Oh, so you like Hearthstone? Name every spell.

MANA BURN.name: Mana Burn
MANA BURN.flavorText: One way to ensure that they are not prepared.

HALDURON BRIGHTWING.name: Halduron Brightwing
HALDURON BRIGHTWING.flavorText: I wanted to generate a legendary, but I held da wrong Brightwing.

KABAL TALONPRIEST.name: Kabal Talonpriest
KABAL TALONPRIEST.flavorText: Inkmaster Solia had to figure out how to tattoo feathers.

SEAFORIUM BOMBER.name: Seaforium Bomber
SEAFORIUM BOMBER.flavorText: Dress for the bomb you want, not the bomb you have.

SOLAR FLARE.name: Solar Flare
SOLAR FLARE.flavorText: Saruun is quite the dancer. Their pirouette is deadly.

AUSPICIOUS SPIRITS.name: Auspicious Spirits
AUSPICIOUS SPIRITS.flavorText: "I'm not AWE-spicious, but I am a little spicious."

INFESTED TAUREN.name: Infested Tauren
INFESTED TAUREN.flavorText: The Overmind and the Old Gods are surprisingly similar.

MECHAROO.name: Mecharoo
MECHAROO.flavorText: Its project name was KAN-GA. The little one was R-00.

BODY WRAPPER.name: Body Wrapper
BODY WRAPPER.flavorText: She uses pickle slices for the eyes. Keeps them well-preserved.

MIXOLOGIST.name: Mixologist
MIXOLOGIST.flavorText: You can't put your pinky up when you only have 3 fingers.

DIRE FRENZY.name: Dire Frenzy
DIRE FRENZY.flavorText: It's always Huffer. And Huffer. And Huffer. And Huffer.

HELPLESS HATCHLING.name: Helpless Hatchling
HELPLESS HATCHLING.flavorText: It can’t be all that helpful. Not wif dose widdle wings!

SHADOW OF DEMISE.name: Shadow of Demise
SHADOW OF DEMISE.flavorText: Each time you cast a spell, transform this into a copy of its flavor text.

DEW PROCESS.name: Dew Process
DEW PROCESS.flavorText: All part of dewing your dew diligence.

CLOWNFISH.name: Clownfish
CLOWNFISH.flavorText: His jokes are hilarious if you know Nerglish.

CORPSE EXPLOSION.name: Corpse Explosion
CORPSE EXPLOSION.flavorText: What? It's not like they were using them anymore.

MYTHICAL TERROR.name: Mythical Terror
MYTHICAL TERROR.flavorText: You cannot pet the Terror in Hearthstone.

HOLY COWBOY.name: Holy Cowboy
HOLY COWBOY.flavorText: Wait, but… Isn't he more of a 'holy kodoboy'?

SHADOW WALTZ.name: Shadow Waltz
SHADOW WALTZ.flavorText: They're dancing to one of Rin's demonic symphonies. Her music might not be famous now, but just you wait!

LILIAN VOSS.name: Lilian Voss
LILIAN VOSS.flavorText: She doesn't feel pity, or remorse, or fear. And she absolutely will not stop... ever, until all necromancers are dead.

MENAGERIE MAGICIAN.name: Menagerie Magician
MENAGERIE MAGICIAN.flavorText: Just between us, if things get tight the Menagerie Magician position will probably be the first to go.

STAR VULPERA.name: Star Vulpera
STAR VULPERA.flavorText: He was a star before he even flew his first ship.

QUARTZ ELEMENTAL.name: Quartz Elemental
QUARTZ ELEMENTAL.flavorText: These elementals, along with feldspar and mica, are often taken for granite.

CRYSTAL STAG.name: Crystal Stag
CRYSTAL STAG.flavorText: Arrives alone, but usually leaves with a friend just like him.

SCREAMING BANSHEE.name: Screaming Banshee
SCREAMING BANSHEE.flavorText: Her singing will be sure to wake you up (wake you up inside).

WATER MOCCASIN.name: Water Moccasin
WATER MOCCASIN.flavorText: You need to be specific when you're ordering waterproof shoewear.

ANKA, THE BURIED.name: Anka, the Buried
ANKA, THE BURIED.flavorText: "You look familiar. Were you at my first funeral?"

TWILIGHT SUMMONER.name: Twilight Summoner
TWILIGHT SUMMONER.flavorText: If you strike him down, he shall become more powerful than you can possibly imagine.

INJURED KVALDIR.name: Injured Kvaldir
INJURED KVALDIR.flavorText: Don't worry. With a little skin cream he's going to clear right up.

MISTAKE.name: Mistake
MISTAKE.flavorText: We like to think of it as a happy accident.

BACKSTAGE BOUNCER.name: Backstage Bouncer
BACKSTAGE BOUNCER.flavorText: Doesn't see your name on the list. Also doesn't know how to read the names on the list.

LAVA SHOCK.name: Lava Shock
LAVA SHOCK.flavorText: Chocolate lava cake is shockingly delicious.

LIGHTSHOW.name: Lightshow
LIGHTSHOW.flavorText: Always remember P.L.U.R.: Peace, Laser-beams, Unity, Respect.

IMP GANG BOSS.name: Imp Gang Boss
IMP GANG BOSS.flavorText: His imp gang likes to sneak into Stormwind to spraypaint "Ragnaros Rulez" on the Mage Tower.

INFERNAL STRATAGEM.name: Infernal Stratagem
INFERNAL STRATAGEM.flavorText: Archimonde INSISTS on calling it a stratagem instead of a strategy because it "sounds cooler."

MOJOMASTER ZIHI.name: Mojomaster Zihi
MOJOMASTER ZIHI.flavorText: Sadly, she was still two credits short of her Witch Doctorate.

DIRE MOLE.name: Dire Mole
DIRE MOLE.flavorText: You especially don't want to make a dire mountain out of a dire mole hill.

RAZORPETAL VOLLEY.name: Razorpetal Volley
RAZORPETAL VOLLEY.flavorText: The result of a fundamental misunderstanding of the phrase "flower power".

HARRISON JONES.name: Harrison Jones
HARRISON JONES.flavorText: “That belongs in the Hall of Explorers!”

DARK IRON DWARF.name: Dark Iron Dwarf
DARK IRON DWARF.flavorText: Guardians of Dark Iron Ore. Perhaps the most annoying ore, given where you have to forge it.

CANNIBALIZE.name: Cannibalize
CANNIBALIZE.flavorText: The Silvermoon health inspector has some choice words for the Lich King.

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/6/6c/VO_BT_486_Male_PitLord_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BT_486_Male_PitLord_Play_01.wav Fools! Get in there and crush them!

STABLEMASTER.name: Stablemaster
STABLEMASTER.flavorText: Takes way better care of her pets than her brother, Unstablemaster.

FROM THE DEPTHS.name: From the Depths
FROM THE DEPTHS.flavorText: "This is why I'm afraid of the deep end of the pool."

AL'AKIR, THE WINDS OF TIME.name: Al'Akir, the Winds of Time
AL'AKIR, THE WINDS OF TIME.flavorText: Murozond sought unlikely allies in his fight against the Bronze Dragonflight.

HERALD OF LIGHT.name: Herald of Light
HERALD OF LIGHT.flavorText: Wake up! No sleeping in with the fishes!

RUMMAGING KOBOLD.name: Rummaging Kobold
RUMMAGING KOBOLD.flavorText: "Broken longsword is brand new shortsword." - Kobold Proverb

SEABREEZE CHALICE.name: Seabreeze Chalice
SEABREEZE CHALICE.flavorText: If your luck has been particularly poor lately, try the extra salted rim!

HYLDNIR FROSTRIDER.name: Hyldnir Frostrider
HYLDNIR FROSTRIDER.flavorText: Don't be fooled, that polar bear's the one in charge.

SOULBURNER VARIA.name: Soulburner Varia
SOULBURNER VARIA.flavorText: Captain's Log. 8/11/2023 There are 60 minutes remaining until the Flavor Text is due. It is Friday at 4 PM. We are out of stamina and ideas. Please send funnies, punnies, quippies, or your finest hahas. - The Design Team

LUSHWATER MURCENARY.name: Lushwater Murcenary
LUSHWATER MURCENARY.flavorText: You can't just switch sides because they have more fish!

CURIO COLLECTOR.name: Curio Collector
CURIO COLLECTOR.flavorText: Experts worry that curios are a gateway to face-collecting.

MIRAGE CALLER.name: Mirage Caller
MIRAGE CALLER.flavorText: Mirage is actually the name of its long-lost cat.

TOUR GUIDE.name: Tour Guide
TOUR GUIDE.flavorText: "Here is the original blueprint for the Academy grounds! Don't mind those so-called dark chambers… They'll be at the end of the tour."

SPIRIT OF THE RAPTOR.name: Spirit of the Raptor
SPIRIT OF THE RAPTOR.flavorText: “Loti! LOTI! Drop it. Drop it Loti! Down! Down Loti!”

MUTATE.name: Mutate
MUTATE.flavorText: You'll get the transformation you want when murlocs fly.

SNOOZIN' ZOOKEEPER.name: Snoozin' Zookeeper
SNOOZIN' ZOOKEEPER.flavorText: You snooze, you lose (track of a very large and hungry panther).

SKY CLAW.name: Sky Claw
SKY CLAW.flavorText: Carefully engineered to never grab the Mimiron plush toy.

DISCO AT THE END OF TIME.name: Disco at the End of Time
DISCO AT THE END OF TIME.flavorText: This is what you've been saving the last dance for.

WATER ELEMENTAL.name: Water Elemental
WATER ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Don't summon a water elemental at a party. It'll dampen the mood.

CLUMSY STEWARD.name: Clumsy Steward
CLUMSY STEWARD.flavorText: "Aww, bummer! I spilled coffee all over your cards! Dang it! What a shame!"

EXPLOSIVE EVOLUTION.name: Explosive Evolution
EXPLOSIVE EVOLUTION.flavorText: Let's give a big hand for goblin experimentation!

GOLDPETAL DRAKE.name: Goldpetal Drake
GOLDPETAL DRAKE.flavorText: All that glitters is gold... Petal. Drake.

TWIN TYRANT.name: Twin Tyrant
TWIN TYRANT.flavorText: They can never agree on whether it's too hot or too cold.

BLACKROCK 'N' ROLL.name: Blackrock 'n' Roll
BLACKROCK 'N' ROLL.flavorText: Thank goodness it's not called Black-ska Mountain.

LANDSCAPING.name: Landscaping
LANDSCAPING.flavorText: We'll put a happy tree right here... and give him a little friend.

STARPORT.name: Starport
STARPORT.flavorText: Make sure to arrive 3 light-years early for any intergalactic flights.

SAFEGUARD.name: Safeguard
SAFEGUARD.flavorText: Keep it secret. Keep it safeguarded!

DARING ESCAPE.name: Daring Escape
DARING ESCAPE.flavorText: Impossible to cast without cackling evilly.

ARID STORMER.name: Arid Stormer
ARID STORMER.flavorText: Some people chase storms, some storms chase elementals.

SNAPDRAGON.name: Snapdragon
SNAPDRAGON.flavorText: Good synergy with Crackledragon, not so much with Popdragon.

ROLLING FIREBALL.name: Rolling Fireball
ROLLING FIREBALL.flavorText: Why don't they ever run perpendicular?

BLADESTORM.name: Bladestorm
BLADESTORM.flavorText: Dear minions: Woosh, woosh, woosh, woosh, woosh. Best regards, Bladestorm

CURSED DISCIPLE.name: Cursed Disciple
CURSED DISCIPLE.flavorText: Politer than his brother, the cursing disciple, but far more evil.

GUARDIAN OF KINGS.name: Guardian of Kings
GUARDIAN OF KINGS.flavorText: Holy beings from the beyond are so cliché!

THASSARIAN.name: Thassarian
THASSARIAN.flavorText: A natural born leader. And an unnatural reborn leader.

KEENING BANSHEE.name: Keening Banshee
KEENING BANSHEE.flavorText: "What are your strengths?" the interviewer asked. "Well," she replied, "I'm really good at keening."

LOTHRAXION THE REDEEMED.name: Lothraxion the Redeemed
LOTHRAXION THE REDEEMED.flavorText: So infused with the Light, he has to wear double sleep masks at night.

TRANSFER STUDENT.name: Transfer Student
TRANSFER STUDENT.flavorText: Oh, the places you'll go! There is so much to fight! There are boards to be explored. There are dreams to take flight.

NYTHENDRA.name: Nythendra
NYTHENDRA.flavorText: Bug Report: Minion split into 1/1 Beetles and then reformed at the start of next turn.

KUL TIRAN CHAPLAIN.name: Kul Tiran Chaplain
KUL TIRAN CHAPLAIN.flavorText: The maritime Kul Tiran clergy are unique among priests for using holy saltwater.

MC BLINGTRON.name: MC Blingtron
MC BLINGTRON.flavorText: If this is the outcome of the robot uprising, then sign me up!

GIANT TUMBLEWEED!!!.name: Giant Tumbleweed!!!
GIANT TUMBLEWEED!!!.flavorText: Skarr's second-biggest hobby after laying waste to the Badlands is bowling.

ICE RAGER.name: Ice Rager
ICE RAGER.flavorText: He's a lot cooler than Magma Rager.

DIVINE TOLL.name: Divine Toll
DIVINE TOLL.flavorText: Never send to know for whom the bell tolls.

PROUD DEFENDER.name: Proud Defender
PROUD DEFENDER.flavorText: It'll take a humble offender to defeat him.

MUROZOND, THIEF OF TIME.name: Murozond, Thief of Time
MUROZOND, THIEF OF TIME.flavorText: By unwinding the fall of C'Thun, Murozond would claim the Old God's power, and with it, the world.

DEVOTED MANIAC.name: Devoted Maniac
DEVOTED MANIAC.flavorText: There are plenty of apathetic maniacs, but they couldn't be bothered.

KNIGHT OF THE DEAD.name: Knight of the Dead
KNIGHT OF THE DEAD.flavorText: A Paladin will follow their oath to slay the undead, even when they count themselves among them.

INFILTRATE.name: Infiltrate
INFILTRATE.flavorText: Everybody get out of here! Except you. You can stay.

PLAGUEBRINGER.name: Plaguebringer
PLAGUEBRINGER.flavorText: One sip and you've got the grippe.

MISTRESS OF MIXTURES.name: Mistress of Mixtures
MISTRESS OF MIXTURES.flavorText: Her favorite mixture is cola and lime.

CLOUD PRINCE.name: Cloud Prince
CLOUD PRINCE.flavorText: "In West Cloudidelphia, born and raised; flinging lightning for the rest of my days."

MURLOC TASTYFIN.name: Murloc Tastyfin
MURLOC TASTYFIN.flavorText: He was destined for the soup. One way or another…

DEATHBRINGER SAURFANG.name: Deathbringer Saurfang
DEATHBRINGER SAURFANG.flavorText: "In hindsight, maybe I should have let the Alliance have all the fun back at the Wrathgate."

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e9/VO_RLK_082_Male_Orc_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_RLK_082_Male_Orc_Play_01.wav Embrace the gift of death, as I have!

PARTY ANIMAL.name: Party Animal
PARTY ANIMAL.flavorText: He's the wildlife of the party!

BLOOD SHARD BRISTLEBACK.name: Blood Shard Bristleback
BLOOD SHARD BRISTLEBACK.flavorText: I'm bringin' bristle back (Yeah) Those other minions don't know how to act (Yeah) I think it's special how these crystals crack (Yeah) So turn around and I'll give you a smack (Yeah) (Take 'em to the Barrens)

VIVID NIGHTMARE.name: Vivid Nightmare
VIVID NIGHTMARE.flavorText: "I… I dreamed I accidentally crafted a golden Millhouse! It was so REAL!"

GOBLIN SAPPER.name: Goblin Sapper
GOBLIN SAPPER.flavorText: He’s not such a binge exploder anymore. These days, he only explodes socially.

DON'T FEED THE ANIMALS.name: Don't Feed the Animals
DON'T FEED THE ANIMALS.flavorText: They're still cleaning up the mess from the last time someone fed the basilisk a deep fried candybar.

RAMBUNCTIOUS STUFFY.name: Rambunctious Stuffy
RAMBUNCTIOUS STUFFY.flavorText: The Lich King can't sleep without his stuffy.

TO THE FRONT!.name: To the Front!
TO THE FRONT!.flavorText: Except healers. You go to the back.

JUNGLE GYM.name: Jungle Gym
JUNGLE GYM.flavorText: Yeah, I work out at the gym. The one with all the plushies and toys.

ETHEREAL AUGMERCHANT.name: Ethereal Augmerchant
ETHEREAL AUGMERCHANT.flavorText: According to him, undamaged minions just spell problems.

NATURE STUDIES.name: Nature Studies
NATURE STUDIES.flavorText: "I have a first edition! Go ahead, count the rings."

GROVE TENDER.name: Grove Tender
GROVE TENDER.flavorText: Likes: Hiking and the great outdoors. Dislikes: Goblin shredders and sandals. (Can’t find any that fit!).

GLORY CHASER.name: Glory Chaser
GLORY CHASER.flavorText: When you've reached the peak of competition twice, how hard can winning one valley be?

DEAD AIR.name: Dead Air
DEAD AIR.flavorText: We'll be right back after a word from our specters.

SHADOW SCULPTOR.name: Shadow Sculptor
SHADOW SCULPTOR.flavorText: Carving out new territory in the realm of shadow puppetry.

BEASTMASTER LEOROXX.name: Beastmaster Leoroxx
BEASTMASTER LEOROXX.flavorText: Father of Rexxar, Champion of the Horde, and Flexxar, Champion of the Gym.

COUNTERFEIT COIN.name: Counterfeit Coin
COUNTERFEIT COIN.flavorText: There is something funny about this coin… can't quite put my finger on it…

RAVENOUS PTERRORDAX.name: Ravenous Pterrordax
RAVENOUS PTERRORDAX.flavorText: For better results, feed your pterrordax low-fat, high-fiber minions.

NETHERSPITE HISTORIAN.name: Netherspite Historian
NETHERSPITE HISTORIAN.flavorText: She can tell you all about the history of people not STANDING IN THE GREEN BEAM!

DESERT NESTMATRON.name: Desert Nestmatron
DESERT NESTMATRON.flavorText: Not as sweet as the Dessert Nestmatron, but still just as refreshing!

JUNGLE JAMMER.name: Jungle Jammer
JUNGLE JAMMER.flavorText: When asked what animal they would be, people always say things like "I'd be wolf-lion hybrid mix. King of the jungle, but still sociable and ferocious." No, you'd be a rat.

SPLITTING AXE.name: Splitting Axe
SPLITTING AXE.flavorText: The ancient shaman chant, "Control Axe, Control Vee."

BOOK WYRM.name: Book Wyrm
BOOK WYRM.flavorText: His favorites are classic tragedies like "The Hobbit" and "Grendel".

MOUNTAIN BEAR.name: Mountain Bear
MOUNTAIN BEAR.flavorText: If they want your picnic basket, I recommend giving it to them.

ARA'LON.name: Ara'lon
ARA'LON.flavorText: If I had a nickel for every time a Hunter Legendary minion in Castle Nathria summoned three different companions, I'd have two nickels - which isn't a lot, but it's weird that it happened twice.

GRAND MAGISTER ROMMATH.name: Grand Magister Rommath
GRAND MAGISTER ROMMATH.flavorText: A powerful mage known for his proficiencies in Fire, Frost, and Algebra.

SIR FINLEY MRRGGLTON.name: Sir Finley Mrrgglton
SIR FINLEY MRRGGLTON.flavorText: In addition to fluent Common, he also speaks fourteen dialects of 'mrgl'.

GONK, THE RAPTOR.name: Gonk, the Raptor
GONK, THE RAPTOR.flavorText: There’s a word for Zandalari druids who refuse to pledge loyalty to Gonk: “Delicious.”

FIELD CONTACT.name: Field Contact
FIELD CONTACT.flavorText: That's not a knife... THIS is a knife!

BUNNY STOMPER.name: Bunny Stomper
BUNNY STOMPER.flavorText: Has a PhD in stomputational chemistry.

HIDDEN GEM.name: Hidden Gem
HIDDEN GEM.flavorText: This will be a staple in Unicorn Priest.

MOROES.name: Moroes
MOROES.flavorText: Moroes runs an army of stewards, but still ends up inflating the balloons himself.

RED MANA WYRM.name: Red Mana Wyrm
RED MANA WYRM.flavorText: It has double the Attack. "Go on." And double the Health. "Yes??" And its trigger has twice the effect. "WHAT???" And it costs… Five times more.

SPIRIT HEALER.name: Spirit Healer
SPIRIT HEALER.flavorText: "You again? What did I tell you about trying to fight ALL the quilboars."

CROOKED COOK.name: Crooked Cook
CROOKED COOK.flavorText: There are many things not called poison which can kill a man. But in this case, it is poison.

SHADOWCRAFTER SCABBS.name: Shadowcrafter Scabbs
SHADOWCRAFTER SCABBS.flavorText: Sneaking behind enemy lines isn't so different from being a line cook. People are hostile, something's on fire, and your only hope is to get out of there with all your fingers.

WICKERCLAW.name: Wickerclaw
WICKERCLAW.flavorText: They say pets tend to look like their owners.

LIGHTRAY.name: Lightray
LIGHTRAY.flavorText: Lightrays, much like rays of light, tend to be seen closer to the surface.

DIRDRA, REBEL CAPTAIN.name: Dirdra, Rebel Captain
DIRDRA, REBEL CAPTAIN.flavorText: Under Velen's command, the Draenei avoid engaging with the enemy in fear of eradication. Under Dirdra's command, the Voronei fight the Legion head on in hopes of eradication.

MELTEMENTAL.name: Meltemental
MELTEMENTAL.flavorText: "Who left these wet bracers on the ground?"

LIVING DRAGONBREATH.name: Living Dragonbreath
LIVING DRAGONBREATH.flavorText: If you want that muscular physique, you've really gotta feel the burn.

APOTHECARY HELBRIM.name: Apothecary Helbrim
APOTHECARY HELBRIM.flavorText: The best way to maintain your health is to poison everyone else.

ROCK RAGER.name: Rock Rager
ROCK RAGER.flavorText: Still doesn't understand why he can't beat Paper Rager.

SOLEMN VIGIL.name: Solemn Vigil
SOLEMN VIGIL.flavorText: Each year, folk gather in front of Blackrock Mountain to mourn those who were mind-controlled into the lava.

MISTWRAITH.name: Mistwraith
MISTWRAITH.flavorText: One little Mistwraith sitting in a tree. M-I-S-T-I-N-G.

BLOODFURY POTION.name: Bloodfury Potion
BLOODFURY POTION.flavorText: You know what really makes my blood boil? The skyrocketing price of Bloodfury potions!

VETERAN WARMEDIC.name: Veteran Warmedic
VETERAN WARMEDIC.flavorText: In times of war, warmedics bring their own medics.

HALAZZI, THE LYNX.name: Halazzi, the Lynx
HALAZZI, THE LYNX.flavorText: Remember, you’re only as strong as your weakest lynx.

KNICKKNACK SHACK.name: Knickknack Shack
KNICKKNACK SHACK.flavorText: In a hole in the ground there... was a tourist trap?

RAPTOR HERALD.name: Raptor Herald
RAPTOR HERALD.flavorText: Huh, is that meteor getting bigger?

AUCTIONMASTER BEARDO.name: Auctionmaster Beardo
AUCTIONMASTER BEARDO.flavorText: Gadgetzan has always run an under-the-table auction house, and business has been PRETTY good for Beardo since the population explosion. And since the explosion that destroyed the competing auction houses in the city.

SPLITTING FESTEROOT.name: Splitting Festeroot
SPLITTING FESTEROOT.flavorText: No use crying over split Festeroot,

BREATH OF SINDRAGOSA.name: Breath of Sindragosa
BREATH OF SINDRAGOSA.flavorText: Is it cold in here or is it just Sindragosa?

PET COLLECTOR.name: Pet Collector
PET COLLECTOR.flavorText: "And I'll call you Mrs. Snugglepants, and you Bubblecuddle, and you Cutie Cakes, and you ..."

BURNDOWN.name: Burndown
BURNDOWN.flavorText: Trust me, the next 3 cards in my deck are FIRE.

ORBITAL HALO.name: Orbital Halo
ORBITAL HALO.flavorText: I can see your halo. HALO. Haaaalo.

SPLINTERGRAFT.name: Splintergraft
SPLINTERGRAFT.flavorText: We're going to need some bigger tweezers.

JOLLY ROGER.name: Jolly Roger
JOLLY ROGER.flavorText: That's a great pose, Roger. But this time try happier, and with your mouth open.

FEN CREEPER.name: Fen Creeper
FEN CREEPER.flavorText: He used to be called Bog Beast, but it confused people because he wasn't an actual beast. Boom, New Name!

INTERSTELLAR WAYFARER.name: Interstellar Wayfarer
INTERSTELLAR WAYFARER.flavorText: This card is way fairer than most.

N'ZOTH'S FIRST MATE.name: N'Zoth's First Mate
N'ZOTH'S FIRST MATE.flavorText: Hates when N'Zoth yells "Ahoy Matey!!", but there's not really much he can do about it.

SIGIL OF ALACRITY.name: Sigil of Alacrity
SIGIL OF ALACRITY.flavorText: Red means stop. Purple means GO REALLY FAST.

SPLITTING IMAGE.name: Splitting Image
SPLITTING IMAGE.flavorText: Sometimes you get punched so hard they see double.

XARIL, POISONED MIND.name: Xaril, Poisoned Mind
XARIL, POISONED MIND.flavorText: It's basically your own fault if you go around drinking weird green potions handed out by creepy mantid dudes.

SEEDCLOUD BUCKLER.name: Seedcloud Buckler
SEEDCLOUD BUCKLER.flavorText: A shield to some, a frisbee to others (mainly dogs).

LIBRAM OF WISDOM.name: Libram of Wisdom
LIBRAM OF WISDOM.flavorText: The best wisdom is passed on.

TOY CAPTAIN TARIM.name: Toy Captain Tarim
TOY CAPTAIN TARIM.flavorText: Whizbang is now the sole proprietor of Un'Goro.

BLOODCLAW.name: Bloodclaw
BLOODCLAW.flavorText: This weapon – ow! Requires a little – OWW! Finesse.

HOWLFIEND.name: Howlfiend
HOWLFIEND.flavorText: The problem is that he carries those cards in his mouth.

LIGHT OF THE NAARU.name: Light of the Naaru
LIGHT OF THE NAARU.flavorText: "Light it up!" - Command given to both Lightwardens and Goblins holding Flamecannons.

SHADOW WORD: STEAL.name: Shadow Word: Steal
SHADOW WORD: STEAL.flavorText: Anduin will literally take your stuff and say it's a Shadow Word.

DISCIPLE OF GOLGANNETH.name: Disciple of Golganneth
DISCIPLE OF GOLGANNETH.flavorText: Warning: If you are not made of rocks, do not stand in lightning water.

STRONGSHELL SCAVENGER.name: Strongshell Scavenger
STRONGSHELL SCAVENGER.flavorText: It isn't "grave robbing" when there's no grave. It's just scavenging…

THERAZANE.name: Therazane
THERAZANE.flavorText: You thought we forgot about her, didn't you? *nervous laughter*

BLUR.name: Blur
BLUR.flavorText: "What are you trying to tell me? That I can dodge axes?" "I’m trying to tell you that when you’re a Demon Hunter, you won’t have to."

INCORPOREAL CORPORAL.name: Incorporeal Corporal
INCORPOREAL CORPORAL.flavorText: You won't believe how long this was called "Incorporal Corporeal"…

ARCANOSMITH.name: Arcanosmith
ARCANOSMITH.flavorText: He’s really just a Blacksmith, but he thought the fancy title would bring in more business.

HUDDLE UP.name: Huddle Up
HUDDLE UP.flavorText: Spell, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga, Naga...

RAMMING MOUNT.name: Ramming Mount
RAMMING MOUNT.flavorText: Tavish has some road rage issues to work through.

ZAP!.name: Zap!
ZAP!.flavorText: The material components for this spell are wool socks and a rug.

CLERIC OF SCALES.name: Cleric of Scales
CLERIC OF SCALES.flavorText: If she can't find a spell, it's a clerical error.

SUCKERHOOK.name: Suckerhook
SUCKERHOOK.flavorText: A moderately better dining companion than Suckerbeard.

VELEN'S CHOSEN.name: Velen's Chosen
VELEN'S CHOSEN.flavorText: Velen wrote a "Lovely Card" for Tyrande with a picture of the Deeprun Tram that said "I Choo-Choo-Choose you!"

FLINT FIREARM.name: Flint Firearm
FLINT FIREARM.flavorText: You'll never guess why they call him that.

UNDERLIGHT ANGLING ROD.name: Underlight Angling Rod
UNDERLIGHT ANGLING ROD.flavorText: "I said I wanted the ASHbringer not FISHbringer!"

THE GALACTIC PROJECTION ORB.name: The Galactic Projection Orb
THE GALACTIC PROJECTION ORB.flavorText: Look closely in the ball and you'll see the expansion of space and time itself. Or their projections, anyway.

MAEXXNA.name: Maexxna
MAEXXNA.flavorText: Maexxna gets super mad when people introduce her as "Maxina" or "Maxxy".

BLINGTRON 3000.name: Blingtron 3000
BLINGTRON 3000.flavorText: PREPARE PARTY SERVOS FOR IMMEDIATE DEPLOYMENT.

CHIEF INSPECTOR.name: Chief Inspector
CHIEF INSPECTOR.flavorText: Empty your pockets, I know you’ve got a Wandering Monster in there!

CRUISE CAPTAIN LORA.name: Cruise Captain Lora
CRUISE CAPTAIN LORA.flavorText: To your left is our award winning spa area! And to the right, THE PRISON OF YOGG-SARON!

Q'ONZU.name: Q'onzu
Q'ONZU.flavorText: "Where did Sarge go? Anyone seen Sarge?" - Harth

EVIL HECKLER.name: Evil Heckler
EVIL HECKLER.flavorText: To be honest, heckling is not the most effective form of evil.

TWILIGHT WHELP.name: Twilight Whelp
TWILIGHT WHELP.flavorText: The twilight whelps are basically magic-vampires. Despite this, they are not a reference to any popular series of novels.

JEWEL OF N'ZOTH.name: Jewel of N'Zoth
JEWEL OF N'ZOTH.flavorText: This coveted gem calls for you to free it… and unleash an inescapable prison.

SEADEVIL STINGER.name: Seadevil Stinger
SEADEVIL STINGER.flavorText: Pretty harmless unless you're a Seadevil.

GNOMISH INVENTOR.name: Gnomish Inventor
GNOMISH INVENTOR.flavorText: She's never quite sure what she's making, she just knows it's AWESOME!

DJ MANASTORM.name: DJ Manastorm
DJ MANASTORM.flavorText: Do not sleep on his Tinker Town deep house set - absolutely legendary.

INSATIABLE FELHOUND.name: Insatiable Felhound
INSATIABLE FELHOUND.flavorText: Back-to-back winner of the annual hot dog eating contest... and the judge-eating contest.

ARENA FANATIC.name: Arena Fanatic
ARENA FANATIC.flavorText: Her fantasy Rumble league gives double points for dismemberment.

ENSMALLEN.name: Ensmallen
ENSMALLEN.flavorText: Come on, you know- I ensmallen, you ensmallen? He she me Ensmallen? Ensmallogy: the study of ensmallening?! IT'S FIRST GRADE.

ACOLYTE OF AGONY.name: Acolyte of Agony
ACOLYTE OF AGONY.flavorText: It takes many years of practiced study in order to fully master agony.

INCINDIUS.name: Incindius
INCINDIUS.flavorText: "I had nothing to do with that eruption! I never even met Kezandius!"

SHIELD OF HONOR.name: Shield of Honor
SHIELD OF HONOR.flavorText: "Sir, this shield would've been more helpful last turn!"

VALEERA THE HOLLOW.name: Valeera the Hollow
VALEERA THE HOLLOW.flavorText: "Run away. Hide in your precious keeps, behind your walls and your bodyguards. Night always falls, and shadows will fill your hallowed halls. One day, one of those shadows will be me."

PANTRY SPIDER.name: Pantry Spider
PANTRY SPIDER.flavorText: You have to admit, they make a cute couple.

SILVERMOON BROCHURE.name: Silvermoon Brochure
SILVERMOON BROCHURE.flavorText: It's lovely to visit this time of year. Just ignore that enormous scarred area outside.

CONDITIONING (RANK 1).name: Conditioning (Rank 1)
CONDITIONING (RANK 1).flavorText: Now drop and give me 5 Mana.

ICECROWN BROCHURE.name: Icecrown Brochure
ICECROWN BROCHURE.flavorText: The Icecrown ski slopes really are to die for.

DRAKEFIRE AMULET.name: Drakefire Amulet
DRAKEFIRE AMULET.flavorText: "...and I only had to climb up the mountains in Winterspring 50 times!"

STARLIGHT WANDERER.name: Starlight Wanderer
STARLIGHT WANDERER.flavorText: Not all who wander are lost, but some most definitely are and could really use directions right about now.

ANTI-MAGIC SHELL.name: Anti-Magic Shell
ANTI-MAGIC SHELL.flavorText: Using a spell to counter magic - a bit hypocritical don't you think?

DERAILED COASTER.name: Derailed Coaster
DERAILED COASTER.flavorText: So long as it doesn’t kill you, it's considered part of the ride "experience."

LUCKYSOUL HOARDER.name: Luckysoul Hoarder
LUCKYSOUL HOARDER.flavorText: Always brings his own reusable shopping bag, satchel, barrel, trunk, tray, and fluffy pillow.

FORCE-TANK MAX.name: Force-Tank MAX
FORCE-TANK MAX.flavorText: There is a factory in Tanaris for crafting force-tanks, but it only ever made two, because of cost overruns.

FEROCIOUS HOWL.name: Ferocious Howl
FEROCIOUS HOWL.flavorText: Have you ever heard the wolf cry to the blue corn moon?

GUESS THE WEIGHT.name: Guess the Weight
GUESS THE WEIGHT.flavorText: "And then at the last second, I'll shapeshift into cat form!"

CITY TAX.name: City Tax
CITY TAX.flavorText: "Look pal, I don't care what kind of legion you saved the world from, pay up or else."

BLESSING OF WISDOM.name: Blessing of Wisdom
BLESSING OF WISDOM.flavorText: Apparently with wisdom comes the knowledge that you should probably be attacking every turn.

CHEESEMONGER.name: Cheesemonger
CHEESEMONGER.flavorText: Secretly, the Big Cheese of SI:7.

COLOSSUS OF THE MOON.name: Colossus of the Moon
COLOSSUS OF THE MOON.flavorText: Strike him down, and you'll face the Colossus of the New Moon.

DEMONIC ASSAULT.name: Demonic Assault
DEMONIC ASSAULT.flavorText: Right next to the demonic pepper.

SELFLESS HERO.name: Selfless Hero
SELFLESS HERO.flavorText: "Don't worry about me… I'll just be here... under these tentacles."

DIREHORN HATCHLING.name: Direhorn Hatchling
DIREHORN HATCHLING.flavorText: His mom could beat up your mom.

JUNGLE GIANTS.name: Jungle Giants
JUNGLE GIANTS.flavorText: Forming the Golakka Crater was the end of Barnabus' disastrous career as a dancer.

ABYSSAL ENFORCER.name: Abyssal Enforcer
ABYSSAL ENFORCER.flavorText: The Kabal print this on every package of illicit Mana Crystals: WARNING - DO NOT PUT WITHIN REACH OF ABYSSALS. THIS IS NOT APPROVED FOR USE BY FLAMING DEMONS OF ANY KIND.

RISING WAVES.name: Rising Waves
RISING WAVES.flavorText: How do you expect them to do the wave if their arms are buried in the sand??

DRAGONBANE.name: Dragonbane
DRAGONBANE.flavorText: *Thunk* "That wasn’t a dragon!" *Thunk* "THAT wasn’t a dragon!"

CLASS ACTION LAWYER.name: Class Action Lawyer
CLASS ACTION LAWYER.flavorText: "Have you or a loved one ever been injured in a Consecration?"

NOSTALGIC INITIATE.name: Nostalgic Initiate
NOSTALGIC INITIATE.flavorText: Nostalgic Initiate: "Man I wish I could relive my college days..." Kel'thuzad: "Say no more."

COMPETITIVE SPIRIT.name: Competitive Spirit
COMPETITIVE SPIRIT.flavorText: Competition can be an inspiration to improve oneself. Or kill all the competitors.

SUNSTRUCK HENCHMAN.name: Sunstruck Henchman
SUNSTRUCK HENCHMAN.flavorText: There is E.V.I.L. here that DOES sleep.

LYNESSA SUNSORROW.name: Lynessa Sunsorrow
LYNESSA SUNSORROW.flavorText: A diet of pure magic is great for the complexion but wreaks havoc on one's mood.

LIGHT OF THE PHOENIX.name: Light of the Phoenix
LIGHT OF THE PHOENIX.flavorText: It's 3 in the morning, could you PLEASE put out that phoenix?!

RAIN OF FIRE.name: Rain of Fire
RAIN OF FIRE.flavorText: You know it’s autumn when the skies rain brimstone and fire. Also: pumpkin spice!

STONEHEART KING.name: Stoneheart King
STONEHEART KING.flavorText: I, too, am a king at playing Heart Stone.

DRAGON TALES.name: Dragon Tales
DRAGON TALES.flavorText: "Once upon a time, there was a maaaagical toy shop, filled with wonder and Dragons!"

DETONATION JUGGERNAUT.name: Detonation Juggernaut
DETONATION JUGGERNAUT.flavorText: Did you really need a whole giant mecha-suit just for one bundle of dynamite?

CATACLYSM.name: Cataclysm
CATACLYSM.flavorText: RUN FROM SKY CANDLES! THEY BURN! RUN!

INVENTOR'S AURA.name: Inventor's Aura
INVENTOR'S AURA.flavorText: Ok, fine, I'll read the manual…

HAKKAR, THE SOULFLAYER.name: Hakkar, the Soulflayer
HAKKAR, THE SOULFLAYER.flavorText: ATTENTION: Do not enter any major city while infected with the Corrupted Blood!

THE DEMON SEED.name: The Demon Seed
THE DEMON SEED.flavorText: Just need some elbow grease to get this working. Oh, and your soul.

HIGH ABBESS ALURA.name: High Abbess Alura
HIGH ABBESS ALURA.flavorText: She's all about hitting the books. Literally.

CROSSROADS WATCH POST.name: Crossroads Watch Post
CROSSROADS WATCH POST.flavorText: All of Barrens Chat is recorded and kept on thousands of scrolls stored beneath this tower.

EXARCH HATAARU.name: Exarch Hataaru
EXARCH HATAARU.flavorText: Severely outmatched by the Burning Legion, the Draenei had no hopes of survival… That changed with the invention of arkonite crystals, giving Hataaru and his Artificers new ways to empower their people.

ILLUSORY GREENWING.name: Illusory Greenwing
ILLUSORY GREENWING.flavorText: "MORE LIKE, A LOSER-Y GREENWING! MUAHAHA!" - Nightmare Lord Xavius

SIF.name: Sif
SIF.flavorText: She is Sif. He is Malygos. They are not the same person. They may have similar spell damage, they may have similar colors but they are different nonetheless.

PSYFIEND.name: Psyfiend
PSYFIEND.flavorText: Listens to a LOT of K-pop.

UNPOWERED MAULER.name: Unpowered Mauler
UNPOWERED MAULER.flavorText: After a stressful work day it really needs an outlet.

GRAND CRUSADER.name: Grand Crusader
GRAND CRUSADER.flavorText: A veteran of a number of crusades, she is a force for light and goodness. Her latest crusade is against goblin telemarketers.

UR'ZUL GIANT.name: Ur'zul Giant
UR'ZUL GIANT.flavorText: Nothing personal, tiny human. I have many mouths to feed.

SHINING SENTINEL.name: Shining Sentinel
SHINING SENTINEL.flavorText: OMG, I FINALLY GOT A SHINING SENTINEL AFTER 3 PHASES AND 8192 RESETS!!!!!

DARKEST HOUR.name: Darkest Hour
DARKEST HOUR.flavorText: It's always darkest just before you find the light switch.

HUNGRY DRAGON.name: Hungry Dragon
HUNGRY DRAGON.flavorText: Hungry Hungry Dragon is NOT a fun game.

FIREGUARD DESTROYER.name: Fireguard Destroyer
FIREGUARD DESTROYER.flavorText: Ragnaros interviews hundreds of Fire Elementals for the position of "Destroyer" but very few have what it takes.

RAJ NAZ'JAN.name: Raj Naz'jan
RAJ NAZ'JAN.flavorText: When you play the Coin, he deals emotional damage.

BOG BEAST.name: Bog Beast
BOG BEAST.flavorText: I'm sure at least one of those bones is from an actual beast.

TRINKET TRACKER.name: Trinket Tracker
TRINKET TRACKER.flavorText: Dashing through the snow On an undead trinket craze Over the hills we go Tracking all the way!

SAVAGE YMIRJAR.name: Savage Ymirjar
SAVAGE YMIRJAR.flavorText: When is an Undead door not an Undead door? When it's a(Ymir)jar!

XHILAG OF THE ABYSS.name: Xhilag of the Abyss
XHILAG OF THE ABYSS.flavorText: When ancient heroes drove a felhunter into the sea, they thought it was the end. But for Xhilag, it was only the beginning...

RAY OF FROST.name: Ray of Frost
RAY OF FROST.flavorText: If you have zero chill, this can help.

KABAL CHEMIST.name: Kabal Chemist
KABAL CHEMIST.flavorText: Sure you could have that Polymorph potion, but wouldn't you rather have this mystery potion? It could be anything. Even a Polymorph potion!

TOURNAMENT ATTENDEE.name: Tournament Attendee
TOURNAMENT ATTENDEE.flavorText: He was so excited to get season tickets to this year's Grand Tournament. He normally doesn't get them at first and has to buy them from Ogre scalpers.

KATHRENA WINTERWISP.name: Kathrena Winterwisp
KATHRENA WINTERWISP.flavorText: She’s not one of those treehugger elves – but she does like the occasional cuddle.

BLOODSAIL HOWLER.name: Bloodsail Howler
BLOODSAIL HOWLER.flavorText: They saw their fate a closin' Aboard a pirate ship On deck: The Howlin' Hozen About to let one rip.

GHASTLY GRAVEDIGGER.name: Ghastly Gravedigger
GHASTLY GRAVEDIGGER.flavorText: Some people take their secrets to the grave.

KHAZ'GOROTH.name: Khaz'goroth
KHAZ'GOROTH.flavorText: Creator of the titan-forged races, Khaz'goroth intended them to safeguard the world of Azeroth from corruption and discord.

UNSTABLE FELBOLT.name: Unstable Felbolt
UNSTABLE FELBOLT.flavorText: Warning! Your minions are seated in the splash zone.

OBSESSIVE FAN.name: Obsessive Fan
OBSESSIVE FAN.flavorText: "Obsessed? No! I'm just really really really really really really really really really really into E.T.C.'s music and everything he says, does, thinks, lives, and breathes!"

PRISMATIC LENS.name: Prismatic Lens
PRISMATIC LENS.flavorText: Mined exclusively from the dark side of the moon.

ASTRAL COMMUNION.name: Astral Communion
ASTRAL COMMUNION.flavorText: Hey! Moon! Can I have some mana crystals?

SHIRVALLAH, THE TIGER.name: Shirvallah, the Tiger
SHIRVALLAH, THE TIGER.flavorText: On bended knee Thekal placed his weapon upon Shirvallah’s altar, whereupon she slowly knocked it off with her paw.

TYRANDE.name: Tyrande
TYRANDE.flavorText: High Priestess of the Moon Goddess, Tyrande has journeyed into the Emerald Dream to find Malfurion. Discovering Xavius’s nightmarish influence, she is determined to thwart those seeking to corrupt it.

CLAY MATRIARCH.name: Clay Matriarch
CLAY MATRIARCH.flavorText: I hope you didn't need all that purple clay.

ASTRAL SERPENT.name: Astral Serpent
ASTRAL SERPENT.flavorText: Call it lazy all you want, but it does have two more cards than you.

PROTECT THE KING!.name: Protect the King!
PROTECT THE KING!.flavorText: Form ranks! Everyone into the King's Tuskarr Defense!

THE LOBOTOMIZER.name: The Lobotomizer
THE LOBOTOMIZER.flavorText: This may hurt a little, but don't worry, you won't remember it.

FROSTWEAVE DUNGEONEER.name: Frostweave Dungeoneer
FROSTWEAVE DUNGEONEER.flavorText: It's a woven blanket of ice but surprisingly comforting.

RELIQUARY OF SOULS.name: Reliquary of Souls
RELIQUARY OF SOULS.flavorText: These three represent Anger, Desire, and Suffering. Much like raid night guild chat.

SPINE CRAWLER.name: Spine Crawler
SPINE CRAWLER.flavorText: Give him one second, he's rooting! ... Ok give him one more second he's almost done!

FEIGN DEATH.name: Feign Death
FEIGN DEATH.flavorText: The hardest part about doing a "Feign Death" convincingly is learning how to make the right smell. It takes a lot of commitment.

GRAND MAGUS ANTONIDAS.name: Grand Magus Antonidas
GRAND MAGUS ANTONIDAS.flavorText: He's really disappointed Jaina became a frost mage.

ETHEREAL ORACLE.name: Ethereal Oracle
ETHEREAL ORACLE.flavorText: I see 2 spells in my future.

LOVE EVERLASTING.name: Love Everlasting
LOVE EVERLASTING.flavorText: Poison Bloom was accused of plagiarizing the "Ooh, how long can this go on (ooh yeah)" hook from an old-school musical group called The Saronite Chain Gang.

SKETCHY STRANGER.name: Sketchy Stranger
SKETCHY STRANGER.flavorText: More of a 'Painted Stranger' if you ask me.

SHADOW STRIKE.name: Shadow Strike
SHADOW STRIKE.flavorText: It's like a backstab, only from the front. And with two more stabs.

PRISON OF YOGG-SARON.name: Prison of Yogg-Saron
PRISON OF YOGG-SARON.flavorText: "We've finally captured Yogg-Saron! How should we keep him contained?" "How about... an open pit... right below us... with four loose chains?" "PERFECT!"

MYSTERY EGG.name: Mystery Egg
MYSTERY EGG.flavorText: Which came first, the Mukla or the egg?

PLUCKY PODLING.name: Plucky Podling
PLUCKY PODLING.flavorText: "When I grow up I wanna be a Deathwing!"

WARHORSE TRAINER.name: Warhorse Trainer
WARHORSE TRAINER.flavorText: He doesn't even get Sundays off. Every day he's hostling.
