voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/3/3c/VO_AT_075_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_075_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

PRINCESS TALANJI.name: Princess Talanji
PRINCESS TALANJI.flavorText: Everyone wants to be a princess, but nobody ever considers the size of the hat.

ECHO OF MEDIVH.name: Echo of Medivh
ECHO OF MEDIVH.flavorText: Medivh's echo haunts Karazhan, eternally cheating at chess and Hearthstone.

HIDDEN OASIS.name: Hidden Oasis
HIDDEN OASIS.flavorText: Amazing that it's been hidden, given the twenty-foot treant splashing around in it.

DRAGON'S BREATH.name: Dragon's Breath
DRAGON'S BREATH.flavorText: Dragons breathe fire, sure, but did you know they can also breathe Cotton Candy? It's harder to give them a reason to do that, though.

FORBIDDEN HEALING.name: Forbidden Healing
FORBIDDEN HEALING.flavorText: No one's quite sure why it's forbidden. And yes, that should make you nervous.

HAUNTING NIGHTMARE.name: Haunting Nightmare
HAUNTING NIGHTMARE.flavorText: Not as scary as the one where all my teeth fall out.

GIFT OF THE WILD.name: Gift of the Wild
GIFT OF THE WILD.flavorText: The gift that keeps on living.

FUTURE EMISSARY.name: Future Emissary
FUTURE EMISSARY.flavorText: When Murozond attacked the past, Nozdormu sought help from the future, even journeying as far as the Forbidden Reach.

SINSTONE GRAVEYARD.name: Sinstone Graveyard
SINSTONE GRAVEYARD.flavorText: A graveyard in the realm of the dead; a bit redundant, don't you think?

SHATTERED REFLECTIONS.name: Shattered Reflections
SHATTERED REFLECTIONS.flavorText: Get mad at your mirror once, see Shattered Reflections forever :(

RITUAL OF DOOM.name: Ritual of Doom
RITUAL OF DOOM.flavorText: "Who wants to sing the Doom song?!"

SPELLCOILER.name: Spellcoiler
SPELLCOILER.flavorText: "Look, I know plenty of spells. I just need to see one first is all."

PIRANHA SWARMER.name: Piranha Swarmer
PIRANHA SWARMER.flavorText: One Fish, Two Fish. Less Fish? You wish.

DRAGON BREEDER.name: Dragon Breeder
DRAGON BREEDER.flavorText: Deathwing would have been more well-adjusted if he'd been raised by this guy.

DREAMWAY GUARDIANS.name: Dreamway Guardians
DREAMWAY GUARDIANS.flavorText: They're a nightmare to deal with.

JANDICE BAROV.name: Jandice Barov
JANDICE BAROV.flavorText: Her parents own Scholomance. Of course she's going to play tricks on the students!

DOOMED APPRENTICE.name: Doomed Apprentice
DOOMED APPRENTICE.flavorText: Jaina was never good at keeping up apprentices.

SPIRIT OF THE BADLANDS.name: Spirit of the Badlands
SPIRIT OF THE BADLANDS.flavorText: That's the spirit! Of the Badlands.

QUESTING EXPLORER.name: Questing Explorer
QUESTING EXPLORER.flavorText: Earned her merit badges the hard way—twelve zhevra hooves at a time.

GIBBERLING.name: Gibberling
GIBBERLING.flavorText: "As a Linguistics student I have studied the Gibberlings. I have determined they are speaking Gibberish."

CALL TO ADVENTURE.name: Call to Adventure
CALL TO ADVENTURE.flavorText: Even the smallest minion can change the outcome of the game.

LIFE FROM DEATH.name: Life from Death
LIFE FROM DEATH.flavorText: Just because you came up with a nicer name for it doesn't mean that necromancy is any more justified.

MARIN THE FOX.name: Marin the Fox
MARIN THE FOX.flavorText: My name is Marin the Fox. You took my treasure. Prepare to die.

MAELSTROM PORTAL.name: Maelstrom Portal
MAELSTROM PORTAL.flavorText: They bill this as a popular resort attraction, but they try and get your money up front.

STAR STUDENT STELINA.name: Star Student Stelina
STAR STUDENT STELINA.flavorText: Cheating is just using your resources wisely.

BONEGUARD LIEUTENANT.name: Boneguard Lieutenant
BONEGUARD LIEUTENANT.flavorText: Underneath all that impressive armor, he's just skin and bones. Okay, maybe just bones.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/50/VO_AT_089_PLAY_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_089_PLAY_01.wav
voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/7/7b/VO_AT_089_ATTACK_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_089_ATTACK_02.wav You face death!
voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/58/VO_AT_089_DEATH_03.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_AT_089_DEATH_03.wav <death sound>

FURIOUS FELFIN.name: Furious Felfin
FURIOUS FELFIN.flavorText: Signature moves include Eye Bream, Feast of Soles, and Metamorphofish.

BIOLOGY PROJECT.name: Biology Project
BIOLOGY PROJECT.flavorText: Step 1: Grow giant evil strawberry. Step 2: ???? Step 3: Rule Azeroth!

POWER WORD: REPLICATE.name: Power Word: Replicate
POWER WORD: REPLICATE.flavorText: Available as a bundle, along with Power Words: Detonate, Animate, Annihilate, and Paper Weight.

POWER WORD: GLORY.name: Power Word: Glory
POWER WORD: GLORY.flavorText: The promise of glory is a powerful tool to get minions to do your bidding. Only slightly less powerful than the promise of an ice cream bar!

DRINK SERVER.name: Drink Server
DRINK SERVER.flavorText: Make sure to tip to help him with his fin-ances.

GREEDY SPRITE.name: Greedy Sprite
GREEDY SPRITE.flavorText: Sparkliest of the seven deadly sprites.

POSSESSED LACKEY.name: Possessed Lackey
POSSESSED LACKEY.flavorText: If you don't keep up with your payments, it'll be a repossessed lackey.

HALEH, MATRON PROTECTORATE.name: Haleh, Matron Protectorate
HALEH, MATRON PROTECTORATE.flavorText: Oh, how do you solve a problem like Onyxia?

CORNELIUS ROAME.name: Cornelius Roame
CORNELIUS ROAME.flavorText: Raised two perfectly normal daughters. Then one died and brought doom to Stormwind.

ARKWING PILOT.name: Arkwing Pilot
ARKWING PILOT.flavorText: Delivered in under 30 minutes, or your Arkwings are free!

SATHROVARR.name: Sathrovarr
SATHROVARR.flavorText: Just wait until you also find a copy in your pocket. And your desk! And your FRIDGE!!

JACKPOT!.name: Jackpot!
JACKPOT!.flavorText: Find someone who looks at you the way Hooktusk looks at loot.

CANDLESHOT.name: Candleshot
CANDLESHOT.flavorText: Once called Cahn’delar, Shortbow of the Ancient Whisker.

BRILLIANT MACAW.name: Brilliant Macaw
BRILLIANT MACAW.flavorText: He's been repeating the same shanty for a month. Four pirates walked the plank last week. Middle of the ocean, just walked right off.

PARAGLIDE.name: Paraglide
PARAGLIDE.flavorText: I can see my hand from here!!!!!

FOE REAPER 4000.name: Foe Reaper 4000
FOE REAPER 4000.flavorText: Foe reaping is really not so different from harvest reaping, at the end of the day.

HI HO SILVERWING.name: Hi Ho Silverwing
HI HO SILVERWING.flavorText: I swear this minion had 3000 Attack at one point!

THE RYECLEAVER.name: The Ryecleaver
THE RYECLEAVER.flavorText: Legend has it that this dreaded blade is be able to slice through even the most stale of sourdough baguettes.

COSTUMED SINGER.name: Costumed Singer
COSTUMED SINGER.flavorText: Who knows which forgotten, washed-up, former C-list celebrity might be in there!

LUNAR TRAILBLAZER.name: Lunar Trailblazer
LUNAR TRAILBLAZER.flavorText: Changing legend into fact, she will ride into history.

AIR GUITARIST.name: Air Guitarist
AIR GUITARIST.flavorText: Nailing that solo was a breeze.

CLASH OF THE COLOSSALS.name: Clash of the Colossals
CLASH OF THE COLOSSALS.flavorText: Don’t let this distract you from the fact that in 1998, Ozumat threw Neptulon off Shell in a Cell, and plummeted 16 fathoms through an announcer’s table.

LADY VASHJ.name: Lady Vashj
LADY VASHJ.flavorText: Personal handmaiden to Queen Azshara turned lieutenant to Illidan Stormrage. Also quite the hair sssstylist.

EREDAR DECEPTOR.name: Eredar Deceptor
EREDAR DECEPTOR.flavorText: But they were all of them deceived, for another Eredar was made.

WASTE REMOVER.name: Waste Remover
WASTE REMOVER.flavorText: Always follow the three Rs: REDUCE their world to ash, REUSE their bones as paperweights, and RECYCLE!

DRAKKARI DEFENDER.name: Drakkari Defender
DRAKKARI DEFENDER.flavorText: Sometimes, the best defense is an offensive troll.

BEAR TRAP.name: Bear Trap
BEAR TRAP.flavorText: You'll never guess what's in that conveniently bear-sized, bear-smelling box.

INQUISITIVE CREATION.name: Inquisitive Creation
INQUISITIVE CREATION.flavorText: This mech eats books for breakfast.

IL'GYNOTH.name: Il'gynoth
IL'GYNOTH.flavorText: Well, that just sounds like damage with extra steps.

SNOWCHUGGER.name: Snowchugger
SNOWCHUGGER.flavorText: Do the slow chant when he waddles by: "Chug! Chug! Chug!"

PRIMAL TALISMANS.name: Primal Talismans
PRIMAL TALISMANS.flavorText: All that remained from the first kobold colony: a single talisman and the word "Flamestrike."

CAVE HYDRA.name: Cave Hydra
CAVE HYDRA.flavorText: Can be upgraded into a Cave Lurker.

SANDSTORM ELEMENTAL.name: Sandstorm Elemental
SANDSTORM ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Doot doot doot doot doot [Pause] Doot doot doot doot doot DEE doot doot doot doot doot!

SILITHID SWARMER.name: Silithid Swarmer
SILITHID SWARMER.flavorText: If your hero doesn't attack, it's just "Silithid Loner".

DANCING SWORDS.name: Dancing Swords
DANCING SWORDS.flavorText: They like to dance to reggae.

MEDIVH'S VALET.name: Medivh's Valet
MEDIVH'S VALET.flavorText: "Magus Medivh sir, I've brought the flaming balloons, as you requested."

DEAD MAN'S HAND.name: Dead Man's Hand
DEAD MAN'S HAND.flavorText: I got two pair, Rags and Armorsmiths. What you got?

TROLLEY PROBLEM.name: Trolley Problem
TROLLEY PROBLEM.flavorText: If only there were thousands of hypotheticals to prepare me for this moment!

CHEF NOMI.name: Chef Nomi
CHEF NOMI.flavorText: His cooking is always very well done.

SWARM OF LOCUSTS.name: Swarm of Locusts
SWARM OF LOCUSTS.flavorText: Good things never come in swarms.

SYMPHONY OF SINS.name: Symphony of Sins
SYMPHONY OF SINS.flavorText: Makes for some killer final boss music.

SERVICE ACE.name: Service Ace
SERVICE ACE.flavorText: No shirt, no shoes, YES service!

KORRAK THE BLOODRAGER.name: Korrak the Bloodrager
KORRAK THE BLOODRAGER.flavorText: “I live, I love, I slay, and I am undying.”

MARSH DRAKE.name: Marsh Drake
MARSH DRAKE.flavorText: She would have gotten away with it, if it weren't for that meddling Drakeslayer.

WINGED GUARDIAN.name: Winged Guardian
WINGED GUARDIAN.flavorText: Take these broken wings, be reborn, and learn to fly again.

FOSSILIZED DEVILSAUR.name: Fossilized Devilsaur
FOSSILIZED DEVILSAUR.flavorText: This was the only job he could get after the dinosaur theme park debacle.

PLOT OF SIN.name: Plot of Sin
PLOT OF SIN.flavorText: It's a great plot, but it's riddled with holes.

CALL OF THE WILD.name: Call of the Wild
CALL OF THE WILD.flavorText: "Hello. Misha, Leokk and Huffer aren't here right now, but if you leave a message we'll get back to you right away." BEEP.

SNAKE EYES.name: Snake Eyes
SNAKE EYES.flavorText: Hey, put ALL of your hands on the table!

RIMESCALE SIREN.name: Rimescale Siren
RIMESCALE SIREN.flavorText: She will freeze the Scourge dead in their tracks.

OVERGROWN BEANSTALK.name: Overgrown Beanstalk
OVERGROWN BEANSTALK.flavorText: You'd need to be pretty jacked to climb this.

LADY ANACONDRA.name: Lady Anacondra
LADY ANACONDRA.flavorText: Do you think she got her name before or after she turned into a snake?

FEROCIOUS FELBAT.name: Ferocious Felbat
FEROCIOUS FELBAT.flavorText: A tree in the hand is worth two in the Nightmare.

ASHTONGUE BATTLELORD.name: Ashtongue Battlelord
ASHTONGUE BATTLELORD.flavorText: Demons have destroyed the lives of the Ashtongue draenei. Now he’s got a shoulder-axe to grind.

PAPARAZZI.name: Paparazzi
PAPARAZZI.flavorText: When you're a Legendary minion, you get a shiny orange gem, a dragon emblem, and about 100 of these people following you everywhere.

CORRUPTED HEALBOT.name: Corrupted Healbot
CORRUPTED HEALBOT.flavorText: Not so much "corrupted" as "has terrible aim".

TIMELESS BLESSING.name: Timeless Blessing
TIMELESS BLESSING.flavorText: To defeat the combined power of Murozond and C'Thun, Nozdormu would need heroes of Azeroth's past, present, and future.

CARRION STUDIES.name: Carrion Studies
CARRION STUDIES.flavorText: A good read but a little too much fluff.

NETHERWIND PORTAL.name: Netherwind Portal
NETHERWIND PORTAL.flavorText: More aromatic than a regular portal.

LEARN DRACONIC.name: Learn Draconic
LEARN DRACONIC.flavorText: Upon taking up the spellbook, Reno realized with a start: "I can't read."

DEATHWARDEN.name: Deathwarden
DEATHWARDEN.flavorText: Ride or die takes on a new meaning.

QUICK PICK.name: Quick Pick
QUICK PICK.flavorText: QUICK! Pick which quick pick trick will stick in the thick of the wick! Lickety split!

ASTRAL VIGILANT.name: Astral Vigilant
ASTRAL VIGILANT.flavorText: Draenei are so dedicated that they remain vigilant even in death.

SPORE EMPRESS MOLDARA.name: Spore Empress Moldara
SPORE EMPRESS MOLDARA.flavorText: Sorry for not explaining the Spores in the textbox. We just didn't have that mushroom.

GIGGLING INVENTOR.name: Giggling Inventor
GIGGLING INVENTOR.flavorText: "I shall build a mighty golden paladin! And he will GREET the WORLD!"

TWIN SLICE.name: Twin Slice
TWIN SLICE.flavorText: The slice so nice, it'll cut you twice.

LIGHTFORGED ZEALOT.name: Lightforged Zealot
LIGHTFORGED ZEALOT.flavorText: Card-carrying member of the Paladins Only Paladin Club.

TREACHERY.name: Treachery
TREACHERY.flavorText: Never look a gift minion in the mouth.

TERON GOREFIEND.name: Teron Gorefiend
TERON GOREFIEND.flavorText: "You’re fine, friendly minions! You're fine! Don’t tell Mom!"

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/f2/VO_BT_126_Male_UndeadOrc_Play_02.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BT_126_Male_UndeadOrc_Play_02.wav I was the first, you know.

WAGGLE PICK.name: Waggle Pick
WAGGLE PICK.flavorText: Kobolds informally refer to its effect as a deathwaggle.

BARRENS BLACKSMITH.name: Barrens Blacksmith
BARRENS BLACKSMITH.flavorText: "Maybe someday you’ll make it to Gadgetzan, kid."

FORMER CHAMP.name: Former Champ
FORMER CHAMP.flavorText: The last time he saw action, Undertaker ruled the meta.

DETAILED NOTES.name: Detailed Notes
DETAILED NOTES.flavorText: The Rangari Scouts pride themselves on their highly accurate notes.

LIBRAM OF CLARITY.name: Libram of Clarity
LIBRAM OF CLARITY.flavorText: Ah, I get it! I should play this for 0 Mana.

K'ARA, THE DARK STAR.name: K'ara, the Dark Star
K'ARA, THE DARK STAR.flavorText: Velen had never seen a shooting star in real life, so when the opportunity arose…

LAZUL'S SCHEME.name: Lazul's Scheme
LAZUL'S SCHEME.flavorText: "What's that you're dreaming? You're weak and you're screaming! It must be my scheming..."

AKAMA.name: Akama
AKAMA.flavorText: "To many of my people, I am known as a traitor... as Illidan's lapdog. I will remain in the shadows, for now... Actually, maybe I'll just remain in the shadows forever."

CUTLASS COURIER.name: Cutlass Courier
CUTLASS COURIER.flavorText: It may be a cutlass, but you can cut lads with it too.

MIDWAY MANIAC.name: Midway Maniac
MIDWAY MANIAC.flavorText: Faire owners hate him! Learn his secrets with one simple spell!

POTION OF ILLUSION.name: Potion of Illusion
POTION OF ILLUSION.flavorText: Unfortunately, there's no potion that can make you unsee all the faces in that bottle.

BOTTOMFEEDER.name: Bottomfeeder
BOTTOMFEEDER.flavorText: Someone keeps adding fish to my deck, and I'm going to get to the bottom of it.

KRYXIS THE VORACIOUS.name: Kryxis the Voracious
KRYXIS THE VORACIOUS.flavorText: Tried intermittent fasting. It didn't stick.

CACTUS CONSTRUCT.name: Cactus Construct
CACTUS CONSTRUCT.flavorText: "I am not Malfurion! I am CACTUS LORD!"

MAGNATAUR ALPHA.name: Magnataur Alpha
MAGNATAUR ALPHA.flavorText: Playing him also gets you into the Magnataur Beta.

CANNON BARRAGE.name: Cannon Barrage
CANNON BARRAGE.flavorText: Why fire your cannons strategically when you can fire them all at once?

WING BLAST.name: Wing Blast
WING BLAST.flavorText: Emeriss uses Wing Blast. It's super effective!

FEL ORC SOULFIEND.name: Fel Orc Soulfiend
FEL ORC SOULFIEND.flavorText: "Doc says the persistent burning sensation in my soul is probably just an ulcer."

IMPROVE MORALE.name: Improve Morale
IMPROVE MORALE.flavorText: "The beatings will continue until MY morale improves."

ACE HUNTER KREEN.name: Ace Hunter Kreen
ACE HUNTER KREEN.flavorText: This grandmaster marksman loves winning tournaments and eating a bit of ice cream.

MEAT GRINDER.name: Meat Grinder
MEAT GRINDER.flavorText: After the Horde and Alliance sieged Icecrown Citadel, they took these back to use in their delis.

FATE WEAVER.name: Fate Weaver
FATE WEAVER.flavorText: Do not draw the attention of a Fate Weaver, for it will always loom over your destiny.

DRAGON'S FURY.name: Dragon's Fury
DRAGON'S FURY.flavorText: “C’mon Hucklemuck. She’ll never notice if we take just one little coin.”

WARPATH.name: Warpath
WARPATH.flavorText: "Left, right, left, right, there's none of the enemy left… Right?"

TIP THE SCALES.name: Tip the Scales
TIP THE SCALES.flavorText: Hold on, I need to get some murlocs to weigh in on this.

DISARMING ELEMENTAL.name: Disarming Elemental
DISARMING ELEMENTAL.flavorText: "You can have these back when you learn to play nice."

BOMB SQUAD.name: Bomb Squad
BOMB SQUAD.flavorText: Please don't explode! Please don't explode! Please don't explode!

RAISE DEAD.name: Raise Dead
RAISE DEAD.flavorText: Technically, it’s just really late healing.

TRINKET ARTIST.name: Trinket Artist
TRINKET ARTIST.flavorText: Many Draenei found new hobbies on the long journey from Argus.

FRACTURED POWER.name: Fractured Power
FRACTURED POWER.flavorText: Look what Warlocks need just to mimic a fraction of our power!

PEBBLY PAGE.name: Pebbly Page
PEBBLY PAGE.flavorText: A good friend will lighten your Overload.

SOUL CLEAVE.name: Soul Cleave
SOUL CLEAVE.flavorText: The way to a demon's soul is through its stomach.

TOTEMIC SMASH.name: Totemic Smash
TOTEMIC SMASH.flavorText: Trolls are the first group to have a totem survive atmospheric re-entry.

FREEZING POTION.name: Freezing Potion
FREEZING POTION.flavorText: This is delicious! Oh no. BRAIN FREEEEEEEZE!

SARGERAS, THE DESTROYER.name: Sargeras, the Destroyer
SARGERAS, THE DESTROYER.flavorText: Formerly the Defender of the Pantheon, he became disillusioned by his mission and formed the Burning Legion to destroy all life within the universe.

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/5/57/VO_TTN_960_Male_DemonicTitan_Attack_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_TTN_960_Male_DemonicTitan_Attack_01.wav Death is a mercy!

INSATIABLE DEVOURER.name: Insatiable Devourer
INSATIABLE DEVOURER.flavorText: You're not you when you're anima-starved.

DREADHOUND HANDLER.name: Dreadhound Handler
DREADHOUND HANDLER.flavorText: The handler being undead speaks to a spotty safety record.

SIGIL OF FLAME.name: Sigil of Flame
SIGIL OF FLAME.flavorText: "Huh, it reads F-I-R-E. Wonder what that means?"

WYRMGUARD.name: Wyrmguard
WYRMGUARD.flavorText: They think they're trusted guardians. Dragons think they're convenient snacks.

SOUL SHEAR.name: Soul Shear
SOUL SHEAR.flavorText: "Just a little off the sides please."

DESERT SPEAR.name: Desert Spear
DESERT SPEAR.flavorText: Goes on the right, next to the desert spoon.

DEVOLVE.name: Devolve
DEVOLVE.flavorText: Ragnaros looked down. He looked like some kind of War Golem. "WHAT HAVE YOU DONE TO ME," he yelled. But all that came out was a deep grinding sound. He began to cry.

SERVICE BELL.name: Service Bell
SERVICE BELL.flavorText: The bell tolls for us! Waiter, we need more water!

STORMWIND FREEBOOTER.name: Stormwind Freebooter
STORMWIND FREEBOOTER.flavorText: "Just don't stab the ankles! I want his boots!"

RINLING'S RIFLE.name: Rinling's Rifle
RINLING'S RIFLE.flavorText: This rifle needs a muzzle for its muzzle.

RECURRING VILLAIN.name: Recurring Villain
RECURRING VILLAIN.flavorText: Mwahahaha! You'll never catch him this time!

RISKY SKIPPER.name: Risky Skipper
RISKY SKIPPER.flavorText: Sworn enemy of the Safety Matey.

KOLOGARN.name: Kologarn
KOLOGARN.flavorText: "So am I just supposed to stand here forever, or...?"

VOLCANIC POTION.name: Volcanic Potion
VOLCANIC POTION.flavorText: The secret ingredient in Kazakus's award-winning chili recipe.

BLOODSCENT VILEFIN.name: Bloodscent Vilefin
BLOODSCENT VILEFIN.flavorText: Tired of eating Jellyfish and Peanut Butter fish, it’s moved on to more gruesome meals.

SINFUL SOUS CHEF.name: Sinful Sous Chef
SINFUL SOUS CHEF.flavorText: If this dinner party goes well, she thinks she has a good shot at being on Fel's Kitchen.

PARTY UP!.name: Party Up!
PARTY UP!.flavorText: Random? But what if we don't get a tank?

MURLOC WARLEADER.name: Murloc Warleader
MURLOC WARLEADER.flavorText: Do Murlocs ever get tired of making the same old sound? Nope! Mrglglrglglglglglglgl!

SEA SHANTY.name: Sea Shanty
SEA SHANTY.flavorText: Time for some well-earned arrr and arrr.

SECURITY!!.name: SECURITY!!
SECURITY!!.flavorText: Check all of the boxes that contain VENGEANCE to play this card.

RESKA, THE PIT BOSS.name: Reska, the Pit Boss
RESKA, THE PIT BOSS.flavorText: Overseer of the Bloodrock Mine, Reska will work you to the bone. They'll then reanimate your bones and work THOSE bones to the bone.

HAWKSTRIDER RANCHER.name: Hawkstrider Rancher
HAWKSTRIDER RANCHER.flavorText: I prefer the Hawkstrider Nacho Cheeser.

OVERLORD SAURFANG.name: Overlord Saurfang
OVERLORD SAURFANG.flavorText: Eats more than his fair share of sour candy.

SCREWJANK CLUNKER.name: Screwjank Clunker
SCREWJANK CLUNKER.flavorText: If it breaks, just kick it a couple of times while yelling "Durn thing!"

LIGHTSTEED.name: Lightsteed
LIGHTSTEED.flavorText: All the steed, half the calories.

ALTERED CHORD.name: Altered Chord
ALTERED CHORD.flavorText: I'll never understand how bands and orchestras allow musicians that just…. play... off-key. Would love opinions on this.

TURBULUS.name: Turbulus
TURBULUS.flavorText: "Passengers, we will be experiencing some minor Turbulus in the next few expansions."

ORACLE OF ELUNE.name: Oracle of Elune
ORACLE OF ELUNE.flavorText: Even the moon goddess needs to back up her databases.

BONECHEWER RAIDER.name: Bonechewer Raider
BONECHEWER RAIDER.flavorText: And if that minion has a frisbee, LOOK OUT!

ICE REVENANT.name: Ice Revenant
ICE REVENANT.flavorText: There must have been some magic in that old ice mace we found.

TOMB LURKER.name: Tomb Lurker
TOMB LURKER.flavorText: She hangs out in all the tombs, but she rarely posts.

ETERNAL LAYOVER.name: Eternal Layover
ETERNAL LAYOVER.flavorText: Get away from it all! Forever.

CURSED VAGRANT.name: Cursed Vagrant
CURSED VAGRANT.flavorText: Little did he know… it was really the talbuk leg that was cursed.

SMALL-TIME RECRUITS.name: Small-Time Recruits
SMALL-TIME RECRUITS.flavorText: Now we know why they wear tiny watches.

AMORPHOUS SLIME.name: Amorphous Slime
AMORPHOUS SLIME.flavorText: A crucial component of the Lordaeroneon Choice Awards.

HANDLE WITH BEAR.name: Handle with Bear
HANDLE WITH BEAR.flavorText: We guarantee your luggage will arrive at the speed of bear.

FRIGID SNOBOLD.name: Frigid Snobold
FRIGID SNOBOLD.flavorText: Ironically, the natural enemy of the snobold is THE CANDLE.

GANG UP.name: Gang Up
GANG UP.flavorText: If you are thinking about visiting Moonbrook, you better roll deep.

INFECTIOUS GHOUL.name: Infectious Ghoul
INFECTIOUS GHOUL.flavorText: They call him that because of his laughter! Also his plague.

CRITTER CARETAKER.name: Critter Caretaker
CRITTER CARETAKER.flavorText: She teaches all her critters two things: heel and heal.

WEE SPELLSTOPPER.name: Wee Spellstopper
WEE SPELLSTOPPER.flavorText: Bane of spellcasters and spelling bees everywhere.

PREDATORY INSTINCTS.name: Predatory Instincts
PREDATORY INSTINCTS.flavorText: Somebody’s been eating their funnel cakes.

SPIRIT BOMB.name: Spirit Bomb
SPIRIT BOMB.flavorText: Might take a few episodes to power up.

CONCOCTOR.name: Concoctor
CONCOCTOR.flavorText: "A dash of death, with a pinch of death, and a sprinkle of… death!"

OHN'AHRA.name: Ohn'ahra
OHN'AHRA.flavorText: Revered by the tauren and centaur, Ohn’ara’s power over wind remains an inspiration to many.

ORION, MANSION MANAGER.name: Orion, Mansion Manager
ORION, MANSION MANAGER.flavorText: The secrets of the universe are vast... and will be revealed sometime later this game.

SWAMP LEECH.name: Swamp Leech
SWAMP LEECH.flavorText: A face only a druid could love.

TRAM HEIST.name: Tram Heist
TRAM HEIST.flavorText: How are they gunna steal the whole tram!?

POWERMACE.name: Powermace
POWERMACE.flavorText: People assume that shamans control the elements, but really, they have to ask them stuff and the elements are like, "Yeah ok, sure."

GRIM PATRON.name: Grim Patron
GRIM PATRON.flavorText: If you love getting your face punched, come to the Grim Guzzler!

EATER OF SECRETS.name: Eater of Secrets
EATER OF SECRETS.flavorText: You don't want to be around after it has eaten an explosive trap. You thought Sludge Belcher was bad...

EARTH REVENANT.name: Earth Revenant
EARTH REVENANT.flavorText: Have you guys seen a pair of rock legs lying around anywhere?

NECRIUM VIAL.name: Necrium Vial
NECRIUM VIAL.flavorText: Two near-death experiences for the price of one!

BLOODSWORN MERCENARY.name: Bloodsworn Mercenary
BLOODSWORN MERCENARY.flavorText: You look really hurt. You could use a friend!

LIBRAM OF FAITH.name: Libram of Faith
LIBRAM OF FAITH.flavorText: They used to do leaps of faith until Maraad fell into the void.

TITANFORGED TRAPS.name: Titanforged Traps
TITANFORGED TRAPS.flavorText: Always place it underneath their health pack.

SABOTEUR.name: Saboteur
SABOTEUR.flavorText: Listen all y'all it's a saboteur!

RUSH THE STAGE.name: Rush the Stage
RUSH THE STAGE.flavorText: Left Shark, get to the stage now!

DRYWHISKER ARMORER.name: Drywhisker Armorer
DRYWHISKER ARMORER.flavorText: Kobolds use anything for armor: Pots, pans, garbage cans… even other kobolds.

PRESSURE POINTS.name: Pressure Points
PRESSURE POINTS.flavorText: Have you ever heard of the 5 Point Palm Exploding Heart Technique?

LAKKARI SACRIFICE.name: Lakkari Sacrifice
LAKKARI SACRIFICE.flavorText: They asked, “And what must we give in return?” Gul’dan lowered his hood and answered: “Six… cards…”

KINGSBANE.name: Kingsbane
KINGSBANE.flavorText: But it has a soft spot for emperors.

UMBRAL SKULKER.name: Umbral Skulker
UMBRAL SKULKER.flavorText: "Three gold?! Do you have any idea how long this quest chain was?"

TOL'VIR STONESHAPER.name: Tol'vir Stoneshaper
TOL'VIR STONESHAPER.flavorText: He spends a lot of time keeping himself in stoneshape.

SERPENTSHRINE PORTAL.name: Serpentshrine Portal
SERPENTSHRINE PORTAL.flavorText: This is why you never flush a three-cost minion.

CHO'GALL, TWILIGHT CHIEFTAIN.name: Cho'gall, Twilight Chieftain
CHO'GALL, TWILIGHT CHIEFTAIN.flavorText: He's got it all, the gumption, gall, and Cho.

SWORD EATER.name: Sword Eater
SWORD EATER.flavorText: How tough is he? He eats swords for breakfast! Without any milk.

REPLICATING MENACE.name: Replicating Menace
REPLICATING MENACE.flavorText: It's a car! *Whomp whomp whomp* It's a robot! *Whomp whom-CRUNCH* It's… three.. smaller robots!

RAZORMANE RAIDER.name: Razormane Raider
RAZORMANE RAIDER.flavorText: "Call me hedgehog one more time. I dare you."

RAINBOW GLOWSCALE.name: Rainbow Glowscale
RAINBOW GLOWSCALE.flavorText: She prefers saying that she has Arcane, Fel, Fire, Frost, Holy, Nature, and Shadow Spell Damage +1.

CATHEDRAL GARGOYLE.name: Cathedral Gargoyle
CATHEDRAL GARGOYLE.flavorText: Fly like an eagle, drop like a rock.

LIGHTNING REFLEXES.name: Lightning Reflexes
LIGHTNING REFLEXES.flavorText: If you can dodge a lightning bolt, you can dodge a ball.

K9-0TRON.name: K9-0tron
K9-0TRON.flavorText: You merely adopted the Battlegrounds. I was born in it. Molded by it.

WHISPERS OF THE DEEP.name: Whispers of the Deep
WHISPERS OF THE DEEP.flavorText: And in the darkest of depths, the sailor heard a command from inside his own mind… “You will also buff my original card to 9 Mana.”

DARING FIRE-EATER.name: Daring Fire-Eater
DARING FIRE-EATER.flavorText: A few hours later he DESTROYED the arena bathrooms.

RAM WRANGLER.name: Ram Wrangler
RAM WRANGLER.flavorText: Not getting trampled is really the trick here.

MANA CYCLONE.name: Mana Cyclone
MANA CYCLONE.flavorText: It'll put a good spin on your spells.

CHAOS GAZER.name: Chaos Gazer
CHAOS GAZER.flavorText: No matter the game rules, it's always playing Go Fish.

REMIXED DISPENSE-O-BOT.name: Remixed Dispense-o-bot
REMIXED DISPENSE-O-BOT.flavorText: "Mine gave me free money!" "Mine gave me free ice cream!" "… mine gave me two sheep that explode. They were free but I still want a refund."

AEGWYNN, THE GUARDIAN.name: Aegwynn, the Guardian
AEGWYNN, THE GUARDIAN.flavorText: With Medivh as her son, nothing YOU do could ever disappoint her.

BARBARIC SORCERESS.name: Barbaric Sorceress
BARBARIC SORCERESS.flavorText: Her four arms are for casting, and her forearms are for crushing.

HARBINGER OF THE BLIGHTED.name: Harbinger of the Blighted
HARBINGER OF THE BLIGHTED.flavorText: The more pretentious the name, the eviler the character.

SPITEFUL SUMMONER.name: Spiteful Summoner
SPITEFUL SUMMONER.flavorText: Sometimes she'll summon a Doomsayer. Out of spite.

RAZORMANE BATTLEGUARD.name: Razormane Battleguard
RAZORMANE BATTLEGUARD.flavorText: Where there's a quill, there's a way.

DARKMOON DIRIGIBLE.name: Darkmoon Dirigible
DARKMOON DIRIGIBLE.flavorText: "It's dirigible? I don’t even know what diriging is!"

FEAT OF STRENGTH.name: Feat of Strength
FEAT OF STRENGTH.flavorText: Generally happens right after the airing of grievances.

WITCH'S CAULDRON.name: Witch's Cauldron
WITCH'S CAULDRON.flavorText: Eye of murloc, ear of bat, foot of Fordring, fur of cat…

RUSTY RECYCLER.name: Rusty Recycler
RUSTY RECYCLER.flavorText: Ironic. It could recycle others, but not itself.

OBSIDIAN REVENANT.name: Obsidian Revenant
OBSIDIAN REVENANT.flavorText: What is this? A Reven for Ants?!

SERVANT OF KALIMOS.name: Servant of Kalimos
SERVANT OF KALIMOS.flavorText: He's doing his best, but his mom thinks that if he had just applied himself in school Kalimos would be working for HIM.

FRESH SCENT.name: Fresh Scent
FRESH SCENT.flavorText: *Sniff, sniff* Elite troops... *sniff, sniff* ...armed to the teeth and... *sniff, sniff* ...BAAACON!

A. F. KAY.name: A. F. Kay
A. F. KAY.flavorText: Talk to the hand 'cause the mouth is sippin'.

EDWIN, DEFIAS KINGPIN.name: Edwin, Defias Kingpin
EDWIN, DEFIAS KINGPIN.flavorText: He’s not going to tear down the walls of Stormwind sitting around in the Hall of Fame.

GOBLIN AUTO-BARBER.name: Goblin Auto-Barber
GOBLIN AUTO-BARBER.flavorText: This guy is excellent at adjusting your haircut and/or height.

MURLOC KNIGHT.name: Murloc Knight
MURLOC KNIGHT.flavorText: Hee hee! Look at his cute little feet.

CHAOS NOVA.name: Chaos Nova
CHAOS NOVA.flavorText: Illin' Illidan laying down the damage, flinging out the chaos as far as he can manage.

ARCANE ANOMALY.name: Arcane Anomaly
ARCANE ANOMALY.flavorText: He used to get work as a Spatial Anomaly, but he got tired of having his polarity reversed.

DOOMGUARD.name: Doomguard
DOOMGUARD.flavorText: Summoning a doomguard is risky. Someone is going to die.

WRETCHED QUEEN.name: Wretched Queen
WRETCHED QUEEN.flavorText: Mind your head when you're around her.

ZOMBEEEES!!!.name: ZOMBEEEES!!!
ZOMBEEEES!!!.flavorText: In your brain, in your brain, Zombees, Zombees, Zombees-ees-ees.

DIRE FROSTWOLF.name: Dire Frostwolf
DIRE FROSTWOLF.flavorText: Tips to survive a frostwolf attack: -Stay calm -Lay down -Drizzle steak sauce over your body Brought to you by the Frostwolf Council for Alliance Safety.

INARA STORMCRASH.name: Inara Stormcrash
INARA STORMCRASH.flavorText: A fan favorite, Inara is always met with thunderous applause.

DOUBLE AGENT.name: Double Agent
DOUBLE AGENT.flavorText: And under the Alliance tabard? Another Horde tabard.

LAB RECRUITER.name: Lab Recruiter
LAB RECRUITER.flavorText: Join the chemistry lab! We've got all the solutions.

OGRE WARMAUL.name: Ogre Warmaul
OGRE WARMAUL.flavorText: Simple, misguided, and incredibly dangerous. You know, like most things ogre.

TIGHT-LIPPED WITNESS.name: Tight-Lipped Witness
TIGHT-LIPPED WITNESS.flavorText: People keep asking for her award-winning vegetarian chili recipe, but she just can't spill the beans.

MAD SCIENTIST.name: Mad Scientist
MAD SCIENTIST.flavorText: His mother wanted him to be a mage or a warlock, but noooooooo, he had to go and be a scientist like his father.

PARTY PLANNER VONA.name: Party Planner Vona
PARTY PLANNER VONA.flavorText: She's known for her popular "occult ritual to summon an otherworldly being" parties.

CLOAKED HUNTRESS.name: Cloaked Huntress
CLOAKED HUNTRESS.flavorText: She's practically GIVING your secrets away!

DARK POSSESSION.name: Dark Possession
DARK POSSESSION.flavorText: Wanted on three counts of gnomish possession.

BOGSTROK CLACKER.name: Bogstrok Clacker
BOGSTROK CLACKER.flavorText: This clacker's crackers for hacking slackers into whack attackers.

ALIEN ENCOUNTERS.name: Alien Encounters
ALIEN ENCOUNTERS.flavorText: Close encounters of the cuddly kind.

ALLEYCAT.name: Alleycat
ALLEYCAT.flavorText: To be a cool cat in Gadgetzan, you gotta have bling.

DARK BARGAIN.name: Dark Bargain
DARK BARGAIN.flavorText: A prime example of lose-lose negotiating.

PACK KODO.name: Pack Kodo
PACK KODO.flavorText: He looks simple, but there’s a lot to unpack.

SCORCH.name: Scorch
SCORCH.flavorText: The hoof. The hoof. The hoof is on fire.

HYDRALODON.name: Hydralodon
HYDRALODON.flavorText: Deep beneath the waves, this hydra grew to incredible size based on a steady diet of literally anything that crossed its path.

SHELDRAS MOONTREE.name: Sheldras Moontree
SHELDRAS MOONTREE.flavorText: Sheldras really went to the park for his pilgrimage.

PHANTOM MILITIA.name: Phantom Militia
PHANTOM MILITIA.flavorText: Recruited from the Gilnean opera house.

BULK UP.name: Bulk Up
BULK UP.flavorText: "For breakfast I usually go for a couple of kodo steaks, 5 Plainstrider eggs and an ice-cold milk to wash it down… all raw."

VAL'ANYR.name: Val'anyr
VAL'ANYR.flavorText: Recently unearthed in one of the deepest kobold caves. Traded for a large candle.

HEMET, JUNGLE HUNTER.name: Hemet, Jungle Hunter
HEMET, JUNGLE HUNTER.flavorText: The goblin travel agency lost his luggage, but he's still having a great vacation!

WRATHSPINE ENCHANTER.name: Wrathspine Enchanter
WRATHSPINE ENCHANTER.flavorText: If he could see, he might be better at targeting.

BLOOD TROLL SAPPER.name: Blood Troll Sapper
BLOOD TROLL SAPPER.flavorText: Main supplier of Blood Troll Syrup to the Intercontinental Hut of Funnel Cakes.

BELLIGERENT GNOME.name: Belligerent Gnome
BELLIGERENT GNOME.flavorText: Maybe don't put this one in your garden.

DESERT OBELISK.name: Desert Obelisk
DESERT OBELISK.flavorText: The Obelisk of the Stars can hide an entire land from prying eyes! Or zap a rando.

COLD FEET.name: Cold Feet
COLD FEET.flavorText: Looks like some of the dancers still need to warm up.

SHADOWBOXER.name: Shadowboxer
SHADOWBOXER.flavorText: Punching is its primary function. Also, its secondary function.

WISDOM OF NORGANNON.name: Wisdom of Norgannon
WISDOM OF NORGANNON.flavorText: Now all we need is the power and courage of Norgannon.

WRECK'EM AND DECK'EM.name: Wreck'em and Deck'em
WRECK'EM AND DECK'EM.flavorText: ...and Check'em for any signs of life.

RAID BOSS ONYXIA.name: Raid Boss Onyxia
RAID BOSS ONYXIA.flavorText: Onyxia chose her guises to manipulate mortals, but her true form? That was reserved for ending them.

DEMONBOLT.name: Demonbolt
DEMONBOLT.flavorText: Or as it’s known in troll, “De bolt, mon.”

SWORD OF THE FALLEN.name: Sword of the Fallen
SWORD OF THE FALLEN.flavorText: Hoarding secrets is no fun, so play each and every one.

RELIC OF EXTINCTION.name: Relic of Extinction
RELIC OF EXTINCTION.flavorText: Faster than an asteroid, and just as effective.

DOMINO EFFECT.name: Domino Effect
DOMINO EFFECT.flavorText: WHY DO THEY NEVER RUN TO THE SIDE?????

GALAKROND, THE UNBREAKABLE.name: Galakrond, the Unbreakable
GALAKROND, THE UNBREAKABLE.flavorText: The ground quaked beneath the behemoth as Dr. Boom continued: "…with over 400 TONS of solid Storm Silver plate." Then he beeped a small remote. "And luxury spikes!"

THUNDERHEAD.name: Thunderhead
THUNDERHEAD.flavorText: Most of his friends are still Metalheads.

BLACKSMITHING HAMMER.name: Blacksmithing Hammer
BLACKSMITHING HAMMER.flavorText: Passed through the hands of countless smiths, and eventually the skulls of their enemies.

ARCANE FLETCHER.name: Arcane Fletcher
ARCANE FLETCHER.flavorText: Stop trying to make fletch happen. It's not going to happen.

MONSTROUS PARROT.name: Monstrous Parrot
MONSTROUS PARROT.flavorText: What kind of crackers are you feeding that thing?

HERALD OF NATURE.name: Herald of Nature
HERALD OF NATURE.flavorText: A mother of plants in mother of pearl.

HOT SPRING GUARDIAN.name: Hot Spring Guardian
HOT SPRING GUARDIAN.flavorText: NONE SHALL PASS until at least an hour after eating.

BLESSING OF AUTHORITY.name: Blessing of Authority
BLESSING OF AUTHORITY.flavorText: A paladin fights with honor! We don't go face... until next turn!

MYSTERY WINNER.name: Mystery Winner
MYSTERY WINNER.flavorText: Yeah, but the mystery prize could be anything! Even a boat!

CLAWFURY ADEPT.name: Clawfury Adept
CLAWFURY ADEPT.flavorText: The Inept Clawfury is a danger only to themselves.

DEVOURING PLAGUE.name: Devouring Plague
DEVOURING PLAGUE.flavorText: "How’d we miss this one in Uldum?" —Rafaam

WEASEL TUNNELER.name: Weasel Tunneler
WEASEL TUNNELER.flavorText: He's the reason the First Bank of Gadgetzan has steel floors.

ANNOYING FAN.name: Annoying Fan
ANNOYING FAN.flavorText: No, Annoy-o-Tron, an air horn is not an instrument.

STAR GRAZER.name: Star Grazer
STAR GRAZER.flavorText: Star gazing and star grazing aren't too different. Except for the part where you eat stars.

PERPLEXING ANOMALY.name: Perplexing Anomaly
PERPLEXING ANOMALY.flavorText: I'm so confused... this is really a headscratcher... it doesn't make any sense... why does it cost 3 Mana?

GIANT SAND WORM.name: Giant Sand Worm
GIANT SAND WORM.flavorText: Banned from every all-you-can-eat buffet on Azeroth.

TYRANTUS.name: Tyrantus
TYRANTUS.flavorText: Millennia of evolutionary pressures turned his species into the Faerie Dragons we know today.

LOATHEB.name: Loatheb
LOATHEB.flavorText: Loatheb used to be a simple Bog Beast. This is why we need stricter regulations on mining and agriculture.

BOGBEAM.name: Bogbeam
BOGBEAM.flavorText: Some think the mysterious bright lights in the bog are alien invaders, others think they're just swamp gas. Turns out, it's just druids.

RUSTSWORN CULTIST.name: Rustsworn Cultist
RUSTSWORN CULTIST.flavorText: "Rust… I love it. It's all coarse, and rough, and irritating. And it gets everywhere."

LIVING SEED (RANK 1).name: Living Seed (Rank 1)
LIVING SEED (RANK 1).flavorText: Every desert needs an oasis. And it's Guff's duty to make it happen.

ANCIENT VOID HOUND.name: Ancient Void Hound
ANCIENT VOID HOUND.flavorText: What happened to my 1/1 Void Pup? And the glee club?!

ROKARA.name: Rokara
ROKARA.flavorText: "Tread carefully, but stand tall, and stand together. For strength and honor!" —Rokara

ENERGY SHAPER.name: Energy Shaper
ENERGY SHAPER.flavorText: '"I can do a snake for you?"

MICROTECH CONTROLLER.name: Microtech Controller
MICROTECH CONTROLLER.flavorText: Best-selling author of "How to Make Friends You Completely Control."

THE SCOURGE.name: The Scourge
THE SCOURGE.flavorText: “You speak of justice? Of cowardice? I will show you the justice of the grave and the true meaning of fear.”

RAZZLE-DAZZLER.name: Razzle-Dazzler
RAZZLE-DAZZLER.flavorText: Look out Dancin' Deryl, he's coming for your job.

MAWSWORN BAILIFF.name: Mawsworn Bailiff
MAWSWORN BAILIFF.flavorText: Bailiff, bring in the dancing lobsters!

WHIRLWIND TEMPEST.name: Whirlwind Tempest
WHIRLWIND TEMPEST.flavorText: And your minions with mega-windfury get... dizzy.

AVIANA, ELUNE'S CHOSEN.name: Aviana, Elune's Chosen
AVIANA, ELUNE'S CHOSEN.flavorText: The Mistress of Birds takes a special interest in all creatures of the sky, as well as those who have wings but have yet to fly.

CANAL SLOGGER.name: Canal Slogger
CANAL SLOGGER.flavorText: "Another Monday in the canals huh? What a slog."

AMALGAM OF THE DEEP.name: Amalgam of the Deep
AMALGAM OF THE DEEP.flavorText: Most explorers call it a success to find just one new species. Imagine Finley's excitement when he identified ten at once!

GALVANIZER.name: Galvanizer
GALVANIZER.flavorText: Also known as a power zinc.

VORONEI RECRUITER.name: Voronei Recruiter
VORONEI RECRUITER.flavorText: He has an eyepatch but isn't a Pirate. He's a Recruiter but doesn't Recruit. Smh my head.

HODIR, FATHER OF GIANTS.name: Hodir, Father of Giants
HODIR, FATHER OF GIANTS.flavorText: Giant ladies, this one's a Keeper.

TALGATH.name: Talgath
TALGATH.flavorText: Talgath betrayed his people by accepting Sargeras's promise of power. Talgath also saw Velen's refusal of that same power as a betrayal. I'm not convinced Talgath knows what that word means.

YMIRJAR FROSTBREAKER.name: Ymirjar Frostbreaker
YMIRJAR FROSTBREAKER.flavorText: Also gains +1 Attack for each time your opponent mispronounces his name.

JOURNEY BELOW.name: Journey Below
JOURNEY BELOW.flavorText: Don't stop believing there's something below.

CRUEL DINOMANCER.name: Cruel Dinomancer
CRUEL DINOMANCER.flavorText: As that old saying goes: "you don't get into dinomancing to make friends."

DEFIAS CLEANER.name: Defias Cleaner
DEFIAS CLEANER.flavorText: His house cleaning service is quite thorough. Not a spot to be found... or any of your stuff!

ENTER THE COLISEUM.name: Enter the Coliseum
ENTER THE COLISEUM.flavorText: You have to get past the vendors first. So many are lost to shopping...

RUMBLE ENTHUSIAST.name: Rumble Enthusiast
RUMBLE ENTHUSIAST.flavorText: There's always room for one more game in the tavern!

REAP WHAT YOU SOW.name: Reap What You Sow
REAP WHAT YOU SOW.flavorText: With a hat like that, I'd say their tailor did all of the sowing.

IMMORTAL PRELATE.name: Immortal Prelate
IMMORTAL PRELATE.flavorText: She protec. She attac. But most importantly, she come bac.

FREQUENCY OSCILLATOR.name: Frequency Oscillator
FREQUENCY OSCILLATOR.flavorText: Our lawyer made us change the flavor text of this card so we wouldn't get sued.

THE LAST KALEIDOSAUR.name: The Last Kaleidosaur
THE LAST KALEIDOSAUR.flavorText: “Impossible!” exclaimed the Silver Hand Recruit, his eyes filled with fear. Uther shook his head, turning the crystal until it caught the light: “Life finds a way.”

FOOL'S BANE.name: Fool's Bane
FOOL'S BANE.flavorText: A fool and his bane are soon parted.

ULTRALISK CAVERN.name: Ultralisk Cavern
ULTRALISK CAVERN.flavorText: Don't let your ultralisk get stuck on a ramp.

HADRONOX.name: Hadronox
HADRONOX.flavorText: The viziers of Azjol-Nerub released Hadronox as a last-ditch effort to hold back the Lich King. They did so by VERY carefully scooping him up in a LARGE newspaper and releasing him.

FARRAKI BATTLEAXE.name: Farraki Battleaxe
FARRAKI BATTLEAXE.flavorText: Only two things in life are certain: death and axes.

GARRISON COMMANDER.name: Garrison Commander
GARRISON COMMANDER.flavorText: He'll never admit it, but he pushes you hard because he really cares about you.

BONEDIGGER GEIST.name: Bonedigger Geist
BONEDIGGER GEIST.flavorText: He's a grave-half-full kind of geist.

VIOLET SPELLWING.name: Violet Spellwing
VIOLET SPELLWING.flavorText: A bird in the hand is worth three missiles in the grave.

FEL GUARDIANS.name: Fel Guardians
FEL GUARDIANS.flavorText: What happened after the guardians tripped? They Fel.

ZEALOUS INITIATE.name: Zealous Initiate
ZEALOUS INITIATE.flavorText: Ok, Initiate. You need to settle down and do your job. In this case, that means die so someone else can get a minor buff.

MINDRENDER ILLUCIA.name: Mindrender Illucia
MINDRENDER ILLUCIA.flavorText: "…and that's how I ended up with a Murloc Cultural Studies major."

LANCE CARRIER.name: Lance Carrier
LANCE CARRIER.flavorText: Lance Carrier is an obscure entry level position in orcish armies. A mystery, since orcs don't generally use lances.

LEYLINE MANIPULATOR.name: Leyline Manipulator
LEYLINE MANIPULATOR.flavorText: The shortest distance between two points is a leyline.

BLAZING ACCRETION.name: Blazing Accretion
BLAZING ACCRETION.flavorText: Much like the Draenei, this Elemental just wants a place to call home. Unlike the Draenei, it incinerates everything it touches.

GRAND FINALE.name: Grand Finale
GRAND FINALE.flavorText: Considering all the other hazards at Darkmoon, overindulgent pyrotechnics seem downright pedestrian.

NOFIN'S IMP-OSSIBLE.name: Nofin's Imp-ossible
NOFIN'S IMP-OSSIBLE.flavorText: They have faces only a morrglr could love.

RHEASTRASZA.name: Rheastrasza
RHEASTRASZA.flavorText: Rheastrasza ascends above loyalty to just her dragonflight to serve all dragonkind. She believes all flights deserve a future and will give her life for the future dragon prince.

RED GIANT.name: Red Giant
RED GIANT.flavorText: Lots of cards get played around it, but it's the real star.

FROZEN BUCKLER.name: Frozen Buckler
FROZEN BUCKLER.flavorText: "Hey, I bet I could shatter this."

LADY S'THENO.name: Lady S'theno
LADY S'THENO.flavorText: Only a S'theno deals in absolutes.

SEA SHILL.name: Sea Shill
SEA SHILL.flavorText: She shills shea sells down at the sea shtore.

SHIFTING SHADE.name: Shifting Shade
SHIFTING SHADE.flavorText: Yeah, it's cooler in the shade, but you're also more likely to get JACKED.

MAGISTER DAWNGRASP.name: Magister Dawngrasp
MAGISTER DAWNGRASP.flavorText: Magister is a humble title for one who united warring armies against the greatest threat to Azeroth.

PROSECUTOR MEL'TRANIX.name: Prosecutor Mel'tranix
PROSECUTOR MEL'TRANIX.flavorText: "Your Honor. The Defense isn't a clown, he's the whole circus."

ARCANE TYRANT.name: Arcane Tyrant
ARCANE TYRANT.flavorText: Tyrant is such a strong word.

SETHEKK VEILWEAVER.name: Sethekk Veilweaver
SETHEKK VEILWEAVER.flavorText: The Sethekk weren't able to survive this long by being wasteful with their power. Or their wacky hats.

FLASH SALE.name: Flash Sale
FLASH SALE.flavorText: HOW LOW! HOW LOW! HOW LOW!

REDEEMED PARIAH.name: Redeemed Pariah
REDEEMED PARIAH.flavorText: "Look at this stick. Look at it!"

ICICLE.name: Icicle
ICICLE.flavorText: This may appear weak at frost glance, but it's actually a very ice spell.

UNSLEEPING SOUL.name: Unsleeping Soul
UNSLEEPING SOUL.flavorText: It's 3 am. Do you know where your soul is?

BONESHREDDER.name: Boneshredder
BONESHREDDER.flavorText: Is that his makeup or just his natural fur pattern?

SOUL SPLIT.name: Soul Split
SOUL SPLIT.flavorText: Spoiler: they're both the evil twin.

TINYFIN'S CARAVAN.name: Tinyfin's Caravan
TINYFIN'S CARAVAN.flavorText: Movin' right along, mrgl mrg mrgl mrg.

RELENTLESS WORG.name: Relentless Worg
RELENTLESS WORG.flavorText: It's the Year of the Worg! Wait - what do you mean 'wolf'?

TOMB TRAITOR.name: Tomb Traitor
TOMB TRAITOR.flavorText: You enjoy raiding, I enjoying traitoring. We are not the same.

GIFT OF LUMINANCE.name: Gift of Luminance
GIFT OF LUMINANCE.flavorText: You get a small version of yourself in a snow globe to remember the moment.

TWILIGHT ELDER.name: Twilight Elder
TWILIGHT ELDER.flavorText: Just doesn't understand those Twilight Youngsters any more - with their comic books and their rock music.

EREDAR BRUTE.name: Eredar Brute
EREDAR BRUTE.flavorText: After a while, the glowing purple stress ball became ineffective at containing his rage.

SEASIDE GIANT.name: Seaside Giant
SEASIDE GIANT.flavorText: Everywhere's the shallow end when you're 88 feet tall.

SQUIRMING TENTACLE.name: Squirming Tentacle
SQUIRMING TENTACLE.flavorText: Yeah, I think we can agree that killing the squirming tentacle first is a good idea.

MAILBOX DANCER.name: Mailbox Dancer
MAILBOX DANCER.flavorText: He is the reason why we have 7 mailboxes in this district.

MECHAGNOME GUIDE.name: Mechagnome Guide
MECHAGNOME GUIDE.flavorText: Theme park? Tropical island? Fiery pit of despair? We've got something for everyone.

DANGEROUS CLIFFSIDE.name: Dangerous Cliffside
DANGEROUS CLIFFSIDE.flavorText: It's not as dangerous as it looks… IT'S EVEN MORE DANGEROUS!

DREDGER STAFF.name: Dredger Staff
DREDGER STAFF.flavorText: The dredger staff held the dredger knife and said, "Dredger bow before the Sire!"

DUBIOUS PURCHASE.name: Dubious Purchase
DUBIOUS PURCHASE.flavorText: Beauty is in the eye of the scorpidholder.

PRIMORDIAL STUDIES.name: Primordial Studies
PRIMORDIAL STUDIES.flavorText: A long forgotten tome whose very essence seeps of magic. 40 dust, used.

CRAZED CONDUCTOR.name: Crazed Conductor
CRAZED CONDUCTOR.flavorText: "The Twisting Nether is singing to me… WHAT IS THAT MELODY!?"

DREAMBOUND DISCIPLE.name: Dreambound Disciple
DREAMBOUND DISCIPLE.flavorText: I'm not taking a nap, I'm just doing some extra studying about the Dream!

SIPHON MANA.name: Siphon Mana
SIPHON MANA.flavorText: Why spend mine when I can take yours?

REDGILL RAZORJAW.name: Redgill Razorjaw
REDGILL RAZORJAW.flavorText: One fish, two fish, red fish replaces blue fish.

PIPSI PAINTHOOF.name: Pipsi Painthoof
PIPSI PAINTHOOF.flavorText: "Earthmother guide my paintbrush strokes, especially on the eyes."

COOKIE THE COOK.name: Cookie the Cook
COOKIE THE COOK.flavorText: Unsurprisingly, "Seafood Surprise" was no one's favorite dish.

PLUCKY PAINTFIN.name: Plucky Paintfin
PLUCKY PAINTFIN.flavorText: Not everyone can become a great painter. But a great painter can come from anywhere.

STONEBORN GENERAL.name: Stoneborn General
STONEBORN GENERAL.flavorText: Leads with an iron fist and a stony demeanor.

POPULAR PIXIE.name: Popular Pixie
POPULAR PIXIE.flavorText: Popular Pixie personally prefers particularly powerful pop performances.

HEDRA THE HERETIC.name: Hedra the Heretic
HEDRA THE HERETIC.flavorText: Hedra was cast out millennia ago for her divisive opinions among the Naga, such as "Turning into evil underwater serpent people was bad, actually."

MURDER ACCUSATION.name: Murder Accusation
MURDER ACCUSATION.flavorText: Quote From Man Murdered: "What are you gonna do, murder me?"

SCORP-O-MATIC.name: Scorp-o-matic
SCORP-O-MATIC.flavorText: Back in my day, we had to manually scorp.

ARCANE BOLT.name: Arcane Bolt
ARCANE BOLT.flavorText: Just you wait until I have 8 mana!

SOUL SEEKER.name: Soul Seeker
SOUL SEEKER.flavorText: The Soul Seeker's job is to look for a snitch.

RATCHET PRIVATEER.name: Ratchet Privateer
RATCHET PRIVATEER.flavorText: There's a fine line between privateering and pirating. It comes down to tax breaks.

MI'DA, PURE LIGHT.name: Mi'da, Pure Light
MI'DA, PURE LIGHT.flavorText: Unfortunately, Mi’da’s touch will not turn things to gold.

GNOMEREGAN INFANTRY.name: Gnomeregan Infantry
GNOMEREGAN INFANTRY.flavorText: The gnomes are valiant and ready to return to their irradiated, poorly ventilated homeland!

CIRCUS MEDIC.name: Circus Medic
CIRCUS MEDIC.flavorText: Just be careful not to mix this with any creepy eyeballs, tentacles, or dark whispers, and you'll be fine in the morning.

INVENT-O-MATIC.name: Invent-o-matic
INVENT-O-MATIC.flavorText: The inventor was really proud, until they realized inventing something that invents things makes for poor job security.

FELWALKER.name: Felwalker
FELWALKER.flavorText: How it feels to chew Fel Gum.

BLACKWATER CUTLASS.name: Blackwater Cutlass
BLACKWATER CUTLASS.flavorText: Popular around Stormwind for slashing prices.

MOONFANG.name: Moonfang
MOONFANG.flavorText: Moonforehead just didn't have the same ring to it.

RIGHTEOUS CAUSE.name: Righteous Cause
RIGHTEOUS CAUSE.flavorText: "And I hereby dub thee a cadet of the Explorer’s League! NEXT!"

GRANITE FORGEBORN.name: Granite Forgeborn
GRANITE FORGEBORN.flavorText: If he stops being useful, just turn him into a kitchen countertop.

TRAVELING HEALER.name: Traveling Healer
TRAVELING HEALER.flavorText: Some heroes have soft hearts and hard shells.

DREADSTEED.name: Dreadsteed
DREADSTEED.flavorText: Crescendo himself summoned this steed, riding it to victory in the Grand Tournament. Wherever he rides, an army of riders ride behind him, supporting the legendary champion.

BLAZECALLER.name: Blazecaller
BLAZECALLER.flavorText: For when a flamecaller just won't do.

MANIC SOULCASTER.name: Manic Soulcaster
MANIC SOULCASTER.flavorText: When casting a tournament, you really have to put your soul into it!

POSSESSIFIER.name: Possessifier
POSSESSIFIER.flavorText: Beating the best, being the best, and brainwashing the rest.

CRYSTOLOGY.name: Crystology
CRYSTOLOGY.flavorText: "The Light is neither a particle nor a wave. It's more of a juice, really."

TEMPLE BERSERKER.name: Temple Berserker
TEMPLE BERSERKER.flavorText: He's back. He's angry. And he's here to wrap things up.

FLANKING MANEUVER.name: Flanking Maneuver
FLANKING MANEUVER.flavorText: So, do we have advantage? Can I sneak attack?

SHADOW WORD: HORROR.name: Shadow Word: Horror
SHADOW WORD: HORROR.flavorText: It's more succinct than "Shadow Word: Suck Into Vortex."

NAGA CORSAIR.name: Naga Corsair
NAGA CORSAIR.flavorText: Hook-tails are nice and all but she keeps getting stuck on things.

TRAM MECHANIC.name: Tram Mechanic
TRAM MECHANIC.flavorText: He looks at life through sludge-tinted glasses.

PILE OF BONES.name: Pile of Bones
PILE OF BONES.flavorText: It's a very well-organized pile, I'll give you that.

MINDBREAKER.name: Mindbreaker
MINDBREAKER.flavorText: He's a mind breaker, dream taker, ghoul trainer, don't you mess around with him.

FROSTWOLF KENNELS.name: Frostwolf Kennels
FROSTWOLF KENNELS.flavorText: The 1 reason Alliance members defect to the Horde is to adopt a cute frostwolf puppy.

DEEPWATER EVOKER.name: Deepwater Evoker
DEEPWATER EVOKER.flavorText: "Cap'n! We've hit an iceberg! ...No, it’s not my fault!"

ICE WALKER.name: Ice Walker
ICE WALKER.flavorText: Ice Walker you say? He doesn't have feet!

BILEFIN TIDEHUNTER.name: Bilefin Tidehunter
BILEFIN TIDEHUNTER.flavorText: Bile actually makes for surprisingly sturdy fins.

PIERCING SHOT.name: Piercing Shot
PIERCING SHOT.flavorText: Goblins hate wasting money on unnecessary ammunition.

TWILIGHT DECEPTOR.name: Twilight Deceptor
TWILIGHT DECEPTOR.flavorText: Nobody asks questions if you're carrying a clipboard.

GRIFTAH.name: Griftah
GRIFTAH.flavorText: With Griftah in your deck, sometimes you start the game with The Coin!

SPARK OF LIFE.name: Spark of Life
SPARK OF LIFE.flavorText: Just don't spark that life too close to the World Tree.

MUTALISK.name: Mutalisk
MUTALISK.flavorText: A flock of seagulls. A murder of crows. A ball of mutalisks.

FORGED IN FLAME.name: Forged in Flame
FORGED IN FLAME.flavorText: Don't worry, your wounds are self-cauterizing!

PYROS.name: Pyros
PYROS.flavorText: If you strike her down, she shall become more powerful than you can possibly… well, she'll become a 6/6 anyways.

SHATTERSHAMBLER.name: Shattershambler
SHATTERSHAMBLER.flavorText: Someone didn’t realize the ‘cold, black heart’ thing was supposed to be a metaphor.

TENDING TAUREN.name: Tending Tauren
TENDING TAUREN.flavorText: That racial bonus to Herbalism finally paid off.

THE GRAVITATIONAL DISPLACER.name: The Gravitational Displacer
THE GRAVITATIONAL DISPLACER.flavorText: You ever wonder why some planets have two moons?

PRINCE RENATHAL.name: Prince Renathal
PRINCE RENATHAL.flavorText: A lot of kids go through a rebellious phase, but Prince Renathal's was a bit extreme.

DIMENSIONAL CORE.name: Dimensional Core
DIMENSIONAL CORE.flavorText: At the core of every Starship is a Naaru giving its own energy as a power source. At the core of every Draenei is their unbridled faith in the Naaru.

DECK OF WONDERS.name: Deck of Wonders
DECK OF WONDERS.flavorText: "Pick a card, any card. Wait! No! Not that one!" - Last words of previous owner

UNCHAINED GLADIATOR.name: Unchained Gladiator
UNCHAINED GLADIATOR.flavorText: We can't possibly buff this card any more, just look at him!

voicelines.attack: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/e/e6/VO_TTN_475_Nonbinary_Elemental_Play_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_TTN_475_Nonbinary_Elemental_Play_01.wav Are you not entertained?!

ILLUMINATOR.name: Illuminator
ILLUMINATOR.flavorText: "LUMOS!" is not what they yell. What do you think this is, Hogwarts?

BLINK.name: Blink
BLINK.flavorText: Highly mobile. Solid range. Awful at staring contests.

DEATH STRIKE.name: Death Strike
DEATH STRIKE.flavorText: A little embarrassing when used on large minions.

BRONZE GATEKEEPER.name: Bronze Gatekeeper
BRONZE GATEKEEPER.flavorText: "You have my shield! And the rest of me too."

GALAKROND, THE UNSPEAKABLE.name: Galakrond, the Unspeakable
GALAKROND, THE UNSPEAKABLE.flavorText: Lazul called Galakrond’s name, her voice echoed by whispers from the deep. Both of Galakrond’s eyes opened… and then other eyes opened, as well.

MOR'SHAN ELITE.name: Mor'shan Elite
MOR'SHAN ELITE.flavorText: "Fear not the orc who has slain a million training dummies, but the orc who keeps CAMPING MY CORPSE!"

TORTOLLA.name: Tortolla
TORTOLLA.flavorText: Tortolla survived the Burning Legion’s invasion unscathed, but the Nightmare’s corruption really got under his shell.

EVIL CABLE RAT.name: EVIL Cable Rat
EVIL CABLE RAT.flavorText: Gradually driven to darkness by the promise of unobtainable cheese.

BLACKJACK STUNNER.name: Blackjack Stunner
BLACKJACK STUNNER.flavorText: "I'm about to ruin this 10-cost minion's whole career."

MAGIC TRICK.name: Magic Trick
MAGIC TRICK.flavorText: The world is not ready for an illusion of this depth and intricacy!

SHIELD OF GALAKROND.name: Shield of Galakrond
SHIELD OF GALAKROND.flavorText: Realistically, she's the shield for Galakrond's big toe.

SCAVENGER'S INGENUITY.name: Scavenger's Ingenuity
SCAVENGER'S INGENUITY.flavorText: "A beast, barely alive. Gentlemen, we can rebuild it! Make it stronger, faster... spikier."

BRAINSTORMER.name: Brainstormer
BRAINSTORMER.flavorText: Her hair was always like that.

RESISTANCE AURA.name: Resistance Aura
RESISTANCE AURA.flavorText: Perfect for defending against Beasts. Specifically small ones. Like, a very specific species of small insectoid animal. Ants. It resists ants.

RESERVED SPOT.name: Reserved Spot
RESERVED SPOT.flavorText: She needs a spot to make sure she can quickly get to her trunk.

ANCESTRAL GUARDIAN.name: Ancestral Guardian
ANCESTRAL GUARDIAN.flavorText: No one knows whose ancestor he is, but he's still upset that you never call.

RECYCLE.name: Recycle
RECYCLE.flavorText: Druidic recycling involves putting plastics in one bin and enemy minions in another bin.

BREAKDANCE.name: Breakdance
BREAKDANCE.flavorText: "Commander! Uhh... I'm... Pretty sure we just got served? I'm not really trained for this."

RING TOSS.name: Ring Toss
RING TOSS.flavorText: If you liked it, then you shoulda put a ring on it!

OVERGROWN HORROR.name: Overgrown Horror
OVERGROWN HORROR.flavorText: Fetch me the garden shears. The BIG shears.

CYCLOPIAN HORROR.name: Cyclopian Horror
CYCLOPIAN HORROR.flavorText: What are the qualifications for being a 'Horror?' Just how horrible do you have to be?

BELLRINGER SENTRY.name: Bellringer Sentry
BELLRINGER SENTRY.flavorText: "Who are you? Eh, none of my business."

EXARCH NAIELLE.name: Exarch Naielle
EXARCH NAIELLE.flavorText: The Great Dark Beyond is vast, with each world containing unknown wonders and horrors alike. To distinguish between the two, Naielle leads the Rangari in surveying all planets the Draenei set foot on.

LUNAR ECLIPSE.name: Lunar Eclipse
LUNAR ECLIPSE.flavorText: When the Azeroth is between the Sun and the Moon.

BRITTLEBONE BUCCANEER.name: Brittlebone Buccaneer
BRITTLEBONE BUCCANEER.flavorText: How much does a pirate pay for corn? A buck an ear arr arr arrr arrr!

CHATTY MACAW.name: Chatty Macaw
CHATTY MACAW.flavorText: Stop repeating yourself! Stop repeating yourself!

ADAPTATION.name: Adaptation
ADAPTATION.flavorText: Pray for salvation. If that fails, pray for extra horns or bigger teeth.

BRONZE DRAGONKNIGHT.name: Bronze Dragonknight
BRONZE DRAGONKNIGHT.flavorText: He had been here before, and in some ways, he would always be fighting in Silithus.

PUDDLESTOMPER.name: Puddlestomper
PUDDLESTOMPER.flavorText: He pays homage to Morgl, the great murloc oracle! (Who doesn't??)

WAXADRED.name: Waxadred
WAXADRED.flavorText: Waxadred the dragon fought for his king, frolicking through the fields melting everything!

THE JAILER.name: The Jailer
THE JAILER.flavorText: At one point, The Jailer served as Arbiter over the souls of the Shadowlands. He was the epitome of an unbiased, righteous judge of character. WAS.

DAMAGED STEGOTRON.name: Damaged Stegotron
DAMAGED STEGOTRON.flavorText: Sadly the warranty does not cover fireballs or acts of Boom.

RUNAWAY BLACKWING.name: Runaway Blackwing
RUNAWAY BLACKWING.flavorText: It has been 5 minutes since our last Azeroth Racing League violation.

SOULBOUND SPIRE.name: Soulbound Spire
SOULBOUND SPIRE.flavorText: Ah yes, EVERY Starship needs a fragile obelisk full of dead people!

KANGOR, DANCING KING.name: Kangor, Dancing King
KANGOR, DANCING KING.flavorText: After Dr. Boom's involvement with the League of EVIL, Kangor cut ties with the Boomsday Labs and began pursuing his true passion - DISCO!!!

DRILLY THE KID.name: Drilly the Kid
DRILLY THE KID.flavorText: "I HATE that nickname. Call me Drilliam!"

BUSY PEON.name: Busy Peon
BUSY PEON.flavorText: Chopping wood, mining gold and repairing buildings? None of these pursuits called to Grob...pencil doodling on wood was his true labor of love.

X-21 REPAIRBOT.name: X-21 Repairbot
X-21 REPAIRBOT.flavorText: The circle bolt goes in the square hole.

CAPTAIN GREENSKIN.name: Captain Greenskin
CAPTAIN GREENSKIN.flavorText: He was this close to piloting a massive juggernaut into Stormwind Harbor. If it weren't for those pesky kids!

FRIZZ KINDLEROOST.name: Frizz Kindleroost
FRIZZ KINDLEROOST.flavorText: Frizz knows that baby dragons need warmth, care, and the highest possible level of goblin engineering.

AMBER WHELP.name: Amber Whelp
AMBER WHELP.flavorText: What is a Bronze Whelp's favorite garnish? A little thyme!

ETERNAL SERVITUDE.name: Eternal Servitude
ETERNAL SERVITUDE.flavorText: What do you mean I don't get overtime pay for this?!

UNIDENTIFIED SHIELD.name: Unidentified Shield
UNIDENTIFIED SHIELD.flavorText: The kobold stared at the bundle for a long time. “Ah hah!” he said. “It’s a shield.”

TRAPDOOR SPIDER.name: Trapdoor Spider
TRAPDOOR SPIDER.flavorText: I can respect that they're important for the ecosystem, as long as you keep them waaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaay over there.

SNAP FREEZE.name: Snap Freeze
SNAP FREEZE.flavorText: Lick the ice block. I triple-double-dog-dare-you.

FUNHOUSE MIRROR.name: Funhouse Mirror
FUNHOUSE MIRROR.flavorText: Funhouse mirror on the wall, Who's the tallest gnome of all?

HEART OF THE LEGION.name: Heart of the Legion
HEART OF THE LEGION.flavorText: It grew 3 sizes after trying to steal Winter Veil.

STARSTRUNG BOW.name: Starstrung Bow
STARSTRUNG BOW.flavorText: Shoot for the stars, but if you miss, aim for the enemy hero.

COMMANDER RHYSSA.name: Commander Rhyssa
COMMANDER RHYSSA.flavorText: Two people can keep a secret as long as neither of them are Commander Rhyssa.

LASER BARRAGE.name: Laser Barrage
LASER BARRAGE.flavorText: "I say we take off and laser barrage the entire site from orbit - it's the only way to be sure."

BREATH OF DREAMS.name: Breath of Dreams
BREATH OF DREAMS.flavorText: Ysera has the worst morning breath.

BACKSTREET LEPER.name: Backstreet Leper
BACKSTREET LEPER.flavorText: Quit playing games with his heart. And his fingers. And foot. It's rude.

BLADED CULTIST.name: Bladed Cultist
BLADED CULTIST.flavorText: He has a poor understanding of the law of diminishing returns.

DART TRAP.name: Dart Trap
DART TRAP.flavorText: Five years of tap-dancing lessons are FINALLY going to pay off!

CORAL KEEPER.name: Coral Keeper
CORAL KEEPER.flavorText: This here is Carl. They're in charge of these elementals. Not all of them get along, so sometimes Carl corrals the quarreling coral.

BATTLEGROUND BATTLEMASTER.name: Battleground Battlemaster
BATTLEGROUND BATTLEMASTER.flavorText: Farm! No wait… Mine! No wait… 3 to Smith—they're taking Farm. Get there now!

COGMASTER.name: Cogmaster
COGMASTER.flavorText: After a while, you don't see the cogs and sprockets. All you see is a robot, a spider tank, a deathray...

BITTERBLOOM KNIGHT.name: Bitterbloom Knight
BITTERBLOOM KNIGHT.flavorText: Every rose has its thorn, beard, and shield.

HOOKED REAVER.name: Hooked Reaver
HOOKED REAVER.flavorText: The hook is just an accessory. He can reave just fine without it.

CHEMICAL SPILL.name: Chemical Spill
CHEMICAL SPILL.flavorText: I said spill the TEA, not the acid!

BOOM SQUAD.name: Boom Squad
BOOM SQUAD.flavorText: Discover the meaning of squad goals.

SHALLOW GRAVEDIGGER.name: Shallow Gravedigger
SHALLOW GRAVEDIGGER.flavorText: It's hard to put them six feet under when you're three feet tall.

SPAWNING POOL.name: Spawning Pool
SPAWNING POOL.flavorText: Looks more like a spawning hot tub to me, just based on the size.

JAM SESSION.name: Jam Session
JAM SESSION.flavorText: Their skills will make you jelly.

DREAMBOAT.name: Dreamboat
DREAMBOAT.flavorText: As the only member that can sing underwater, Paz saved Poison Bloom's Zin-Azshari tour from failure.

CLUTCHMOTHER ZAVAS.name: Clutchmother Zavas
CLUTCHMOTHER ZAVAS.flavorText: A bit of a snob: still refuses to drive anything with automatic transmission.

NAT, THE DARKFISHER.name: Nat, the Darkfisher
NAT, THE DARKFISHER.flavorText: You can take away his humanity, but you will never take away his fishing pole.

SAUNA REGULAR.name: Sauna Regular
SAUNA REGULAR.flavorText: She's getting that "falls off the bone" tenderness.

BLOODBOIL BRUTE.name: Bloodboil Brute
BLOODBOIL BRUTE.flavorText: Call Gurtogg a brute if you like, but no one else cares about the wounded like he does.

TWISTED FROSTWING.name: Twisted Frostwing
TWISTED FROSTWING.flavorText: Not currently valid in the Twist format.

LIGHTNING BLOOM.name: Lightning Bloom
LIGHTNING BLOOM.flavorText: Curiously, this plant never blooms in the same place twice.

SPIDER BOMB.name: Spider Bomb
SPIDER BOMB.flavorText: Wrecks a dude, any size. Catches thieves, eats those guys. Look out! Here comes a Spider Bomb!

SPIRIT MOUNT.name: Spirit Mount
SPIRIT MOUNT.flavorText: Bru'kan said his spirit would always be with us. He failed to mention that his raptor’s would be too.

MEDIVH, THE GUARDIAN.name: Medivh, the Guardian
MEDIVH, THE GUARDIAN.flavorText: If you think the party's great now, just wait 'til he invites the orcs over!

OGRE BRUTE.name: Ogre Brute
OGRE BRUTE.flavorText: Ogres have really terrible short-term chocolate.

DIG FOR TREASURE.name: Dig for Treasure
DIG FOR TREASURE.flavorText: "Woohoo! I'm so glad I dug up a pirate!"

WATCHER OF THE SUN.name: Watcher of the Sun
WATCHER OF THE SUN.flavorText: "I've got my eye on y-AAA I'M BLIND!"

FREE ADMISSION.name: Free Admission
FREE ADMISSION.flavorText: "Quick, get in before someone sees you, or worse, someone sees me."

WISH UPON A STAR.name: Wish Upon a Star
WISH UPON A STAR.flavorText: "What are you going to wish for?" "I wish I had just a liiiiiiiittle more Attack and Health!" "...Really? You don't want, like, a million more?"

THE AMAZING RENO.name: The Amazing Reno
THE AMAZING RENO.flavorText: "Reno!" "Please address me by my proper title." " Amazing Reno..."

APEXIS BLAST.name: Apexis Blast
APEXIS BLAST.flavorText: Lonely mages can still have a blast!

WAX ELEMENTAL.name: Wax Elemental
WAX ELEMENTAL.flavorText: Takes double damage from wick-based weapons.

voicelines.play: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/f/fd/LOOT_117_WaxElemental_PLay.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ LOOT_117_WaxElemental_PLay.wav

BOUNTY WRANGLER.name: Bounty Wrangler
BOUNTY WRANGLER.flavorText: With a smile like that and Coins in her hands, she's one greedy grinner.

BLADE DANCE.name: Blade Dance
BLADE DANCE.flavorText: The surest way to clear the dance floor.

GILNEAN ROYAL GUARD.name: Gilnean Royal Guard
GILNEAN ROYAL GUARD.flavorText: Admittedly, they kind of dropped the ball with Prince Liam.

DOUBLE JUMP.name: Double Jump
DOUBLE JUMP.flavorText: The key to every speed run.

VOLCANOMANCY.name: Volcanomancy
VOLCANOMANCY.flavorText: Do it again, this time with Pompeii and circumstance.

GLAIVESHARK.name: Glaiveshark
GLAIVESHARK.flavorText: Can smell a drop of vengeance in the water up to a mile away.

BOGGSPINE KNUCKLES.name: Boggspine Knuckles
BOGGSPINE KNUCKLES.flavorText: I would NOT want to put my hand in there. It's... SQUISHY.

GUFF RUNETOTEM.name: Guff Runetotem
GUFF RUNETOTEM.flavorText: "By the twins above and twins below, our companions will lead us through." —Guff Runetotem

voicelines.death: https://hearthstone.wiki.gg/images/a/aa/VO_BAR_720_Male_Tauren_Attack_01.wav" type="audio/wav" />Link▶️ VO_BAR_720_Male_Tauren_Attack_01.wav Not looking to fight.

DOCTOR HOLLI'DAE.name: Doctor Holli'dae
DOCTOR HOLLI'DAE.flavorText: If anything can heal the Badlands, it is the power of frogs!

MUCKMORPHER.name: Muckmorpher
MUCKMORPHER.flavorText: Fan favorite in the muck morphin' sewer strangers.

DEATHWEB SPIDER.name: Deathweb Spider
DEATHWEB SPIDER.flavorText: The itsy bitsy spiders climbed up the village wall. Then came the witch and the spiders ate them all.

MASS HYSTERIA.name: Mass Hysteria
MASS HYSTERIA.flavorText: Black Friday gets worse every year.

CHRONO BOOST.name: Chrono Boost
CHRONO BOOST.flavorText: Just think of all the tempests I can make! ...Ah, who am I kidding? I'm just going to use this on probes.

CRYSTAL BROKER.name: Crystal Broker
CRYSTAL BROKER.flavorText: Broke: Crystals Woke: Blueberry Fruit Gummies

HIDDEN CACHE.name: Hidden Cache
HIDDEN CACHE.flavorText: There is an urban legend that the first Toxic Sewer Ooze was born because a rookie Goon stashed an open container of milk in a Hidden Cache.

SCOURGELORD GARROSH.name: Scourgelord Garrosh
SCOURGELORD GARROSH.flavorText: "You dare to challenge me? Come! Draw your last breath - and then, you are mine."

LOTHAR.name: Lothar
LOTHAR.flavorText: Has been around since before there were paladins and those newfangled paladin mechs.

WARGEAR.name: Wargear
WARGEAR.flavorText: WAR! GEAR! What is it good for?

MAKING MUMMIES.name: Making Mummies
MAKING MUMMIES.flavorText: "I do say, this gives me the vapors every single time!"

CAT TRICK.name: Cat Trick
CAT TRICK.flavorText: "I know some new tricks, a lot of good tricks. I will show them to you. Medivh will not mind at all if I do."

WOODCUTTER'S AXE.name: Woodcutter's Axe
WOODCUTTER'S AXE.flavorText: It's a lumberjack's axe and that's ok.

ASTROMANCER SOLARIAN.name: Astromancer Solarian
ASTROMANCER SOLARIAN.flavorText: Loyal to Kael'thas Sunstrider, this blood elf mage sought arcane power in the Void. Did she find it... or did IT find her?

FLESH BEHEMOTH.name: Flesh Behemoth
FLESH BEHEMOTH.flavorText: Perfect for fleshing out your Undead deck.

FEARLESS FLAMEJUGGLER.name: Fearless Flamejuggler
FEARLESS FLAMEJUGGLER.flavorText: This is incredibly easy with 6 arms.

HUNTING PARTY.name: Hunting Party
HUNTING PARTY.flavorText: Not sure I’d call it a good party if everyone ends up beside themselves.

GLOWSTONE GYREWORM.name: Glowstone Gyreworm
GLOWSTONE GYREWORM.flavorText: Believe it or not, this is Tram Conductor Gerry's Gyreworm. But is it pronounced Gerry's Gyreworm, Gerry's Gyreworm, Gerry's Gyreworm, or Gerry's Gyreworm?

ARENA PATRON.name: Arena Patron
ARENA PATRON.flavorText: Everybody with a ticket get in here!

DISEASED VULTURE.name: Diseased Vulture
DISEASED VULTURE.flavorText: He's off the twig! He's kicked the bucket! THIS IS AN EX-VULTURE!

TWISTED TREANT.name: Twisted Treant
TWISTED TREANT.flavorText: You twist me right round baby right round like a treant baby right round round round

AZSHARAN SCAVENGER.name: Azsharan Scavenger
AZSHARAN SCAVENGER.flavorText: Some local Murloc populations have adapted to survive in the harsh conditions of the ruins, much to the fascination of Sir Finley.

DREAMING DRAKE.name: Dreaming Drake
DREAMING DRAKE.flavorText: Some dragons dream of conquering Azeroth, some just dream of being 5/6s.

VINECLEAVER.name: Vinecleaver
VINECLEAVER.flavorText: George and Karl! Thank the Light we found you!

HECKLEBOT.name: Hecklebot
HECKLEBOT.flavorText: Built by goblins, designed by a troll.

DUNK TANK.name: Dunk Tank
DUNK TANK.flavorText: "When I said bring a tank to the dungeon, this is not what I had in mind!"

BEAKERED LIGHTNING.name: Beakered Lightning
BEAKERED LIGHTNING.flavorText: Working in a shaman's lab, it's important to be well-grounded.

PROVOKE.name: Provoke
PROVOKE.flavorText: "Heh, Greetings. Heh, Greetings. Heh, Greetings. I will crush you!"

FLUTTERWING GUARDIAN.name: Flutterwing Guardian
FLUTTERWING GUARDIAN.flavorText: Flutterwing in the skyyyyy, I can go twice as highhhhhh

LUNARWING MESSENGER.name: Lunarwing Messenger
LUNARWING MESSENGER.flavorText: Back in my day this is how we got friend requests.

ELISE THE ENLIGHTENED.name: Elise the Enlightened
ELISE THE ENLIGHTENED.flavorText: From cartographer to combatant, Elise has taken the road less traveled—because no one else could find it on a map.

SHOCK HOPPER.name: Shock Hopper
SHOCK HOPPER.flavorText: Who is shocked about a frog hopping?

THRIVE IN THE SHADOWS.name: Thrive in the Shadows
THRIVE IN THE SHADOWS.flavorText: Why would your spells be afraid of the dark? It's easier to nap there.

AUDIO SPLITTER.name: Audio Splitter
AUDIO SPLITTER.flavorText: "I tried to give him some constructive criticism but gosh, he really hates feedback!"

FORBIDDEN FRUIT.name: Forbidden Fruit
FORBIDDEN FRUIT.flavorText: Not forbidden if you have a good dentist!

FLAME WARD.name: Flame Ward
FLAME WARD.flavorText: Not to be confused with the burn ward.

SPIRIT OF THE DRAGONHAWK.name: Spirit of the Dragonhawk
SPIRIT OF THE DRAGONHAWK.flavorText: Dragonhawks aren’t known for their accuracy.

VICIOUS FLEDGLING.name: Vicious Fledgling
VICIOUS FLEDGLING.flavorText: A youngster who is truly hungry for self-improvement.
